bem_transcription: Ibumba lyabashitata nabeminina mumbali mumusebo
eng_translation: A group of men is standing on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Ninshi bashitata aba bonse bakolonganina pamo mumusango wa waso? bushe finshi balelolela olo finshi balelweisho kucita?
eng_translation: Why are all these men gathered in such a way? What are they waiting for or what are they trying to do?

bem_transcription: aba bashitata balelolela ukuculuka umusebo, balelolela imyotoka shipite
eng_translation: They are waiting to cross the road, they are waiting fo the vehicles to pass.

bem_transcription: Nomba bambi bashitata tabalemoneka nokupoosa amano kumusebo balemoneka fye nabena balifye mucalo fye icabo, bushe nibonse abalefwayo kulwisho abalelwisho ukuculuka umusebo uyu?
eng_translation: They do not seem to be paying attention to what's happening, they seem to be focused on something else, are they all trying to cross the road?

bem_transcription: Endita, bonse balelwisho kuculuka, aba bambi abalemoneka abashipooseleko amano balelolesha uko balaiminikila imyotoka ishakubasenda
eng_translation: Yes, they are all trying to cross the road, the ones that do not seem to be paying attention are just trying to see where they can get vehicles to get on.

bem_transcription: shikulubantu alelya mukabale kabuuta
eng_translation: A man is eating from a white plate.

bem_transcription: shikulubantu wine alemoneka napoosa amano uko alelolesha, bushe ninshi cingalenga apoose so amano uko alelolesha?
eng_translation: This man seems to be focused on where he is looking, why is he this focused?

bem_transcription: Ali na bantu abo ekele nankwe pacipuna ebo alelanda nabo eko alelolesha
eng_translation: He is sited with some people on the chairs, they are ones he is looking at.

bem_transcription: Ngako akalemoneka akabuuta akeminine pambale iilemoneka apo kumbali yakashikulu?
eng_translation: What is that white thing standing on the plate that is beside him?

bem_transcription: Ni kendo nga malaiti yaya eyo basanika ukukwato lubuuto
eng_translation: It is a candle that they lit up when there is power, they use it for light.

bem_transcription: Bawishi no mwana baleangala mumenshi
eng_translation: A father and a child are playing in water.

bem_transcription: Bawishi no mwana bene balemoneka aba nsansa sana, bushe kuti caba ati nabomfwa bwino ukula-angala mumenshi aya?
eng_translation: They both seem very happy, could it be because they are playing in water?

bem_transcription: Ee, kuti caba icansansa, balemoneka aba nsansa pamulandu wakweba ti umwana balemufunda ukusamba
eng_translation: It could be so, they seem happy because the father is teaching the child to swim.

bem_transcription: Ninshi umwana wine afwalile ici ico afwele kumuulu, bushe nacikwate ncito cilebomba olo afwele fye?
eng_translation: Why is the child wearing that thing on top, is there any reason or is he just dressed like that?

bem_transcription: Nacikwate ncito eyo cilebomba, cilemwafwa ukukana nwena mumenshi
eng_translation: There is reason, it is helping the child not to drown.

bem_transcription: Umwana naime baaka mumuulu
eng_translation: The child has jumped so high up.

bem_transcription: Kuli abana nabambi abali kunuma ya uyu mwana uwimine baaka balemoneka nabapoosa sana amano kufyo balecita pafyo baletinika, bushe nifinshi bale-angasha?
eng_translation: They are other kids behind this child that has jumped, they seem to be focused on what they are pressing, what are they playing with?

bem_transcription: Bale-angasha, umo ali necibotolo ico alenwamo amenshi, umubiye aletamba ifikope pali lamya
eng_translation: They are playing, one with a bottle and drinking water while the other one is watching something on phone.

bem_transcription: Nga uyu umbi uusendeme panshi? bushe ninshi asendemene panshi so? bushe cinshi cingalenga?
eng_translation: What of the other one lying down? Why he is lying down? Could there be a reason?

bem_transcription: Aletuusha, acifuma mukutoloka naena elo lyena ati asendameko atuusheko
eng_translation: He is resting, he is also from jumping so he wants to rest.

bem_transcription: Shikulubantu naikala pamupando wa mwinshi pengilile myotoka
eng_translation: A man is siting in front of an entrance of a garage.

bem_transcription: Ngechi cimbayambaya cili kunuma yakwe, cilemoneka kwati cilabombe ncito iikankala sana, bushe ca nshi?
eng_translation: What about the vehicle behind him, it seems to do important work, what does it do?

bem_transcription: ici cimbayambaya cili kunuma yakwe, cibomba ukutapilila amenshi ku fikuulwa ifilepya nomulilo
eng_translation: This vehicle is a fire fighting truck.

bem_transcription: So ninshi uyu shikulu wikele pantashi apa eucenshe ici cimotoka? Eubomba incito yakushimyo mulilo?
eng_translation: Is he this man the one that drives it? Is he a fire fighter?

bem_transcription: Endita e, eubombo ukucensha, alabomba nababiye elo balafwa-ana
eng_translation: Yes, ofcourse he is the one, he has some colleagues that help him.

bem_transcription: Umuntu ali pancinga ale-ensha mumusebo
eng_translation: A person is on his bike riding it on the road.

bem_transcription: incinga ine iyi naibutusha sana umulumendo yu, alecilika na motoka, elo ninshi motoka ilabuutuka ukucila incinga, bushe nikwisa alelola uko alebutukila?
eng_translation: He is riding it so fast,faster than a vehicle, even though vehicles are faster,where is he rushing to?

bem_transcription: Talebukila ukuli konse, ale-ensha fye, ukwenda uko aleya
eng_translation: He is not rushing anywhere, he is just riding to wherever he is going.

bem_transcription: Ngeci cimpompo afwele ku mutwe? bushe nacikwate ncito iyo cilembomba olo acifwele fye pantu nacitemwa?
eng_translation: What of the helmet of his head, is there a reason for wearing it or he just likes it?

bem_transcription: Nakalya, tafwalile ati nacitemwa, acifwalile ukumucingilila kumasanso nga apona!
eng_translation: No, he does not just like it, it is meant to protect him incase he falls.

bem_transcription: Ulupwa nalwikala nembwa pacipuna
eng_translation: A family is sited with a dog on a couch.

bem_transcription: Ulupwa lwine luli ulwalingana, bawishi, banyina, umwana umwanakashi elyo no umwana umwaume nomba bushe imbwa nasho ishi pali iyanakashi neyaumme?
eng_translation: This is a complete family, the father, the mother, a girl child and a boy, are the dogs also male and female?

bem_transcription: Kuti caba, kuti pabe ya iikota ne lume
eng_translation: It could be so.

bem_transcription: Nomba ninshi amenso ya mbwa yalemonekela aya aka kwati li liti?
eng_translation: But why are the dog eyes as bright as light?

bem_transcription: Ico yalemonekela aya aka ca kweba ukuti kuntanshi kwaleba uwalebakopa
eng_translation: They are this bright because there is someone capturing them in front.

bem_transcription: Ibumba lya bana mayo na bashi tata lili kuntanshi ya bantu
eng_translation: A group of men and women are standing in front of people.

bem_transcription: Bushe ninshi beminine kuntanshi ya bantu mu musango wa so?
eng_translation: Why are they standing in front of people in this way?

bem_transcription: Cipalile ukweba ati ba mushika nyimbo baleimba kuntashi ya bantu
eng_translation: It seems they are musicians performing in front of people.

bem_transcription: Nyimbo nshi baleimba? Bushe kuti baba ni bakemba ba nyimbo mu ncende yama pepo?
eng_translation: What songs are they singing? could they be performers in a church?

bem_transcription: Ee cipalile kwati baleimba mwitempele lya mapepo
eng_translation: Yes they are performing inside a church.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu nasendama pamupando panse
eng_translation: A man is sleeping on a couch outside.

bem_transcription: imisendamine yakwa shikulu bantu uyu tailemoneka iyaibela. Bushe ilifye bwino olo taleumfwa bwino iyo nalwala
eng_translation: The way he is sleeping seems alittle off, could he just be sleeping or is he unwell?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya teti cishibikwe but ishi mipando bekala nga naunaka wafuma mukubomba
eng_translation: That's unknown, but these are chairs people sit on when they are tired after working.

bem_transcription: Apa pancende aikele uyu apo eletushisha, bushe ninungama ukutila ukuti paba ni pan'ganda yakwe?
eng_translation: This place is where he is resting, am I right to say this is his place?

bem_transcription: Namulungama ni kunuma ya ng'anda yakwe.
eng_translation: Yes, you are right, this is behind his house.

bem_transcription: Umwana umukashana aleangala kunuma ya ng'anda
eng_translation: A young girl is playing behind the house.

bem_transcription: Finshi ifi ifyaputika ifileikata umwana umukashana uyo?
eng_translation: What are these things blown things the child is playing with?

bem_transcription: Fintu fye baputa ifyakuwamishafye incende ilemoneka iyabukata
eng_translation: These are just blown decorations to make this place look beautiful.

bem_transcription: Ngotu tumbi utulemoneka utwabuta pa ncende iyi ine , bushe kuti twaba twanshi?
eng_translation: What of these white things, what could they be?

bem_transcription: Tuntu bamupangile utulepululuka mu mulu utwakuti aleangala asendwe amano
eng_translation: They use them them to make amusing things that fly high to amuse a crowd

bem_transcription: Umukashana no mulumendo baletolokela mu menshi.
eng_translation: A man and a lady are diving into water

bem_transcription: Umukashana uyu naimya amaboko ale nomba ninshi cinshi engemisha amaboko?
eng_translation: The lady has stretched her hands out why is it so?

bem_transcription: Emishe amaboko pamulandu wa kuti alefwaya ukutolokela apali.
eng_translation: It is because she is trying to jump to the ground

bem_transcription: Amenshi yalemoneka ayafiituluka. Bushe mumana uukulu olo mumana uunono?
eng_translation: The water seems a little dark, is this sea huge or small?

bem_transcription: Eco yalemonekala ayafitulukila nikumulandu wa kweba ukuti libemba ili, menshi nayafula.
eng_translation: The water looks like this because this sea is very big

bem_transcription: Bakafundisha bali nabana balebafunda ukwimya amaboko  mu muulu.
eng_translation: An instructor is with his students teaching them to raise their hands

bem_transcription: Bushe ukwimya kwamaboko uku mafunde aya? Nangula cilemoneka kwati nababapanika abaice.
eng_translation: Is lifting hands a rule or has he punished them?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya tababapanike nga namumona kafundisha uuli kunuma yabo kulya alemwentula.
eng_translation: No he hasn't punished them because there's another instructor behind smiling.

bem_transcription: Ninshi bengalabafunda ifyakwimya amaboko bushe ni kwisukulu uku bali nolo kwangala fye baleangala
eng_translation: Why would he be teaching them to lift their hands? Are they in school or are they just playing?

bem_transcription: Ni kusukulu bali endita ee. Balebafunda ukulatota pa kwimba.
eng_translation: They are in school of course, he is teaching them to clap as they sing

bem_transcription: Umwana umulumendo ale-angala mumusebo.
eng_translation: A little boy is playing on the road

bem_transcription: Bushe cinshi ekelepo umwana umulumendo uyu pantu cilemoneka kwati ali pa mwela.
eng_translation: What is he seated on? he seems to be suspended on air

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya tali pa mwela nakwata eco aleshelemukapo.
eng_translation: No he isn't suspended on air at all, he is sliding on something

bem_transcription: Nomba ninshi afulile isheti muncende iyaisuka so?
eng_translation: Then why is he shirtless in an open place?

bem_transcription: Afulile ishati ku mulandu wakweba ati nakukaba akasuba nakapya.
eng_translation: It is because it's very hot and sunny

bem_transcription: Abakashana batatu bale-enda mumbali ya musepo mupepi nama shopu.
eng_translation: Three ladies are walking on the road side close to some shops

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Balelola ku restranti uko balaya balile icakulya ca bushiku.
eng_translation: They are heading to a restaurant to have supper

bem_transcription: Umukashana uyu uushalilile panuma alemoneka kwati alependa ifintu muminwe bushe ni ndalama shilya?
eng_translation: The lady behind seems to be counting something is that money?

bem_transcription: Ee kuti caba balependa impiya ukweba ati beshibe umutengo wa fyakulya balaya bakwanishe.
eng_translation: Yes, it should be, they are trying to see how much they will spend on food

bem_transcription: Umukashana alemwentula mukwikata icisabi icikalamba.
eng_translation: A lady is smiling as she is about to touch a big fish

bem_transcription: Bushe lisabi lya shani ili ilyakula ifi ukulalingana no muntu kwaliba isabi lya so?
eng_translation: What sort of fish is this that is as huge as a person, does such fish exist?

bem_transcription: Endita, e eko lyaba isabi ilikalamba elyo lyena talimoneka moneka.
eng_translation: Yes it does though it's rare.

bem_transcription: Umukashana wine alemoneka uwa nsansa ilyo aleikata icisabi bushe bukulu bwa cisabi bulemupapusha ubwalenga asangalale?
eng_translation: She looks very happy touching the fish, is she amazed by the size and that's why she's happy?

bem_transcription: Ee, ecilelenga nacimupesha amano ukumona icisabi eco alingene nankwe umubili.
eng_translation: Yes she's amazed to see a fish as big as her self.

bem_transcription: Bashi tata nabana mayo bali abamwentula.
eng_translation: Some men and ladies are smiling.

bem_transcription: Cinshi bekete aba bashitata na banamayo muminwe?
eng_translation: What are they holding in their hands?

bem_transcription: Bekete imfuti ishakwangasha isha menshi.
eng_translation: They have some toy guns they are playing with

bem_transcription: Ngefi ifilemoneka ifya buta nokubekabeka pama beya yabo?
eng_translation: What of those white and shiny things on their shoulders?

bem_transcription: Ifyo ifyabuta bekwete fikete kwilaya ilyo bafwele ilyo babomfya pa kwangala ubwangalo ubo bwine.
eng_translation: The white things are stuck to their dresses that they are using to play this game

bem_transcription: Umuntu alesamba no bwato mu menshi.
eng_translation: A person is playing with a boat on water

bem_transcription: Ibemba lya menshi ili lilemoneka iluku, bushe talyamuse umuntu uyu nokumwibisha?
eng_translation: The sea looks huge, won't the person drown?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya balikanshiwa pakuya mukusamba kwi bemba lya menshi yamusango ulya.
eng_translation: No, they are able to swim for them to go to such a huge sea

bem_transcription: so ninshi umuntu uyu aleumfwa fye bwino ukulayangala pali bemba lya menshi ili?
eng_translation: Does this mean that he is happy to be playing in such water?

bem_transcription: Endita, e eco elileko nimusangala, ukwangala pe bemba line ili .
eng_translation: Yes, that's why he is here to play in the sea.

bem_transcription: Nabwinga nashibwinga bafuma muceci mukupalwa icupo cabo.
eng_translation: A bride and a groom are from having their wedding blessed in a church

bem_transcription: Shibwinga na nabwinga uyu bali abansansa bushe emukuti baliitemwana sana?
eng_translation: They seem so happy, are they in love?

bem_transcription: Endita ee, eco bopanine ni kumulandu wakuti balitemwana icine cine.
eng_translation: Yes of course, that's why they have gotten married.

bem_transcription: Ngoku ukuboko ukuli pamolu wa ka shibwinga uyu mwati ukuti kwaba kuboko kwaba nani?
eng_translation: What of the hand over the groom, whose is it?

bem_transcription: Uku ukuboko cipalile kwati kwaba shimapepo abalebapala icupo cabo.
eng_translation: It should be the priest's that's blessing their marriage.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu naikata icitabo icikulu.
eng_translation: A man is holding a huge book.

bem_transcription: Bushe citabo ca shani ici icakula ifi elo finshi alecibomfesha uyu shikulu bantu?
eng_translation: What sort of book is this? It's so big what does he use it for?

bem_transcription: Ici ictabo calembwamo amafunde ayakukonka.
eng_translation: It is a book of rules to follow.

bem_transcription: Ninshi uyu shitata nomba asalile fye ukwisa funda fye ubushiku?
eng_translation: But did he just choose to come and teach this late?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya enshita fye baumfwene fye ukukumana.
eng_translation: No, they certainly agreed to meet at this time.

bem_transcription: Umwana umunono umulumendo aleanga mumatipa.
eng_translation: A little boy is playing in mud.

bem_transcription: Umwana wine naunfwa bwino alemoneka ali ne nsansa. Bushe kwangala mumatipa kulelenga ati omfwe bwino so?
eng_translation: The boy seems so happy, is it playing with mud that's making him this excited?

bem_transcription: Namusosa umwana natemwa ukwangala mumatipa.
eng_translation: Yes, you are right, he is very excited to play in mud.

bem_transcription: Bushe ena nomba teshibe ati amenshi aya yafiko yali ne ndoti kuti aambula ubulwele?
eng_translation: Doesn't he know the water is dirty and can make him sick?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya teshibe nangu panono pantu umwana munya.
eng_translation: No he doesn't, he is a baby.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu alekaka ifyela umupita ishitima.
eng_translation: A man is fixing rails.

bem_transcription: Ifyela fipitamo ishitima fyaba ifyafina ala fyalilema nomba shitata uyu mwati kuti akwanisha ukukaka palwakwe?
eng_translation: These rails look very heavy, will be manage alone?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya ali nababiye abalemwafwa abaliko akatalamukila tabalemonekela.
eng_translation: No, be has some people helping him at a distance.

bem_transcription: Nge ci afwele mumatwi na kumutwe cimpompo canshi?
eng_translation: What about those things around his ears and the helmet what are they for?

bem_transcription: Ico afwele icimpompo ku mutwe  cakumucingilila  amasanso elyo ifyo ifili mumatwi fyakumucingilila icongo mu matwi.
eng_translation: The helmet is to protect his head from any injuries and the ear plugs are meant to protect his ears.

bem_transcription: Utubwa utunono baletusambika.
eng_translation: Puppies are being washed.

bem_transcription: Iminwe ishi ishilemoneka ishileitila utubwa amenshi, bushe sha mulumendo nelyo sha mukashana?
eng_translation: Are the hands washing the puppies male or female?

bem_transcription: Shamukashana kuti mwamwena fye ku maala yali ayalepalepa.
eng_translation: They are female, it's clear from the long nails.

bem_transcription: Ngomu baletusambila utubwa utu bushe ni mwisa?
eng_translation: Where are these puppies being washed from?

bem_transcription: Baletusambikila muci dishi cakusambilamo na bantu.
eng_translation: From a bath tub that people use.

bem_transcription: Umwana umunono umukashana naikala pamupando wa panse.
eng_translation: A little girl is sited on a chair outside.

bem_transcription: Ninshi umwana wine uyu afumishe ululimi panse bushe aleumfwa fye bwino ifi fine?
eng_translation: Why has she stuck her tongue out, is she enjoying this way?

bem_transcription: Eya mukwai afumishe ululimi panse pa mulandu wakuti natemwa ukwikala pa mupando.
eng_translation: Yes, she has her tongue out because she's excited to be sited outside on this seat.

bem_transcription: Bushe uku ukwikele umwana uyu ni ng'anda yabafyashi bakwe olo ni mu musebo fye ekele?
eng_translation: Is this her parent's place or is she just sited on the roadside?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya ni pa ng'anda yabafyashi bakwe tekumusebo fye, nga ali ku musebo nga alifwala insapato ya kumakasa.
eng_translation: No, she's not on the road side but home, if she were on the road side, she would have shoes on.

bem_transcription: Umwaume nabika ifimapofu kumyefu alebeya imyefu.
eng_translation: A man has soap foam on his beards as he shaves.

bem_transcription: Alemoneka uwa nsansa nelyo alebeya imyemfu.
eng_translation: He seems so happy as he shaves.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati ifi alebomfya ukubeyala imyemfu filekalipa sana pantu nafimusha notuma pumbapumba.
eng_translation: It seems whatever he is using to shave is painful because he has razor bumps.

bem_transcription: Imyemfu shine te shonse alefumya pantu shimbi nashako mumbali.
eng_translation: He is not shaving completely because he has left some hair on the sides.

bem_transcription: Umwaume uyu wine pakubeya imyemfu nabendeka na kanwa pakutila imyemfu shingafuma shonse.
eng_translation: He has even bent his mouth so that he can shave well.

bem_transcription: Bashitata abengi sana bambi nabekala bali ku maliketi baleshitisha ifintu ifyapusana pusana.
eng_translation: A number of men, some sited are in a marketplace selling different items.

bem_transcription: Aba bshitata batatu bali pa maliketi baleshitisha ifyakulya pamo nga bacilemba, ba tomato elyo nomusalu, kabili balemoneka ukuti nabanaka icine cine pa mulandu wakuposa inshita iikalamba ukushitisha fintu baleshitisha.
eng_translation: The three men are selling food such as beans, tomatoes and other vegetables, and  they seem so tired because of spending so much time selling.

bem_transcription: Elyo pali aba bashitata bambi beminine fye te bonse kwena abaleshitisha bambi nabekata mu misana shabo bambi bapwenekefye nshishibe ne fyo balelolesha.
eng_translation: Not all the men however are selling, some are just standing and aimlessly looking at something while holding their waists, I have no idea what they are looking at.

bem_transcription: Cilepala ukuti iyi emaliketi ikalamba sana kuncende bekalila. Elo pali aba bashitata abengi nabafwala amatoloshi bambi abengi bafwele ifipalile ukuti fitenge.
eng_translation: It seems this is the biggest market in this place. A number of these men are in trousers while others are in African attires (fitenges).

bem_transcription: Elo pali ababene bashi tata abengi bafwele ifyakufwala ifyabuta kumuulu nomba balemoneka kwati bonse bali ne nsala cilepala kwati tabalile
eng_translation: Many of these men are dressed in white on top but they look so hungry, it's like they haven't eaten.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili bacitile kwati nabafukama elyo baimya ukuboko kumo mu muulu kumbi kuliko munshiko panono elyo balelolesha mu muulu
eng_translation: Two young have each put one hand in the air then the other on a bottle top and they are facing the sky.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba nga cakutila walilolekeshe pali ici cikope finshi ulemona bushe iyi incende ilemoneka shani?
eng_translation: What are you seeing on this picture, how does this place look like?

bem_transcription: Kwena ici icikope naciwama icine cine kabili ne ncende baliko ilemoneka iyayemba kabili icikulwa icili kunuma yabo cilemoneka icakulwa bwino icine cine.
eng_translation: This is a beautiful picture and the place is lovely, the building behind them too is well built.

bem_transcription: Cishinka naulungika emulandu wine balemonekela abansansa pantu ne cikulwa baliko cisuma, incende ilemoneka iyayemba bwino sana.
eng_translation: Yes you are right, that is why they look so happy because even the building they are in is beautiful, indeed this is a very nice place.

bem_transcription: Imbwa iya yemba bwino sana ili palubansa lwa ng'anda ileangala.
eng_translation: A very nice dog is playing outside a house.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi ine imbwa ilemoneka iya yemba bwino sana amasako yayako yantu yafita kabili yabeka. Naitoloka naikwata nacimo ku kanwa icapala umupila.
eng_translation: This is a very pretty dog with black and shiny fur. It has jumped has something like a ball stuck to it's mouth.

bem_transcription: Ala iyi imbwa yalisalapuka icine cine kabili naitoloka naikwata no mupila kukanwa kaiko. Ala we mbwa wee walicenjela
eng_translation: This dog is so cleaver and it has something like a ball on its mouth. Indeed it is cleaver.

bem_transcription: Cishinka cilemoneka kwati umwine uwaiteka alibikako amano mukuisambilisha ifya kutoloka kumona fye fintu itolweke
eng_translation: Its true and its looks like the dogs owner knows how to teach his dog you can just see from the way the dog has jumped.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali pali bemba uwapabuka sana aleanga icangalo icakushelemuka ukubonfya imbao iyapapatala
eng_translation: A young man is on sea playing with his surfing board.

bem_transcription: Wee bemba umukalamba ee kabili alemoneka bwino sana elo amenshi yalemoneka ayayemba icine cine kabili umulumendo naima pamulandu wa kuti bemba acimwimya
eng_translation: What a big beautful sea it is and a young is way up high on his surf board.

bem_transcription: Elyo uyu wine shitata na fwala ne cimpompo ku mutwe icakumucingilisha, kabili nafwala na kaputula iya makumbi makumbi mwapita nefyakashika
eng_translation: This same old man is putting on an helmet for protection and is also putting on a blue short with red stips.

bem_transcription: iyi icende ilemoneka ukuti yaliwama icine cine kabili eko abantu baya mukwangalila kabili uyu umulumendo alemoneka uwashipa icine cine ukwangalila pali bemba pantu taca-anguka iyo
eng_translation: This is a lovely place and it looks like its where people go and fun and this young man is really brave to be surfing like this.

bem_transcription: Elyo pa mulu wakushipa cilepala kwati mu minwe yakwe nakwata ne intambo ilemutinta lintu aleangalila pali bemba kuli icapala indeke ku muulu
eng_translation: And on top of him  being brave he has a rope in his hands which is tied so something pulling him has he is surfing.

bem_transcription: Na mayo ali mucibansa ca fyangalo aleteya icangalo cintu aishibisha ukuteya elyo alemoneka alicenjela muli ici cangalo
eng_translation: A lady is in the tenis court playing and she is good at it.

bem_transcription: umukashana ubusuma ee alemoneka uwayemba icine cine kabili umushishi wakwe walilukwa bwino kabili nafwala necitambala ku mutwe wakwe
eng_translation: What a beautful lady her hair is well plainted and she has a head wrap.

bem_transcription: Nimbona akatambala uyu umukashana afwele kalemoneka akayemba pantu kantu kabuta elyo napacongewa akatu akakashika akalemoneka bwino sana
eng_translation: And She has a nice white head wrap with a symbol of Nike

bem_transcription: Ifyakufwala afwele uyu mukashana filemoneka ifisuma icine cine, ilaya afwele lilemoneka ilisuma kabili nama sikiyo yakayena naya yemba icine cine
eng_translation: She is putting on very nice clothes awell as nice hear rings.

bem_transcription: Elo kunuma yakwe nangula cakutila takulemwenekesha sana, kulemoneka kuli na bantu abengi abeshile mukutamba ici cangalo cilepala kwati balicitemwa.
eng_translation: Even though we can't see clearly from behind its looks like there are a lot  of people who have come to watch the game.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naimina pe libwe elyo tafwele ne shati.
eng_translation: A  young boy is standing on a rock shirtless

bem_transcription: Kuncende ali kulemoneka ukusuma sana kabili kuli ifimuti, utufyani, elo na kabili kulemonako akamumana akanono
eng_translation: The place he is at looks very nice with trees and grass and there is a river from a distance.

bem_transcription: Aka akamumana kalemonaka kwati kashiba fye elyo mwalifula amabwe ayengi sana pantu ne ncende fye nga twalolekesha ilemonekafye kwaisula fye amabwe.
eng_translation: This river looks deep and there are rocks every where.

bem_transcription: Nga fintu balandilepo kale uyu umulumendo takwete icakuflwa kumulu pamubili wakwe kabili nafwala na kaputula yakashikila elyo ne nsapato kabili alelolesha amenshi
eng_translation: The boy is shirtless and he is putting a short Red pants with shoes on while stairing in the water .

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati uyu mulumendo akasuba nakamoca sana emulandu wine nafula naipekanya alefwaya ukuwingila mu menshi
eng_translation: It looks like a suuny day thats why he has taken off his shirt in readyness for swiming.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naikala pe tebulo naikata akapala kwati ni ka kapu akanono kabili akabuta
eng_translation: A boy is sited on the table with a small cup in his hands.

bem_transcription: Cine cine uyu umulumendo naikala pe tebulo, kabili ukuboko kwa kwe kumbi kuli petebulo elo nafwala necampepo
eng_translation: True he is sited on the table and his other hand is on the table too and is puttin on something warm.

bem_transcription: Nomba nga kutila walimulolekeshe uyu wine mulumendo fintu alemoneka, bushe kuti watila alemoneka shani?
eng_translation: If you look closely how can you describe this boy?

bem_transcription: Nga kulolekesha sana uyu mulumendo cipalile kwati nakalimo paciba ifyo acilanwa muli ka kapu akanono akabuta, pantu nga kumulolekesha bwwino sana natonta sana amenso kuli aka ka kapu akanono.
eng_translation: If we look closely its like he was taking drinking something from the white cup because his eyes are foused on the cup.

bem_transcription: Nomba ine nga nalolekesha ndemona kwati nakolwa kabili acilanwa ubwalwa nangula umwangashi kumona fye  amenso fintu yalemoneka nayaya na ku muulu.
eng_translation: I am thinking he is drunk, he was drinking beer you can just tell from the way his eyes are looking.

bem_transcription: Na mayo ali mucikulwa ico bakula bwino sana kabili ici cikulwa mwaliba ifintu ifyalekana lekana ifyo bapanga bwino sana.
eng_translation: A lady is ni a nice building with a lot of nice things they have made.

bem_transcription: Ca cine uyu namayo ali mu cikulwa kabili alewamya ifya kuwamya wamya kuli ici icilemoneka ica mbao kabili icikwete utushimbi
eng_translation: Its true  this lady is in the room doing some cleaning.

bem_transcription: Ici cine icikwtete utushimbi cilemoneka kwati cintu ba bonfya mukuteya icangalo pantu nga nalolesha apeminine uyu umukashana pali notumipila utunono.
eng_translation: And the same thing she is cleaning looks like its something they use to play a game, beacuse they are balls

bem_transcription: Kabili muli ici cine cikulwa muli ifintu ifyalekana lekana pamo nge tebulo elo na kabili kuli cimo icilemoneka icakashikila kashikila icilepala icishimbi.
eng_translation: In the same room, there are a lot of things on the table and there is a red steel.

bem_transcription: Elyo uyu namayo alemoneka temukashana iyo alemoneka mukalambako panono elyo alikwata ne mishishi ishipi teshitali.
eng_translation: And this is not a young woman she is a little bit older and she has short hair.

bem_transcription: Abantu aba pusana pusana bana mayo, bashi tata, abana abanono, abakashana na baume bali mucikulwa icikalamba sana.
eng_translation: Diffrent people, woman, men and children are in the building.

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: And if i look closely in the same building there is something that looks like a big ball in the middle.

bem_transcription: Kabili ici icapala umupila balicipikula ne nsalu iyakwata amalangi ayalekana lekana, kabili ne cikulwa cakaena cilemoneka icakosa icine cine.

eng_translation: This is a strong building beacuse they have build it with big steel that holds it and the glasses look very strong.

eng_translation: Two old disabled men are standing on the middle of the road.

eng_translation: Its true they are standing on the middle of the road and they are sited on something that look like small motor cycles and they are putting on sun glasses.

eng_translation: And it looks like a sunny day thats why they are putting on sun glasses

eng_translation: The two old men are standing on the store and there are different things around them.

bem_transcription: Aba bashitata bonse babili apo balilemana cilemoneka kwati tabakumanisha ukuyendela abene emulandu wine balebonfesha utu ututukutuku.
eng_translation: The fact that the two old men are disabled and can't walk on their own thats they are using something like small motor cycle.

eng_translation: A man is in the wild bush it look like he has gone hiking.

bem_transcription: Ku ncende kuli shitata uku kulemoneka ukwayemba icine cine kabili kusuma ifimuti ifyo fye filemoneka, filemoneka ifingi kabili ifyatitikana kabili ifisuma.
eng_translation: This is a beautful place with many trees.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ifi fimuti fyalititikana sana nangula fyalipalamana sana, elyo nga nalolekesha fyaba pamulu wa lupili.
eng_translation: Indeed this are nice packed tree so close to each other and it like they have grown on the mountain.

bem_transcription: Kabili nga twamona sana uyu shitata kuncende kuntu ali kulemoneka kuli akasuba sana emulandu wine afwalile ama galashi pakuti alecingilila amenso yakwe ku kasuba
eng_translation: and it looks like  its sunny thats why the man is putting on sun glasses.

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata nga twalolesha umushi wakwe ulemoneka uwafulungana cilepala kwati tasakwile cimo cine fye no mwemfu wakwe.
eng_translation: The man hasn't combed his hair as well as the beards.

bem_transcription: Bashi tata batatu nabeka panshi bonse batatu balemoneka ababulanda.
eng_translation: Three old men are sited looking very sad.

bem_transcription: Cine aba bashitata balemoneka nabanaka icine cine kabili bekele pa muulu napeta amolu yabo elo umbi uuli pesmba nankwe napeta amolu yakwe
eng_translation: True, the old men are looking very tired. Two are sitted on top folding their legs and the other one is sited on the ground.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati uyu shitata ena uwikele panshi alepanga ifyapala kwati mutondo pantu nakwata nefibombelo ifyo abikile panshi
eng_translation: The one sited on floor is making something like a pot and he has a lot of things around him

eng_translation: Indeed the man is a potter you can tell by the pots he has around him.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutiala pakupanga nangula pakubumba ishi inongo nangula ifyapala imitondo albomfya no umulilo emulandu wine kunuma yakwe kuli inkuni.
eng_translation: And the other thing is that for him to make these pots he also needs fire that's why he has the fire wood behind him.

bem_transcription: Cine cine aya amabimbi yalemoneka bwino sana kabili bemba ikalamba icine cine.
eng_translation: Indeed the waves are nice and the sea is so big.

bem_transcription: Nga wamulolekesha uyu wine umulumendo mulandu nshi uletontonkaya afwalile icakufwala camusango ulya?

bem_transcription: Umulandu afwalile ici cakufwala pantu ecasuminishiwa nga cakuti muleteya icangalo cakwangalila pali bemba mukalamba.
eng_translation: Beacuse it's the right atire for such games.

bem_transcription: Ee cishinka cimbi cakutila ici icakufwala cilamwangukila nangula nacibomba nalintu aleangala ici icangalo.

eng_translation: Its true he has taken some time to clean his house so that it looks clean.

bem_transcription: Nomba mona fye nefyo ifibumba fya ng'anda yakwe filemoneka ubusaka, bushe naumona?

bem_transcription: Nimbona icine cine cilepala ukuti uyu umulemendo wabusaka icine cine kanshi emulandu wine lyonse afwaila ukutila ing'anda yakwe ilemoneka bwino emulandu wine aleiwamisha.
eng_translation: Its true the young loves his house to be clean thats why he always wants to keep it clean.

eng_translation: He is using a bucket full of water and a ladder to clean his house.

eng_translation: It seems he is outside a shop because it seems they are two doors and he seems to be looking at something inside the shop.

eng_translation: This picture shows a young man with an two elderly people, where are these people?

bem_transcription: Umu nimumuputule wakwipikilamo pantu nabacitofu emo bali elyo nababikapo nefimapoto ifikulu baleipika fyakulya.
eng_translation: This is inside a kitchen because it is full of stoves where they put huge pots.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Bafwele fye ifyapusana-pusana aba bantu, uyu uuli kuntashi afwele fye icampepo icamakumbi makumbi mwapita notumilaini twamutuntula,elyo umbi afwele fye ishati ilya buuta tuutu.
eng_translation: They are all differently dressed, the one in front is wearing a blue and yellow jersey while the one is wearing a very white shirt.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walondolola efyakufwala bafwele kabili balebombesha sana pakuti bengapange ndalama atemwa pakuti bengasafoola indalama pa mweshi.
eng_translation: Yes, that's how they are dressed, they work so hard in order to get paid on the month-end.

bem_transcription: Nangu cakutila icikope tacilelanga bwino bwino sana abantu, lelo pali umo uwiminine nakwata lamya kumaboko yakwe, bushe naumona?
eng_translation: Even though this picture is unclear,  there's a person standing with a phone in his hands, have you seen him?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, elyo uyu wine shitata aliine icine cine, kumona fye ifyakufwala ukukula fintu afwele pantu icakufwala cakwe cimo abantu babili kukumana nga cakutila balibapele.
eng_translation: I have seen, he is a very fat man, it's clear from the huge clothes he is wearing that can fit two people at once if given.

bem_transcription: Cishinka walanda, ala uyu aliine cine cine! Icampepo cakwe fye libulangeti, bushe finshi afwele kumutwe?
eng_translation: That's true , he indeed is very fat, he's jersey is literally a blanket, what's that he is wearing on his head?

bem_transcription: Uyu muntu nafwala akasote akafiita kumutwe, nomba umutwe wakwe ukalamba nawena walinina kumo, waina kwati lifwesa.
eng_translation: He is wearing a black hat, he has a really fat head, as fat as a hippo.

bem_transcription: Ala cishinka ifi walanda ala aliino-mutwe kabili amakalashi yakwe nayacepa kumenso yakwe kabili cipalile ukuti aletonta amenso kumo ilyo alelanda pali lamya.
eng_translation: Indeed his head is fat such that even his glasses are not fitting his face and he is focused on one side as he talks on phone.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope cilelangilila abantu abengi sana bale-enda kabili kuli shitata umo uwikele panshi, bushe naubamona abantu abale-enda na shitata uwikele panshi?
eng_translation: This picture is showing a number of people walking with a man sited down, have you seen them?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu nimbamona elyo uyu shitata uwikele panshi euleshitisha fintu atantike mumbali yamusebo pantu pali ifyakufwala fintu aleshitisha.
eng_translation: I have seen them, the man sited down is the one selling the clothes that he has displayed on the side walk.

bem_transcription: Cishinka walanda uyu shitata naikala mumbali yamusebo umo ashitisha ifyakufwala fyakwe kabili ifilemoneka bwino bushe fyakufwala nshi afwele?
eng_translation: Yes he is the one selling the good looking clothes, what clothes is he wearing?

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata afwele fye ishati ilipi amaboko namupita ifyafiita, utumulaini utwakashika elyo notwabuuta, nafwala netoloshi afwala nefyapala bamakapa.
eng_translation: He is wearing a short sleeved shirt with white and red stripes, a trouser and slippers.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, efyakufwala afwele kabili wacikalamba icine cine, kabili napatulako inshita yakwe pakuti engayashitisha amakwebo yakwe pakuti engasangamo indalama ishakubomfya mubumi bwakwe.
eng_translation: Yes those are the clothes he is wearing and he is an elderly man that has spared some time to do business to sustain himself.

bem_transcription: Uyu namayo nafwale citambala elyo nafwala nendeleshi iyafiitulukila, nafwala namagalashi, cilepala kwati amenso yakwe tayamwensa bwino.
eng_translation: This woman is wearing a head covering and a brown dress, spectacles, it seems she has an eye problem.

bem_transcription: Kuminwe yakwe nakwata icakukopelako ifikope, kuntu atontele amenso kuli ifiliko emulandu wine alekopela ifikope.
eng_translation: She is holding a camera in her hands and focused on something that she is capturing.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka naulungika, elyo utu utubwa tulecena, aka akafiita nakelikisha akankwe panshi kaleilingana napanshi.
eng_translation: Yes, you right, the dogs are playing and the black has the other dog on the ground.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifi walanda tulecena, tule-angala atemwa kamo kacicenjesha akankwe emulandu wine wine tulelwila, bushe kulya ukuli utubwa kuli finshi?
eng_translation: Yes you right, they are playing or it could be one tricked the other that's why they are fighting, what's in this place?

bem_transcription: Kulemoneka icikuulwa, nangula cakutila tacilemoneka bwino, cilemoneka cikuulwa ca mbao elyo lubali lumbi kulemoneka nolubao ulukalamba ulwabuuta.
eng_translation: From a distance is a building made of timber and there is also a big barrier.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifyo walanda efiliko, kabili utu utubwa, cipalile ukuti twalitemwana sana emulandu wine tule-angalila uyu musango.
eng_translation: Thats true and it seems thats these dogs are friends thats why they are playing like this

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila motoka, elo pali nabantu abafwele ifyapalana, elo umbi naikala, elo umbi ale-enda, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: On this picture is a vehicle with people wearing the same clothes, one is sited while the other is walking. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona, iyi nimotoka yabakapokola iili apa, intu yabuuta mwapita nomulaini uwafiita, lubali lumbi kuli nouleyendela fye.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen this is a police vehicle and it is painted white with a black line on it. On the other hand is someone walking.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, iyi yena nimotoka yabakapokola, kumonafye ifyo baipanga elyo nababikapo neciishibisho icilelangilila ukuti nimotoka yabakapokola, nomba fyakufwala fyamusango nshi bafwele?
eng_translation: That's true this is a police vehicle you can just see from the way it was designed and there is a symbol showing that its is a police vehicle. Now what type of clothes is he wearing?

bem_transcription: Elyo lubali lumbi ,kulemoneka icikuulwa icabuuta kabili ici cilemoneka cikalamba, nakalimo bakapokola eco balelonda.
eng_translation: On the other side is a big building maybe the police are guarding it.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, cipalile kuti beshile mukulonde cikuulwa icikalamba apo emulimo babomba kabili emulimo wabo, cine cine nabesa mukulonde cicikuulwa kabili umbi alelanshanya no munankwe.
eng_translation: That's true they have come to gurad the building because that's their work and the police man is chatting with a friend.

bem_transcription: Uwacaice umukashana ale-enda pamenshi, kabili uyu umumana waba nomucanga, kabili alelolenkana ukuli fyoni, bushe naumona imyendele yakwe?
eng_translation: A young girl is walking on water and this river has a lot of sand, she is walking towards the birds. Have you seen the way she is walking?

bem_transcription: Nimbona nomba uku ali nikululamba lwa mumana emulandu wine no mucanga wingi sana, elyo alefwaya ukupepeka ifyoni ifi ifingi ifili mupepi nankwe.
eng_translation: I have seen she is on a beach  thats why there are alot of sand and she wants to case these birds.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, ala uyu wacaice uyu alelolenkana ukuli ifyoni kabili ifi fyuni filenda pa menshi, nomba finshi fimbi ulemona pali ici cikope.
eng_translation: Thats true this young girls is walking toward the birds and the birds are on water. Whats else are you seeing on the picture?

bem_transcription: Lulya lubali lumbi, kwena kulemoneka fye mucanga uwabuuta tuutu! elyo ifyoni nafyena nafipupuka ifingi.
eng_translation: On the other side there is  just a lot of white sand and the birds are flying.

bem_transcription: Ca cine! Ala baliupanga bwino uyu mumuma kabili waba ukwabe fimuti ifingi sana, cipalile ukuti eko abantu besa mukwangalila atemwa ukuleseshamo icitendwe.
eng_translation: Thats true this river is well built and there are lot of trees and it looks like people come here to have fun.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope cilelangilila isabi ilikalamba nalifuma mumenshi, bushe naumona ifyo limine ukufuma mumenshi?
eng_translation: The picture is showing a fish out of the water, have you seen how high it is from the water?

bem_transcription: Nomba isabi lyakaena likalamba, elyo lilemoneka ilya katapa-katapa, nshatalamonapo isabi lyamusango yu, nakalimo nabaikata kundobo.
eng_translation: This is a big green fish i have never seen such a big fish. may it has been caught with a fishing hook?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Icimumana cilemoneka icapabuuka sana, elyo tapali na mabimbi, amenshi yalemoneka ayatekanya bwino bwino.
eng_translation: The sea looks wide and there are no waves the water looks calm

bem_transcription: Cishinka! Ala umufumine isabi mumana uukalamba, cipalile kuti mwabe sabi ilyalekana-lekana ilingi kabili ilya misango yonse. We muman busuma e!
eng_translation: Thats true. This is a huge sea and there are different types of fish in it. What a beautful sean it is!

bem_transcription: Ici icikope cilelangilila abalumendo babili abakashika kabili nabafwalako fimo kumutwe, bushe nikwisa uku bali?
eng_translation: This picture is showing two white men and they are putting on something on their head. where are they?

bem_transcription: Aba balemoneka kwati nimumuputule wakwipikilamo bali pantu bafwele filya bakepika bafyakulya bafwala, nababikapo notusote utwabuuta.
eng_translation: This looks like a kitchen beacuse they are wearing clothes thats chiefs wear when they are cooking and they are putting on head wraps.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati kuli ifyo balebuula munshi yetebulo ifyo balebika pa mbale, pantu nga twalolesha pa mbale palemonekapo fimo ifyabuuta ifyo alebiikapo.
eng_translation: Its like they are getting something under the table which they are putting on the plate. And if you look closely their is something white on the plate.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, uyu umulumendo aloleshe ukulefume fyakulya elo umubiye alemulolesha, pacipampa cimbi pali ifyebo ifingi ifyalembwa mucitundu cimbi, elo pali notupampa utunono apalembwa umutengo wafyakulya.
eng_translation: Thats  true this man is looking where the food is coming from a friend is looking at him. there is something written on the board in foregn language and the small board they are prices of the food.

bem_transcription: Ici ickope cilelangilila abalumendo batatu bale-enda, elyo umo natangila nakwatako fimo, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: This picture is howing three men walking one is ahead of them and he has something. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, lelo kwena tebonse abale-enda, umo pali aba uuli kuntashi eminine fye ale-engasha utumupila tutatu muminwe yakwe elyo aletwikatila pamo
eng_translation: I Have seen though not every one is walking the on in front  is just standing palying with tree balls in his hands.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, aletwangasha kaili natukwata amalangi ayalekana-lekana kaili natupusana amalangi, elo aba bambi kunuma bale-enda elo balelanshanya ngo yu umbi ali mwisa?
eng_translation: Thats true he is playing with them and they have different colours, others behind are walking while charting. Where is the other one?

bem_transcription: Uyu umbi alemoneka kwati engile mwituuka ilyo babikako fye ifipepala ifyabeeka ifimwensha mukati elyo nafwala namagalashi.
eng_translation: He is in the store wearing glasses and the store is coverd with something that makes it shine so that you can see inside.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ici icikope cilelangilila uwacaice umulumendo naikala panshi kabili ali mumuputule wakwe, nomba finshi alelolesha uyu uwacaice?
eng_translation: On this picture you can a young boy sited in his room, now what is he looking at?

bem_transcription: Uyu umwaice alelolesha icakwangasha icilemoneka icakatapa-katapa kabili icilemoneka nga kamotoka, elyo nikamotoka kene pantu nakakwata namawilo.
eng_translation: He is looking at his green toy that looks like a car with wheels.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana uyu uwacaice atontele amenso yakwe pakalubi atemwa kamotoka ako bapanga fye akayendela, nomba naumona ifili kunuma yakwe?
eng_translation: Thats true he is looking at his favorite toy. Have you seen whats behind him?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, kulemoneka ubusanshi ubo baashinke bwino sana, kabili ifyakufimbana ifilipo filemoneka ifyabusaka, abene bamwana balibikako amano mukuwasha.
eng_translation: I have seen there is a nice well prepared bed with nice and clean bedings, his parents really takes care of him.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, uyu umuputule ulemoneka bwino sana kabili uwabusaka no busanshi bwakwe bulemoneka ubwabusaka! Ala babusaka icine cine kabili balipoosako amano kuli uyu mwana.
eng_translation: Thats true this bed room looks really clean awell as the bed. They have kept this room very clean!

bem_transcription: Abakashana babili, nakamwana, nomulumendo, nabeminina mumbali ya mpanga.
eng_translation: Two girls, a bady and a boy are standing on the road side..

bem_transcription: Elo kabili balemoneka aba nsansa nakalimo pali icilebaseekesha.
eng_translation: They seem happy maybe they are looking at something funny.

bem_transcription: Nga ni uyu umukashana uuli kuntashi ala naceensa, cilepala kwati kuli ifyo amwene ifisuma kuntashi.
eng_translation: The girl in front has really smiled its look like there is something fuuny in front

bem_transcription: Incende yakaena ilemoneka ni ilye ncende eyo baya fye mukutushishako.
eng_translation: The place looks like an amusement park

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilemoneka kwati nikuparka uko abantu baya mukulesesha fye icitendwe, pantu ilemoneka iyafunda bwino sana fye iyayemba, iyakatapa-katapa.
eng_translation: This is a park where people go and fun and play and it is well maintained with green plants.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila abantu babili, ekutila umulumendo elyo nomukashana, umukashana naikala panshi elo umulumendo naima amabaka, bushe naumona fintu acitile?
eng_translation: On this picture there are two people a girl and a boy, a gilr is sited while the boy has jumped with a kick. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo naima sana, elyo nafumya icibaaka icikali, nga cakutila califikile umuntu, umuntu kupona napanshi.
eng_translation: The boy has jumped wth a nice kick, If this kick lande on someone they can fall.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana uyu umulumendo alyanguka kabili alema amabaka icine cine, kabili umukashana alemwentula ukumona ifyo emine amabaka, bushe finshi fimbi ulemona?
eng_translation: The boy is really flexable and he knows how to do flips and the girl is smiling seein the boy . What else can you see?

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana naumfwa bwino sana cilemoneka kwati nacimupapusha ukumona uko umulumendo emine amabaka elyo nacimupapusha sana.
eng_translation: It seems the girl is really happy seen the boy doing the kick and she is amazed.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifi walanda kabili namwentula ukumona umwaume uyu naima amabaka, kabili ukutukusha umubili nokuicingilila caliwama sana cine cine.
eng_translation: Thats true she is smiling seeing the boy, with no doubt it is good doing exerses.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila umukashana uwacikalamba, naiminina kabili ali pancende pamo, bushe finshi akwete kuminwe yakwe?
eng_translation: On this picture we can see an old lady standing on a certain place. What is she holding?

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana muminwe yakwe akwete umwamfuli uwamakumbi makumbi mwapita nefyabuuta nakalimo imfula ileloka.
eng_translation: The woman is holding a blue umbrella with white stripes and it is rainning.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifi walanda kaili kumbi kuminwe naikata nakapu, kabili nafwala ne fyakufwala ifilemoneka bwino icine cine, bushe nipesa apa ali?
eng_translation: What you have said it true, on the other hand she is holding a cup and she is wearing nice clothes. Where is she at?

bem_transcription: Apa ali nipa ng'anda pantu ing'anda ilemoneka elyo no mwinshi uukwete iciibi icakashika panse balibyalapo notumaluba.
eng_translation: She is at home you cvan see the house witha red door and they have planted flowers.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ifi walanda, ala in`ganda isuma icine cine kabili umukashana naipekanya ukuicingilila pakuti nga cakuti imfula nga yaisa engaasha umwamfuli kabili nafyala nefyampepo.
eng_translation: Thats true this is a nice house and she has prepared herself so that when the rain starts she can use the umbrella and she is also putting on warm clothes

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila abacifyashi babili, bambi nabakontama elyo bambi nabeminina balelolesha panshi, bushe nikwisa kuntu uku bali?
eng_translation: On the this picture they are teo parents, one one had bowled down the other on is looking on the ground. Where are they?

bem_transcription: Aba bashitata bonse babili bali pancito, emulandu wine bafwalile ifimpompo nefyakubombelamo lelo ifimpompo bafwele fili ifyapusana.
eng_translation: These men are working thats why they are putting on helments and work suits though they have diffent helments.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifi walanda, bali pamulimo untu balebomba kabili nabafwala nefyakuicinga ilintu balebomba, nomba fyakufwala fyamusango nshi bafwele aba bantu babili?
eng_translation: What you have said is true they are working they have put on protective clothes. Now what are they wearing?

bem_transcription: Shitata uuli kunuma afwelwe icafiita fititi abikapo netoloshi ilyamakumbi makumbi elyo shitata uuli kuntashi afwele icakashika mukati abikapo necakatapa katapa kunse.
eng_translation: The man behind is wearing black with a blue trousor the one infront is  wearing  a red shirt  a green pants.

bem_transcription: Calicindama sana ukubomba incito yakumubili kabili calicindama sana ukufwala ifyakuicinga ilyo tulebomba umulimo pakutila tatubikile ubumi bwesu mubunsanso.
eng_translation: Its good to have a job to sustain you aswell as protective cothes when working so that you safe gaurd your life.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila uwacaice umukashana uwakwata imishishi ishitali kabili naikala pacipuna naikata nakumutwe, bushe tefyo fine?
eng_translation: There is girl with long hair on this picture holding her head is it not so?

bem_transcription: Nifyo fine, elyo uyu umukashana cilepala kwati alefisa pamenso talefwaya ukutila bamukope icikope, elyo nga twalolesha ukuboko kwakwe ala aliina kumona fye ukuboko ifyo kulemoneka ukwanenepa.
eng_translation: Thats true its seems she is clovering her face she doesn't want to captured on a picture and she looks fat just seeing her hand.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifi walanda, ala aliina! nomba nga twalolesha sana bushe kuncende kuntu ali bushe te ku cipatala?
eng_translation: Thats true she is fat. Now if you look closely its looks like she is at the hospital.

bem_transcription: Uku niwebo walungika, elo nalolekesha nimucipatala umu, elyo alemoneka alilwala, emulandu wine akwatile icapala kwati cipepala kumaboko yakwe.
eng_translation: You are right i have just seen its the hospital she seems sick nowander she is holding something like a paper.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ifi walanda, uwacaice naikatako fimo icipalile ukuti cakupeemenako, kanshi uyu uwacaice ala cilemoneka ukuti alilwala ubulwele ubumucusha.
eng_translation: Thats true. this young one is holfing something like a oygen tube this young girl looks sick.

bem_transcription: Ici cikope cilelangilila uwacaice uwaseeme kukanwa uufwele kaputula uwamakumbi makumbi elo neshati ilipi kabili kunuma kuli abantu, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: This Picture is showing a young one with his mouth open wearing a blue short and a short t-shirt behind him there are alot of people.

bem_transcription: Nimbona elo cilepala kwati balesefya iciila, emulandu wine pacikope pali nabwinga na shibwinga, nabwinga ni uyu uufwele ilaya ilyabuuta tuutu.
eng_translation: It looks like there is a wedding, you can  see a bride and the groom the bride is the one with a white dress

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, ala bali ku ciila, cipalile ukuti bali kubwinga balesefya, nga natumona imishanine yabo nabasekelela icine cine, bushe naumona icikuulwa cintu baliko?
eng_translation: Thats true, Its a wedding they are celebrating you can tell from their dances. Have you seen the venue?

bem_transcription: Nimbona icikuulwa cilemoneka icayemba bwino sana, nga twalolesha umutenge babomfya fye imbao ukupangila umutenge icilemoneka bwino sana.
eng_translation: I have seen, the venue looks nice if you look at the roofing they have just used timber to make nice roof.

bem_transcription: Tecikuulwa fye ceka icilemoneka bwino nabali pabwinga nabo nabamoneka bwino, imifwalile yabo iisuma! Ala nakuwama icine cine emulandu wine balemwentula.
eng_translation: Its not just the venue looking nice even the people on attedning the weeding are looking nice they are well dressed.  They are really enjoying.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila abacaice babili nabasekelela icine cine, kabili nabekala pacintu cimo, bushe naumona ukusekelela kwabo napo bekele?
eng_translation: On this picture they are two happy young ones and they are sitting on something. Have you notice what i have said?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona, nomba pantu bekele nipacimpeelwa pantu nabaninina pacimpelwa elyo balepeluka emulandu wine balemwentula.
eng_translation: Yes i have they sited on a swing and they are swinging thats why they are happy.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Incende ilemoneka iyayemba mumbali yacimpelwa balikamo nolunkoto ulo batapilila, kabili balibikapo notupuna apakwikala.
eng_translation: This is a nice place and around the swing they have plainted green grass and they are chairs aswell.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ala incende naimwama icine cine! Ala ukukwatako utushita utwamusango uyu ukuya mukwangala nabanensu kwaliwama icine cine.
eng_translation: That's true this is a nice place. Having such times to have fun with friends it's important

bem_transcription: Icikope ciletulangisha fye abalumendo batatu elo nabakashana nabakwatako nafimo kuminwe yabo, bushe finshi balecita aba bantu bakwe?
eng_translation: On this picture there are three  young men and girls and they have something on their hands. Whats are they doing?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu baleimba inyimbo, emulandu wine bakwatile aya amabuuku kuminwe yabo elyo umu mulemoneka nimu calici.
eng_translation: These people are singing thts why hey are holding music sheets and it looks like they are in the church.

bem_transcription: Ee, cishinka nimucalici, baleimba, elyo umbi nakwatapo cimo ico balelishapo pakuti baleimba, bushe fyakufwala fyamusango nshi bafwele?
eng_translation: Yes they are in a church singing and one is holding a musical intrument he is playing  so thats they sing along, what are they wearing?

eng_translation: That's true, it has a stick stuck to it's mouth and it's a huge, have you seen the place it is at?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, iyi incende nikumpanga kabili ukwabe fimuti ifingi kabili ifitali, kumona fye nefyo umushili ulemoneka, takwaba nabapyangako.
eng_translation: Yes I have, it is in the bush full of trees and looks very dark, it's clear from the ground that no one sweeps this place.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, ala kusuma uku kuncende kabili ifimuti fyakaena filemoneka fye bwino kabili namabula yakaena ayaponene panshi yalemoneka ayasuma icine cine.
eng_translation: That's true, this place is beautiful it is, the trees, the leaves look so good even the ones that have fallen on the ground.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila bemba umukalamba kabili uwapabuuka icine cine, kabili lulamba lwabemba kwabe fimuti, bushe nibani abo bali pali bemba?
eng_translation: This picture shows a sea and trees on it's shore, who are those on it's shore?

bem_transcription: Pali bemba pali abantu babili abakwete isumbu lye sabi balefwaya ukupoosa ili isumbu pali bemba wine.
eng_translation: Among the people are two with a fishing net that are trying to toss it into the sea .

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, ala ili isumbu likalamba icine cine kabili balefwaya ukwikata isabi ilingi sana, nomba cinshi cacibafwa ukuya pamumana?
eng_translation: Yes, that's true, and that is a huge fishing net, they want to catch lots of fish, but what helped them get on the sea?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu nabakwata ubwato ubunoono, elyo kunuma kwa uyu uwiminine kuli umuntu uwikele uuleowa ubwato.
eng_translation: They have a tiny boat with a man behind that's paddling

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, ukwabula ubu ubwato ngatabacifika pali bemba mukalamba nge fi, kabili aba bantu balondo besabi icine cine.
eng_translation: Yes, you are right, they would not be on the sea without the boat, these people are fishermen.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila umulumendo nafwala icisote kumutwe elyo nabikako nacimo mumukoshi, nomba finshi alecita uyu umuntu?
eng_translation: This picture shows a young man wearing a hat, and something around his neck, what is this person doing?

bem_transcription: Uyu muntu ali kumbali yamumana, kumbali yamumana balikuulako ukwakwiminina, apalemoneka kwati cilibwe icikalamba epo eminine.
eng_translation: He is at the sea shore, standing on some elevated bank that looks like a huge rock.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, naiminina apo bakuula icintu icikalamba sana kabili aleloba isabi ukubomfya akakulobelako, nomba naumona umumana untu alelobamo?
eng_translation: That's right, he is standing on something huge that has been built while he fishes using his fishhook, have you seen the river he is fishing from?

bem_transcription: Oh! elo namona! Nshacimona ukutila aleloba nokuloba, elo uyu umumana ulemoneka ukalamba sana! kumona fye ifyo ulemoneka elyo walishike icine cine elyo tapali namabimbi.
eng_translation: This is when I have, he is even fishing and the river looks big, it's clear from the way it looks and it is deep with no waves on it.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangisha abantu abengi sana kuncende kumo, kabili kusuma icine cine, kabili kulaya abantu, nomba bushe naumona uyu uuli pantashi?
eng_translation: This picture shows lots of people in one place, a beautiful place frequently visited , have you seen this person in front?

bem_transcription: Nimumona, uyu alemoneka mukashana elyo nafwala kasiketi kamasenkebele, abikapo nakasote elyo muminwe yakwe nakwata ifyo ale-angasha.
eng_translation: Yes I have, it is a lady in a skirt with tiny ropes at the bottom, a hat and she is holding a toy in her hands.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, nafwala icisote kabili atontele amenso ku-ulemukopa kabili aleangashoko fimo pakuti alesekesha abantu kufyo alecita.
eng_translation: Yes that's true, she's wearing a hat and focused on the person capturing her, she is playing with the toy in her hand so as to make people laugh.

bem_transcription: Nomba nga walolekesha kunuma kwakwe kuli shitata uulemoneka nolufumo ulukuulu, nafwala nakepi amaboko, kabili akamakumbi makumbi, nga fimbi finshi ulemona?
eng_translation: When you pay attention you will notice a man with a big belly behind her in a short sleeved blue shirt, what else can you see?

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, ala uyu shitata aliina icine cine, kabili umbi napapa umwana elo umbi naikata umwana kumaboko, elyo bambi baleshitako fimo pali ako kantu.
eng_translation: Indeed this man is very fat. Then there's someone with a baby on their back, while another is holding a child's hand while another is buying something from a stand.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Uyu nakwata mukolwe muminwe yakwe, uyu mukolwe alemoneka uwayemba kabili uwaina elyo alemoneka uwafiitulukila.
eng_translation: He has a really good looking brown fat hen in his hands.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala naikata mukolwe umukalamba, kaili natonta sana amenso yakwe kuli uyu wine mukolwe, bushe finshi fili kunuma yakwe?
eng_translation: Yes he is a fat hen and he is focused on the hen, what's that behind him?

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe kulemoneka icikuulwa icapala kwati litenti bapoopa fye, elyo kuli nefimuti ifitali sana kabili ifyayemba nangula cakuti tafyafunda bwino.
eng_translation: There's a tent set outside with tall trees that are not so broad.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, ala palemoneka bwino panshi, ulunkoto lwalimena bwino kabili lwalifunda, lulemoneka fye katapa-katapa, ala baliwamya iyi incende.
eng_translation: That's true and the ground looks nice, with broad grass that's very green, this is a very beautiful place.

bem_transcription: Pali ici icikope pali abantu abengi sana abeshile mukutamba ici icangalo, kabili nabaposesheko sana amano, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: On this picture are lots of people that have come to watch and are paying attention, have you seen them?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbamona, nomba cilepala kwati umo aciipununa mumunakwe nokupona, nokuyuma akanwa mumushili alemyanga iloba.
eng_translation: Yes, I have seen, one bumped into the other and has fallen to the ground with soil in his mouth.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ici icangalo cilemoneka ukuti bacibomfya ukuteya kabola akanoono, nga cakuti wasukusa waikata, kubutuka mucibansa, nomba naumona uyu umuntu uuposesheko sana amano kuli aba bantu babili?
eng_translation: That's amazing, this game is played using a small ball, you throw it, then you run around in the pitch, have you you noticed the man looking at the other two?

bem_transcription: Uyu umuntu nikawikishanya waici icangalo, eulolekesha pafyo aba bantu baleteya icangalo cabo kabili eulesha umo nga alufyanya ukuteyako ici icangalo.
eng_translation: He is the referee , he is the one that's ensures that if one makes a mistake they no longer play.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Pali ici icikope ciletulangilila uwacilumendo kabili no wacikashana, kabili kunuma kuli abantu, bushe finshi acitile uyu umulumendo kumukashana?
eng_translation: This picture shows a man and a lady with people behind them. What has the man done to the lady?

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo naimyo mukashana, cilemoneka kwati acimuposela mumenshi, elyo aisa amwimya, nomba alesekelela nakalimo aleseka uyu wine umukashana.
eng_translation: He has lifted the lady, it seems he threw her into water, and took her out of it. And he seems happy, it seems he is laughing at her.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana baleangalila pa menshi kabili amenshi nayema busaka busaka, bushe tauletontonkaya ukuti uyu mulume nomukashi?
eng_translation: Yes they are playing with water, are they a married couple.

bem_transcription: Efyo balemoneka, balemoneka mulume no mukashi, nangula tabalaupana lelo kwena baleishishanya fye.
eng_translation: It seems they are husband and wife, or could be people that are yet to get married to each other that are courting.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala ifyo bamwimishe, namwimya busaka busungu kabili alesekelela icakutila balemwentulila pamo!
eng_translation: You are definitely right, it's clear from the way he has lifted her so perfectly.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Aba bantu babili baleimba, emulandu wine uyu uushibete nakwata necilimba ca nsale muminwe yakwe, nakalimo ifilengele ukutila ashibata nico aleumfwa bwino.
eng_translation: Two people are singing, that's why the one with stringed instrument had his eyes shut , it's possible he is enjoying.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ala munankwe nasekelela ukumona ifyo ashibete umunakwe kabili cipalile ukuti nateka umutima aleumfwa fintu ulwimbo fintu lulelila. Bushe finshi fili kunuma  yabo?
eng_translation: Even he's friend is very happy to see the other's eyes shut implying how drowned in the song he is, what's behind him?

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo kulemoneka kulefuka icushi elyo nakwaka amaliti ayo alemwenesha icisebele bwino elyo kuli nefisoselo fimbi ifyo balebomfya.
eng_translation: There is special effect haze behind them making the stage look better with other microphones being used.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana uyu umbi ufwele ishiti ilya fita ilya maboko ayepi apalamine ne cakwimbilako kabili amaboko yakwe yatontele pa cintu alelisha icakulishako inyimbo.
eng_translation: That's true because the man is short black sleeved shirt is next to a microphone while he's hands are on the sound instrument he is playing.

bem_transcription: Incende bali-iyenfya icine cine kabili kusuma icine cine elyo abantu nabesa kuli iyine incende. Bushe naumona ifili kuli iyi incende?
eng_translation: This place is beautiful and well built, with people that have come to this place. Have you seen what's in this place?

bem_transcription: Ala iyi incende isuma icine cine bali ikula bwino kabili bai iiyenfya kumona fye ifyo icishiba ca menshi cilemoneka, cilemoneka icabusaka kabili amenshi yalaposa na mu mulu
eng_translation: This place is beautiful and well built, very beautified, it's clear from the springs of water flowing into the clean pool.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala cilemoneka icisuma sana kabili amenshi yafuma panshi olo yaleiposa. Bushe ifnshi uyu umulumendo uwaina alecita mu menshi?
eng_translation: It looks very nice with springs of water flowing. What is this fat man doing with the water?

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo uwaina uufwele ishaiti ilya makumbi makumbi kabili ne toloshi ilyafita alewamya mumenshi elyo alemoneka alitemwa uyu umulimo.
eng_translation: The fat man is wearing a blue shirt and black trousers. He is cleaning the pool and seems to love he's job.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ala e mulimo abomba kabili naposeshako sana amano pakuwamya aya amenshi ala yalemoneka ayalengama kabili ayasuma.
eng_translation: Yes, this is he's job, and he is paying attention to cleaning the pool, it looks very clean.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila uwacaice umulumnedo nafwala kaputula iya makumbi makumbi  shati ilya buta ilya maboko ayepi elyo nakasote akafita, bushe finshi alecita?
eng_translation: This picture shows a little boy in blue pants and a white short sleeved shirt and a black hat, what is he doing?

bem_transcription: Uyu muntu aleteya icangalo beta kutila tenis mu cingeleshi nakwata necakuteyelako mu minwe yakwe kabili ne fyakufwala afwele naipangasha kuli ici icangalo.
eng_translation: He is playing tennis with a racket in his hands and he is well dressed for the game.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda  ici icangalo bacibomfya ukuteya ka bola akanono elyo ne cakubomfya ukuteya kabola akanono kabili naposeshako sana amno elyo aleteya ici icangalo. Bushe tauletontonkanya ukuti aleteya nomunankwe?
eng_translation: Yes, indeed,  this game is played is played with a small tennis ball, don't you think he is playing against his friend?

bem_transcription: Nifyo fine pantu ici icangalo tekutila uteye weka nomba incende aliko ilemoneka iyabusaka sana. Bushe naumona ifyo ilemoneka?
eng_translation: That's right, it's because you can't play this game alone, this place is very tidy. Have you seen how it looks like?

bem_transcription: Cine aleteya nomunakwe pantu cipalile ukuti cangalo icakucinfyanya sana emulandu wine baleteyela bonse kabili uyu muntu alishibisha ukuteya ici cangalo.
eng_translation: Yes, he is playing with his friend and it seems to be a stiff competition that's why they are playing  and he seems to know this game very well.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Uyu muntu ali pa mulimo uwakakala sana kumona fye fintu alemoneka ukulamba ifyakufwala filemoneka ifya fiko kulemoneka kwati mafuta yacilaitikilako.
eng_translation: He is doing a very hard job it's clear from how dirty he's clothes are, they look stained with oil.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimbona ici ni cimazembe nicilya babonfya ukwimbilako umushili nokulaimishako fimo elyo apa cilemoneka kwati cilelongapo fimo muli cimotoka ici icakashika.
eng_translation: I have seen, it is an excavator used to dig out stuff from the ground and it seems to be packing some things into the red car.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana fintu walanda ici ci mashini cikalmba sana kabili uku kuli ne cikulwa icikalamba sana icaonaika cipalile  kuti kampani.
eng_translation: Yes, indeed it is a huge machine and the building that fell should have been a great company.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila kuncende kumo uko bapangila ne tenti ilikalamba ilya buta kabili ilyakosa ilyo ba bomfya ne fishimbi. Bushe uletintonkanya ukuti finshi abantu balecita?
eng_translation: This picture shows a place where a huge white tent has been mounted with metal bars. What do you think the people here are doing?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu balemoneka bali ku mutebeto muntu bali ni mwitenti fye ilyo bakomene ilya buta elyo balepokelela ifyakulya.
eng_translation: It seems these people are at a function and they are receiving food from inside the white tent.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana cintu walanda beshile mukulya ifyakulya ifyo bepike kabili ifilemoneka bwino na bakepika nabo nokobali kabili nafwala utusote ututali utwabuta. Bushe naumona umwangashi
eng_translation: Yes you are right, they are here to have the food that looks delicious and well prepared, and they are wearing white hats. Have you seen the beer?

bem_transcription: Nimbona pe tebulo pali amabotolo ya myangashi ayengi sana elyo amabotolo yakaena yalemoneka yakatapa katapa kuli na namayo uulepoka
eng_translation: Yes, I have, they are so many green beer bottles on the table and the lady is the one getting them.

bem_transcription: Ee pali umwangashi uwingi sana kabili uwapusana pusana cipalile ukuti nabasansamuka sana ukunwa umwangashi elyo nokulya ifaykulya ifyanunkila kuti wayako mwe!
eng_translation: Yes, there's lots of different beers and they seem so happy to be taking it and have delicious food, I wish I was there.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimbona ala ici icikuulwa balicikula bwino sana ifibumba filemoneka ifya busaka imipando shilemoneka ishayemba nama liti yelemoneka bwino sana.
eng_translation: I have seen, this is a well built building even the walls, chairs and lights are altogether very nice.

bem_transcription: Cine cine ala baliciyemfya ifyo bacipenta fye awe mwandini cilemoneka bwino imipando fye sheka sheka  awe shamutengo. Bushe naumona ubukulu bwa cilola?
eng_translation: It really has been beautified, the chairs look expensive. Have you seen how huge the mirror is?

bem_transcription: Nimbona icilola cikalamba elyo cilangilashamo na abantu abengi abeminine fye ukutali muli abalumendo batatu elyo umbi umulumendo aleipitila fye.
eng_translation: I have seen the huge mirror and reflections of four men from afar with one among them walking.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ici icikope cilelangilila kuncende kumo ukuli abantu abengi sana kabili incende balikulako icikulwa icikulu sana. Bushe uletontonkaya ukuti finshi  aba bantu abengi balecita?
eng_translation: This picture shows a place full of people and a huge building. What do you think this huge number of people is doing?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu beshile mukutamba abalumendo abaciba pa cangalo cakucinfyanya icakucofa amajinga kumona fye nabakwata namajinga.
eng_translation: These people are here to watch the young men in a bike racing competition, it's clear because they have bicycles.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ici cangalo cakucinfyanya ica kwensha amajinga emulandu wine abantu abengi bakwatile amajinga kabili bambi nabafwala ne fyakucinga ku mutwe. Mulandu nshi bafwalile?
eng_translation: Yes, indeed it is a bike racing competition that's why they have bicycles and are wearing helmets. Why the helmets though?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu balafwala ifi ifimpompo ifyakucingilisha imitwe yabo pakutila nga cakutila baisanga mubusanso umutwe tekuti ucenaike sana.
eng_translation: The helmets are worn so that they are protected from getting their heads hurt in cases where they find themselves in accidents.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana kanshi ukufwala icakuicinga kumutwe calicindama sana kabili cilangilila  ukuti twalicindika sana ubumi. kabili kwaciba abantu abengi abacisa mukutamba ilyo bacilacinfyanya.
eng_translation: Yes indeed wearing an helmet is imperative and shows respect for life. These are lots of people that came to watch the game.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Apa alele ni pacimpelwa cilemoneka alepeluma nomba imipelumine tekelepo pacimpelwa alelepo fye ubunkupeme
eng_translation: She is swinging face down on the swing .

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana alepeluma ilyo alele ubunkumpeme kabili cipalile ukuti aleloleshapo fimo. bushe naumona ubwingi bwa fimpelwa kabili nefyo bafipanga?
eng_translation: Indeed she is  and if seems she is looking at something. Have you noticed the number of swings and how they are made?

bem_transcription: Ifi impelwa balifipanga bwino sana kabili ifyakosa babomfya inshimbi ifyaikata fyene elyo pancende balictilapo no mucanga.
eng_translation: These swings are strong and well made with metal and mounted on sand.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana balifipanga ne fishimbi kabili balifikatanya ku fishimbi kabili icaikata ifishimbi bacipangila ne myando isha fishimbi kabili ishapikana
eng_translation: Yes, they have been made with lots of metal that have folds into other metal such that they are very strong.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila utunama tubili kamo nakema mu mulu elo kambi nakanyata pacilibwe. Bushe uletontonkanya ukuti tunama nshi utu?
eng_translation: This picture shows two animals, one is in the air while the other is stepping on rock, which animals do you think these are?

bem_transcription: Utu ni tukolwe. Elyo palemoneka pali kamwana naka nyina pantu aka katolweke mu mulu kalemoneka akanono sana ukucila aka kali paliclibwe.
eng_translation: These are monkeys and it seems the one on the rock is the mother while the other smaller one in the air is the child.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda utu utunama ni tukolwe kabili tuleangala kumonafye ne ifyo tucensele ku kanwa. Nomba ulemona kutila nikwisa uku tuli.
eng_translation: Indeed they are monkeys, it's clear from the way they are smiling. Where do you think they are?

bem_transcription: Uku ni ku mpanga pantu nga twalolesha kunuma ya tuko tulemonako ifimuti ifingi kabili ifya citikana nangula cakuti icikope tacilemonekesha bwino sana.
eng_translation: They are in the bush, it is clear from the trees behind that are close to each other, even though this picture is a little unclear.

bem_transcription: Walungika pantu ba kolwe basangwa mu mpili kabili mu mpanga kabili batemwa sana ukutanauka ku fimuti ala natwangala pamo.
eng_translation: That's true because monkeys are found in hills and in trees, they love jumping from one tree to the other as a group.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope ciletulangilila uwacilumendo umukalamba naikala panshi kabili napeta nama kunda kabili nakwatako nafimo panshi ni finshi ifi?
eng_translation: This picture shows an elderly man sited on the floor with his legs folded and has something, what does he have?

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata asendele fye imbale sha mu ng'anda namapoto abika panshi asenda nama sipuni notuminko atampa ukulisha ingoma.
eng_translation: He has plates, pots, spoons and cooking sticks that he is using to play

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING
