bem_transcription: Ee nimbamona kabili nabekata insalu iya makumbi makumbi kabili insalu bekete naipalana sana ne fyakufwala fintu bafwele.
eng_translation: Yes I have, they have green clothes similar to the clothes they are wearing.

bem_transcription: Elyo abengi apo ndemona ni bashitata nomba kuli bashitata abeminine babili nabafwala fimo fine nama toloshi aya fita elyo nama shati ayakashika.
eng_translation: I can see some men, among them are some standing wearing the same black trousers with red shirts.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana cipalile ukuti icila icilecitika atemwa balesefya ubuntungwa emulandu wine bafwalile umusango uyu.
eng_translation: Yes, that's true, it seems this people are celebrating their independence and that's why they are dressed like this.

bem_transcription: Bantu abali uku balemoneka nabatemwa ukuba ku ncende iyi kabili nabasangalala pakusefyako ico balesefya emulandu wine bonse balemonekela abasekelelela
eng_translation: These people seem very happy and excited to be here that's why they are all celebrating.

bem_transcription: Imbwa iisuma sana iya kwata amasako ayasuma kabili ayengi ili mucibansa ileangala. nomba bushe naumona ifyo icitile?
eng_translation: A very cute dog with lots of fur is playing in the field, have you noticed what it's done?

bem_transcription: Nimbona naitonta amenso uko ilebutukila kabili nayasama akanwa kabili iletoloka imilando isho babikile isho bapenta.
eng_translation: I have seen it is focused on where it's running with it's mouth open as it jumps the painted bars that have been put up.

bem_transcription: Iyi imbwa yalikwata amasako ayasuma kabili ayabeka mu mukoshi yalikwata amasako aya buta tutu ku kanwa nakwena kwaliba utu masako utwabuta nga twalolesha ku molu nakwena kuli utu masako utwabuta.
eng_translation: This dog has very shiny fur, it's neck, it's mouth and it's feet all have white fur.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala iyi imbwa iyi baliisambilisha bwino kabili ishile mukwangala atemwa ukucinfyanya icangalo icakutoloka imilando kabili balisambilisha ifya kutoloka.
eng_translation: This dog is well taught and here to play or compete in this game of jumping over the bars

bem_transcription: Elo Lubali lumbi ukulepwila icibansa ici kulemoneka na bantu cilemoneka iyi te mbwa fye yeka iyiliko aba bantu beshile mu kutamba ici icangalo.
eng_translation: On the edge of the field are some people, this dog is not here alone, they are people here to watch the game.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ili pa menshi ilesamba elyo lwa mupepi kuli fye ne fyoni ifileisambila fye. Bushe ulemona  kwati fyoni inshi  ifi?
eng_translation: A dog is swimming on water with some birds swimming at a distance, which birds do you think these are?

bem_transcription: Ifi ifyoni fibata ifyangalila pa mesnhi kabili cilepala kwati iyi mbwa ilebendelela ifi fine ifibata pakuti ingasendapo cimo.
eng_translation: These are swans and the dog is seeking to catch one.

bem_transcription: Iyi imbwa taiposeleko na mano ku fibata nomba nga twalolesha amenshi yalemoneka ayalengama sana kabili icimumana cilemoneka icapabuka.
eng_translation: No, the dog is not even paying attention to the swans and the water looks so good, it is a huge river.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala bemba uyu alipabuka kabili na menshi yalemoneka fye ayabusaka kabili aya wama ayalengama kuti wanwa amenshi aya!
eng_translation: This is a huge river with water splashing all over, it looks so good and tempting to drink.

bem_transcription: Ala iyi imbwa yalishiba ukusamba elyo naikwatapo na kamo aka kashika mumusana nailalika namatwi pakusamba awe yalishiba.
eng_translation: This dog is a skilled swimmer with something red tied to it's waist and has it's ears down as it's swims.

bem_transcription: Abakashana babili bale-enda mu musebo, nomba bushe nga cakutila twabalolekesha aba bene abakashana ifyo balemoneka bushe fyakufwala ninshi bafwele?
eng_translation: Two ladies are walking on the road, when you pay attention to them how are they dressed?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka elyo iyi incende tailemoneka iya busaka sana, incende ilemoneka iya fiko tabapyanga bwino nangula yakale fye.
eng_translation: That's true, this is a very dirty place, it could be it is not well kept or it's an old place.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo pakati ka musebo balibikapo ne cimu pipe icikulu nakalimo cimu pipe ca menshi nga cakuti kwali umulilo kwisasenda fye amenshi apapene.
eng_translation: There's a huge pipe on the middle of the road, it should be a water pipe, whenever there's a fire they simply use it.

bem_transcription: Abantu bali mucikulwa elyo kuli shitata uwikele panshi naikatapo na fimo mu minwe. Bushe naumumona?
eng_translation: Some people are inside a building, there's a man sited holding something, have you seen him?

bem_transcription: Ee namumona shitata nakwata icilimba ca nsale kabili mu pepi pali necilimba icikalamba ico babomfya ukulacijinshako iciunda ca cilimba kabili napalamina ne ca kwi mbilamo.
eng_translation: Yes, I have, he has a stringed instrument in his hands and sited next to an amplifier and close to a microphone.

bem_transcription: Ici icikulwa cilemoneka kwati cikulwa ca bwalwa ngu icikulwa cakulilamo lelo balafwayako uwakubasansamusha lintu balelya.
eng_translation: This looks like a bar or restaurant and he is meant to entertain the people as they eat.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo pe tebulo paliko ama kapu napekala na bantu palemoneka ne mbale ishabuta abantu abalemoneka fye aba fita bonse balelya ifi ifya kulya
eng_translation: The table is filled with cups and white plates and all the people sited on it look dark as they eat.

bem_transcription: Bashitata abengi bali pacisebele ala nabafwala bwino sana ifyakufwala filemoneka ifya yemba kabili ifya busaka  nabakwata na fimo mu minwe yabo.
eng_translation: A number of men are on stage, they are impressively dressed, they look clean and are holding something in their hands.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana uku bali niku calici kabili nabafwala ifya kufwala fimo fine elyo mukati babikamo no twabuta elyo kabili baleimba ne nyimbo nabafwala ne nsapato shimo shine.
eng_translation: They are inside a church dressed in the same clothes with white inside, they are singing and are wearing the same shoes.

bem_transcription: Niwe walingika pantu napantanshi yabo pali ifisoselo nakaili aya amabuku bakwete ku minwe emuli inyimbo shintu baleimba elyo ifisoselo ifyo balebomfya pa kwimba
eng_translation: You are right, they are microphones in front of them that they are using to sing and are holding song books in their hands from which they are singing.

bem_transcription: Cishinka aba bantu balemoneka ukuti kwaciba uwacisa umukalamba wa calilci atewmwa nabapokelelako abeni elyo balimba inyimbo kabili kuli nabalebakopa.
eng_translation: It seems a important church member came or they have guests hence the singing and there's someone capturing them.

bem_transcription: Elyo icisebele balicipanga bwino sana cintu cayemba kabili ica busaka panshi balibikapo ne nsalu iya kashika cee
eng_translation: The stage is well built and clean with red linen on it's surface.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo aleangasha inicinga lelo natoloka nayo mu muulu apatali sana.
eng_translation: A young man is playing with his bicycle and is high up in the air with it.

bem_transcription: Nimbona ala efyo emishefye incinga nacipapusha abantu kabili nafuma apakwikala elyo icanuma cili mu pepi ne wilo kabili nafwala necakucinga ku mutwe pakuti nga apona taicenene.
eng_translation: I have seen how amazed people are at him, he is not on the bike sit and is wearing an helmet on his head to avoid getting hurt.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo alemoneka alishibisha sana ukucofa incinga emulandu wine aleangalila nayo umusango uyu pantu nafuma apakwika elyo acicitile kwati alefwaya ukupona cibe acili mu muulu.
eng_translation: He is very skilled at bike riding that's why he is playing like this, he is not on his sit but diy in the air, it's as though he wants to fall, impressive!

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende baliipanga bwino sana ilifye pakati ka fikulwa ifilesaninka ama liti elyo bushiku ubu umuulu ulemoneka fye uwafita.
eng_translation: This place is well made and built in between buildings full of lights on.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo nangula bashi tata bali kuncende balecitapo fimo elyo nabafwala ifya kufwala ifya pusana pusana. Nomba kuti watila finshi balecita?
eng_translation: Some men dressed differently are in one place and doing something, what can you say they are doing?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu bashilika kumona fye imifwalile yabo kabili bashilka ba myaka ne myaka te bashilka aba nomba abafwala ifyakufwala ifibalangilila ati bashilika kabili nabakwata imfuti fyabo.
eng_translation: These are soldiers that have served for so many years, it's clear from their outfits and their guns.

bem_transcription: Cishinka balelisha infuti nakalimo niku malilo uku bele nangu balebasabilisha fye ifya kulisha ishi shine infuti, pantu nimbona no mulumendo umbi uleasha umulilo.
eng_translation: They are firing guns, they are either at a funeral or they are learning to fire, I have also seen a young man making a fire.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo eko balelishisha uku ni ku mpanga takulemonekako na mayanda ayengi kulemoneka fye ing'anda imo  lelo ififiulilkeo fimuti ifingi kabili ifitali elyo fifkulu.
eng_translation: They are playing in a bush full of tall trees with no houses in sight.

bem_transcription: Bashitata aba cikalamba na bana mayo bonse bali mucibansa cakuteyelapo umupila baleteya umpila  waku molu.
eng_translation: Some elderly men and women are in a football pitch.

bem_transcription: Nimbona uyu shitata ufwele itoloshi ilya fita abikapo nama galashi alepepeka uyu umunyamata cipalile ukuti uyu umunyamata ufwele kaputula yama cunga macunga eukwete umupila.
eng_translation: I have seen this man in a black short with glasses chasing after the young man in an orange short the one with the ball.

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata uli mucipanda ca bola alemoneka kwati ekekata nomba nafwala amagalashi yafita abikapo na kasote nomba nshatalamonapo kekata ufwala umusango uyu alaikata shani?
eng_translation: This man is the goal keeper and in black glasses with a hat, I have never seen such a goal keeper how is he going to hold the ball this way?

bem_transcription: Nshatala monapo goli ufwala amagalashi mucipanda elyo kabili ufwala itoloshi ne shati ili amaboko. Ala nshatala monapo nacimpapusha icine cine.
eng_translation: I have seen a goal keeper dressed like this, glasses, shorts and a long sleeved shirt, I am very shocked.

bem_transcription: Elyo ukwabela icibansa ici kusuma balikusunga bwino kwashingulukwa ne fimuti ifikalamba kabili ifyalelema bwino sana.
eng_translation: The location of this sports field is very nice and well maintained surrounded by lots of trees.

bem_transcription: Babaice baili abalumendo baleyangala elyo palemoneka kwati kuli ifyo baletina nangula kuli ifyo baletamba .Bushe ulemona kwati finshi fimbi ifyo balecita aba?
eng_translation: Two young boys are playing, it's like they are afraid of something or watching something, what else do you think they are doing?

bem_transcription: Aba abacice babili nabafumina panse kabili uwacaice ufwele kaputula ilemoneka iyabutulukila ukwabula ne shati cipalile ukuti kufimo fimo ifyo aletamba ifilengele ukuti aposesheko sana amano.
eng_translation: They are both very outside, the one in grey shorts but shirtless seems to be watching something that has caught his attention.

bem_transcription: Iyi ncende ilemoneka bwino sana elyo nama laiti nayaka bwino kunuma yabo kuli ifyani muntu uwi-ikalile pakamupando akanono kabili akepi sana.
eng_translation: This place looks nice with lights on and glass glass around the small sit built for people to rest.

bem_transcription: Uyu umunankwe uwacaice ufwele kaputula ya makumbi makumbi abikapo ne shati lya mutuntula ena alelengelela fye mukati cipalile ukuti kuli fimo ifyalenga ukti bafumine panse baletamba.
eng_translation: The other friend in blue shorts and a yellow is just peeping, it seems there's a reason they stepped out.

bem_transcription: Elyo utu utubana tonse tubuli utwaume tulemoneka kwati ni tumpundu pantu tulemoneka fye umushiku umowine elyo kabili natufwala nabakaputula twalyonda sana.
eng_translation: These are twins because they look the same age, are both in shorts and both very slim.

bem_transcription: Bantu baleteya icangalo mucibansa cafyangalo elyo ici icangalo baleteya ni cilya icakuma akamupila. Bushe, bushe naumona ifyo icibansa cilemoneka?
eng_translation: Some people are in a sports field playing a game where they are playing tennis have you seen how the sports field looks like?

bem_transcription: Nimbona ici icabansa balicipanga bwino kabili balibyala ulunkoto
eng_translation: I have seen it, it's well built with grass in it.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ifyo uyu uuli pantashi afundumene lintu alefwaya ukuuma umupila ukubomfya icintu cintu akwete kuminwe yakwe?
eng_translation: Have you noticed how the one in front is trying to hit the ball using the racket?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona uyu muntu nakwatako icilemoneka ukuti ni mbao muminwe yakwe, kaili aka kabola akaleisa akabuuta alefwaya ukukooma noyu munankwe uuli kunuma alelolela ukuti nga apusa engekata ka bola.
eng_translation: Yes he has a racket in his hands trying to hit the ball that will be thrown to him and there's another person behind him that will catch it Incase he misses.

bem_transcription: Cishinka, uyu uuli kunuma alefwaya ukwikata akamupila, elyo kuli na bantu abengi abeshile mukutamba, abengi pali aba bafwele ifyafiita.
eng_translation: Yes there's someone behind trying to hold the ball and they are lots of people dressed in black that have come to watch the game.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali mucibansa, napamo cakucimfyanishishamo, elyo nanina pa lubao ulo aleputula ukubomfya akasembe.
eng_translation: A young man is inside what seems like a sports field and sitting on top of wood that he is cutting with an axe.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, nakwata isembe ilikalamba kabili ilyafina , nafwala nefyakufwala ekutila itoloshi ilyabuuta, abikapo insapato iyabuuta, abikapo nakashati akabula amaboko akamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: I have noticed the axe looks very heavy, he is wearing a white trousers, white shoes and a sleeveless blue shirt.

bem_transcription: Muli ici icibansa, nakwisa nabantu abengi abeshile mukutamba uko aba bantu balecimfyanya ukuputule mbao, nabaposako na mano sana.
eng_translation: They are lots of people here to watch the cutting competition and are paying attention.

bem_transcription: Cipalile ukuti ali kucangalo uko baangala ica kucimfyanya ukuputula imilando kabili aleputula umulando busaka busaka kabili balefwaya ukumona uwingapwisha ukuputula umulando bwangu.
eng_translation: Yes this is a competition and he is taking part from the way he is cutting the wood well, the goal is to see who cuts faster.

bem_transcription: Elyo imiputwile ya mbao, teciputule putule fye iyo, kuli kwati kuli ifyo balekonka lintu baleputula, pantu nga twamona imbao aleya alefonkola bwino bwino.
eng_translation: This wood cutting competition has rules, it's clear from the way he is cutting the wood.

bem_transcription: Shitata naiminina alecitapo fimo elyo nafwala ishati ilyakatapakatapa, bushe ulemona kwati finshi uyu shitata alecita?
eng_translation: A man is standing while doing something, he is wearing a green shirt

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata afwele akasote akabutulukila elo abikapo necampepo icakatapa katapa, mumukoshi nafwalamo ico apikila icilemoneka icakashika kaili naikata nomukate kuminwe kumwakwe.
eng_translation: This man is wearing a brown hat and a green jersey, a red scarf and is holding bread in his hand.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, uyu shitata alapanga imikate elo alashitisha, ishi shine imikate naputala tupimfya tupimfya.
eng_translation: You are right he makes bread and then sell them in small pieces.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING.

bem_transcription: Awe te chuulu mune cibumba, lelo icibumba cilitabililwa namaluba ayakatapa katapa ayalemwenesha kwati chuulu.
eng_translation: No its a anthill its just a wall it well mainted with green flowers thats why it looks like an anthill.

bem_transcription: Abana baleowa mucishiba elo lintu aleowa nafwala necakashika pacifuba cakwe, nafwala namagalashi mumenso.
eng_translation: A Child is in  the pool swiming while putting on a life jacket and glasses.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, ici icishiba cilemoneka bwino sana kabili amenshi yalemoneka ayalengama kabili ayasuma, kabili uwacaice nainuna amenso yakwe mumuulu kabili nafwala amakalashi ayamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: I have seen the pool is really clean and the water is so clear and a child eyse are looking up, he is putting blue glasses.

bem_transcription: Ici icishiba, ciipi sana, mwakusambila fye abana abanoono, kumona fye naikata na panshi lelo umubili onse tawibile mumenshi kanshi tekutila anwine.
eng_translation: The pool is not deep its for children only you can see even his all body is not in the water like tgis you can't drown.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PALYING

bem_transcription: Ala aya amenshi yasuma icine cine, yalilengama kabili baliyasunga ubusaka, abana tekutila balwale nga cakutila balesamba muli ici icishiba pantu amenshi tayakowela.
eng_translation: The swimming pool is clean and the water is clear children  can't get sick when they are swimming in such clean swimming pools.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo no mukashana nabeminina pamusebo kabili nabakumbatana, cimbi nacho ico balecita, baletomonana.
eng_translation: A boy and a girl are hugging on the road side and they are kissing.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, cipalile aba bantu baleshishanya, kaili ilyo baleitomona nabatekanya, kaili umukashana napisha amaboko mumusana yamulumendo kaili umulumendo napisha amaboko pamoolu yamukashana.
eng_translation: I have seen, its seems they are dating as they kiss each other a girl is holding a boy on his waist and a boy is holding her sholders.

bem_transcription: Cishinka baleshishanya pantu nga tabeshishanya tekutila baleitomona, elo apa bali nipanse fye yacikuulwa nabantu bambi balepita tabaleumfwako insoni.
eng_translation: Its true they are dating if they are not dating they can not be kissing and they are outside in the public and they are not shy.

bem_transcription: Kaili apo baleitomona nipacikuulwa fye icikalamba icisuma kaili cilepala ukuti lishitolo ilikalamba sana, kaili ilyo baleitomona umukashana nasansama ilyo aletomona uo eshishanya nankwe.
eng_translation: They are standing outside the building store a girls is standing on her toes as they are kissing.

bem_transcription: Elo iyi incende isuma sana yaliyemba, panse yacikuulwa balibikapo namaluba ayalemoneka bwino sana.
eng_translation: This is a nice place outside the buildig they have even put nice flowers.

bem_transcription: Abantu abapusana pusana baleyendela mumusebo uwabela mupepi necikuulwa, elo balepusana fye cila muntu uko aleya.
eng_translation: People are walking on the road near the building and they are walking pass each other.

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbamona bele-enda, bambi balefuma muli ici cikuulwa elo bambi baleya muli ici cikuulwa, kabili ici icikuulwa catunti kabili balipanga bwino sana, kabili cikalamba, kabili icitali.
eng_translation: Yes i have seen some are coming out from the store others are going in, and this building as floors and it is well built.

bem_transcription: Elyo panse yacikuulwa palemoneka apabusaka kabili apayemba, utumuti balituntantamika bwino sana elo cilemoneka kwati tumuti twamacungwa namaluba yalemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: The sourrounding of the buiding is nice they are nice alined trees that looks like oranges trees and there are flowers.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING.

bem_transcription: Elo pacikope apa nga twalolekesha palemoneka fye abanakashi beka beka, nshimwenepo umwaume uuli onse, elyo abanakashi bambi bafwele amatoloshi, bambi bafwele bashiketi elyo bambi bafwele amandeleshi, nomba kuli abacikalamba abeleyendela fye kuntashi.
eng_translation: On this picture i can only see women, other women are putting on trousers others are wearing skirts others are wearing dresses and there is and old lady walking in front.

bem_transcription: Umwana umwanakashi kabili umwaice alepeluma pacimpelwa, elo ici icimpelwa cakwata apakwikala pabili nangu apakupeluka pabili lelo ena ekele pali cimo.
eng_translation: A girl is swinging on a swing, that has two places to sit as you swing.

bem_transcription: Nimbona napeta amoolu yakwe kabili nakontamina panshi, kaili nalambalala apali icimpelwa kaili imishishi shakwe nashisalangana.
eng_translation: I have noticed he has folded his legs and facing down, and laying on a swing with the hair scattered

bem_transcription: Pakati ka cimpelwa, balibikapo umucanga uwingi, uyu wakwafwa aba abana nga cakutila balepeluka, pakutila tabaicenene.
eng_translation: In the middle of the swing there is a lot of sand to protect the children in case they fall as they are swinging.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili nafwala ne shati ilyakashika, kabili cilecita ati camutwala uku kabili cabwelela uku, kabili kuli ici cine icimpeelwa balimikako icishimbi icamakumbi makumbi kabili icikalamba nga nshi.
eng_translation: she is wearing a red shirt as she swings she keeps going back and forth. The swing has blue steel stands.

bem_transcription: Elo apalepwila umucanga paletampa ulunkoto ulwafuunda bwino sana kabili ulutali, lulemwenesha iyi incende iyabusaka kabili iyayemba.
eng_translation: Where the sand ends there is green grass which is adding beauty to this place.

bem_transcription: Banamayo babili baleshana kabili nabafwenkula, elo balemoneka abansansa lintu baleshana panshi yabo nababikapo necibokoshi umo abantu balepose ndalama lintu balepita.
eng_translation: Two women are dancing and they are happy, on the floor is a box where people are putting the money as they pass.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, ala balecinda bwino sana elo bonse nabafwala amalaya ayapusana, lelo kumuulu bafwele ifyafiita elo abalebaliishisha ifilimba fyansale beminine akatalamukila.
eng_translation: I have seen they are dancing and they are wearing diffrent dresses but they are putting balck on top and the ones playing gitters are at a distance.

bem_transcription: Pambali yabo kuli nashitata uufwele icakashika icampepo, mukati abikamo neshati ilyabuuta nafwala nakasote akakashika elyo ne toloshi ilyafiita.
eng_translation: On the other side there is a man putting a red jacket,black trouser with a white shirt inside and a cape.

bem_transcription: Elo uko balecindila nikuncende ukusuma sana kabili kwaba ifikuulwa ifikulu kaili ifyantunti ishikalamba kabili paba ifimuti pakati.
eng_translation: They are dancing on a very nice place with tall buildings and trees in the middle.

bem_transcription: Ifikuulwa ninfimona fingi icine cine elo fyaliyemba, pakati kafiko balibyalapo nefimuti elo ifimuti nafyena tefilya ifikalamba sana, finoono fye.
eng_translation: I Have seen nice tall buildings and in the middle they have planted nice short trees.

bem_transcription: Shitata nikala mwishitima elo kabili nashipula, uyu shitata alikwata imwemfu ishitali bushe naumona fimbi ifyo akwete?
eng_translation: A man is sited while sleeping in a train and he has long beards. What else does he have?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elo uyu shitata nakwata akantu akabuuta kantu abikile mumatwi akakumfwilako inyimbo, elyo mumaboko yakwe naimya icampepo icatiikama, nakalimo iyi incende yalitalala.

bem_transcription: Awe nshishibe ifyo baleseka, nakalimo ifyo baleseka fili kuntashi yabo, nangula kuli uulebasekesha, uyu ena umbi asekelela mukati.

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: And these women are putting on nice clothes, they are puttion warm clothes.

bem_transcription: Bashitata bane bali pamulimo elyo uyu umulimo ulemoneka naukaba sana, elyo nabaipekanya pakubomba uyu umulimo, bushe naumona ifyo bafwele?
eng_translation: Four men are working and its seems like a hard job and they are well prepared for work. Have you seen what they are wearing?

eng_translation: Thats true my friend, these my  people are ready for wok and it seems they are working at night near the river side and they have flood lights

eng_translation: Its like they are cutting something if you look closely, Its like they want to build a bridge because they are at the river.

bem_transcription: Elyo nimululamba lwamumana muli ifikuulwa nafimbi ifishingulwike ifitali, ifisuma kabili ifyayemba, pamuulu waciko pali nefimalaiti ifileaka bwino.
eng_translation: Along the river side they are nice and tall buildings around , onto of them they are light.

bem_transcription: Iye uyu umukashana, ala alyanguka amafupa elyo umubili walyanguka kumonafye fintu amishe ukulu kumo elyo akupeteka.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda mune ifyo alemoneka fye cipalile kwati alalwako ulubuli lwakuposa ifibaka, kumona fye ifyo emishe nefyo abikile fye ukulu kwakwe kumbi panshi.
eng_translation: Thats true it seems like the she is a kick boxer fighter you can tell from the way she has raised her leg and folds the other.

bem_transcription: Naulungika elyo neyi iyi incende ilemoneka kwati balimbako yaliibilako panshi, pantu ilemoneka iyafonka elyo baliwamyamo pakutila baleangalilamo.
eng_translation: You are right, the place is well made and designed for games.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, nomba imifwalile yakwe ilemoneka bwino sana, insapato ishafiita mwapita notwabuuuta, elyo akatoloshi afwele nakafiita abikapo ne shati ilitali amaboko.
eng_translation: Thats true, She is waering nice clothes, she is putting on black shoes with white stripes, a black trouser with a long sleveed shirt.

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana nimbona ukutila nakwata ne mishishi ishitali sana, nomba pa mpumi imishishi shakwe alishiputula lelo shilemoneka kwati kasote.
eng_translation: She has long hair except she has cut on her forehead and it looks like a cape.

bem_transcription: Abantu abapusana pusana banamayo nabashitata bali kuncende yakulilako elyo balecita ifyapusana pusana tebonse balelya.
eng_translation: Men and women are in a eating place and they are doing diffrents things.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Kuli bashitata babili abafwele ifyabuuta ifyakufwala ukubikako fye notusote, elo ifisote fyabo fitali nomba ifisote filemoneka kwati fyulu bushe naumona?
eng_translation: Two men are wearing white clothes aswell as their hats and their hats are looking like ant hills. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Walungika aba ebapekanishisha abantu abeshile mukushite fyakulya elyo nakabili bonse nabafwala ifyakufwala fimo fine.
eng_translation: You are right they are the ones who serve people who came to eat they are putting same clothes.

eng_translation: A boy is in the store where they sell food and he is happy looking at the food with his eyes wide open. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune, ala uyu mwaice cipalile ukuti eshilepo mukushitapo ifyakulya kumonafye ifyo alelolesha alesala ifyakulya fintu engalya
eng_translation: I have seen my friend, they boy has come to buy some food you can tell by the he is looking at the food.

bem_transcription: Cishinka elo ifi ifyakulya filemoneka bwino sana, filemoneka ifyalowa, filemoneka ifyapekanishiwe bwino sana, emulandu wine aposeleko sana amano.
eng_translation: Thats true, the food is really nice and sweet and well prepared no wander the boy focused.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ifyakulya fyena nafiwama, muli ifyapusana pusana muli imikate, ifilemoneka ukuti fitumbuwa elyo pali ifi fine ifyakulya nababikapo nomutengo wafyakulya fine.
eng_translation: Its true the food is nice there is bread and something like fritters and other nice food awell with price tags.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwana ala nichanga fye engishemo fye nomutwe muli ififine ifyakulya lintu aleloleshamo elyo alikwata imishishi ishisuma ishatelela kabili ishalala bwino.
eng_translation: He likes the food somuch that he can put his head there and hes has nice hair.

bem_transcription: Ala uyu shitata alemoneka fye uwaluba, cilepala kwati teshibe ifyo alefwaya mwe, naikala pacintu icapala kwati cishimbi, elyo naimya nokulu kabili aleloleshepo fimo.
eng_translation: This man seems lost it looks like he doesn't know what he wants and he is sitting on something while his has raised his leg.

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi, alemoneka fye uwaluba icine cine kabili apo ekele palemoneka ukuti nicimashini kabili ali kwibala kumyakwe.
eng_translation: I have seen too he looks lost and he is sited on something like a machine in his farm.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, nimbona kuli ne bala nalikwata nomusalu uwalelema bwino sana, umusalu uuteku elyo bushe naumona ifilemoneka kulya kumbi?
eng_translation: You are right. there is a farm with green vergetables. What else is there?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune cilepala ukuti nimfula ilya kaili yacilaloka olo atemwa cushi elo ukukwine kwalifula ifimuti.
eng_translation: It  looks like it was raining or its just smoke and this place has a lot of trees.

bem_transcription: Ee, naulungika elo pakati ke bala ndemona kwati balatamapo namatafwali pantu nabatantikapo amatafwali ayaocelwa calimo.
eng_translation: Yes you are right And on the middle of the the farm there are burnt bricks.

bem_transcription: Shitata alesoshikila elyo ifyakulya filemoneka bwino sana, nafwala nefyakufwala fyakwipikilamo, nomba bushe naumona ifyo aleipika?
eng_translation: A man is cooking and the food looks delicious and he putting a hurprone as he is cooking. What is he cooking?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi, cipalile ukuti aleipika inama, kabili nakwata umwele uukalamba, uyu babomfya nga baleputula inama iyakosa, cipalile ukuti aleipika inama.
eng_translation: I have seen he is cooking meat, he is holding a big knife they use to cut meat.

bem_transcription: Ee, naulungika, nomba cilepala kwati bonse natuluba, pamulandu wakutila taleipika lelo aleoca loleshafye pali nomulilo apo.
eng_translation: Yes you are right now it seems we are wrong he is not cooking he is grilling just look at the fire.

bem_transcription: Walungika boi, aleoca kabili pali ici cine icitofu icikalamba pali imbale ishabuuta apo alebika ifyo aleputula.
eng_translation: You are right he is grilling and the same stove they are white plates where he is putting when is done.

bem_transcription: Kuncende uku kuli nabamotoka, motoka imbi ili mupepi nokufuma elyo imbi yalifwa elo baimika fye tayenda.
eng_translation: They are a lot of vihecles in this place, one car is about to go out and the othe one does't work.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo nafundumana ilyo alekweleka ulupili elo ulu ulupili nalukwata icilibwe icikalamba, nomba bushe naumona ifyo alecita?
eng_translation: The boy is busy climbing the mountain with big stone. Have you seen what he is doing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi ilyo aleninika boi nafundumana kabili nafula ne shati kabili alemoneka fye uwapompa pompa.
eng_translation: I have seen  he is not putting a shirt and he is climbing ans he looks mascullar.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco mune ico namona cakutila uyu muntu tali eka kuli naumbi uulemukonka panuma uulekweleka ici chuulu panshi lelo ena eucilike alipantashi.
eng_translation: And he is not alone there is some behind following him and he is in front.

bem_transcription: Namumona naine wine alimwisamba kabili ndemona ukuti pali ifyo akwete nomba tafilepala amolu nshishibe nga ninshi lelo ico ndemonako fye ndemonako kwati nalimo cishimbi.
eng_translation: I have seen him too he is under him he is holding something i can't see cleary but it seem like steel.

bem_transcription: Cishinka nakwata icishimbi ico akakile mumusana nakalimo ici icishimbi cakwimbilako muntu alefwaya ukwikata lintu alekwela.
eng_translation: Its true he tied a steel on his waist maybe he is using it to climb.

bem_transcription: Ala ici icibwa cisuma sana elyo caliina calikwata amasako ayasuma elyo calikwata namatobo bushe naucimona?
eng_translation: This is a nice dog and it is fat it has nice futhers. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nincimona mune cikalamba sana kabili calikwata ilangi ilyakashikila kabili nacipomya namatwi kabili cili namumenshi.
eng_translation: I Have seen it, its is big and it has a nice colour and the ears are flat.

bem_transcription: Elyo ici icibwa cili mumenshi, aya amenshi teyatali sana, yalecifika fye mupepi namucifuba nakalimo cilelunga.
eng_translation: and it is in the water and the river in not deep because the water is just reaching on the body maybe it is hunting something.

bem_transcription: Awe boi naiwe tacilelunga, cishile fye mukwangala mumenshi elo amenshi yalemoneka bwino sana kabili ayalelema kaili eko cili kwaba notumuti utusuma.
eng_translation: No it is not hunting it is just playing in the water and the water looks nice aswell as the sorrounding.

bem_transcription: Utu utumuti twabela fye kululamba lwamumana elo natupantakana nefyani, utu twine utumuti nakabili tatulakula nokukula tulifye utunoono twiipi.
eng_translation: The small trees are just along the river with grass. the trees are not yet fully grown.

bem_transcription: Cishinka naulungika nefyakufwala afwele fisuma pantu nafwala kaputula yabuuta isati lyabuuta mwapita notwa makumbi makumbi elyo mwapatankana notwamituntula.
eng_translation: He is putting a white short and shirt with blue and yellow stripes.

bem_transcription: Ee, nifyo fine, elo kukuulu kwakwe nakakilako akabuuta elyo kabili mumutwe wakwe nabikamo akatambala kabili ici icangalo cakucimfyanya.

eng_translation: People have come to watch others are taking pictures, he is so focused on the his game. people love tenins.

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi cipalile ukuti ici icikuulwa bacikulila kumpanga, pantu ndemonapo utumuti utunoono cipalile ukuti pali ifyo alolesha ifili ukutali lelo alefwaya ukufimwena mupepi.
eng_translation: Have seen it looks like this building is built in the bush because i can only see trees, she is looking at something from afar.

bem_transcription: Naulungika emulandu wine nakucibumba kuli icikope apali ifyoni fimbi filesamba elyo fimbi filepupuka nakalimo efyo alelolesha muli iyi ine mashini.
eng_translation: You are right thats n the wall there is a picture of birds maybe she is looking the birds.

bem_transcription: Ee,elyo kabili ifyakufwala afwele nafiwama sana, elyo ici icikuulwa balicipanga ukubomfya imbao elyo namabuloko, iyi mashini isuma icine cine ukuibomfya.
eng_translation: Yes, she is putting on nice clothes. they have built this place using timber and blocks. This is a nice machine,

bem_transcription: Nomba icimpapushe fye cakutila alikwata imishishi ishitali ndemona kwati shilemufimba napamenso lintu alelolesha muli iyi mashini elyo shalifiita imishishi shakwe.
eng_translation: Now what is amazing me is that she has long hair  and the hair is disturbing her.

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata nafukama elyo aleikata kwishitima nakalimo kuli ififwile ifyo alelungisha tefyo fine?
eng_translation: This man is fixing something from the train.

bem_transcription: Nifyo fine mune cipalile ukutila naishima atemwa naifwe kabili nasunsumana ilyo alewamya ili ishitima.
eng_translation: Thats true the train is not working he is fixing it while squating.

bem_transcription: Cishinka naulungika elyo nafwala ifyakufwala fyakubombelamo nafwala ifyamakumbi makumbi futi icilemoneka kwati cintu cafiita pamuulu napo nabikapo cimo.
eng_translation: You are right he is wearing a blue work suit and there a black thing on top.

eng_translation: Indeed. Have you seen on the other side it looks like people wants to start fighting people are running . Have you seen?

eng_translation: I have seen it looks like the woman is chasing a man and the man running away maybe she wants to sone him.

eng_translation: Have seen how his friends are looking at him, one is really amazed so much that his mouth is open

bem_transcription: Ni fyo fine walanda, nacibapapusha sana pantu tabatalamonapo umuntu ukwima umusango yu, mune bushe taponene panshi nokuicena?

bem_transcription: Naine efyo ndetontonkanya kuti apona mwe, nomba icibipileko cakutila nga cakuti aliponene kuti aitula umutwe pantu tafwele icimpompo afwele fye akasote akaanguka.
eng_translation: I think he can fall the only bad is when he fall he doesn't have an helment to protect his head he is only wearing a cape.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: This is dry grass and they are along the river and on the other side of the river there are buidings.

bem_transcription: Nimfimona, ala fikuulwa ifyayemba sana lelo kwena tefitali fiipi fye fikwete fye intunti shibili elo fintu fyabuuta tuutu.
eng_translation: Have seen  they are nice buidings they are not tall buildings just two stories each.

bem_transcription: hahaha, boi, boi somone ifyo alemoneka uyu kwati lishilu ai nanina napali cimo somone.
eng_translation: Hahhahah mu friend come and see this one he looks like a mad person.

eng_translation: Hahahah is this how he is looking ahahaha and he is slim how can he do such a thing goin there!

eng_translation: Really!! (Scoffs) he is really crazy he is insane as old as he is and when he falls.... just look at his dressing.

eng_translation: He looks scare thats why he is looking like that on the face even his lips looks swollen.

bem_transcription: Elo umu mulemoneka nimucipatala aba bantu bele fye mukusansamushako aba bashitata abashiyendela pantu nimbona bambi bekele fye patumipando uto babensha.
eng_translation: This looks like a hospital they have gone to entain these disabled ones because i can see the wilchairs.

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: If it's the other man that's sited, he is very happy to see his friend that's on his feet dancing, he wishes he were the one dancing.

eng_translation: A man is busy as he skates on the mountain and there's dust everywhere around him.

eng_translation: I have seen him, he is wearing a head cover, carrying a bag, dressed in black and the place he is in is full of sand.

eng_translation: Another thing is that he is wearing an helmet so that even if he were in an accident he wouldn't get hurt.

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: Being a child, umm, it's something else, are you able to see what he is using to cut my friend?

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: That's true, and what he is using to cut has very sharp edges for cutting even though he is not using it rightly to cut, it might hurt him.

bem_transcription: Ala uyu umwaice wamawala pantu napilibula nakasote kantu afwele akalosha kunuma elyo ine nintemwa ifyakufwala fintu afwele abikapo nolusapato ulupaleneko necakufwala cili kumuulu netoloshi lyamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: This child is hyper, because he is wearing his hat in opposite directions, I love his clothes and the shoes similar to his clothes and his blue shirt.

bem_transcription: Nga aba nabo finshi balefwaya mumpanga nabemya notumilando nakalimo nabalufye nsoka, nakalimo balelunge nsoka, mona fye ifyo alemoneka uyu.
eng_translation: Who are these people in the bush lifting logs as though they have lost or trying to kill a snake, look at this one.

bem_transcription: Niwe walungika,elyo nimbona lubali lumbi kuli namatafwali nakalimo emulandu balewamisha iyi incende balefwaya ukukuulapo fimo
eng_translation: You are right, they are some blocks on the other side, perhaps that's why they are cleaning this place

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo wafyamba fye elyo nacimukola kumona fye fintu apeteke ishati buluku buluku fye lilemoneka kwati liipi amaboko kanshi litali.
eng_translation: This young man is on drugs and high right now, it's clear from the way he has folded his long sleeved shirt as though it short.

bem_transcription: Shitata alewamya panse pe tuuka lyakwe elo nakwata akasalu kantu akwete muminwe eko alepukutilako pe wiindo.
eng_translation: A man is cleaning outside his store, he is holding a cloth a cloth in his hand that he is using to wipe the window.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona, fyakulya bashitishamo umu, pantu ndemonamo inkoko isho basalula bwino shimbi balishumika nabashitantika ukutila abantu baleshimona.
eng_translation: You are right it is food they sell in here because I can see well fried chicken there and some dried chicken on display.

bem_transcription: Naulungika elo ici icikuulwa cilemoneka bwino sana, cipalile ukuti lishitolo ilikalamba sana, umo abantu besa mukulila kabili inama shilemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: Yes you are right and this building looks very nice. it looks like it is a big store where people come to eat. The meat looks very appetizing.

bem_transcription: Muntu wandi lolesha pambali pali netebulo elo balishungulushamo notumipando apakwikala, umuntu nga ashita ifyakulya kuya ikalapo fye alya aikuta.
eng_translation: Look! There is also a big table with chairs around where a person can sit and eat when he buys food.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo aleumfwa bwino lintu aleimba, apa nipacisebele ali elyo icisoselo cili fye mupepi nakanwa kakwe.
eng_translation: This young man is enjoying as he is singing on the stage and the microphone is just close to his mouth.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Walasa boi apo, uyu muntu kumona fye fintu apuneme lintu aleimba nakwata ne cilimba ca nsale nangula iyo ine banjo wacitila elyo pambali yakwe pali ne ngoma.
eng_translation: You are right my friend, you can tell from the way he is bent and singing while holding his stringed instrument or could be a guitar with drums on his side.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimumona umulumendo uyu uuli pantashi yakwe acitile kwati natuundama elyo alelisha icilimba ca nsale muminwe yakwe.
eng_translation: I have seen this young man in front of him that's bent a little while singing and playing the stringed instrument in his hands.

bem_transcription: Boi mona uyu shitata balemufumya umwemfu nakalimo uyu umwemfu wacitalimpisha sana emulandu wine aciya kwituuka ukutila bamubeyako.
eng_translation: My friend look at this man whose beard is being shaved off, he should have gone to the barber because it was too long.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Awe tesafu, ili lipofu, muti untu babomfya uo babika kumwemfu elo batampa ukubeya pakutila shonse shingafuma.
eng_translation: No, this is foam coming from some lotion chemical that they apply to beards as they shave so that they shave it all off.

bem_transcription: Ala musuma umu kumona fye icipuna ifyo bacipanga kabili kumona fye negalashi ifyo lili, bushe boi taulemonapo kapompi apo?
eng_translation: This place is nice, it's clear from chairs inside and the glasses, have you seen the tap?

bem_transcription: Aka kapompi ninkamona, elo kalabomfiwa kumusango uwapusana pusana, uyu muntu uo balebeya nga alefwaya ukusamba kumutwe kusamba,elyo noulebeya umunankwe nga alefwaya ukusamba kuminwe nankwe alasamba, nga alefwaya ukulya alasamba.
eng_translation: I have seen it, it is used in different ways, the one being shaved can wash his head when done, the one shaving the other can wash their hands when done, or if they want to eat something they can wash.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo nabakashana bale-enda baleyapo kumo, nomba umo umukashana naceensa naeseeka katwishi ifyo bamwebele, bushe boi naumona aba bambi ifyo balecita?
eng_translation: We young men and women are heading somewhere , one lady has laughed out so loud, I wonder what she's been told, have you seen what the others are doing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi bambi bali pama lamya, elo bambi nabapusha amaboko mumatumba yabo mumatoloshi elo umunyamata uuli kunuma alemwentula fye ena.
eng_translation: Yes I have, some are on their phones, others have their hands in their trouser pockets, while the young man behind is smiling

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo uuli kunuma uulemwentula, euleshimikisha uyu umwanakashi, cilepala kwati ilyashi baleshimika bonse naliwama elyo pambali ya aba bantu kuli no muntu uwikalile panshi.
eng_translation: Yes he is smiling, he is the one chatting with the lady, it seems their story is really nice, there's another person standing beside them.

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune ala umbi naikala cilepala ukuti alesoma elo aba balemoneka ukutila nibakasukulu bali pasukulu ilikalamba.
eng_translation: I have seen him, he is studying, it seems they are at the University.

bem_transcription: Elo incende fye baliko naena ala boi ilemoneka bwino icine cine yalikwata ifimuti icakutila onse uulefwaya ukubelenga kuyaikalafye mwisamba lya cimuti atampa ukubelenga.
eng_translation: The place they are at looks nice my friend, it's full of trees such that whoever wants to study has to just sit under a tree and do so.

bem_transcription: Ala uyu umulumendo alemoneka aliishibisha ukwimba, kumona fye fintu ekete icilimba cakwe ica nsaale lintu ali pacisebele elyo aleimba, bushe naumona?
eng_translation: This man looks like a skilled singer, it's clear from the way he is holding his stringed instrument on the stage, have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona aleimba kabili nakwata banjo elyo abanankwe balelishe ngoma, ala nacilila uku kuntu.
eng_translation: I have seen he is singing, he has a guitar while his friend is playing the drums, this place is on fire!

bem_transcription: Nawishiba mune, tufwile twayako ku ncende ya musango ifi naifwe, twasangalalako mona  fye ifyo amalaiti yakile bwino, abantu baleyumfwisha fye bwino
eng_translation: You know what my friend, we should also go to such a place and have some fun, cause it's full of lights and people are having fun.

bem_transcription: Walungika, naifwe bene tulingile ukuyako pakutila twingayasangalala, nomba bushe tauletontonkanya uku kuntu balalipilisha pakuya mukumfwa ifyo baleumfwa?
eng_translation: You are right, we need to find time to do so, but don't you think people have to pay for such?

bem_transcription: Awe tapali ubwafya, nga kulipila kupila, mona fye kuli na bakashana abasuma elyo nga ni uyu ena naikobeka nefintu ifyapala kwati tumalaiti utunoono.
eng_translation: That's not a problem, we can pay, just look at the beautiful ladies, one of them has hangings on her like that of lights.

bem_transcription: Yangu tata incende ukuwama, we ncende ulawama we! Walikwata notumenshi utuipitila fye, emulandu wine aba bantu bekalile pamabwe.
eng_translation: Oh my goodness, what a beautiful place! With a stream like farrow, that's why people are sited on rocks.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ala iyi incende isuma nomba amenshi yafiko, nakalimo kwaliba amatipa sana tekutila umuntu anwe nangu nakwata icilaka
eng_translation: This place is beautiful but the water is so dirty and muddy, a person can't drink it no matter how thirsty they are.

bem_transcription: Iyi incende boi yalifula ulupili kabili kwabe impili icine cine, kabili ulupili lutali, elo umulumendo alesamba kumoolu.
eng_translation: This place my friend is full of rocks and hills, there's one very high mountain with a young man washing his feet.

bem_transcription: Ulu ulupili lwalikwata umucanga kabili ifyafulamo mabwe, pamuulu wampili paliba notumuti, utwamena fye patali patali utwiipi.
eng_translation: This mountain is full of sand and rocks and on it's top are trees that have grown each one far from the other.

bem_transcription: Muntu wandi mona ifyo banamayo banyanyangele ulubilo, ukubutuka fye imfula, mwati naumona intampu shintu baleuma?
eng_translation: My friend, look at how these ladies are running, they are running from the rains, have you seen how fast they are running?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi ala nailoka kabili ikalamba icine cine bonse nabakwata imyamfuli, nomba icimpapusha cakutila abantu balatiina imfula lelo imyotoka tabatiina, mulandu nshi?
eng_translation: I have seen, it's raining heavily and they all have umbrellas, what amazes me is that people are afraid of the rain but not vehicles, why's that so?

bem_transcription: Iwe uleishiba utuntu, mulandu wakutila tabafwaya imishishi shabo shalokwa, tawamona ukutila banamayo balibika sana amano kumishishi shabo?
eng_translation: Be smart my friend, they don't want to get their hair wet, haven't you noticed ladies pay attention to their hair?

bem_transcription: Walungika mune, ala balasakamana sana umushishi wabo, emuandu wine tabafwaila umushishi walokwa, nomba mune tabaishiba ukuti motoka ilepaya?
eng_translation: You are right, they really care about their hair, that's why they never want it soaked,.but don't they know a vehicle kills?

bem_transcription: Kwena motoka ilepaya nomba nga naumona fye apa pantu baletolokela tapali na motoka,imyotoka nisho beminike kumbali yamusebo imbi ilemoneka iyakatapakatapa.
eng_translation: That's true, but there's no vehicle where they are crossing from, the vehicles are parked on the road side, one of them is green.

bem_transcription: Ala uyu umumana usuma icine cine elyo ukalamba kabili pali namabwato, nomba naumona ubu ubwato bashikile fye nomulundu
eng_translation: This is a beautiful big river with boats on it, have you seen the boat next to the hill?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi ala ubu ubwato bukalamba icine cine kaili nababukaka kuli cimo pakutila bwi-enda,elyo pamuulu paliko fimo, bushe nifinshi filya?
eng_translation: This is a big boat that has been tied so that it doesn't move, and there's dirt on top, what's that?

bem_transcription: Nimbona pamuulu ya ubu bwato pali ifikopo fyashimbi ifyamafuta elyo fingi, nomba ninshi umutenge wa ubu ubwato walikosa sana?
eng_translation: On top of the boat are lots of oil bottles, is the roof of this boat strong?

bem_transcription: Awe boi, walipofula fye iwe tefikopo ifi madalamu yali pamuulu kaili mukati na mwena muli amadalamu, cipalile ukuti baleya mukushitisha, bushe naumona ubwato bumbi?
eng_translation: No, you are blind, these are not bottles, they are drums and they also drums inside, it seems they are going to sell them, have you seen the other boat?

bem_transcription: Awe boi, nshacilalolekesha, elo namona, nacilamona kwati mukati muli abantu kanshi muli fye amadalamu, elo namabwato wacilalando ayali pakati ka bemba ninjamona.
eng_translation: I just didn't see it well, but now I have, I thought those were people inside but they are drums, and I have also seen the other boats on the middle of the sea.

bem_transcription: Shitata uwaishiba ukulwa bwino no lupanga, ali kuncende imo uko aleangasha ulu lwine ulupanga, bushe naumona boi?
eng_translation: A man skillful at using the sword is in a place playing with his sword, have you seen him my guy?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi elo naima mumuulu, kwati nakalimo pali ifyo aleputula kaili naimya no lupanga mumuulu cipalile ukuti pali uo balelwa nankwe.
eng_translation: Yes I have, he is in the air as though he wants to cut something with his sword in the air, it seems he is fighting someone.

bem_transcription: Awe boi uyu muntu aleisambilisha fye umwine nangula kuli abantu abo alelanga ifya kubomfya ulu ulupanga, bushe naumona ifyo afwele?
eng_translation: No my friend, he is only teaching himself to fight, or he could be showing some people how to use the sword, have you seen how he is dressed?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi, ifyakufwala afwele ekutila itoloshi ilyabutulukila, abikapo ne ndeleshi iyamakumbi makumbi, akaka nomushipi uwakashika, nakumutwe afwalako citambala icakashika.
eng_translation: Yes I have have, he is wearing a brown trousers, a blue shirt, a red belt and a red bandana on his head.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, elo iyi incende isuma icine cine, panshi tapaba nomucanga elyo kabili kwaliba nefimuti ifyo babyala bwino ifyashinguluka iyi incende.
eng_translation: Yes you right, this place is beautiful without any sand, full of trees planted around this place.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo bali mucibansa cafyangalo baleangala ubwangalo bwamupila bwakuminwe, nomba naumona ifyo ababili bafundumene?
eng_translation: Some young men are inside a sports field playing handball, have you seen these two?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi cipalile ukutila balelwila kabola, ici icangalo cakubutuka elo naukwata kabola muminwe, nga bakusanga kukupuunka.
eng_translation: Yes I have my guy, it seems they are fighting for the ball, this is rugby, if one has they ball others run toward him and get the ball.

bem_transcription: Cishinka nomba uyu ena uuli kunuma nakwata uto aikakile utwabuuta kukuboko elo natufyanta, nomba ifyakufwala bafwele bushe naumona ifyo filemoneka? lolekesha kuti watila nifinshi?
eng_translation: That's true, the one behind has tied something white so tightly, have you seen how their clothes look like? What can you say about them?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi, umbi nafwala ifyabuuta fyeka fyeka,elo umbi nafwala icalemonekako icakashika, kabili nabafwala necakuicinga kumutwe, icakutila nangu bengapona tabaicenene kumutwe.
eng_translation: I have seen my friend, one is dressed in white, another in red, they are all wearing helmets to protect them from injuries.

bem_transcription: Ee, cishinka elo cimbi naco cakutila ifi ifyakufwala balemoneka abaina pantu mukati balabikamo ifyakucingililamo ififuba fyabo elyo namafupa.
eng_translation: That's true, the other thing is that they look fat in these clothes, because they have worn things inside to shield their chests and bones inside.

bem_transcription: Kalisha wafilimba umulumendo uwayemba icine cine kabili uufwele ifyakufwala ifyayemba aleenda  ukuya pacisebele.
eng_translation: A very handsome musician musician that is well dressed is heading to the stage.

bem_transcription: Ee, elo icisebele cilemoneka bwino sana, kabili icisuma kabili nakwatako nacimo ico alisha ukubomfya fye akanwa ala namoneka bwino.
eng_translation: The stage looks very nice and he has some sound instrument he is playing with only his mouth, he looks so handsome.

bem_transcription: Mune nomba nga nalolekesha uyu, nakwatako necapala kwati mutolilo icakulisha icikalamba, elyo ala icisebele caliyemba icine cine palibeeka.
eng_translation: If you pay attention to him, he has something like a huge flute and the stage is nice and very shiny.

bem_transcription: Olo pacisebele pene pali cimo icikalamba icilemoneka ukutila eco balisha ukutinika ne minwe kaili nacikwata namawilo, bushe boi naucimona?
eng_translation: And there's also something like looks like a huge piano with wheels on the stage have you seen it?

bem_transcription: Ala nincimona, cintu cayemba kabili icapangwa ubusaka, elyo imbao shintu babomfeshe pakupanga ici nishilya ishatelela kabili ishabeeka.
eng_translation: Yes I have, it's very beautiful and well built, it was made with very smooth and shiny wood.

bem_transcription: Boi mona uyu umwaice ai, kwati takwete ifyakucita ukuyalaala fye pafyani, nalala elo ifyani fili fye mupepi notumenshi, bushe naumona ifyo acitile?
eng_translation: My friend look at this kid, as though she has nothing to do just sleeping on grass next to water, have you seen her?

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana nalambalala panshi, kabili nainuna nomutwe wakwe elo aloleshe ku-ulemukopa naimyako necikondo kabili ali ne mishishi ishisuma sana.
eng_translation: She is laying down, facing up and looking at the camera person while lifting her fingers and she has nice hair.

bem_transcription: We cibusa wandi nincimona ici icinama, elyo ici nicilya beta ukutila chifulwe, elyo cikalamba kumona fye necipapa cikalamba.
eng_translation: My dear friend, I have seen this animal called a tortoise, it's very big, it's clear from it's shell.

bem_transcription: Uko ali, balicingako ne linga ilya mawaya,elo ifyani babyala filemoneka bwino ifyalelema, bushe boi naumona icili panshi?
eng_translation: This place has a wire fence, and there's broad grass, have you seen what's on the ground?

bem_transcription: Namona, nomba kunuma yakwe utumenshi tulemoneka utusuma utwalengama bwino sana elyo kamufoolo fye akanoono akapisha amenshi.
eng_translation: Yes, there's water behind her and a small drainage were water is passing.

bem_transcription: Yangu tata Lesa mona uyu umwaice ifyo atolweke ukufuma pancende iyasansuka sana ukutolokela panshi ukubomfya akantu ako ensha amoolu fye.
eng_translation: Oh my goodness! Look at how this little child has jumped from so high on his skateboard.

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune ala natoloka icakutila aleya mukuponena apatali atemwa pa mushili apali atemwa amabwe bushe taletontonkanya ukutila aleya aicene?
eng_translation: I have seen my friend, he is about to land on something or some rocks, do you think he is going to get hurt?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, elyo icibipileko cakutila tafwele necimpomopo icakumucingilila, nga cakutila apona, uyu umwaice alisamwa samwa fye nokubilima pamuulu.
eng_translation: I have, the bad part is he is not wearing an helmet, he might get hurt, he is so hyper and over excited.

bem_transcription: Ummm.. boi, bushe naumona ifyo ndemona,ah! kanshi napesamba paliko no muntu uukonteme cilepala kwati alekopa uyu uulefuma pamuulu, bushe uletontonkanya shani?
eng_translation: um! my friend are you seeing what I am seeing? There's another person on the side that seems to be capturing the one on the top. What do you think?

bem_transcription: Ee nalolekesha nomba nacimona kwati cisote kanshi cikopelo akwete cilepala kwati alepanga video ya uyu wine umulemendo uletoloka.
eng_translation: yes, I have observed now, I thought it was a hat but it's a camera that he has, it seems like he's making a video of this same guy jumping.

bem_transcription: Iye uyu namayo alafulamuka pantu uyu kabalwe temine bwino icine cine. Bushe naumona ifyo uyu kabalwewe emine?
eng_translation: oh my goodness! this woman will fall off because of the way this horse will land, have you seen how it's up in the air?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi naima ica kutila akontamina na panshi amolu yabili aya kuntanshi nayema elyo ukulu kumo ukwa kunuma nakwima kumbi nakwikala panshi.
eng_translation: I have seen my friend, it's up such that it's head is facing downwards, both it's frontal legs are up then one of it's hind legs is stood the other is kneeling.

bem_transcription: Nomba alemoneka kwati alifye nipacangalo pantu umu ni mu cibansa elyo icibansa cakaena calikwata no lunkoto ululemoneka kwati lwalyuma.
eng_translation: but it seems like it's just putting on a show because they're in the ground, and the ground has grass that looks dry.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimumona uyu uninine pali kabalwe mukashana elyo uwaonda nafwala ishati ilya buta ilitali amabko lelo napeteka abikapo netoloshi no lusapato lwafita.
eng_translation: I have seen the slim lady on the horse, she's wearing a long sleeved white shirt which she's folded with a pair of trousers and some black shoes.

bem_transcription: Ummmm aba bantu balemoneka abalubana lubana wee cila muntu ali ne fyakwe nomba kuli shitata uyu uli no mwana wakwe, naumona ifyo alemoneka pa menso?
eng_translation: wow, these people look so messed up and disorganized, each person is doing his own thing, then there's a man with his son, have you seen his facial appearance?

bem_transcription: Nimona boi naikata umwana wakwe ku kuboko kabili pamenso palemonenka fye apafulwa kwatishi ico afuliwe kabili uyu wine wishi aba no bupipi. Nomba aba finshi balecita pali ici cikulwa?
eng_translation: I have seen my friend, he's holding his son's hand and he looks upset, who knows why he's upset. And this father has lots of fur. what are these doing at this building?

bem_transcription: Elyo uyu shitata nabifya napamenso efyo akwatila amatobo mona fye tekutila umuntu afulwe mu musango uyu napasha no mwana na matobo umwana  eko alekonka.
eng_translation: and this same man is frowning that's why he has big cheeks, there's no way a person can be this upset, his son even resembles the father's cheeks the son follows his father's steps.

bem_transcription: Aba bantu batatu baleingila muli Ici cikulwa nshi shibe nga cikulwa nshi kabili nafwala ifya fita babili elo umbi afwele ifya makumbi makumbi. Bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: These three men entering the building, I don't know the building,and

bem_transcription: Nimbamona aba bantu cipalile kwati baleingila mucikuulwa ca bwala nangula umuli amalila muli ici cikulwa pantu pacipampa pali apo balembele ukutila mwaiseni.
eng_translation: I have seen these people, they are entering either a bar or restaurant because there's a poster with a welcome writing on it.

bem_transcription: Boi somone uyu shitata alemoneka kwati wa fyamba nomba nona ifyo alecita nafulilako ne shati pakukwampa ulunkoto....Somone!!
eng_translation: My friend come and see this man that's on drugs is doing, he is shirtless while mowing a lawn, come and see!

bem_transcription: Mmmm nimumona boi nomba icifuba ici te cakufumisha pa bantu pa amala palemoneka ukuti alipo mubusanso. Bushe naumona?
eng_translation: I have seen him, this chest shouldn't even be left outside, it looks as though he was in an accident, have you seen that?

bem_transcription: Awe ulelokesha boi ehehe.. Bupipi ubu tekutila aliko mubwafya nangula mu busanso bupipi ubwamena palufumo lwakwe ululemoneka kwati mukofu.
eng_translation: No my friend, (laughs out), he is just hairy not that he was in an accident, he has lots of hair on his chest.

bem_transcription: Elyo namwenekesha nacilamona ukuti alipo mu busanso elyo bamubila pamala nomba machine alebomfya ikalamba sana kabili nabikapo na fimo mu matwi bushe naimona machine kabili ibomba finshi
eng_translation: Oh yes, I have now noticed, I have thought he was in an accident then had to undergo an operation. The machine he is using is very big because he has even covered his ears to avoid the noise.

bem_transcription: Iyi machine eyo alebonfya pa ukukwampa ulukonto ulu lwine uli panshi kumona uko ilefuma naikwampa akale nailinganya elyo kunuma yakwe kuli ne ng'anda ilemoneka bwino sana.
eng_translation: It is a lawnmower, it has done a good job where he is coming from and behind him is a house that looks clean.

bem_transcription: Abantu ubwingi ababungene kuli iyi ncende nomba nshi shibe  nga finshi babunganine uku teti babungane umusango uyu. Boi ulemona ukuti finshi filecitika uku?
eng_translation: Some many people are gathered in one place, I wonder why they are gathered in such a way, my friend what do you think is happening?

bem_transcription: Umm nshi shibe mune mbwene fye nabalongana kabili uubalonganineke naminako pamo kabili cipala ukuti alebebapo fimo. Bushe tefyo fine?
eng_translation: I have no idea my friend though the one spear heading the gathering is standing on one place telling them something.

bem_transcription: Nimbona uyu shitata uwinine apa sansuka eulebebapo fimo kabili nabaposako amano sana lintu alebeba.Nomba naumona uyu shitata uwimine uku?
eng_translation: I have seen this man on the stage is telling them something, have you seen the other man this side?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimbona ici cikuulwa ukwabula no kutwishika balicikula bwino sana kabili abalekula  baliposeleko amano kabili calikosa nefibi fya ciko fyalikashika
eng_translation: I have seen this building, without a doubt it was well built, the builders put in so much effort, it's clear from how strong the red doors are.

bem_transcription: Boi mona uyu namayo alemoneka kwati takwete ifyakucita emulandu ekali fye paka mupando lelo tabatulangile icinso cakwe kanshi tatwisbe nga mubi nangula musuma. Nomba bushe ulemone ukwati finshi fimbi alecita?
eng_translation: My friend, look at this lady that has nothing to do and is sited alone on a chair, her face is not showing, it's hard to tell whether she's beautiful or not not. What else do you think she's doing?

bem_transcription: ummmm cipalile ukuti ali pa ng'anda pa myakwe elo alemona fye ifyo amaluba yalelema kabili natonta amenso ku ng'anda ku mwakwe. Nomba bushe naumona ifili panuma?
eng_translation: Ummm, this looks like her house and she amazed by the blooming of her flowers and she's focused on her house, have you seen what's behind?

bem_transcription: Pakubala nacimonapo kwati afwele fye amaboko akashati akepi amaboko lelo elo namwenesha ukutila ailenga fye ifya katapa katapa katwishi uyu umukashana nga cali shani.
eng_translation: At first I thought she's wearing a shirt sleeved shirt but it's like she's painting herself green, I wonder what's going on with her.

bem_transcription: Awe mune tekutila ukuti taishibe ifyo aletontonkanya abanesu  abakwata inkanda yamusango uyu balitemwa fye ukuilenga lenga nga waliposko amano sana kabili no mushishi ulemoneka fye uwakashika kashika.
eng_translation: No my friend, it's not like she doesn't know what she's doing, white love tattoos and her hair looks reddish.

bem_transcription: Ee cishinka kuntanshi yakwe kuli amaluba ayalekana lekana kabili ayakwata amaluba ayakwata amalangi aya pusana pusana nintwemwa ifyo yalemoneka ukuyemba.
eng_translation: Well that's true, they are different colored flowers in front of her and I like how beautiful they look.

bem_transcription: Banamayo balemoneka aba nsansa kabili abasekelela kumona fye fintu bamwentwile, elyo bushe naumona ifyo uyu namayo umbi ekete ku minwe?
eng_translation: Some ladies look very happy, it's clear from their smile, have you seen what the other lady is holding in her hands?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi nakwata amaluba ayengi ayo bakakile pamo kabili nababika mucipepala kabili alemoneka bwino sana. Bushe naumona umbi ifyo amenso yakwe yakashike?
eng_translation: I have seen my friend, she's holding a bouquet of flowers that's well wrapped and looks beautiful, have you noticed how red the other one's eyes are?

bem_transcription: Nimbona uyu icalengele ukuti amenso yakashike umusango ilyo balemukopa ilaiti yalimubyasha mu menso emulandu wine yalemonekela ayabeka kabili aya kashika
eng_translation: Yes I have, her eyes look this way because the time she was being captured a flash was used and made her eyes look red and shiny in this way.

bem_transcription: Awe mune taumwenekeshe bwino pantu ine ndemonako ibotolo lya mwangashi cipalile ukuti acinwamo kabili ecalenga amenso yakwe yakashike. kabili abantu nabafula uku uletontonkanya finshi balecita?
eng_translation: No, my friend you are incorrect, I have seen a bottle of beer she's drunk and that's why her eyes are red. This place is full of people what do you think they are doing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona ibotolo lya mwangashi lili fye kunuma ukwa cipuna elyo talilemonekesha bwino bwino uku kulemoneka kuli umutebeto pantu bana mayo abengi nabekala napanshi elyo kuli  fyo balelya.
eng_translation: I have seen a beer bottle behind the chair that's a little unclear with a number of ladies sited and having a feast.

bem_transcription: We cikuulwa ulawama we ala ici cikulwa caliyemba cilemoneka icabusaka, bushe naumona ifintu ifilemoneka mukati?
eng_translation: What a beautiful building! Such a beautiful and clean building, have you seen the things inside?

bem_transcription: Awe boi teti ndondolole bwino ifili mukati nacimpesha amano nshishibe napabelele umwinshi nepo uyu namayo aleya mukwingilila.
eng_translation: I can't even explain my friend, I can't even see where the entrance is that this lady will use.

bem_transcription: Awe kwena kuti cakupelenganya amano pantu cilemoneka calikwata apakwingila apengi elyo lubali lumbi kuli na shitata uwimine fye nafwala ifya fita ku mulu abikako ne camakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: Yes, you can be amazed, it has so many entrances and on one side is a man dressed in blue with a blue shirt.

bem_transcription: Kuli namayo ulefuma muli ici cikulwa kabili ici cikulwa nacimpesha amano kabili nacimpelenganya amano icakutila nshaishiba ifyo bacipanga.
eng_translation: There's also a lady walking out of this building that has left me in awe because of its make.

bem_transcription: Cishinka icine cine nakabili panshi ya ici cikulwa balibikapo amabwe ayatelela sana ayamwensha bwino kabili ayabeka.
eng_translation: That's true, they are shinny stones on the ground

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana alemoneka uwabulanda kabili ne myendele yakwe tailemoneka bwino nomba bushe ni kumatobo uku ekete nagula alelanda pali lamya. Boi ulemona ukuti finshi alecita ai?
eng_translation: This lady looks so sad as she walks, is she holding her cheek or is she talking on phone? What do you think she's doing my friend?

bem_transcription: Boi cipalile ukuti ali pali lamya cilepala ukuti pali abo alelanshanya napo atewmwa emuku wakubalilepo ukwisa kuli iyi incende kabili aletunina abakwisa musenda.
eng_translation: I think she's on phone my friend and she's excited about being in this place for the first time so she's calling someone to come and pick her up.

bem_transcription: Ala cishinka elo uku kulepala kwati niku citesheni ce shitima emulandu wine eminine mumbali umusango uyu nakalimo alelolela ukuti ishitima lise anine.
eng_translation: That's true and this looks like a train station and that's why she's standing on one side waiting for the train to come so that she can board.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Aahh niwebo walingika unjeleleko mune cilepala kwati amenso yandi tayalemwenesha pantu namona ukutila nomba ici cikulwa calikwata intunti nangula shibili nangula ishingi ko kanshi apa ali nipamulu fye.
eng_translation: Yes you are right my friend, I'm sorry my eyes seem to be failing me because now I have seen this is a storey building that could be two or more, this is just the top.

bem_transcription: Iye boi mona uyu ali kusamwa konse uku mona apo aninine apo aleshelemuka pakantu akacepesha awe namona ukuti tatemwa ameno yakwe umuntu uyu.
eng_translation: My friend, look at this over excitement, this person is on a skateboard, he doesn't seem to love his teeth.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ala nomba nga twalolekesha futi cilemoneka kwati alishibisha ukwangala ici cine cangalo we lolekesha fye fintu atolweke pantu nga taishiba nga afulamuka kale.
eng_translation: I have seen, when you pay attention it seems he knows how to skate, just look at how he is in the air, if he doesn't know he would have fallen off by now.

bem_transcription: Naulanda wasosa bwino sana elo apo aleshelemuka pesamba paliko naka motoka akanono aka makumbi makumbi kabili kalemoneka kwati ni kacula. Bushe naukamona?
eng_translation: Yes you are right, there's a small blue vehicle that looks like a frog close to where he skating, have you seen it?

bem_transcription: Ee ni njimona motoka iyi nomba cilemoneka kwati eikwete akashimbi kantu uyu muntu aleshelemukapo elyo lubali lumbi kuli no tushimbi fye utwikete aka kene kantu anininepo.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen it, it seems it's the one holding the board that he is skating on, and they are other metal rods holding the same skate board.

bem_transcription: Iye nakumbwa ifyo aba bana balecita pantu balecena elyo umwana ucepeshe pali bena eo baninike pa cimpelwa. Bushe naumona?
eng_translation: I really admire what these kids are doing, the youngest is the one on the swing, have you seen them?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi nomba uku tekucena iyo baleangala limbi cilepala ukuti balecita ati uyu uwaninapo bamupelusha elo umbi aninapo nankwe bamupelusha.
eng_translation: They are playing, they are taking turns, after one swings then another goes to swing.

bem_transcription: Ee cishinka nomba ni ntemwa ifyo incende ilemoneka bwino pantu yaliyemba bwino icine cine elyo lubali lumbi kuli namabala uko balima ifintu ifya pusana pusana.
eng_translation: Yes that's true, I love this how beautiful this place looks with fields on the other side where they have planted different things.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana pantu kumona fye ifyo kulemoneka kabili ifimuti fingi kabili ifya funda elyo kabili no uko babikile icimpelwa cine calikosa icimuti.
eng_translation: That's true, just look at the many trees on it and the tree where the swing has been hang is very strong.

bem_transcription: Elyo abana aba umo mulumendo uyu ufwele itoloshi ilya buta emulumendo nakwata ne mishishi isha fita elyo abashala babili bonse bakashana ala abana balitemwana.
eng_translation: One of the kids is a boy wearing a white trousers and has black hair while the other two are girls, these kids really love each other.

bem_transcription: Muntu wandi lolekesha kuno pacikope mona ifyo inkunda shitanteme ubusaka kwati shile matcin'ger wee kwati bashilika.
eng_translation: My friend focus on this picture, look at how well the doves are arranged as though they are matching.

bem_transcription: Ala shile-enda busaka busungu kabili shilendela pamo nakumbwa ala ishi inkunda shalikatana icine cine.
eng_translation: Wow, so impressive, they are well aligned, this is admirable.

bem_transcription: Cishinka pantu shonse shitampwile ukulu kwa ku kulyo shonse fye shilemoneka balishisambilisha bwino ifya kwenda ishi inkunda.
eng_translation: That's true because all of them have their right leg in front, they have been well trained.

bem_transcription: Cipalile ukuti shaya mukutandalila ishinankwe atewmwa shayako ukuliko ifyakulya. Bushe naumona icikulwa ici icili apa?
eng_translation: It's like they are visiting others doves or going to look for food, have you seen the building close by?

bem_transcription: Ee nincimona ici icikulwa elo teciliko fye ceka apataliko palemoneka icikulwa nacimbi isuma sana ica yemba icikwete ilangi ilya katapa katapa elyo ne nceshi ishabuta.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen it's not the only building, there's another beautiful green building at a distance.

bem_transcription: Shitata alemoneka insala naimupuma kumone fya pa mesno alemoneka lushile lushile emulandu wine aleisendela fye ifyakulya munshita yakuti alolele bamupele.
eng_translation: This man looks so hungry, it's clear from his face, that's why he can't even wait to be served but serving himself.

bem_transcription: Awe boi naiwe taimumine insala kabili talelolela ukuti  bamupele cipalile ukuti balelila pamo nabakashi kabili cila muntu aleibulila ifyo alefwaya kulya. Bushe taumwene?
eng_translation: No I don't think he is that hungry, he is only having food with his wife and it's self service, that's why he is serving himself.

bem_transcription: Ee awe naulungika balelila pamo aba nacilamona kwati uyu umukashi uwikele uku ewacilamupela ifya kulya.
eng_translation: Oh yes they are having food together, I just thought the lady sited on this side was giving him food.

bem_transcription: Elyo boi pali inkomeki shibili ishamagalashi kabili mu nkomeki muliko umwangashi kabili pali ne botolo lya mwangashi. Bushe naumona?
eng_translation: They are two glass keys that have beer bottles, have you seen them?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona aba bantu baleumfwa bwino mwe elyo ifya kulya filemoneka nafiwama palya paliko no musalu elyo lubali lumbi pali fye ifya kulya fimbi ifya pusana.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen these people seem to be enjoying because the food looks so nice, they are some vegetables and other different foods.

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata alitemwa umwana wakwe icine cine elyo umwana wakwe alimupala umutwe emulandu wine namupapa no kumusenda ku ncende imo.
eng_translation: This man loves his child that has a head like he's, he has carried him and taken him to some place.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana elyo amupapile pa ntanshi elyo bekele pe libwe elyo uyu wine wishi nafwala na magalashi ala  uyu umwana musuma icine cine.
eng_translation: Yes that's true, he has carried him in front and they are sited on a rock, the man is wearing glasses and the child is good looking.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwana na kabili alemoneka kwati mwaume no mulandu wakuti nakwata tu mishishi utwipi elyo ne fwakufwala bamufwalike fya caume afwele fye ifyapala ka kaputula.
eng_translation: This child looks like a boy because he has short hair and wearing boys clothes like this short.

bem_transcription: Cipalile ukuti boi bacisenda umwana ba wishi ukuti baleya batandalepo kumo kanshi beshilie uku kwine ku ncende no kwikalako pamabwe nokulatamba ifyo baletamba.
eng_translation: It seems the man took his child to come and tour and watch this place as they sit on rocks.

bem_transcription: Aba bantu balitemwana emulandu wine basendanine ku mpanga elyo iyi  incede kulemoneka fye ifimuti ifitali ne fimabwe elyo no mucanga.
eng_translation: These two love each other alot, that's why they came to visit this bush full of tall trees, rocks and sand.

bem_transcription: Abantu nabaya mukuipakisha ku ncende imo ilemoneka bwino sana kabili iyayemba nomba bambi nabapapa ne fyola nakalimo bacili pa lwendo tabalafika.
eng_translation: These people came to enjoy the scenery, some are even carrying their bags it's as though they are yet to reach their destinations.

bem_transcription: Eee aba bengi bena abantu cipalile ukutila kuli fye fimo ifyo beshile mukutamba pantu bambi nabapapa ifyola elyo bambi nabekala fye apa epo bali panshi
eng_translation: These are lots of people, it seems they came to watch something, some are carrying their bags while others are just sited.

bem_transcription: uku kuntu kulemoneka kwati nikwibungano emulandu wine abantu bekalile mu ncede ishapusana pusana elyo aba bapapile ifyola cilepala kwati elyo bafika fye ku ncende iyi.
eng_translation: This place seems like a convention that's why people are sited in different places and the ones carrying their bags have just arrived.

bem_transcription: Ala ni fyo fine ba boi mwalanda kumona fye ne fyola basendele cipalile ukuti beshile mukutambapo fimo elyo iyi incende naikwata ulubuto lwa malaiti naumona kwati te cungulo bushiku?
eng_translation: You are right my friend, from what they are carrying it's clear they are here to watch something and the lights are on so bright as though it's not evening.

bem_transcription: Awe amaliti yena balyuma yalemoneka ayayemba sana elyo kuli na mamotoka fye ayo beminike, lwamupepi kulemoneka ne fikulwa ifitali ifya yemba.
eng_translation: Indeed the lights have been well set, they are also vehicles parked and very tall beautiful buildings close by.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo alecapa ifyakufwala!
eng_translation: A young man is washing.

bem_transcription: Muntu alecapila ni mufilindi elo aya amenshi yalemoneka nayalamba
eng_translation: He is washing from a hole and the water looks very dirty.

bem_transcription: Aya amenshi cilepala yalikalila sana pantu yalemoneka aya fiko ne fyakufwala fyalakowela.
eng_translation: This should be stagnant water, because it looks so dirty he will stain his clothes.

bem_transcription: Ifyakufwala alecapa nacimoneka nalimo nafimushupa sana pantu na kwata ne ifimuti ifyo alepuminako.
