bem_transcription: Cishinka, kabili icisote afwele cabanakashi,namagalashi afwele nayo yabanakashi, nomba fye dalamu fye iyo akobeke mumukoshi ecimpapwishe, bushe talifinine?
eng_translation: That's true, he is wearing a girly hat, girly glasses but the way he has lifted the drum, I'm shocked is it not heavy?

bem_transcription: Awe talifinine pantu iyi ni ngoma elo pakati paba fye icipunda mumbali emo bapisha icililata kanshi tacifinine.
eng_translation: No it's not because this is a drum there's only space on the middle and metal around it, it's not heavy.

bem_transcription: Awe nga nifyo wasosa ninshi cili fye bwino, elo kuli nabambi abafwele ifyabuuta ekutila umukashana elo nomulumendo uufwele amagalashi yafiita.
eng_translation: If you say that then that's true and they are other people dressed in white, a lady and a man dressed in black glasses.

bem_transcription: Uwacilumendo naikala kabili cilepala ukuti pali ifyo aletontonkanya nakwata nomushishi uunoono kabili uwafiita naumona?
eng_translation: A young man is sited and it seems he is thinking about something and has short black hair, have you seen it?

bem_transcription: Ala uyu umulumendo alikwata umushishi uwafiita sana nangula twiipi utumishishi twakwe na kuncende kuntu ali kulemoneka akasuba nakalotoka kumona fye efyo eswile utumenso pakulolesha
eng_translation: This young man has short black hair, he is in a very sunny place such that he is failing to open his eyes.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana kalemoneka akasuba kabili cilepala ukuti eshile mukutusha apo akasuba nakabalika sana, bushe naumona kuncende kuntu ali?
eng_translation: Yes it seems very sunny and it seems he is here to rest, have you seen the place he is in?

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilemoneka yakutushishako fye, elyo baliipanga bwino sana, yalikwata ulunkoto, yakwata ne fimuti ifikalamba kanshi afwaya nga aciya ikala mucintelelwe ca cimuti cimo.
eng_translation: This place should be resting only, it is well built and has a lawn and trees with lots of shade, had he wanted he would have sat under one.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana uku kwine kwalifula sana ifimuti sana kuncende uku kaili balibyala nolunkoto ulusuma kaili ululemoneka bwino kaili nabeminika na motoka.
eng_translation: Indeed this place is full of trees, a beautiful lawn and vehicles that are parked.

bem_transcription: Iyeee, boi somone uyu shitata, talemoneka kwati muntuntula nga walolesha ifyakufwala afwala bushe kuti watila muntu wamusango shani uyu?
eng_translation: My friend come and see this man that doesn't look very sane, what sort of person is this?

bem_transcription: Uku tekupena mune efyo afwala fye ififine taumwene ukuti nafwala itoloshi ilyafiita elo abikapo ne shati ilyafiita elo nakwatapo nacimo abikapo ne nsapato iyafiita?
eng_translation: No my friend, he is normal, haven't you noticed he is wearing a black shirt and trousers, he has something and wearing black shoes.

bem_transcription: Ee, niwebo walungika, tekupena lelo ifyo afwele filemumwenesha kwati napena nakwata icabuuta mumukonso elo necapala kwati mutolilo kuminwe.
eng_translation: You are right he is not crazy, it's just what he is wearing making him look this way, he has something white on his feet and a flute in his hand.

bem_transcription: Ee ca cine walanda alino mutolilo kanshi ecilengele ukuti afwale umusango yu, cilepala ukutila aleimbapo fimo, nga walolekesha sana kuli na fimo kunuma ifyo balepela icilambu.
eng_translation: Yes he is holding a flute that's why he is dressed this way and behind him are other things as though people being awarded.

bem_transcription: Ee, cishinka, nakalimo bacimwita ukuti alishe umutolilo, elyo icikuulwa ici cilemoneka bwino icine cine ne filambu ifyo batantike filemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: That's right, perhaps he was called to play the flute, the building looks beautiful and the trophies are well arranged.

bem_transcription: Iyee uyu umwana, moneni ifyo bawishi bamuposele mumuulu elo nakema mumuulu akamwana akamulumendo, bushe naukamona boi?
eng_translation: Oh my! this little boy, the father has tossed him into the air, have you seen it my friend?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Awe ukuicena boi kwena taicene pamulandu wakutila uku nikululamba kwamumana elyo kuli umucanga uwingi sana.
eng_translation: No my friend he won't get hurt because he is at the sea shore that's full of sand.

bem_transcription: Nga nifyo walanda ninshi taicene apo kuli umucanga uwingi sana lelo nkashi yakwe alelolesha fye ukumona uko ndume nankwe bamuposele mumuulu.
eng_translation: You are right he won't get hurt because there's lots of sand, his sister is just looking at how the brother has been tossed into the air.

bem_transcription: Elyo bonse babili balemoneka nabasekelela, kumona nakamwana ako bapoosele mumuulu nakaasama mumuulu kwati kacilapanduka nga nikakanshi nakaseka.
eng_translation: They are both very happy, it's clear from the excitement of the child's face as he is in the air and also the sister's they are so happy.

bem_transcription: Boi mona akamwana akamulumendo ifyo kemine mu muulu nshishe nga kalefwaya ukuitunsula panshi nangula panshi nabashikapo ifyanaka, bushe ulemona kwati finshi filipo?
eng_translation: Have you seen the little boy is in the air, I wonder if he wants to fall or they have put something soft on the ground, what do you think is there?

bem_transcription: Mukumona kwandi ndemona ukutila pali fye insalu yeka yeka atemwa pali fye ishati lyakwe elyo nakasama nokuposa amaboko mu muulu.
eng_translation: I think there's a cloth or his shirt, he has opened his mouth and stretched his hands out.

bem_transcription: Yangu ye aka akamwana kalailuntula ububi elyo takafwele ne sheti ala fyalakalipa.
eng_translation: Oh my goodness! this child will fall and hurt himself so badly because he is shirtless.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ukulalipa fyalakalipa lelo ifyalakalipa sana makufi nga cakuti kafikilapo ne kufi Kabili cilepala ukuti nabakasansa amenshi.
eng_translation: Indeed it will hurt especially if he lands on his knees and it seems they have splashed some water on him.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo uko kaletolokela kuli icishiba pantu amenshi nayasabuka emulandu wine bonse babili bafulile amashati aba tulemone pacikope ic elo kunuma yabo kuli ing'anda.
eng_translation: There should be a pool here that's why water has splashed everywhere, that's why they are both shirtless and there's a house behind them.

bem_transcription: Boi mona..... mona uyu umulumendo alelya ifyakulya nomba naumona ifyo abilywule amenso kwati ni ulwa umuntu ulefwaya ukufwa.
eng_translation: My friend see this young man having food, he has rolled his eyes as though he is able to die.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo cimoneke kwati ifyakulwa ici nafiwama sana kumona fye fintu ale fyompa ku minwe yakwe naingisha iminwe yakwe itatu mukanwa nicikanga fye engishe ninwe yonse.
eng_translation: And it seems the food is very nice, it's clear from the way he is licking his fingers, he has put three fingers inside his mouth, I think he will put all five in.

bem_transcription: Elo ico ntemenwe pali ena nifi abeyele umushishi wakwe nauwama icine cine elyo ne shati afwele ilya fita nalyo naliwama.
eng_translation: I love the way has cut his hair, he looks so nice and also the black shirt he is wearing makes him even look better.

bem_transcription: Ne cikulwa cintu alimo cilemoneka icabusaka kumona fye pantu alelila tapali ne fiko ifili fyonse elyo apali ne nsalu iyakashika.
eng_translation: Even the building he is eating from is very clean, I can't see any dirt on the ground except a nice red cloth.

bem_transcription: umwana umulumendo naiminina nakwata utumishishi elyo utwafita sana natulala bwino lubali lumbi alelangisha necikumo.
eng_translation: A little boy is standing, he has short flat hair on his head and showing off his thumb.

bem_transcription: Nimbona elyo ukuboko kumbi naikata apali icishimbi afuma muciisha mukusamba emulandu wine imishishi shakwe shilalile
eng_translation: His other hand is resting on a metal rod, he is from ironing after bathing that's why he's hair looks this flat.

bem_transcription: Elyo nga nalolesha te eka ulimo muli ici cishiba kuli na umbi umunankwe ulesamba elo mu mutwe mwakwe nakakamo nakasalu akabuta. Bushe naumumona?
eng_translation: He is not the only one in this pool, there's also another person whose tied a white band in his head, have  you seen him?

bem_transcription: Nimumona ali kunuma ya uyu umwaice kabili cilepala ukuti mukalamaba sana ala icishiba cilemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: I have seen him, he is behind the young one and he is older, the pool looks really nice.

bem_transcription: Naulungika amenshi yalemoneka aya busaka elyo panshi pa menshi palemoneka makumbi makumbi ala aba bantu baleipakisha elyo balesamba
eng_translation: You are right, the pool looks so clean that it's blue at the bottom, these people are enjoying their swimming.

bem_transcription: Muntu wandi lolesha abantu abatemwana babili bale-enda mu musebo umwaume no mwanakashi elyo umwaume ena nafwala icampepo nabika na cimo mu mukoshi bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: My guy look at two lovers on the road, a man and a woman, the man is wearing a jersey and a scarf, have you seen them?

bem_transcription: Nimbamona bale-enda icipale elyo umukashi imishishi shakwe nashisalangana kabili shimbi nashisa pa menso pa mwakwe.
eng_translation: Impressive, I have seen them, the wife's hair all over some of it is on her face.

bem_transcription: Cishinka nakalimo icilenge ukutila shisalangene imishishi kuli icimwela icikalamba elo bonse aba cilepala ukwati tabamona bwino emulandu balebonfesha amagalashi.
eng_translation: That's true, it's because it's windy, and it could be they both have eye problems and that's why they are wearing specs.

bem_transcription: Nifyo fine walanda elyo kabili cilepala ukuti umulume wakwe naumfwa sana impepo emulandu wine afwalile ici icli mu mukoshi pakuti cilekafya umukoshi wakwe.
eng_translation: That's right, the husband seems to be very cold that's why he is wearing a scarf to keep warm.

bem_transcription: Ala iyi incende ilemoneka fye yalitalala mona bonse fye abaliko nafwala ifyampepeo nangu ni shitatya uleisa kunuma yabo nangula ali mukasuba nafwala icampepo.
eng_translation: This place just looks cold because everyone here is wearing warm clothes, even the man walking behind them is in a jersey because being under the sun.

bem_transcription: Iyee nashalamonapo icintu icakwata ibula ilikalamaba nge ci, ico umulumendo ekete ku minwe nakuba te mulumendo ni shitata uyu. Bushe naucimona?
eng_translation: I have never seen such a huge flower as this that the elderly man is holding, have you seen it?

bem_transcription: Nincimona boi nacikata ku minwe elyo fimbi nafifunda fye no kufunda ala fingi, nomba nshishibe nga libula inshi ili?
eng_translation: I have seen it my friend and they are alot others are blooming I wonder what flowers these are.

bem_transcription: Kwena ili ibula nalipalanako ne bula lya cibwabwa pantu nacikula we nemimonekele fye fintu cilemoneka.
eng_translation: It looks like pumpkin leaves because it has grown too big.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila iyi incende ni kumpanga takulemonekapo namayanda elyo mwaliba ifyani ifingi sana.
eng_translation: Another thing is that this is a bush with no houses in sight.

bem_transcription: Akabwa somone ifyo kalefunfuluka mutumenshi utwabela ku ncende ilemoneka kwati ni kumpanga. Bushe naukamona?
eng_translation: Come and see how it's throwing itself it water, have you seen it?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe iyi imbwa taileumfwa ukutalala ummm napapa pantu iyi incende intu yatalala icine cine ne imfula mabwe ili pamushili lelo yena ili mu menshi.
eng_translation: Doesn't this dog feel cold? Ummm because this place is cold with snow on the ground but the dog is playing in water.

bem_transcription: Awe iyo limbi taileumfwa ukutalala naitemwa ukulanyata fye mu menshi cilepala ukutila ileya ku ng'anda
eng_translation: No it doesn't feel cold, on the contrary it's happy to be steeping on water, maybe because it wants to enter the house.

bem_transcription: Elyo uku ni kumpanga fye kumona fye ifimuti ifiliko takulemonekapo na bantu takulemonakapo ne fyani kulemoneka fye utumuti utwaumauma.
eng_translation: This is a bush with no houses nor people in sight except dry trees.

bem_transcription: Iwe somone kuno abantu bali kumpanga elyo namayo alelanshanya nakamwana akamukashana akanono kabili akacepesha.
eng_translation: Come and see people in a bush with a woman talking to her little girl.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Naululungika nimbona fintu alemoneka nakwata utumishishi utwipi elyo namagalashi napapa ne chola munuma nafwala ne campepo nakalimo mwaume.
eng_translation: You are right, I can tell from the way he looks, he has short hair, glasses, carrying a bag, wearing an helmet, he should be a man.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka cimbi naco cakutila tabaliko beka aba kuli nabambi fye abemine akatalamukila bambi nabekalako elyo bambi bekele pafitenge nakalimo epo balala. Elyo kuli nutumisakuta.
eng_translation: That's right, he is not alone though, they are others at a distance, others are sited while others are laying down on material and they are also some hut houses.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo aleteya icangalo nomba cilemoneka kwati nawina. Boi mona ifyo asangalele naimya namaboko.
eng_translation: A young man is playing a game that he seems to have won, look at how he has his hands in the air my friend.

bem_transcription: Cilepala ukuti acilabutuka muli nakatanga walubilo elo acimfya kabili naimyako cimo kumaboko kumwakwe umuli umulilo.
eng_translation: He was racing and won the race, that's why he has has raised his hands this way.

bem_transcription: Nomba lolesha fye ifyo abantu bacankwile nangula ukusangalala ala bonse nabatemwa elyo bonse nicikanga fye balemukopa ifikope.
eng_translation: Look at how excited the people are for him, all of them want to take his picture.

bem_transcription: Ee nabatewma sana apo nacimfya muli nakatanga walubilo kabili bonse nabakwata ifyakukopelako bali ne nsansa icine .
eng_translation: Yes they are happy he's won, the race, they all have cameras and are very happy.

bem_transcription: Elyo ena alifye pakati ka musebo alebutuka nafwala ne fyabuta kunuma ya bantu abalemutamba kuli ne cikulwa icayemba bwino sana icabuta.
eng_translation: He is on the middle of the road dressed in white and behind the people watching him is a white, very beautiful building.

bem_transcription: Ahhh... Boi..... mona ifyo baseme aba babili ala nabacensa umwaume no mukashana. Bushe ulemona kwati finshi filengele bacite ifi?
eng_translation: Ahhhh! my friend look at how this man and woman are opening their mouths, what do you think is making them do this?

bem_transcription: Uku ukwasama tauikubelele mune cilepala ukutila baleimba ulwimbo nomba ulwimbo nalubasenda icakutila nabelilila ilyo baleimba.
eng_translation: it seems they are singing a song and they are taken by it that's why.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila ulu ulwimbo aba bantu balilutemwa kumona fye ifyo utwanwa twabo twaseme elo nga mwaume wena nalolesha na mu muulu natwala na menso ku mulu.
eng_translation: The other thing is that they really love this song, because the man is even facing the sky as he sings.

bem_transcription: Cishinka elyo baleimba bale-enda na mu musebo icakutila mulapita ne myotoka ishingi nga tabaposeleko amano kuti bapunkwa.
eng_translation: Then they are walking on the road as they are singing paying no attention to the fact that they can get bashed.

bem_transcription: Cishinka cimbi naco cakutila ifukulwa ifya uku fyaliyemba kabili mumbali mwaliba namatuka elyo kwaliba nefitali sana ifikulwa ifyayemba bwino icine cine.
eng_translation: Another thing is that they are lots of nice buildings, shops and other storey buildings that look so nice.

bem_transcription: Iyee mona abalelanda pali lamya umwana umukashana uwacepesha alikwata namatobo, bushe naumona fimbi fyo alemoneka?
eng_translation: Oh my goodness look whose the phone! A very little girl with cheeks, can you see how she looks like?

bem_transcription: Nimumona boi nakwata imishishi ishitali kunuma alyo pantanshi paba ishipi kabili alina alikwata namatobo elyo amenso yacepa.
eng_translation: I have seen she has long hair behind but has trimmed the front, she's fat and her eyes look very small.

bem_transcription: Ee cishinka nakalimo icalenga kwina ukutila amenso yesalike mona fye ifyo ukuboko kulemoneka ukwapamfuka ukwamaka kabili ukwaina
eng_translation: The eyes look like they are about to close because she's fat, just look at how her hand looks so big and full of energy.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe kuli na umbi fye shitata uwikele petebulo nakalimo belefye ku ncende imo mukulyako ifyakulya.
eng_translation: Behind him is another man sited on the table, perhaps they have gone to a restaurant to have some food.

bem_transcription: We ncende ulawama we incende iyakwata imisebo ikalamba kabili incende iyakwata imisebo ishaimbauka incende isuma sana iyi.
eng_translation: What a beautiful place, a place with broad roads, roads without potholes, this is a very beautiful place!

bem_transcription: Aw cishinka yaliyemba kumona fye ifyo kulemoneka kwaba ifikulwa fya ntunti ifingi kabili balifipenta bwino.
eng_translation: Indeed it's a very nice place full of storey buildings that are nicely painted

bem_transcription: Cishinka elyo mu musebo muli fye nama motoka beminikefye kwaba na saca ileipitila fye iyabuta ala motoka iyi isuma kuti natemwa ukuninamo.
eng_translation: That's true, they are some vehicles parked on the road with a white bus, this car is so nice that I would like to get on it.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ahhh icilengele ukutila konaike kwati paciba ubusanso apa emulandu wine ndemwena bakapokola bali kunuma na motoka yamo elyo natututu yabo.
eng_translation: Ahh, the reason why it's spoilt is because there was an accident and that's why they are cops behind the vehicle together with their things.

bem_transcription: Iye Incende ububi ni ncende yamusango shani iyi ai pantu tekutila wishibe nga cakutila ni mucimbusu nangula ni mu ng'anda. Bushe naumona?
eng_translation: What a bad place, what sort of place is this that you can not tell whether or not it's a toilet, have you seen it?

bem_transcription: Awe mune iyi ni ng'anda te cimbusu iyo nga cali cimbusu icibi nga calicepele kanshi iyi ni ng'anda te cimbusu iyo.
eng_translation: No this is a house and not a toilet, if it were the door would have been shorter but it's not, so clearly it's a house.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo mukutontonkanya kwandi ndemona kwati mwakubombela  fye umu pantu ndemona na shitata alebomba nafula ne shati nomba naumona ifili ku cimbumba ca ici cikuulwa?
eng_translation: I think this should be a workshop and the man inside is working while shirtless, have you seen what's on the wall of this building?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nga nishitata uwiminine pamwinshi cilemoneka nacimupapusha ukumona ifyo shitata alimukati alecita elyo umutenge wa ici cikuulwa wafyani.
eng_translation: The man standing at the entrance seems shocked to see the man inside is doing and the roof of this house is made of grass.

bem_transcription: Nga aba bantu bonse uku finshi balecita ai? Tekutila bafule umusango yu kwati nikumaliila nangu kwati balebafoleshapo fimo.
eng_translation: What are all these people here doing? They are too many as though they are at a feast or getting some payment.

bem_transcription: Awe mune, temalilila kuntu beshile iyo, cilepala ukuti beshile mukutambapo fimo atemwa nikucitesheni uko besa mukuninina.
eng_translation: No this is a party, they are here to watch something or about to get on a train at a train station.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo naulungika, kuti kwaba nikucitesheni, nangula kuti kwaba nikucangalo nangu kucibansa cafyangalo.
eng_translation: You might be right, he is at the train station, or maybe a s

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, lelo icishinka cakuti tatwishibe, nampo nga nikucibansa atemwa nikucangalo beshile mukutamba.
eng_translation: Yes you are right, but it's hard to tell, whether this is a sports field or they have come to watch a game.

bem_transcription: Elo incende naikwata ifikuulwa ifingi sana, kuli icikuulwa icilemoneka kwati bulalo, nakuba bulalo elo kwaba necilemoneka kwati cibansa camupila.
eng_translation: This place is full of trees and the building looks like a bridge, it infact is a bridge then there's  a stadium

bem_transcription: Abana abakashana abacepesha umushinku balewamya kabalwe. nomba bushe uyu kabalwe mukalamba nangu munoono?
eng_translation: Very little girls are cleaning a horse. Is it a big or small horse?

bem_transcription: Uyu kabalwe munoono sana, pantu bakabalwe balakula icakuti balalepa nokulepa, nomba uyu kabalwe mwana.
eng_translation: It is a small horse because horses usually are tall and big but this one is small.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, uyu kabalwe mwana, elyo aba abana balemusakamana, cilepala kwati kuli ifyo balemuliishako nangu ifyo bamupeele pakutila benga-angala namasako yakwe.
eng_translation: Yes you are right and he is being cared for by kids, and it seems they are feeding it something so that they can play with it's fur.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nakalimo ici icilemoneka ica mawilo ica makumbi makumbi cikocikala elyo iyi incende isuma icine cine pantu kwaliba ifimuti elyo nolunkoto.
eng_translation: Perhaps the blue wheeled thing is an ox-cart, this is a beautiful place full of trees and a lawn.

bem_transcription: Boi Mona imbwa ifyo ifundumane pakupepeka ifyuni bushe naumona? Bushe yalakumaninsha ukwikata ifyuni?
eng_translation: My friend look at how the dog is chasing after the birds, will it manage to catch any bird?

bem_transcription: Tekuti ikumanishe boi pa malundu wakutila ifi ifyuni filapupuka fyaya apatali icine cine nayo imbwa nayo nga cakuti yalikwete amapindo kuti yapupuka kabili yaiakatapo na cimo.
eng_translation: No it won't manage because these birds fly so high, without a doubt if the dog had wings it would also fly to catch one.

bem_transcription: Naulungika elyo umu ni mupanga fye kanshi imbwa ilelepepeka fye umwela nakalimo naipena.
eng_translation: You are right this is inside a bush and the dog is just chasing after the wind, perhaps it's gone crazy.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka elyo nintemwa ifyo aya amasako yambwa iyi yaba. Iyi imbwa yalikwata amasakao aya fita kabili kumaboko kwaba utwafitulukila
eng_translation: I love this dog's fur, it had black fur and has brown on it's hands.

bem_transcription: Ummm kwena ba mayo abacikoloci bakalamba kumona fye ifyo bakwete iminkono pa menso elyo nefyo fye balemoneka pa cinso . Bushe ulemona kwati kuti bakwata imyaka inga?
eng_translation: Wow! this is an old lady, it's clear from the wrinkles on her face and how she looks, how old do you think she is?

bem_transcription: Aba kuti bakwata umwanda umo ekutila 100 kumona fye ifyo balemoneka ukutila nabakota icine cine.
eng_translation: She should be 100, it's clear from her looks.

bem_transcription: Ah cishinka kwena ukulila nabalila aba bamayo pa calo elyo mu mutwe mu myabo nakwata necitambala icafita icifimbile umushishi
eng_translation: She's really enjoyed her life, she's wearing a black head covering her hair

bem_transcription: Elyo cilepala ukuti nabomfwa sana impepeo kumona fye ifyampepe fintu bafwele ubwingi elyo kabili baletungapo cimo awe mwandi nabekala inshiku ishingi pa calo.
eng_translation: It should be very cold because she's wearing a jersey and many others clothes while she's knitting, she's her life!

bem_transcription: Icibumba bashintilielpo nacikwata ne milale nakalimo cakale sana cilefwaya no kuwa namu ncende bekele ala tamuli no lubuto mulemoneka fye umwafita nakalimo bushiku.
eng_translation: The wall they are leaning against has cracks, it's about to fall, it should an old building, and this place they are in looks dark without power in it.

bem_transcription: Iyi motoka ili palwendo elyo muli abantu nangula abantu balimo tabafulile sana. Bushe naumona fimbi ifilecitika muli iyi motoka?
eng_translation: This vehicle is on a journey with not lots of people in it, have you seen what else is happening inside?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune ikalamba sana kabili ifipuna fyali pusana fimbi filelolele kuno elyo fimbi filoseshe kumbi elyo bonse abali muli iyi motoka nabakwata ifyakucita abene.
eng_translation: I have my friend, it is big and has chairs facing opposite directions and everyone inside is doing different things.

bem_transcription: Cishinka aba bantu balemoneka nokwishibana tabaishibana kumona fye tabelelanshanya nokulanshanya cila muntu aletininka fye lamya yakwe.
eng_translation: These people are strangers to one another that they are not even chatting, each one is on their phone.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda cila muntu aposele fye amano pali lamya yakwe elo nga ni aba abali pantanshi nabekala akatamukila  kwati tabalefwaya fye no kulanshanya.
eng_translation: That's true, each one is on their phone, the ones in front don't want to chat either and are sited apart.

bem_transcription: Tekutila balanshenye kwati balishibana emulandu bekalile akatamukula elyo ifipuna fya iyi saca fisuma icine cine kabili balifusunga ubusaka.
eng_translation: They can't be chatting when they are strangers to each other that's why they are sited apart. The chairs inside the vehicles are nice and well kept.

bem_transcription: We munandi lolekesha ifyo uyu namayo alemoneka, alemoneka kwati mukashana pamenso lelo ifyakufwala fintu afwele naumona ifyo filemoneka?
eng_translation: My friend have you seen this one here that looks like a lady, have you noticed the clothes she's wearing?

bem_transcription: Nifimona filemoneka bwino sana kabili nafimulinga nokumulinga nafimuwamina kabili no mwine musuma.
eng_translation: I have seen them, they look nice and are fitting her well.

bem_transcription: Aha iwe naiwe tawaishiba ukulolesha efimuwamine mona fye ifyo akasote kakwe kalemoneka kalemumwenesha kwati mukote icine cine.
eng_translation: Really my friend? This is what you call nice? Just look at her hat, it makes her look old.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Naulungika elyo ifi fintu alepikula alashitisha ifyo cilemoneka mwe pantu mu minwe yakwe nakwata neco alepikula icakashika mwapita no twamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: You are right, it seems she sells what's she's knitting, at the moment she's knitting something red and blue.

bem_transcription: Umukashana naiminina panse ya cikulwa kabili alecitapo fimo nomba boi nga walolesha ifyo alecita uyu kuti watila ni finshi ifi pantu ine nshilemona!
eng_translation: A lady is sited outside doing something I'm not so sure of, what do you think she's doing my friend?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ee cishinka elyo ici cine cimashine cilemoneka kwati cililampi icikulu icine cine na mu miniwe yakwe uyu umukashana nakwata icakukopelako.
eng_translation: That's true, this machine looks like a huge lamp, and she has a camera in her hands.

bem_transcription: Cilepala ukuti ici cimashini bacibomfya nga cakuti ulefwaya ukumona fimo mu muulu, kumona fye ifyo cilemoneka atemwa ilyo ulefwaya ukumona intanda ubushiku.
eng_translation: This machine is a telescope, it is used to view stars.

bem_transcription: Elyo incende iyi ilemoneka kwati ya mpili mpili pantu naikwata utumilundu nakulya ukulepita ba motoka kuli umusebo uukalamba.
eng_translation: This is a hilly terrain and a road on the other side full of vehicles.

eng_translation: This place is full of vehicles, they have filled up the road, the car in front is very nice

bem_transcription: Nimbona fye ishi imyotoka shili ishingi sana kabili nashiminina icilepilibula ukutila kuli bakapokola ku ntanshi abaleshitungulula uko shilingile ukuya.
eng_translation: These are lots of vehicles that are parked and there's a cop in front directing them on where to go.

eng_translation: They are countable people on the but lots of vehicles on it

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana bakupenda fye icilepilibula ukuti tabapita pita sana uku kuntu ukupita imyotoka elo nga ni iyi motoka iili apa yena ilemoneka iya mutuntula konse
eng_translation: Indeed they are few, there even a yellow vehicle here.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco fikulwa, ala iyi incende yalikwata ifikulwa ifingi kabili ifitali ifyayemba ifyakulwa bwino sana.
eng_translation: The other thing is that this place is full of beautiful storey buildings that are well structured.

bem_transcription: Ala uyu shitata alemoneka alishiba ukwimba elyo no kulisha icilimba ca nsale kumona fye fintu akete icilimba mu minwe yakwe icilelangila fye ukutila mukali
eng_translation: This man is a good singer and guitarist, it's clear from the way he is holding his stringed instrument that he is a professional.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana alishibisha kale ayamba kabili alishiba ifya kulisha banjo elyo aleimba pacisebele.
eng_translation: Yes he is actually an excerpt through experience, he knows how to play the guitar and is  singing on the stage.

bem_transcription: Ne cisebele ifyo fye cilemoneka kuti calenga umuntu afwaisha ukwimba kabili kuti calenga umuntu aimba bwino mona fye ifyo cilemoneka.
eng_translation: Even the way the stage looks can motivate someone to sing well.

bem_transcription: Balicikula bwino kabili balaciwamya cila bushiku emulandu wine cilemoneka ica busaka kabili icisuma. Bushe naumona fimbi ifili apa?
eng_translation: It is well built and cleaned everyday that's why is looks so good and clean, what else can you see?

eng_translation: On one of the stairs on the stage are drums, a sound system and a microphone that he is using to sing.

eng_translation: What a cute child! Though it's hard to tell whether it's a boy or girl, what do you think is the sex of the child?

eng_translation: It's clear from his face and hair that he is a boy because if he was a girl his hair would be showing outside the hat.

bem_transcription: Nakalamo naulungika elo uyu umwana wakayena nakwata nomupila mu minwe ala umupila waliyemba walikwata amalangi ayo natewma ifyabuta ne fya makumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: You might be right, he is holding a cute blue and white ball in his hands.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana elo uyu wine umupila ekete ukalamba icine cine icakutila nangu engasukusa kuti aya nawena.
eng_translation: That's trues, the ball is so big that if he tried to throw it, he would fall down with it.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila uku kuncende bali kuli icishiba pantu kuli fye no muntu katwishi nga nishitata uufwele amagalashi yafiita uushikwete ne shati nakalimo afuma mukusamba.
eng_translation: Another thing is that there's a pool in this place with a shirtless man perhaps coming from swimming in the pool.

bem_transcription: Elyo nomba twasanga ifintu natemwa sana boi, batutuutu elyo aba batutuutu, basume cine cine kabili batali, monafye ifyo balemoneka.
eng_translation: Now this is what I love! motorbikes, they are so beautiful and high, just look at that.

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi ala nabafula uku kuntu, kabili abaninine pali batuukutuuku bacikalamba kabili abakwate mwemfu ishingi kabili uyu tuukutuuku mukalamba kaili mutali.
eng_translation: I have seen them, they are alot and the ones on them are elderly people with beards. This motorbike is big and high.

bem_transcription: Ndesubila ukutila yamutengo nokuba pantu tekuti umuntu akwate tutuututu iyawame fi.
eng_translation: I'm so sure it's expensive because a person can't own such a nice motorbike

eng_translation: The people on the motorbikes are all dressed the same way, they are all in black clothes, shoes and helmets.

bem_transcription: Ala aba bantu efyo bafwala nififine, balibelesha ukufwala ifyafiita nangula nakukaba mona fye nabafwala nefyampepo.
eng_translation: These people are always dressed this way even when it's hot they are are wearing jerseys.

bem_transcription: Kwena abantu bambi bamipuulwe kabili bamisamwe tabaishiba ifyo bafwaya mubumi, bushe naumona ifyo uyu umulumendo alecita?
eng_translation: Some people are careless and wreck less as though without purpose, have you noticed what this young man is doing?

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: Because if the food fell he would have to starve, he is clueless about he wants in life, he might be unemployed that's why he is playing with food this way.

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: This place is well built, there's even a small train that carries few people across, do you think it's an actual train?

eng_translation: No my friend, I think it just looks like a train, but it is passing through rail tracks.

eng_translation: Yes you are right, these are rails, there's another yellow similar to this one coming, have you seen it?

eng_translation: Yes I have, it is passing through the same track as the other, and it seems this one parked here has a horse in front have you seen it?

eng_translation: I have seen, he is shirtless and has tied some things on top of his car, it seems he is heading to the beach.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: She's very excited, the mom is pouring some water on the horse as she scrubs it.

eng_translation: That's true, what she's using to scrub it is made of wood and she's holding another bigger scrub in her hand. This little girl has long hair

eng_translation: But you know, the thing that has amazed me is the little boy that's sited doing nothing and watching them scrub the horse, this is just silly.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: He is very clean and pays attention to his job, and clearly obeys that rule that he needs to be clean at work.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: What is this young man doing, because I can't seen anything on the ground can you?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: She's on a skateboard, she's skating and this is at night.

bem_transcription: Um, uyu umulumendo aletiinya, alyonda, nafwale shati elyo ishati lileshelela kwati lyamishingo, mona boi ai.
eng_translation: This man has scared me, he is this slim! He is so slim that even his shirt doesn't fit as though it belonged to someone that's late, just look at this!

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: Why so many people? What's happening here? look at this my friend maybe you can know what's going on.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
Nakalimo kuli ifyangalo fyakucimfyanya kuncende yi, pantu abantu tekutila bafule umusango yu, elyo naumona ifyo bafwele?
eng_translation: There should be game because people just can't be gathered this way, have you seen how they are dressed?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, aba abensha batuukutuuku bafwele ifyakufwala ifyafiita nga filya fine fyo bafwala ilyo baleensha, elyo kabili nabeminika nabatuukutuuku babo.
eng_translation: I have seen the ones on motorbikes are dressed in black, the way people dress when they are about ride and have parked their motorbikes.

eng_translation: These motorbikes are big and nice and they are people of different ages both young and old

bem_transcription: Hahaha, iye, ah. boi mona uyu umulumendo elo nishitata fye, bushe ulemona kwati alibafye bwino? Mona ifyo alecita.
eng_translation: Hahahaha! Look at this man, do you think he is sane? Look at what he is doing.

eng_translation: Where is he? Oh! I have seen him, he is not even feeling shy about taking a picture while bathing with foam on his body.

eng_translation: He is inside a pool swimming in the afternoon, he doesn't even know that someone's taking a picture of him, he is wearing blue shorts.

eng_translation: I have seen how short the shorts are, he is very hairy, I doubt he has seen the people on top.

bem_transcription: Kwena afwile fye ukubamona pantu balifye kunuma yakwe, monafye apo abikile ifyakufwala, ifyakufwala fili fye mupepi napo bekele, nakalimo bali nankwe.
eng_translation: I have he has seen them because they are right behind him, just look at his clothes near them he should be with them

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: There's a huge light shinning on them in this place, they are in a bush and I can see something that looks like a vehicle.

eng_translation: My friend look at this body builder, he has muscles even though he is working, you admire him right?

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: He is working outside his shop and it seems he is fixing something because they are metal bars behind him.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ali pamulimo kabili nafwala icakuicinga kumutwe, elyo cilya icilemoneka icakatapakatapa cakubomfya ilyo alenina pamuulu.

eng_translation: I have seen. This young man is falling into water in the pool and this pool looks deep.

eng_translation: If it's the way you have said that it is a deep pool and he can't hurt himself then so be it. And this pool is surrounded by metal bars and nets.

eng_translation: I love the red and white top and down clothes he is wearing and this place looks very cold.

bem_transcription: Ukutalala kwena yalitalala kumona fye ifyo imfula mabwe iingi iponene panshi, kabili uku kwine kwabe ifimuti ifingi kabili ifyatintinkana.
eng_translation: It is very cold as can be seen by the amount of snow on the ground, and there are a lot of trees that are planted close to each other in this place.

eng_translation: Yes I have seen what they are doing, they are working and are on top tying metals, perhaps they want to make pillars.

bem_transcription: Kumona fye ifyo ifishimbi bafituntinkene cilepala ukuti balefwaya ukukula icikuulwa icatunti ishikalamba sana.
eng_translation: Just looking at how the metals have been piled up, its like they want to build a storey building.

eng_translation: Won't these people fall? Look where they have climbed and what they are doing, they don't even have ropes to hold them if they fell.

bem_transcription: Awe mune taulolekesha nabakakako fimo mumusana elyo bakaka nakucishimbi ica kutila nangu balefwaya ukupona icishimbi kuti cabafwako ukwabula ukufika panshi.
eng_translation: No my friend you are not seeing properly. They have tied something around their waists and tied it to one of the metals so that if they were to fall, the metal will hold them so they don't reach the ground.

eng_translation: And he is in the forest because there are only tall trees and grass around.

eng_translation: And this place where he came to throw trash is in the forest as seen from the many trees and the grass.

bem_transcription: Boi, bushe pamyenu mwalitekapo imbwa yamusango yu? Awe teti muteke imwe kaili imbwa mwateka pano teti ifikeko nokofikako, kumonafye ifyo ilemoneke yi imbwa ikali bushe naumona?
eng_translation: My friend do you have such a dog at your place? No you can't. And the dog you have is no where near this one. Just see how it's looking. have you seen?

bem_transcription: Ici icibwa boi ala cikali, kuti natemwa ukucikwatako, monafye ifyo cilemoneka amenso elo monafye ifyo caaseeme kukanwa, calikwata akanwa akafiita.
eng_translation: This dog is very fierce my friend, I'd love to have one.Just see how it's eyes are looking and how it has opened it's black mouth.

bem_transcription: Nga cakuti nalikuswakishe iyi imbwa boi teti ubutuke napatali ninshi naikwikata, kumonafye ifyo imishe amatwi elo namenso nayakashika.
eng_translation: If I sent this dog after you my friend you cant even reach far before it catches you. Just look at how it's raising its eyes and those red eyes.

bem_transcription: Ala ici icibwa cilemoneka bwino, amasako yaciko yaliyemba kabili ayatelela, bushe naumona umuntu uwiminine kunuma yaciko?
eng_translation: This dog looks very good, with beautiful smooth fur. Have you seen the one standing behind it?

bem_transcription: Nimumona, naiminina kabili nafwala itoloshi ilyamakumbi makumbi abikapo nakabuuta tatwishibe nga mwaume atemwa mwanakashi, elo kuncende kuntu bali kusume cine cine.
eng_translation: I have seen and this person is standing and wearing a blue trousers and a white top. we don't know if this person is male or female. And this place is very beautiful.

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: This woman has opened her mouth very wide and without a doubt she is singing because you can't open your mouth like that.

bem_transcription: Cishinka aleimba mune kumonafye ifyo aseeme kukanwa, kaili necilelangilila ukuti aleimba, kumonafye umulumendo ico alelisha.
eng_translation: Yes she is singing because of how she is opening the mouth and you can also tell that she is singing because of what that young man is playing.

eng_translation: A young man is playing a big flute and has blown his cheeks and made an angry face as if he has eaten something bitter.

bem_transcription: Elo uulelisha umutolilo naputisha icine cine, icakuti umutolilo ulefumya neciunda, elo uuleimba nafwala indeleshi iisuma iyakashika.
eng_translation: The one playing the flute has blown with all his might and it is producing large sound. The one singing is wearing a beautiful red dress.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ala ulu ulupili lwaliibela, takwabapo nolupili ulwakwata amalangi yabili, mukati lulemoneka ulwamakumbi makumbi elo kunse lulemoneka ulwabuuta, we lupili ulawama we!
eng_translation: This mountain is special. I haven't even seen a mountain like this before with two colors, blue one the middle and white outside. What a beautiful mountain!

bem_transcription: Elo ulu wline ulupili lwalingila ingila, nshishibe bwino nacimpesha amano ukumonapo ulupili lwamusango yu.
eng_translation: This mountain has a lot of depressions and it has blown my mind.

bem_transcription: Elo paisula ifimabwe, naumona ukutila pamuulu walupili epalemoneka apabuuta buuta? Elo ngatwaisa munshi umu amabwe yalemoneka fye ayafiituluka filya
eng_translation: And it is full of rocks. Have you seen that the mountain top looks whitish? When we come down the rocks looks blackish.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: Man come and watch a fight! These people are fighting. Well I don't know whether they are fighting or playing. explain for me.

bem_transcription: Aba bantu bonse babili baleisambilisha fye ifyakulwo lubuli ulwakubomfya bapanga, nomba mona, bushe naumona ifyo bafwele?
eng_translation: These people are training how to fight with swords. But have you seen what they are wearing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune, bonse bafwele fimo fine kaili ne nsapato shimo shine, bafwele bakaputula uwafiita babikapo nakapamuulu akabuuta elyo bafwala nefyakucinga kumenso.
eng_translation: I have seen. They are wearing similar things. They are both wearing black shorts with white tops and they have something to protect their faces.

bem_transcription: Cishinka, elo muncende umo baleisambilisisha incende iyi iisuma, yabusaka, panshi fye ala napabeeka.
eng_translation: Very true. And the place they are training in is very nice and the floor is very shiny.

bem_transcription: Ala napabeeka icine cine, elo uyu umbi naima mumuulu nasonteka umunankwe ulupanga, elo umbi nankwe nasunsumana nankwe nasonteka umunankwe ulupanga.
eng_translation: It is very shiny, and this one is high up in the air and has pointed his sword on his friend, and the friend is squatting and pointing his sword on the friend too.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi, aba bantu balitemwana, elo kunuma kwa tractor nababikako nafimo ifilemoneka kwati fisabo elo fimbi filemoneka kwati fimasaka, nomba mona ifyo iyo tractor yacepa.
eng_translation: I have seen that these people love each other and behind the tractor they have put something looking like a fruit and other things are looking like bags. Now looks at how small this tractor has become.

eng_translation: Yes this tractor is very small and they have even to all fit in, but the young woman is just swinging behind.

bem_transcription: Elo epo balepita nipakati kamusebo, elo kumbali uku kuli ichuulu elyo nalubali kumbi kuli ichuulu, elo uku eko bafumine ukulemoneke mpanga.
eng_translation: They are passing in the middle of the road and there are hills on both sides of the road and there is a forest where they are coming from.

bem_transcription: Abanakashi bacikalamba bane nabatantama mumulongo, elyo bambi baloleshe kumbi elyo bambi nababifya pamenso bushe nawishiba ifibasakamike?
eng_translation: Four older women are in a line, and others are looking elsewhere and others have frowned their faces. Do you know what's worrying them?

bem_transcription: Awe boi tekutila njishibe icilelenga ukutila balemoneka ababulanda ifi, monafye ifyo uyu shitata uuli mukubalilapo alemoneka nabifya pamenso icine cine nakaka ne nkanshi.
eng_translation: my friend I can't know what's worrying them. Just see how this man in front is looking with an angry face and a frown.

bem_transcription: Walungika, teti wishibe, naine wine nshishibe ifilebasakamika, cilepala ukuti ifilebasakamika fyamubumi bwabo atemwa munshinku bafikilepo, bushe naumona umuntu uulelanda palamya?
eng_translation: You are right we can't know, I also don't know what's worrying them. It's like what's worrying them is about their life, or their age. Have you seen this person speaking on the phone?

bem_transcription: Nimumona uyu uulelanda pali lamya nafwala, elo kafoni alebomfya kanoono icine cine, uukonkelepo nankwe nafwala akasote ena kukanwa acitile kwati alefyola abantu
eng_translation: I have seen the one on the phone is wearing a hat and he is using a very small phone. The one on the phone is also wearing a hat and has smirked.

bem_transcription: Elo umbi uwikalile kumpela uku nabika ukuboko kwakwe kumutwe, ala ifibasakamike tatwishibe elo kuncende kuntu bali kulemoneka ukusuma sana.
eng_translation: The one on the far end has put his hands on the head. I don't know what is worrying them. The place where they are looks very nice

eng_translation: This person my friend looks like a soldier or he is going to a fight. Have you seen what he is wearing and the sword he has behind him?

bem_transcription: Nimbona nakwata ulupanga, cilupanga? Awe boi mona telupanga kasembe aka akatwa aka sana.
eng_translation: I have seen, he has a very big sword. look closely it's not a sword but a very sharp axe.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka balemoneka kwati balesefyapo fimo, pantu nabafwala kwati imifwalile iyakale ifyo balefwala abakukale elyo naumona aka akamwaice ifyo kafwele.
eng_translation: Yes it seems like they are celebrating something because they are wearing like people of old used to wear. Have you seen what this child is wearing?

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: This dog! Have you seen how it has jumped like a lion? Maybe it is a lion. Is that really a dog?

bem_transcription: Iwe nobe ni mbwa na menso  yenu yalifwa mulefwayako ifyakuti mwingalolekesha bwino naitoloka fye bwino bwino fye nabaibikila apakutoloka. Lolekesha Bwino.
eng_translation: Yes it is a dog! Your eyes do not work, you should find something to help you see. This dog has just jumped nicely because they put a bar for it. Look closely.

bem_transcription: Awe nalolekesha cacinshupa ukushinikisha ukutila ni mbwa lintu nacimona ifyo yacitoka nomba nimbwa nimbona na kanwa no tu matwi utunono no tu menso.
eng_translation: Yes I have see. It was hard to believe that it is a dog after I saw how much it jumped. But I have seen that it is a dog because of the mouth and the small ears and eyes.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: But how can you wear such a jersey when it is this hot. Look at what this your friend is wearing.

eng_translation: No this is weed working because a normal person can't wear this jersey when it is this hot. Just look at him, he is even wearing a hat because of the sun.

eng_translation: My friend you should be playing nicely. That is not how you play. How can you be threatening your friend with a hammer like that? Have you seen the mouth of the one being threatened?

bem_transcription: Ummmmm! Ni mbona boi ala natina icine cine nabifya na kukanwa elo ayasama cilepala kwati napunda ku mwenso.
eng_translation: Uhm! I have seen and they are very scared. It seems they are screaming out of fear.

bem_transcription: Nimbona fye cilepala ukuti abana nakwe bacilamwesha fye ukujmona nga kuti apunda atemwa efyo engacicita nga cakuti balimweseshe ukumuma sando.
eng_translation: I have seen. It seems the friends were just playing with him to see his reaction when they threaten him with a hammer.

bem_transcription: Nomba boi naumona ifyo umunabo uyu uli kunuma alebalolesha? Mona Lolekesha!
eng_translation: But have you seen how this friend of theirs behind is? Look closely.

bem_transcription: Nimbona fye muntu wandi nakwe nakwatako icela ico ekete muminwe yakwe alelolea fye umunakwe nga apwisha nakwe amubolemo.
eng_translation: I have seen that he also has a metal in his hands. He is just waiting for the friends to finish so that he also hits him with it.

eng_translation: My friend, I have never seen such a dog in my life. Just look at how fat it is, it is well fed an has a huge mouth. Just look at the tail and look at it's colour.

eng_translation: Yes I have seen. It looks very big and very nice. Just looks at the cheeks and they head, it looks like a small cow.

eng_translation: Yes you are right and this dog has something in the neck where they connect it's leash. But have you seen how the place is looking?

bem_transcription: Isuma mune kabili balaiwamya bwino kabili balibyala no tufyani utulemoneka utusuma kabili utwalelema.
eng_translation: This place is very nice and well mantained and it has green beautiful grass.

eng_translation: I have seen this man. He is just lying there looking sad and bending in the sun. Have you seen him?

eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: If we look closely, this person could be mad but they just bathe him and wash his clothes for him that is why he is looking like this.

eng_translation: No he is not mad. Just looks at how he is looking. Though the beard makes him look like a mad person he is not, there is just something bothering him.

eng_translation: I have seen this young woman, she is holding the microphone in one hand as she is singing and the other hand is on her chest. Maybe she is singing a sad song.

eng_translation: It is true that is what it looks like and they are helping her sing using guitars and stringed instruments.

eng_translation: There is a young man near her young women who are playing instruments, but the young man has something he is playing with his mouth. Have you seen

eng_translation: I have seen and his instrument is producing a very nice sound and this building they are in is very nice and very well painted.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING

eng_translation: This child is very young but very intelligent. Others would have been crying with their mouths open but it is just quiet and happy.

eng_translation: It is happy and they have given it a yellow smilling doll to play with. Have you seen?

eng_translation: I have seen this doll and it even has missing teeth, and I love how that chair is looking.

bem_transcription: Ala baliupanga bwino uyu umupando ulemoneka bwino kabili baliposeleko sana amano kabili ne ndalama baposelepo pakushita shali shingi.
eng_translation: This chair is beautiful and was well made. The creater of it must have put in a lot of effort and the who who but just have spent a lot of money on it.

bem_transcription: Boi somone kwaba incede isha yemba kabili ishisuma icakutila nga walileko kuti wamona kwati uli mu paradaise soimwene we mwine.
eng_translation: My friend come and see. There are beautiful places on this earth such that if you went there you would think you are in paradise. Come and see for yourself.

bem_transcription: Ala iyi incende isuma icine cine elyo akamwana akamwaice akamukashana nakekala nakapeteka na molu kalelilapo na fimo ifyapala kwati ni ice cream.
eng_translation: This place is nice and a young girl is seated, folding her legs and is eating something that looks like ice cream.

bem_transcription: Cishinka naikala opo babumba icabulungana elo pambali yakwe pali cimo icakwenseshako umwana kabili mukati muli umwana pantu utumolu tulemoneka.
eng_translation: It is true she is sitting on something round and there is a plem on her side with a baby in it because the feet are visible.

bem_transcription: Ee uyu umwana umukashana uwacaice eo bashilile umwana uyu babikile muli aka akakwensha nyina alemoneka kwati euyu ulekopa icikope.
eng_translation: Yes they have left this baby in the plem with this young girl this woman taking pictures looks like is the mother.

bem_transcription: Kabili uku kwine ku ncede mukati mwilinga muli abantu elo panse apekele uyu umwaice apabulungana nababikapo ne beseni umuli amaluba aya mutuntula.
eng_translation: Inside the fence of this place, there are people. And outside where this child is on the round thing, there is also a dish with yellow flowers in it.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Iyeee kushusha icitekwa ifi nangula ifyani tafyafina tefyo afwile alonga nafifulisha elyo twabikapo no mubili wakwe awe kwena icinama nacinaka.
eng_translation: This is abusing the animal. Even though grass is not heavy this is not how you are supposed to load. It is too much. And then we add his weight on top of that. The animal is tired.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana nacinaka kumona fyue ifyo cikonteme nacikontaminina panshi elyo cile-enda kutali uko bafumine mune.
eng_translation: Yes it is tired, you can tell by the way it is walking while bending down. They came Frome somewhere far.

bem_transcription: Elyo uyu kabalwe musuma nicifye balemusunga uwafiko alikwata namasko ayabuta ala nalitemwa  uyu kabalwe wamusango ifi
eng_translation: This horse is very nice it's just that it is kept dirty. I love such horses with white fur.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Muntu wandi somone abashacindika ubumi uyu muntu cilepala ukuti tatemwa ubumi bwakwe aleangala ne mboo elyo iyi imbo-o ikali icine cine
eng_translation: My friend come and see someone who has no respect for life. it seems he doesn't love live because he is playing with a boo and this boo looks fierce.

bem_transcription: Nimbona uyu muntu tatemwa ubumi bwakwe nomba nakalimo alisambilishiwa ifyakwangala ne ci icinama pantu kuti camukontola amafupa.
eng_translation: I have seen that this person doesn't respect life. Maybe he had been trained to play with this animal otherwise it would break his bones.

bem_transcription: Tekuti tuapape boi cilepala ukuti uyu muntu kale batendeka ukwangala ne ci icinama kabili baciba mucibansa emo bacilapepekana neiyi imboo.
eng_translation: We can't be surprised. It looks like this person has been playing with this animal for a long time and they were in a ground that is where they were playing with the animal from.

bem_transcription: Nomba naumona ifyo afwele iwe? Ah! Filesekesha we! Mona akatoloshi ifyo kekete kwati kamukashana.
eng_translation: But have you seen what the person is wearing? it is funny. The trousers is tight like it is for a woman.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Boi somone shitata ifyo aleposa amasha, nakontama kabili nashana icine cine, icakutila umukashana naiminina no mwana muli pulemu kabili alelolesha.
eng_translation: Come and see this man. He has bent and is dancing such that a woman with the child in the plem is watching.

bem_transcription: Takonteme fye uyu shitata lolekesha nakwata icilimba ca nsale muminwe yakwe ico alelisha elyo kukanwa nakwata nacimbi ico alelisha icapala pinchu.
eng_translation: This man is not just bending but also has a stringed instrument in his hands that he is playing and he is playing something that looks like a whistle in his mouth.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana elo napapako nacimo mumusana mumwakwe elo nafwala akasote, mumbali yakasote muli fwaka.
eng_translation: It is true and he has something around his waist and is wearing a hat that has a cigarette on the side.

bem_transcription: Elo iyi incende nakufula abantu icine cine nangula cakutila bushiku, abantu baletamba aba balelishe filimba.
eng_translation: There is a lot of people in this place even though it is in the night. People are watching these playing instruments.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili uyu shitata uuleshana apa tali eka ali naumbi uulelisha icilimba ca nsaale, nafwala namagalashi ayakalamba.
eng_translation: This man dancing is not alone but is with another playing a stringed instrument and is wearing big glasses.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo bane bali pamulimo kabili nabafwala ifilelangilila ukuti bali pamulimo, ekutila ifyamacungwa macungwa ifyo bafwele kumuulu kabili nabafwala nefyakucinga kumutwe bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: Four men are working and are w=earing orange worksuits and they are wearing helmets.

bem_transcription: Nimbamona aba bashitata elyo balebutukila ukuya mukwafwilisha uyu uuli muli motoka pantu motoka yakwe ilefwaya ukufulamuka, nakalimo naifulamuka nokufulamuka.
eng_translation: I have seen these men and they are looking like they are rushing to help the one in the vehicle because it looks like it flipped.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ee, nakalimo uyu namutekenya bacilacimfyanya, nomba umusebo tawaba bwino, mwliba ifilindi ifingi elo itaila limo lyaingila mucilindi.
eng_translation: It looks like this driver was in a race but the road is has potholes so one tire entered into a dich.

bem_transcription: Nshishibenga cakutila balakumanisha ukutinta uyu namutekenya, pantu alemoneka fye uwafine cine cine, ala calabipa nga bafilwa.
eng_translation: I'm not sure if they will manage to pull out this driver because he looks heavy, and it will be bad if he died.

bem_transcription: Umukashana uwamishishi ishitali alesheta cungamu kabili panuma yakushete aiputa, bushe naumona?
eng_translation: A young woman is chewing gum and blowing it. Have you see?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimumona uyu umukashana nakwata cungamu elyo nakwata ne mishishi ishitali sana ala alemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: Yes I have.  This woman has gum and she also had long hair and she looks amazing.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Iyo, umu ali nimumuputule icibumba cilemoneka icabuuta kabili icayemba, takuliko nefiko ifili fyonse.
eng_translation: No, This is inside a room. The wall looks white and clean with no dirt on it.

bem_transcription: Ca cine, cilemoneka ukutila alitemwa fye ukusheta cungamu elyo ilyo asheta alitemwa ukupuuta cungamu.
eng_translation: It is true, it looks like she likes chewing gum and blowing it.

bem_transcription: Uyu umufyashi umwanakashi alikose cine cine pabafyashi bonse, bushe naumona ifyo bacitile kubanabo bakwe?
eng_translation: This female parent is the strongest of all the parents. Have you seen seen what her fellow parents have done?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, elo nimpoopa pantu naimya abana bakwe bonse babili pamuku umo akamulumendo nakamukashana nakalimo aba nibampundu.
eng_translation: I have seen and she has a lot of muscle because she is lifting both the children at once, the boy and the girl. Maybe these two are twins.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo abantu nabafula abali uku, nabafule icine cine, nakalimo nabayapo mukutamba fimo pantu kuntashi kulemoneka kwati kuli icisebele.
eng_translation: They are lots of people here, it's like they are watching something because there seems to be a stage in front.

bem_transcription: Cishinka ala kuli umulongo wabantu cilepala ukutila kuli umo uwishile uuli pacisebele eulya umwene bakambatike pafipepala.
eng_translation: It is true there is a crowd of people that has come. It is like there is a famous person on the stage that has come and is the one that has been stuck ok the posters.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Aba bantu balitemwane icine cine elo baikale myake iingi, nga ninakulu bantu moneni fye ifyo alemoneka ne nsansa namwentula.
eng_translation: These people love each other very much and they have been together for a long time. If it is the old woman, she looks very happy because she is smilling.

bem_transcription: Elyo lintu amwentwile umulume wakwe nabika nafwaka kukanwa kakwe, elo aloleshe umukashi wakwe.
eng_translation: As she is smilling, the husband has held a cigarette to his mouth and is looking at the wife.

bem_transcription: Cishinka, elyo shitata alikwate mfwi, nafwala nakasote akafiita, nintemwa utumagalashi tuntu afwele.
eng_translation: Very true, and this man has white hair and is even wearing a black hat. I love the glasses he is wearing.

bem_transcription: Elo cipalile ukutila baciisa peshitolo elyo bapwisho kulya baletuushako pakutila bengatendeka ubulendo bwabo.
eng_translation: And it's like they were eating at a store and now they are done and just resting a bit before they can start off.

bem_transcription: Boi somone ubusanso buli uku, nshishibe nga busanso kuli umuntu umo nafule shati kabili mumusana wakwe muli umulopa weka weka, bushe mulopa uyu nangu aishingile fye?
eng_translation: Hey come and looks at this accident! I don't know if it's an accident or not, one man is shirtless and has blood around his waist. Is that blood or just something he has smeared?

bem_transcription: Awe cilemoneka kwati temulopa uyu, ifi fintu fye ifyakashika ifyo aciikuba, nomba lintu abomba fyaisapanga kwati mulopa.
eng_translation: No it not blood, it's like he had something red on him and when became wet it started looking like blood.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Iwe, mona naimwe! Tapalipo ifilonda apa, balesefya fye taumwene ati nabafwala ifyapalana nabantu bambi abaletamba icangalo cimbi icilecitika uku kuntashi?
eng_translation: Look closely! There are no wounds there. They are just celebrating. Can't you see that they are wearing similar clothes and others are watching some game in front?

bem_transcription: Ah! niwe wasosa kanshi ine mbwene kwati mulopa, elo ukukwine nabafula kaili nabalongana, cilepala ukuti nakuwama sana.
eng_translation: You have spoken! I thought it is blood. And there are a lot of people gathered here it seems like there is something interesting going on.

bem_transcription: Uwacilumendo nayapo kumo ukwaba sana imfula mabwe kaili nasenda necakutelelapo pa mfula mabwe bushe naumona ifyo aletelela?
eng_translation: A young man has gone some place where there is snow and has carried something to slide on the snow with. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimumona uyu umulumendo, aletentemuka ukufuma palupili ukutentemukila panshi, elyo nafwala nefyakufwala ifyatikame cine cine.
eng_translation: I have seen. He is sliding from the top of the mountain to below and he is wearing warm clothes.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana nafwale fintu ifyakaba sana pantu kuncende ekalila kwalitalala sana kumonfye nefyo afwele.
eng_translation: Yes he is wearing very warm clothes because he is in a very cold place.

bem_transcription: Nimbona ine ifyo afwele, nafwala ifyatikama, elyo nintemwa ifyo amalangi yalemoneka bwino nafwala kumuulu abikako icamakumbi makumbi kunshi abikako icakatapa katapa.
eng_translation: yes I have seen what he is wearing. I just love the colors. He is wearing blue on top and green below.

bem_transcription: CIshinka sana elo uku kwine takulemoneka bwino bwino tatwishibe noko aleya mukutulukila lelo ico twishibe cakuti aletelela pamfula mabwe.
eng_translation: It is true. And this place is not very clear and we can't see where he is going. All we know is he is sliding on small.

bem_transcription: We cikuulwa ulawama we! Elo nefyo akasuba kasanikepo kalemoneka kwati telubuto lwakashuba, kwati lilaiti fye basanikepo ubushiku, bushe boi naucimone ci?
eng_translation: What a beautiful building! And the way the sun is shining, it just looks like a light bulb in the night have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona boi balicikuula bwino kabili bacikuula namabuloko ayakosa kumonafye ifyo cilemoneka.
eng_translation: I have seen. It is well built with very strong blocks.

bem_transcription: Cishinka, elo panse ya ici icikuulwa kuli nanamayo uulebikapo amaluba ayakshika, bushe ulemona kwati ici cikuulwa cibomba mulimo nshi?
eng_translation: You are right. And there is a woman outside this building putting red flowers. What do you think this building is for?

bem_transcription: Ici cikuulwa bacibomfya ukpepelamo munshila imbi kuti twatila litempele, kumonafye iminshi shibili.
eng_translation: This is where people come to worship. It is a temple. You can tell from the two entrances.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, naulungika, nimbona naine, elyo panse yaici icikuulwa palibe ncenshi ishikalamba icine cine ishili shine.
eng_translation: You are right and there are for very big pillars outside this building.

bem_transcription: Umukashana ali mumputule no mwana wakwe elo alemwangasha, nomba mona ifyo asekelele lintu alemwangasha, bushe ulemona kwati ni nyina yu?
eng_translation: A young woman is in a room playing with a child and she is very happy. Do you think she is the mother?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: CIshinka, alemoneka wancito yu, nomba umwana alimutemwa, nakalimo nifi eusangwa nankwe lyonse, kumonafye ifyo balemfwana.
eng_translation: You are right, she looks like she is the maid. But the child loves her because they are mostly together, you can tell by their chemistry.

bem_transcription: Elo umwana talila nokulila apofye balibeleshanya noyu wancito, alimutemwa amusenda ukuti mwana wakwe.
eng_translation: The child doesn't even cry when with the maid because it is used. And the maid loved the child just like her own.

bem_transcription: Nintemwa nefyo uyu umwana umwaume bamufwalike, nabamufwalika icapala kwati cisote icakwata namatwi ayakalamba, nacifimba umubili onse ukufuma kumutwe ukufika kunshi.
eng_translation: He is wearing something that looks like a hat and has ears. It is a wanzie covering his entire body from the feet to the head.

bem_transcription: Uuhmm, nga finshi filecitika uku? Boi bushe kuti watila finshi filecitika uku? Ine ndemoneko fye abantu kwati balebomba we.
eng_translation: What is happening here. Friend, what do you think is happening here? I can only see people working.

bem_transcription: Mune bali pancito, kabili apa epakampani kabo epo babombela, kumonafye ifyo bafwele ifilelangilila ukuti bali pancito.
eng_translation: They are working and they are at their company.  You can tell by their work suits.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, elyo aka kampani bapanga amawilo yamotoka, pantu panse nabayatantika ayengi icine cine.
eng_translation: And this company makes car tires because a lot of them are on diplsplay outside.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda aka akampani kapanga amawilo yamotoka atemwa amawilo yafituukutuuku.
eng_translation: You are right this company makes car tires or motorcycle tires.

bem_transcription: Elyo nga nalolesha sana kuli kwati ukulefuke cushi,kulefume cushi pantu pakati apa apali umulumendo pali icushi icilefuka nakalimo baleocapo fimo, bushe naucimona?
eng_translation: And if I look closely it seems as if there is smoke coming from the middle of where that young man is coming from, it seems they are burning something. Have you seen the smoke?

bem_transcription: Boi mona aba abalumendo bali mucikuulwa cabwalwa baleyumfwishako bwino, elyo nabasekelela nabasangalala.
eng_translation: Friend, these people are in a bar and they are happy and enjoying themselves.

bem_transcription: Nifyo fine walanda bali mucikuulwa icabwalwa kaili balenwako no mwangashi, lelo ebo ndemona abalenwafye nibatatu bushe naumwenekesha?
eng_translation: You are right they are in a bar and are drinking women And I can see three people drinking have you seen?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbamona, batatu fye ebalenwa umwangashi, nakalimo aba batatu tabanwa nangula baleicaila fye
eng_translation: I have seen that only three are drinking. Maybe these three others do not drink or they are just feeling shy.

bem_transcription: Cilepala ukuti nabanwa, lelo umwangashi wabo wena naupwa, icisheleko fye kulasekelela nolashimika.
eng_translation: It seems as if they have finished their wine and so they are just seated and chatting with the friends.

bem_transcription: Elo incende iyi boi, ilemoneka bwino, yalikwata amalaiti ayaka bwino sana, yaleaka ifyakashika, kashika filya.
eng_translation: And this place have very nice lights that appear reddish when they are on.

bem_transcription: Muntu wandi mona, uko aba bantu baleangalila pali bemba, elyo iyi bemba naikwata amabimbi ayakalamba bushe tetibanwine?
eng_translation: Look at these people playing at the sea, and this see has big waves. Any they drown?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka nausosa kaili nabakwata uto baleninapo utwapala kwati tumapulanga utulebafwa ukutantala pamabimbi, bushe naumona ifyo umumana ulemoneka?
eng_translation: You are right and they have surfing boards so that they can surf on the waves. Have you seen how this river is looking?

bem_transcription: Uyu umumana boi walipabuka icine cine kabili ukalamba, icakutila nga cakuti nalikutweleko uku kuntu tekuti usambe nokusamba kuti wanwina.
eng_translation: The river is very big and very wide such that if I took you there you can't swim, but you can drown.

bem_transcription: Awe naiwe nalishiba ukusamba wilambwenamo, nomba mona kululamba lwa mumana kuli namayanda, kwalitantama amayanda ayengi icine cine.
eng_translation: Do not look down on me, I know how to swim. Now look at the sea shore, There are a lot of vehicles lined up there.

bem_transcription: Boi somone amasha yantu watemwa ukushana, yalya yene wibila, mone fyo baleshana, kuti washana naiwe?
eng_translation: Friend come and look at your favourite dance, the one where you go down low. Look at how they are dancing, can you do it?

bem_transcription: Icaanguka fye ngo kunwa nga menshi naiwe, tafyashupe fi, walaba shani emasha tushana cila bushiku aya.
eng_translation: That is as easy as drinking water. This is easy. Are you forgetting that this is how we dance everyday?

bem_transcription: Awe namona, ukansambilisheko bushiku bumo, nomba bushe naumona ifyo ici icikuulwa cilemoneka icilifye kunuma yabo?
eng_translation: I have seen, you should teach me one day. But have you seen how the building behind them is looking?

bem_transcription: Nincimona boi, cilemoneka bwino elo napeminina no muntu, balicipenta ne langi ilyafiita elo balembapo nefyebo.
eng_translation: I have seen my friend and it looks like there is even someone standing on it. It is painted in black and they have written something on it

bem_transcription: Elo namona boi, nshacimona ukutila paliko nefilembelweko napalembwa ukutila Rusell elo lwamupepi pali ne shitolo umo bashitishe fyakufwala.
eng_translation: That is when I have seen. I didn't notice that there was the word "Russel" written on it. And there is a store nearby whey they sell clothes.

bem_transcription: Iye, uyu balamwipaya kuli bakapokola, boi somone ifyo bakapokola batantenye uyu umulumendo katwishi nefyo acitile.
eng_translation: Oh no! The cops will kill him. Come and see how they are carrying him. I wonder what he has even done.

bem_transcription: Nimumona uyu ena, cilepala ukutila aciibapo fimo elyo baisa mukumwikata atemwa kwacibe fyongo elo bamwikata.
eng_translation: I have seen this one. Its like he stole something and they came to arrest him or maybe there was a riot and then they arrested him.

bem_transcription: Kulemoneka kwacibafye fyongo, pantu bakapokola nabafule cine cine abaciya mukuleshelela ifi fine ifyongo.
eng_translation: It looks like there was a riot because there are a lot of cops here who came to stop the rioting.

bem_transcription: Kwacibe fyongo baciisa nabaipangasha kabili nabaipekanya, kumonafye ifyo bafwele bakapokola nefya kuicinga.
eng_translation: There were riots and you can tell by how the cops are dressed that they came prepared.

bem_transcription: Cishinka, elyo iyi incende nimukati ka musumba pantu muli ifikuulwa elyo mwaliba nefimuti ifitali mumbali.
eng_translation: Very true. And this is in the middle of the city because there are buildings and tall trees on the side of the road.

bem_transcription: We munandi watemwikwa lolesha pali ici icikope elyo umone abantu nabekala mucikuulwa bushe kuti watila finshi balecite fi?
eng_translation: My beloved friend, look at this picture and see these people seated in this building. What do you think they are doing?

bem_transcription: Mune cilepala kwati ine nshilelolekesha, lelo ifyo ndemonapo fye ndemona ukuti nabekata balamya babo, nshishibe nga nibalamya atemwa nshishibe ifyo ningalanda fye.
eng_translation: Well you know my sight is poor. what I can only see is that they are holding phones, I don't even know for sure if those are phones they are holding. I don't know what to say.

bem_transcription: Ee, nibalamya, nomba cila muntu nakwata ifyo alecita pali lamya yakwe takuli uulelolesha pali lamya yamunankwe.
eng_translation: Yes they are phones and each one is looking at their phone and no one is looking on another's.

bem_transcription: Cilepala ukutila bali pancito olo atemwa baleteyako icangalo cimo pamakompyuta pamyabo.
eng_translation: It seem they are working or they are playing a certain game on their computers.

bem_transcription: Awe naiwe tebakompyuta, nibalamya aba elo bonse fye nabashinguluke tebulo nabekala kuli nanamayo uulelosha kumbi.
eng_translation: No those are not computers but phones and they all are seated around a table, and there is a woman looking somewhere else.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwaice alishibisha sana ukuteye ci cangalo, mona fye boi ifyo acitile pakuma akamupila akacepesha.
eng_translation: This young person is well known for playing this game. Just see what he has done to hit that small ball.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, acitile kwati nafukamako elo nakwata necipampa muminwe yakwe icikuminako akamupila akanoono.
eng_translation: I have seen. he has knelt down a bit and he has a cane in his hands for hitting the small ball.

bem_transcription: Elyo uku kuncende kuli nabantu abengi sana abaletamba lintu baleipitila fye.
eng_translation: And there are a lot of people watching as they are walking.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana bengi bena elo apa baleteyela palimena ne fyani ifyalelema kabili ifilemoneka bwino kabili ifyafunda.
eng_translation: You are right the people are many and the grass is very green and nice.

bem_transcription: Elo nga nikulya ukwimine abantu kwena kuliko necikuulwa icipiko so, elyo cilemoneka bwino mwe nangula cakale.
eng_translation: If it is there where people are standing, there is a short building which is looking very nice even though it is short.

bem_transcription: Bashitata nangula ntile abalumendo bali mupepi nokutampa ukucimfyanya icangalo camacinga.
eng_translation: Young men are about to start bike racing.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo boi aba bantu bengi icine cine, nomba mwati kuti kwaba nowakucimfya pali aba? Mona fye ifyo bafulile
eng_translation: These people are many. Would there even be a winner here? Just look at how many they are.

bem_transcription: kwalaba uwalacimfya caba nefyo ulebutusha icinga kabili uwalacimfya muli uwacimfyanya muli uyu nakatanga wakwensha incinga ewalapeke cilambu.
eng_translation: There will be a winner depending on how well one will be cycling and the winner will be give a prize.

bem_transcription: Nabantu abalebatamba ala  bengi icine cine icakutila bonse balekopa fye icikope cabo
eng_translation: There are many people watching and they all are taking pictures.

bem_transcription: Boi mona utumisakuta elyo batukula utunoona sana, mona boi bushe aba bantu balikwata amayanda?
eng_translation: Look at those small huts. Do these people even have proper houses?

bem_transcription: Tabakwata, kumona fye ifyo bekala, elo twingi icine cine, balifimbako namantenti icakutila ne mfula nga yalishile teti balokwe.
eng_translation: The do not have. Just look at how they are seated and the huts are many. They have even covered them with tents so that they don't get soaked when it's raining.

bem_transcription: Cishinka elo utu twine utumisakuta twabela fye mumbali yalupili nomba imfula nga yaloka iikalamba kuti twasendwa.
eng_translation: These huts are just on the side of the mountain and they can be washed away if rains came.

bem_transcription: Aba bantu balacula nacinjikata nakumutima ukumona imikalile baleikala kabili ne fyakulya takulemonekako ifili fyonse.
eng_translation: These people suffer so much and I feel very bad for them. There doesn't even look to be any food here.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, naumfwa no bubi ukumona ifyo aba bantu balecula, nshishibe noko batapa amenshi, uku takwaba namaliketi.
eng_translation: You are right. I feel bad to see how these people are suffering. I don't even know where they draw their water from and there isn't even a market.

bem_transcription: Nakulubantu nasekelela lintu aleangala no mwishikulu wakwe mumuputule, bushe naumona ifyo alemoneka?
eng_translation: An old woman is happy playing with her grandchild in a room. Have you seen how she is looking?

bem_transcription: Nimumona boi ala alikota icine cine elo kabili aliipipa kumumona fye ifyo alemoneka.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen her. She is very old and very short.

bem_transcription: Ne fyakufwala afwele ifyabakashana we! mona fye, nafwala akantu akakashika kumuulu elyo kunshi abikako nakatoloshi akafita.
eng_translation: The clothes she is wearing are for young people. Just look she is wearing a red thing in top and a black trousers.

bem_transcription: Ca cine efyakufwala afwele kaili mupepi lwakwe nakumbatila nembwa iyafiita elo apa pali nomwana.
eng_translation: It is true that is what she is wearing and she is hugging a black dog and a child.

bem_transcription: Akamwana aka kalicenjela icine cine, mona fye ifyo kalolesha keka fye takalelila nokulila kaleangasha fye ulukasa lwakako.
eng_translation: The child is very bright. Look at just how it's alone and not crying and just playing with her foot.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo ewaishiba ukuliila mona fye ifyo acitile amatobovyalemoneka fye ayaliila lila napamenso bushe naumona ifyo akete kuminwe?
