eng_translation: Yes the mother is lifting the baby with love and she is smilling as she is talking to the child.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, natemwa ukuba no mwana wakwe kabili umwana wakwe nafwala necifimbo icabuuta.
eng_translation: You are right. she is happy to be with the child, and the child has a white covering.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila umwana wakwe uyu wine ala musuma elo mulumendo nangula ntile mwaume.
eng_translation: Another thing is that the child is very good looking and it is a boy.

bem_transcription: Elo cilepala ukutila bali mung'anda mumyabo elo ine mukumona kwandi, ndemona kwati nyina kale amwenepo umwana echo amwentulile.
eng_translation: It seems like they are in their house and I think the mother has not seen the child in along time that is why she is smiling like this.

bem_transcription: Boi somone, umukashana ali pantashi kabili nakwatapo fimo ifilemoneka ifyakashika, elyo kunuma kuli abalumendo, bushe uletontonkanya ukutila nikwisa uku bali?
eng_translation: My friend come and see, this young woman in front has something red and their is a young man behind her.  Where do you think this is?

bem_transcription: Aba nibalya abantu abasambilila ifyakulwa nakalimo uyu namayo eubasambilisha elyo umu bali fye nimucikuulwa
eng_translation: These are the people that learn how to fight, and this woman looks like the trainer. And they are just in a building.

bem_transcription: Niwe walanda kanshi kumona fye nefyo bafweleifyabuuta kabili bakaka nomushipi uwafiita, ala aba abantu balishiba sana ukulwa nefyakuicingilila.
eng_translation: You are right. You can just see from the white clothes they are wearing and the black belts. These people know how to fight and defend themselves.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo balelosha emulandu wine belile kuli iyi incende mukulanga umucinshi
eng_translation: Maybe they are grieving and that is why they went to this place to show their respects.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo baleloshalelo ico njishibe cakutila balefwaya ukutendeka ukutusha umbili mufyakulwa.
eng_translation: Maybe they are mourning, but what I know is they are about to start training.

bem_transcription: Boi ukuba pamo caliwama sana kabili kulaba ukusansamuka somone ifyo abanensu bali pamo kabili ifyo balelanshanya.
eng_translation: My friend you know it is good to be together and you can enjoy. Look at how our friends are enjoying and chatting.

bem_transcription: Nimbona, ala bonse balemoneka abasekelela elyo kuli shitata uyu uufwele fyafita kabili uwaina nababika mwilyashi nabasekesha.
eng_translation: I have seen they all look happy and there is this man who is fat and dressed in white who is busy telling them stories and making them laugh.

bem_transcription: Cishinka alebashimikisha kumona fye ifyo balesekelela elo aba bambi elo bali uku abanakashi bena bali fye nefyabo.
eng_translation: It is true he is telling them stories and that is why they are laughing. But these other women there are just doing there own things.

bem_transcription: Elo iyi incende abantu nabafule cine cine palibako nakamulundu apali amayanda, ala nakalimo baleshitishapo fimo.
eng_translation: And there are a lot of people in this place and there is a high land where there are houses and it seems they are selling something.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati nakalimo baciisa fye mukubungana kumona fye ubwingi bwa bantu elo bacisendako nefyakulya ifyakuti bengalya apo tabacishiba inshita balabwela.
eng_translation: It seems they came for a gathering because of how many they are and people carried some food because they did not know when they will get back.

bem_transcription: Icibwa icabuuta cafuma mu mpanga, kabili mumpanga muli amenshi ayengi sana, bushe naumona ifyo cilebutuka?
eng_translation: A white dog is coming from the forest, and there is water in the forest. Have you seen how it is running?

bem_transcription: Ala ici icibwa nacinyanyangala mumenshi elo calikwata amaka kabili calikosa pantu amenshi yalanasha.
eng_translation: This dog is running in the water and it has a lot of energy and it is strong because water makes someone tired.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana elo calikwata ne langi ilyabuuta, elo cilepala kwati umwine nacisha kabili cilebutukila ku mwine.
eng_translation: Very true and it has a white color. And it seems the owner left it and do it is running to catch up with him.

bem_transcription: Nomba aya amenshi nayampapusha pantu pakati pali ne fimuti ifyamenapo nakalimo menshi fye yabamilamba.
eng_translation: This water is surprising because there are trees in the middle. Maybe they just came due to rains.

bem_transcription: Te menshi yabamilamba iyo cilemoneka kwati nakalimo kwalifula amenshi nomba, uhm, elo namona ifimuti filemoneka fye ifyaboomba awe imfula yaciloka.
eng_translation: This water did not come because of the rains, there is just a lot of water there. But when I look closely the trees look wet, maybe it was raining.

bem_transcription: Wilashalila mune isa tutambeko naifwe bene umupila, kabili uyu umupila nauwama icine cine, tulefwaya ukumona abalawina, bushe nibesa ebo ulelumba?
eng_translation: Do not lag behind my friend let us watch some soccer. This soccer looks interesting, don't you want to know who will win? Which team are you supporting.

bem_transcription: Ine pali aba nalalumbapofye abafwele ifyakashika pantu ebalemonaka fye ukuti nabakwata amaka, nomba bushe naumona ifyo abantu bafulile?
eng_translation: I will support these in red because they look powerful. But have you seen how the people are many here?

bem_transcription: Ulelolekesha, kuti waya lumba abakashika, ine ndelumba abafwele icakufwala icilemoneka makumbi makumbi, pantu balaingisha nomba line, lelo ubwingi bwa bantu nimbamona.
eng_translation: You should be looking more closely. I am supporting the ones in a blue jersey because they look like they are about to score. And yes there are many people, I have seen them.

bem_transcription: Monafye nabafulilemo bantu abafwele ifyakashika, icilepilibula ukutila abakashika ebalawina, nomba icibansa ici cilemoneka bwino sana lolekesha.
eng_translation: Look closer, the majority are in red, it means they will win. And this stadium looks very nice.

bem_transcription: Nicimona, balicipanga bwino kabili cisuma sana kwati nalimo balyanshikamo fye kapeti, lelo abantu bena balelumba, twalamona awalalusa pali iwe naine
eng_translation: I have seen it is well built and looks very nice as if they have put a carpet in it. The people are cheering, we will see who will win between you and me.

bem_transcription: Tuleya nkusendeko naiwe, wilapwalala fi, ninjishiba naumfwe nsala, taulemona abanobe ukuti nabaya mukulye fyakulya, tuleya nkusendeko nkushitileko ifyakulya.
eng_translation: Let me also take you, don't be looking like this all hungry here. Cant you you see that your friends have gone to eat food? Let me also take you out I buy you something.

bem_transcription: Mwamona fye abantu mucikope ati naimwe mulefwaya ukunsenda, muleibwelamo batata, moneni fye, aba bacaice, nabaya mukuyumfwishako bwino.
eng_translation: You just see people in a picture and you want to take me out? Have some control big man. And look these are children who have gone out to have a good time.

bem_transcription: Emulandu wine boi ndekwebela ati nalakusendeko, tusebululeko insoni, abacaice tekuti baleya fye baisende baye mukuyumfwisha bwino, nalakusenda waumfwa?
eng_translation: That is why I am telling you that I will take you out to remove the shame. These young people can't go out to have a good time on their own. I will also take you.

bem_transcription: Awe cili fye bwino, nomba lubali lumbi kuli nabantu fye abakalamba abalelya, abaleipakisha ukulila pamo, nauamona?
eng_translation: No it is fine, and on the other side there are adults eating and enjoying eating together. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbamona, nabo bene baleyumfwisha bwino bwino, balelila pamo kabili balelanshanya, balesekelela, elyo umbi ali fye eka.
eng_translation: I have seen. They are enjoying themselves, they are eating together, and chatting and laughing. And one is just alone.

bem_transcription: Uyu namayo elyo nouli kunuma nabasekelela icine cine nshishibe ico bamwentwile, kaili uyu namayo wikele apa naimyako namaboko.
eng_translation: This woman and the one behind are very happy, I don't know why they are smiling. And this woman seated here is even raising her hands.

bem_transcription: Naumfwa bwino pantu ali pamulimo, kabili nakalimo balimweba ati tulekukopa icikope, nomba bushe naumona ifyo balepanga?
eng_translation: She is happy because she is working and maybe they told her that they are taking a picture of her. But have you seen what they are making?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune, aba nibakapikula bafyakufwala atemwa ababuutanda, kumona fye ifyo balepikula filemoneka fye ifisuma kabili ifyayemba.
eng_translation: I have seen these are craftsmen who make reed mats, you can tell by what they are making. They look nice and beautiful.

bem_transcription: Elyo aba bantu babombela fye pa n'ganda pantu kunuma yabo kuli ing'anda eloy ilemoneka bwino mwe.
eng_translation: These people are working from home because there is a house behind them and it looks very nice.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana shilemoneka bwino shonse, kabili pa n'ganda pali ne cituukutuuku elo paba necakucinga kumutwe icamakumbi makumbi
eng_translation: It is true they both are looking very good, and there is a motorcycle on the yard and a blue helmet on it.

bem_transcription: Boi somone endesha, imbwa kuno nainwina, yacilaimona iyacenjela ukuti kuti yasamba mumumana,iwe walelanda ukuti imbwa shilasamba lelo wamona ukuti shilanwina tefyo?
eng_translation: My friend come and see a dog is drowning. It thought it is wise and could swim through. You said dogs can swim but have you seen that they drown.

bem_transcription: Awe, ulelolekesha, nalikweba, mona ilesambafye, yacingila mumenshi elo yaabuka, taumwene ati namenshi yaletona?
eng_translation: No just look closely! I told you. It is swimming. It just went in the water and came out. Can't you see that water is even dropping?

bem_transcription: Yangu, naciluba mune,ala nacimona kwati nakalimo nainwina yanwako namenshi kanshi ileowa
eng_translation: Oh no I was lost. I thought it was drowning but it was just swimming.

bem_transcription: Yacilaowa, ilesamba fye, elo yafiita nakukanwa kukuulu, nomba bushe naumona ifyo amenshi yalemoneka?
eng_translation: It was just swimming, and this dog is dark and had a big mouth. But have you seen how the water is looking?

bem_transcription: Uyu umumana muntu muntu wandi ukalamba na menshi yalemoneka ayasuma kabili ayalengama, nimpapa fye nefyo imbwa ingile pali uyu umumana uukalamba
eng_translation: This river is very big my friend and the water looks clear and clean. I'm even surprised how the dog went into this big river.

bem_transcription: Abantu abengi nabayapo kumo, kabili uku bele, nshishibe ifyo bele mukutamba, lelo ico njishibe cakutila nabeminina fye baletambapo fimo, bushe nawishiba wemunandi ifyo balecita kabili ifyo baletamba?
eng_translation: People have gone somewhere and I don't know what they have gone to watch. All I know is they are standing watching something. My friend do you know what they are are doing and what they are watching?

bem_transcription: Awe nshishibe nakalimo kuli ukucimfyanya pantu ndemona kuntashi kuli necisebele elyo nefimalaiti.
eng_translation: I don't know, maybe there is a competition because there is a stage in front and there are lights.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walnada, cilemoneka kwati nalimo kwalaba abalaisa, abalaisa mukucimfyanya, bushe tauletontonkanya ukuti kuti twaya mukutambako?
eng_translation: You are right. It looks like there will be people who will come to compete. Don't you think we can go and watch?

bem_transcription: Awe tekutila uleya mukutamba ukwaso kano nga nabakwita, nangula nga naukwata impiya shakulipila, mona fye ifyo iyi incende ilemoneka.
eng_translation: No you can't go there unless you are invited or you have money to pay. Just see how the place is looking.

bem_transcription: Iyi incende muntu wandi baliwamya, kabili icisebele fye ceka ceka, ciletiinya, ala mwandi nshatalamonapo incende necisebele ico bawamya umusango yu.
eng_translation: This place has been well cleaned and it has a wonderful and intimidating stage. I have never seen a place and a stage this beautiful.

bem_transcription: Iwe somone boi, ine uyu umukashana nampapusha, nshishibe ico abikile pakuboko pamyakwe, ala cilentiinya icakutila no mubili waenda pano opo njikele.
eng_translation: My friend come and see. This girl has surprised me. I don't know what she has put on her hand but it is scary, I even feel chills in my body.

bem_transcription: Ici cilemoneka kwati ni chuula elo futi nga twacilolekesha cilemoneka kwati cimpempe.
eng_translation: The looks like a frog and at the same time it looks like a crab.

bem_transcription: Nshamonapo icishishi camusango ine mubumi bwandi, uyu emuku wakubalilapo, ala ciletiinya nga nacilolesha no mubili pano uletutuma.
eng_translation: I have never seen such an insect in my life. this is my first time. It is so scary that am even shaking right now.

bem_transcription: Nomba iwe uletiina elo ninshi uwikete fye ici mukashana, taumwene ukutila uyu mukashana uuli apa?
eng_translation: You are fearing but the one holding it is just a girl? Can't you see that this here is a girl?

bem_transcription: Nimbona ukuti mukashana, kabili kumona fye imishishi shakwe, nafwala nakasote, nomba fye ifyo ekete efilentiinya, ala uyu alipama.
eng_translation: I have seen that she is a girl because of her hair and she is wearing a hat. But what she is holding is what is scaring me. She is very bold.

bem_transcription: Bakabomba bancito kabili abaishibisha sana ukubomba kabili abaishiba sana umulimo wabo ifyo balingile ukubomba nabesapo kuncende, kabili aba ni aba abashimya ilyo umulilo waaka, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: People who are experts at their work have come to a place. These people are fire fighters have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbamona, cilepala kwati uku kuli ubusanso ubwamulilo elyo nabesa mukushimya pantu monafye nefimatumbo ifyamenshi fili panshi, nomba bushe naumona uyu umukashana?
eng_translation: I have seen them, it's like there was a fire accident and they have come to put it out as can be seen by the big water pipes down. But have you seen this young woman?

bem_transcription: Nimumona uyu umukashana kabili eulipo fye, awe bali babili abakashana, kabili balitemwa umulimo untu babomba aba bantu, naumona uuli panshi?
eng_translation: I have seen this young woman because she is just alone, well no they are two and they seem to love their work. Have you seen below?

bem_transcription: Uuli panshi nimumona, nakalimo aciba mubusanso nabamubika necisalu icabuuta, nabamubika panshi, nomba teti bamwimyeko?
eng_translation: I have seen the one below. They might have been in an accident and they have put them down and put a white cloth on them. But can't they lift them?

bem_transcription: Ukumwimya kwena balamwimya ilyo balapwisha umulimo uo beshile mukubomba, panuma yakumwimya balamutwala kucipatala.
eng_translation: They will raise them when they are done with what they are doing and then take them to the hospital.

bem_transcription: Uku kuncende boi balikuula ifikuulwa ifyapalamana lelo pakati paliba no musebo, bushe naumona ifyo ifikuulwa fyalepa nefyo bafikuula?
eng_translation: This place has buildings that are very close to one another and there is a road in between. Have you seen how close these buildings are to one another and how they are built?

bem_transcription: Ifi ifikuulwa fyantunti elo pakati balishapo akamusebo akakunininapo ngolefwaya ukuya pamuulu, nga cakutila umuputule wobe wabela pamuulu.
eng_translation: This is a storey building and there is a starecase in the middle which you can use if you stay upstairs.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda, balibikapo utwakutantala uto bakuula nacimenti kabili ici icikuulwa bacipenta nelangi ilyakashika.
eng_translation: You are right it has a starecase made of cement and this building is painted red.

bem_transcription: Elyo kuntashi kulya kulemoneka kwati kuli umusebo naumbi elyo pakonka necikuulwa pantu kulefuma ulubuuto.
eng_translation: There seems to be another road in front then followed another building because there is some light coming from there.

bem_transcription: Eya e, walanda pantu uko aleya yu kuli inshila kabili kuli ici cine icikuulwa cimbi ici balibikako ne lampi ilyakisha sana ilyo kwafiita.
eng_translation: You are right. There is a road where this one is going and then on this other building there is a light that shines when it is dark.

bem_transcription: Somone uko bashitata baletukusha umubili ukupitila mukuteye cangalo, kabili bonse bafwele ifyakufwala ifyamalangi yamo yene,bushe naumona ifyo balecita?
eng_translation: Come and see how men are exercising through this game and they all are wearing the same color. Have you seen what they are doing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, elo balemoneka balecimfyanya, elo nga ni uyu nafundumana icine cine.
eng_translation: I have seen and they look like they are competing. if it is this other one, he is very determined.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana nafundumana, cilepala kwati nakalimo alefwaya ukupokelela kabola akanoono akali panshi eko baleteya ukubomfye shinkoto.
eng_translation: Yes he is very focussed. It looks like he wants to recieve the ball that is down that they are hitting with a stick.

bem_transcription: Nomba nintemwe fyo uyu uuli mucipanda afwele, nafwala ifyakuicingilila pakutila tabamumine nkoto lintu baleteya.
eng_translation: I love what the goal keeper is wearing. He is wearing protective clothing so that they don't hit them with the stick.

bem_transcription: Nabafwala kaputula uwafiita kabili bafwala ne shati ilyamaboko ayepi liyamutuntula mwapita notwafiita, elo uyu uuli mucipande afwele icakatapakatapa.
eng_translation: They are wearing a black short and a yellow yellow short sleeved shirt with black one them and this one in the goal post is in green.

bem_transcription: Ine somone kwabe mbwa shikali kabili ishinyanyangala icakutila nga shalikupepeke muntu wandi kuwila napanshi, bushe naumona ubukali bwambwa?
eng_translation: Come and seen. There are some very fierce dogs such that if they chased you, you can even fall down my friend. Have you seen how fierce these dogs are?

bem_transcription: Ala ishi imbwa shikali icine cine, elyo taili yeka shili shitatu kuli shibili ishikwete ayafiita amasako elyo imo ikwete ayabuuta.
eng_translation: This dog is very fierce and it is not alone but they are three. Two have black fur, and one has white fur.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, kabili ishi shifumine muli bemba umukalamba kabili shilepepekana atemwa shilepepekapo fimo ifyo shimwene.
eng_translation: It is very true and these came from a large sea and they are chasing each other or they all are chasing something.

bem_transcription: Bushe boi naumona ukutila cibembe ci cikalamba elyo bushe naubamona abantu abali kulya?
eng_translation: Have you seen that this river is very big, and have you seen the people there?

bem_transcription: Nimbamona, baleangalila muli bemba mukalamba, elo amabimbi nayo yalepama fye, yalolo ku yabwelelo ku.
eng_translation: I have seen, They are playing in the sea my friend. And the waves are just getting closer and closer.

bem_transcription: Mune iwe, bushe walikwatapo umukashi nangu walyupa, ah, ifyo emoneka fye, ulatiina abanakashi, abanobe balasenda abanakashi kuncende kumo baya liila pamo, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: My friend do you even have a wife? from the looks I think you fear women. Look at your friends they take their women out to nice places and eat together. Have you seen them?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbamona, iwe ine nshilaupa, nangula nshilaupa nikumbwa ifyo bacitile, nabaya mukulila pamo elyo balemoneka abansansa, bushe naumona ukutila uyu umwanakashi musuma?
eng_translation: Yes I have seen them. My friend I am not married. but I love what they have done. They have gone to eat together and they look happy. Have you seen that this woman is very beautiful?

bem_transcription: Ala musume cine cine, nacila naulya gelo wakwata, ah! Teti afike nako iyo,haha, mwaba abanakashi abasuma ukucila nebo wakwata nebo umona.
eng_translation: Yes she's very beautiful. Even more than that girlfriend of yours. There are women in this world more beautiful than the one you have and even the ones you see.

bem_transcription: Iwe, kalale,tawishiba ifyo ulelandapo, eh, nomba landa pamulumendo, umulumendo naumona ifyo alemoneka, bushe natemwa yu nangu alelila, finshi alecita?
eng_translation: Just go and sleep. You don't know what you are talking about. Now talk about that young man. Have you seen how he is looking? Is he happy or is he crying? What is he doing?

bem_transcription: Natemwa ukumona nomukashi wakwe napalamana nankwe, nabaya mukulila pamo ne cakulya icili petebulo ifilemoneka bwino, kaili kumbali uku kuli nabantu abekele.
eng_translation: He is happy because he has his wife close to him and they have gone to eat together this nice food on the table. There are even people sitting on the side.

bem_transcription: Iwe somone, nakwima ulukungu ku, balebutusha bamotoka, icakutila awe sure nolukungu nalushala, bushe uletontokanya ukuti tabalecimfyanya.
eng_translation: Come and see the dust that is here. They are speeding their vehicles so much that dust has been left behind. Don't you think these are competing?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu tecakutwishika balecimfyanya pantu kuli motoka naimbi iitangile kuntashi elo iyi naishalila.
eng_translation: We can't doubt that these people are competing because there is another one in front and another one below.

bem_transcription: Awe taishalile nobe, cilemoneka kwati nalimo baleya mukukumanapo kumo, pantu iyi ipitile ku elo imbi yapita lubali lumbi.
eng_translation: No it is not behind but it looks like they are meeting somewhere because this one has passed on one side and another has passed on the other side.

bem_transcription: Iwe ulelolekesha, mona umusebo umo wine, iyi iyo tulemona apa ilikunuma lelo ilya iili kukulyo liyakuntashi ilemoneka iyabuuta iili kuntashi
eng_translation: look closely. This is the same road. The one we are seeing is behind but the one on the is white and looks like it is in front.

bem_transcription: Amenso yobe yalifwa mune, nalakushitila amabotolo pakuti ulemona bwino, so taulemona ukuti ilya iili kuntashi iyo ulemona ili icanuma cili kunuma elyo napeminina no muntu pakati apo balebutusishe myotoka
eng_translation: You eyes are dead man! I will buy you specs so that you be seeing clearly. Cant you see that that the one in front that you are seeing is facing backwards and there is a person standing in between where they are racing?

bem_transcription: Iwe somone abaice abacenjela abakucila amano, ndemona kwati nakalimo nakubwaice bobe iwe tawapangilepo ifi ndebepa?
eng_translation: You come and see children who are more intelligent than you. I think even in your childhood you never made anything like this. Am I lying?

bem_transcription: Umfwa, boi ulelanda bwino ai efilya musanga ati bamyuma, mona umwaice yu alicenjela ee nshilekana elyo ico apangile ci ni pyramid walishiba nokwishiba pyramid iwe?
eng_translation: He! Careful with what you say. Thats why people beat. Yes im not arguing that this child is bright and what he has made is a pyramid. Do you even know what a pyramid is?

bem_transcription: Mona nobe waamba ukubweneshamo nobe, ulemona kwati nshipita kusukulu buti kwena icisungu ici campita mune, hahahaha.
eng_translation: Stop looking down on me! You think I haven't been to school? Ok but honestly I don't know the meaning of what you have just said.

bem_transcription: Wamona so wilaimwenesha elyo uku kulemoneka nikululamba lwamumana pantu kwaliba namatipa nomba naumona ifyo umwana afwele?
eng_translation: You see. Do not think more of yourself. This looks like the seashore because there is mud but have you seen what the child is wearing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, nafwala kaputula elo abikapo nakashati akabutukila mwapita necakashika kabili nabikapo nakasote akafiita naloleshako nakumbali
eng_translation: I have seen. He is wearing a shirt and a blackish shirt with red in it and he is also wearing a black hat and is looking to the side.

bem_transcription: Iwe, bushe naumona ifyo ndemona? Icikope fye ceka ceka cilembwenesha kwati nalikalimo ndetambafye alecofe ncinga, ah! uwakopele aliishiba bushe naumona?
eng_translation: You have you seen what I've seen? This picture is looking like I'm watching him ride the bicycle. The one who took it is very experienced. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, kwena alyesesheko nangula cakutila uyu ali palwendo alimukopa bwino icakutila amoneka nokumoneka nomba
eng_translation: Yes he tried because even if this person is moving, he was nicely captured.

bem_transcription: Lulemoneka bwino kabili lulemoneka kwati nakalimo nalo lulesela ilyo alecofa iyi incinga ala paba ulunkoto ulusuma.
eng_translation: It is looking very nice and it is like it is also moving as he is riding the bicycle. There is very nice grass here.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila uyu umuntu uulecofe ncinga tali eka, balecimfyanya, nomba nawishiba umulandu nalandile fi?
eng_translation: Another thing is this person riding a bicycle is not alone but they are in a race. Do you know why I have said so?

bem_transcription: Ninjishiba, ishi incinga bashibomfesha ilyo balecimfyanya kabili kuli namotoka iilemukonka, bushe waciimona amenso yobe yalifwa iwe.
eng_translation: Yes these bicycle are used in races and there is a vehicle following behind. Did you see it? You are blind!

bem_transcription: Ubu bwena bun'gani ubo tulanda, we muntu wayasenda iipushi waamba ukulacitula namashini, awe ifi efyo nkweba ati uleke ubun'gani.
eng_translation: This is why I always say you are very lazy. You get a pumpkin and start piercing it with a machine.

bem_transcription: Iwe tawishibe nefyo balefwaya ukupanga muli ici icipushi, nakalimo balefwaya ukupanga amenso elyo bacilenge kwati cimuntu.
eng_translation: You don't even know what they want to make out of this pumpkin, maybe they want to make eyes in it so that it looks like a person.

bem_transcription: Oh oh, niwe walanda, nacilamona kwati nakalimo alefwaya ukulepula elo abike mumpoto epike, nga nifyo walanda cili fye bwino.
eng_translation: Yes you are right. I thought he wanted to cut and put in a pot. If that's the case then that's alright.

bem_transcription: Mwebaleyumfwa imwe, twebeniko muli uyu umuputule balimo banga abantu?
eng_translation: You who were boasting. Tell us. How many are they in this room?

bem_transcription: Ulemona kwati nifi wafwa amenso, awe ndamona ine! Muli abantu batatu elo nabakwata nefipushi, ifipushi nafyo fili fitatu, wamona ati ndamona ka?!
eng_translation: You think I'm the way you are blind. I can see. There are three people with and they have pumpkins. The pumpkins are also three. You see that I have eyes?

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata uwacikoloci naikala pacikuulwa cimo kabili nafwala ne fyakufwala, ishati ilyafiita elyo abikapo netoloshi lyakatapa katapa.
eng_translation: This old man is seated at a building, wearing a white shirt and a green trousers.

bem_transcription: Nimumona, elyo alecitika kwati aletoota nakalimo bamwebele ukwimba, mona fye nakanwa efyo kalecita.
eng_translation: I have seen and it looks like he is clapping. Maybe they told him to sing. Just looks at what his mouth is doing.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana cipalile kwati nalimo bacimweba ukuti toota elo twalakupelapo fimo olo atemwa aletambap fimo elo atoota.
eng_translation: It is true. It's like he was told to clap for him to be given something and then he is happy watching something and clapping.

bem_transcription: Nomba cilepala kwati apa tepa n'ganda pamwakwe pamuladu wakutila nakwata ifyola ifyo abikile fye aletuushishapo fye, bushe naumona?
eng_translation: But this doesn't look like his house because he has big and it looks like he is just resting. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nincimona icikuulwa cisuma sana balicikuula bwino kabili cantunti ishingi, nga fimuti fyena balifibyala bwino ala umusebo ulemoneka bwino
eng_translation: I have seen. The building is well built and it is an upstair building. It it's the trees, they are well planted and the road looks very good.

bem_transcription: Mona ifyo alepweneka uyu uwacilumendo, cilepala kwati nalimo aleloleshapo fimo, nomba tauletontonkanya ukuti ukupweneka kwakwe kwalamulengesha ukuti a
eng_translation: Look at how carried away this young man is, it's like he is looking at something. But don't you think being this carried away may be a problem?

bem_transcription: Ee, kwena kuli ifyo alelolesha nakalimo acitile kwati nifilya bamwita ukuti iwe cite, elo aloleshako.
eng_translation: Yes he is looking at something. It's like he was called and was looking to see who called him.

bem_transcription: Iwe nobe amenso yobe yalifwa taumwenekesha, naumonapo ne shitima lileisa apa? Ine mbwenepo fye injanji capwa, ulemwenekesha.
eng_translation: You! You eyes do not work! Have you Sean a train coming here? All I can see is the rail line, you should be looking closely.

bem_transcription: Iwe nakufita kulya, amenso yandi tayacilamwenesha bwino, nomba bushe naumona ukutila abantu balelolele shitima?
eng_translation: It is dark there and so I didn't see properly. But have you seen that people are waiting for a train?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, balelolele shitima pakutila benganina nokuya uko baleya, kabili mucitesheni umu babikamo injanji shibili umupita amashitima yabili imbi ipitila pesamba elo imbi pamuulu.
eng_translation: I have seen. They are waiting for the train so that they can board and go where they are going. There are two rail lines at this station that trains use. One can use the one on top and one can use the one below.

bem_transcription: Abaupana babili nabafwala ifyampepo kabili nabeminina pacikuulwa elo nabafwala namatoloshi yamo yene, bushe nawishiba umo balelola?
eng_translation: A married couple is standing at a building, wearing jerseys and similar trousers. Do you know where they are going ?

bem_transcription: Apa tabalasala nampo nga kwingila mwituuka nangu iyo, elo cilemoneka kwati balelolesha pacipampa apali imitengo libe tabalaingila.
eng_translation: The haven't decided whether they want to enter the shop or not. It looks like they are checking the prices before they enter.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, elyo panse yaici icikuulwa balibikapo napakwikala apaba namatebulo ngolefwaya kuti walila panse atemwa mukati.
eng_translation: True and they have put chairs and tables outside this building. You can decide whether to eat from inside or from outside.

bem_transcription: Ala panse apa balipapanga bwino sana, elo utumatebulo tulemoneka utwayemba babomfya fye amapulanga nangula imbao.
eng_translation: Outside looks very nice. The tables are very nice and they are made of wood.

bem_transcription: Elo ici icikuulwa ca ntunti shibili kabili cakwata insokololo ishikalamba kumonafye nefyo bashipenta ishabuuta.
eng_translation: This is a two story building and it is well painted.

bem_transcription: Namayo nayapo kumo kucikuulwa, kabili uku ele nikulya batukushishapo umubili, bushe naumona epo aninine?
eng_translation: A woman is at the gym. Have you seen where she is standing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona nanina pali mashini iyakubutukilapo elo alemoneka nanaka, mona fye ifyo alemoneka pa menso.
eng_translation: Yes she is on a treadmill and she looks very tired.

bem_transcription: Nimbona ifyo alemoneka, kabili cilepala ukuti kale atendeke, pali ici cimashini palalanga ifyo wabutuka.
eng_translation: Yes I can see how she is looking and its like she started a long time ago. This machine can show how much one has run.

bem_transcription: Ala ici icikuulwa balibikamo bamashini abengi elyo te eka uulimo bushe naumona ukuti kuli abantu nabambi?
eng_translation: This building has a lot of machines and she is not the only one in the room. Have you noticed that there are other people too?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune, muli umwaume naumbi, nankwe aletukusha umubili ukulabutuka pali ici cine cimashini, bushiku bumo nkakusendako uku kwine naiwe ukaye butukako.
eng_translation: I have seen, there is also another man that is exercising on the treadmill. One I will.take you to the gym so that you can also go and run.

bem_transcription: Nabaume bali pamancinga kumonafye ifyo balecofa, cipalile ukutila baleyapo kumo, finshi uletontonkanya?
eng_translation: Three are men on bicycles. Just looking at how they are cycling you can tell that they are going somewhere. What do you think?

bem_transcription: Awe nifyo fine nausosa, aba tebaume beka beka, elyo nga nalolekesha balemoneka kwati banakashi bonse pantu nabakwata amabele pacifuba.
eng_translation: These are not only men because if I look closely they look like they are women because they even have breasts.

bem_transcription: Niwe walanda, nshacimwenekesha elo kabili nabafwala ififimbo icakutila nangu cakuti balibutwishe incinga nga bapona tekuti baicene.
eng_translation: You are right I didnt see properly and they are wearing helmets such that if they fell they wouldn't hurt themselves.

bem_transcription: Elo uko balecofela ala nikumpanga nakalimo nikumabala, ifyani fyalyuma no kuma bushe naumone?
eng_translation: This place they are cycling from is in the bush maybe in the fields with dry grass. Have you noticed?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune fyalyuma, takwaba nowakutapilila atemwa imfula tailoka uku, lelo aba ndemona kwati nakalimo balecimfyanya ukucofe ncinga.
eng_translation: I have seen that they are dry and there is no one to water them and there are no rains. These people are competing.

bem_transcription: Boi somone, kuli umuntu umo uulefwaya ukuifuna, aleninika ulupili kaili tafwele ne shati, bushe uletontonkanya ukuti uyu muntu muntuntulu fye?
eng_translation: Pal come and see. There is a person who wants to hurt their self. They are climbing the mountain shirtless. Do you think they are normal?

bem_transcription: Ah, uyu muntu temuntuntulu nakalimo camba cimukolele, nomba nga cakutila aliponene, ala kuti ayumisha icimutwe pelibwe.
eng_translation: No this man is not normal or maybe the person is high because if they were to fall, they would hit their head on the rock.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati alefwaya ukunina pali ulu ulupili, nga afika pampela ya ulu ulupili elo atolokele pamenshi, bushe ulemona shani?
eng_translation: It looks like the person is climbing the mountain so that when they reach the top they jump intomthe water.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo ifyo walanda fyacine, nomba nangula cibe fyo alebika ubumi bwakwe mukaposa mweo, nomba bushe naumona amenshi?
eng_translation: That could be true, but regardless, they are putting their life at stake. But have you seen the water?

bem_transcription: Nimbona mune aya amenshi yalishunguluka ili line ilibwe ilyo umunyamata atemwa umulumendo aleninako aya amenshi yalilengama.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen. The water is surrounding this same rock that the young man is climbing and the water is very clear.

bem_transcription: Abana abaume kabili abasuma nabamwentula ilyo balesenda icikope nabafwala bwino bushe naumona ifyakufwala bafwele?
eng_translation: Two young boys are smilling as they are taking a picture and they are very well dressed. Have you seen how they are dressed?

bem_transcription: Ala aba boi ebaume, ebaume bene bene, mona fye ifyo balemoneka bwino nabafwala basuti abafiita kabili namashati yabuuta mukati babikapo notwakashika, pamuulu wamajaketi nababikapo namaluba.
eng_translation: These are real men. Just look at how they are looking in those black suits and white shirts and red ties. They even have flowers on their jackets.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala fisume fyo bafwele ifyakufwala, kumonafye nefyo bakakenye mumukoshi utwakshika tweka tweka ne shati ilyabuuta, kabili naumona ifyo bekete kuminwe?
eng_translation: You are right the clothes are very nice. Just looking at those red things they have tied around their necks and the white shirt, they look very good. And have you seen what they are holding in their hands.

bem_transcription: Ninfimona, nabekata ubwalwa ubo beta ukutila wine, nomba utumakapu natucepesha we, pantu ine aka kukakunkunmwina fye kapwa nokupwa.
eng_translation: Yes they are holding wine, but the cups are just too small. I can finish it in one gulp.

bem_transcription: Mwebena Afrika mwalishupa, abanenu banwa fye utunoono, imwe mufwaya mwapwisha fyonse, kabili uku bali bonse babili nikumutebeto uwabwinga.
eng_translation: Africans are sophisticated people. Our friends just take small sips but you want to finish everything. These people are at a wedding.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo alemoneka naluba, kabili kumonafye ifyo eminine ne miloleseshe yakwe, bushe naumona ifyo acitile?
eng_translation: This young man looks lost, you can tell by how he is standing and his look. Have you seen what he has done?

bem_transcription: Nimumona awe nakalimo kuli fye abo alelolela ebo alelolesha kumusebo tekumonafye namenso nayakashika
eng_translation: Yes I have seen, but maybe he is just waiting for someone that he is looking out for and that is why his eyes are red.

bem_transcription: Pambali yakwe pali shitata ali palamya kabili alelandako nabamo, bushe naumona icikuulwa cintu bemininepo?
eng_translation: There is a man on his side ok the phone and talking to someone. Have you seen the building he is standing on?

bem_transcription: Ici icikuulwa ciletiinya, cilemoneka cakale sana, nakalimo kuti caponena no muntu.
eng_translation: This building is looking risky. It looks very old and like it can collapse.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana cakale kabili citali sana kaili kumonafye balibikamo ne nshimbi muli ici cine cikuulwa.
eng_translation: Yes it is old and it is very tall that is why they even put metals in it.

bem_transcription: Boi isa tutambe ulubuli lwambwa ala somone ifyo  balaipaya imbwa inankwe ici icibwa cikali sana bushe naumona ifyo citolweke?
eng_translation: Pal! come we watch a dog fight. This other dog is very fierce it looks like it will kill the other one. Have you seen how it has jumped?

bem_transcription: Ala cikali elyo cikalamba, naumona aka akabwa ifyo aktinine elyo kuli naimbi iileisa ulubilo iilefwaya ukuisuma.
eng_translation: It is big and fierce. Have you seen how scared that small dog is? There is another one coming to bite it.

bem_transcription: Nimbona fye kabili nabakatengamina imbwa shibili elo kena kali fye keka ala balakepaya.
eng_translation: I have seen and the small one is just alone but these other dogs are two. They will kill it.

bem_transcription: Awe teti bakepaye pantu nimbona nimulubilo kali kalebutuka apa nangula cakutila kaleceba kunuma.
eng_translation: They can't kill it because it is running even though it is looking behind.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana walanda,kalabutuka, elo epo shilelwila, mumana uukalamba kabili uusuma kumonafye nefyo amenshi yalemoneka.
eng_translation: And where they are fighting from the river is very big and very nice. You can just see how the water is looking.

bem_transcription: Boi somone shitata kuno he! Nacimpapusha ine, ena alemona kwati ali mucishiba icikalamba ico bapanga fye namatafwali.
eng_translation: hey come and see this man! I am surprised. He thinks he is in a big pool made of bricks.

bem_transcription: Efyo ndepapa fye pano, naumona alemeka nokumeka, awe ukuyumfwisha bwino niwe mwine, tekumona alelilapo nakasabo, ala natemwa.
eng_translation: I'm equally surprised, just look at how he is smiling he is making himself happy and is even eating a fruit.

bem_transcription: Nimbona fye, nomba ici cine ekelemo bapanga fye ne mbao, kaili nafwala nomundeleshi uwabuuta, ala uyu muntu tomfwa.
eng_translation: I have seen. But this thing he is sitting in is made of wood and he is even wearing a white gown. This man is something else.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila amenshi ekelemo yantu yalamba, nakalimo nababikamo fimo.
eng_translation: Additionally the water he is sitting in is very dirty, maybe they have put something in it.

bem_transcription: Nimbona fye nayalamba, kaili naikalafye mufimenshi ifyalamba elo kumbali yakwe kuli abantu abalemulolesha.
eng_translation: yes I have seen and he is just sitting in dirty water and there are even people on his side looking at him.

bem_transcription: Boi somone, kwaba abantu abatiinya, imipentele yeka yeka, kuti watiina nga wamuloleshafye walalota, bushe walatemwa ukulolesha ifyo alemoneka?
eng_translation: Hey pal come and see this. Some people can scare you by just looking at them. The way they have painted their face just can give you a nightmare. Would you like to see?

bem_transcription: Yangu! Ala aletiinya, amenso kwati teyakwe, elyo uyu namayo mukote monafye iminkono kumenso.
eng_translation: She looks very scary! The eyes as if they are not hers. And this woman is old as can be seen from her wrinkled face.

bem_transcription: Awe nobe temukote kumonafye ifyo apentele efilelenga ukuti alemoneka kwati mukote monafye iminwe yakwe ilemoneka fye iyayemba iyacikashana.
eng_translation: No she is not old. It is just the painting that is making her look old. You can tell from the hands that she is a young woman.

bem_transcription: Niwebo walungika, iminwe tayafumba yena, elyo nintemwako fye umushishi untu akwata pantu walifiita.
eng_translation: You are right the arms look young and I love her hair, it looks dark.

bem_transcription: Kuminwe kumyakwe kuli ifintu fibili ekutila icakashika necafiita eco babomfya ilyo balepuputo mwela kabili nafwala ne ndeleshi iyakashika.
eng_translation: There are two things in her hands, a black and a red handfan and she is wearing a red dress.

bem_transcription: Naleumfwa ati kwaba abatali pesamba lya calo abanakshi, lelo elo namona, bushe naumona namayo uyu umutali?
eng_translation: I was just hearing that there are tall women out there and now I have seen one. Have you seen this tall woman?

bem_transcription: Ala uyu umukashana nimbona, ala mutali icine cine, elyo alyonda, nafwala necitoloshi icikulu.
eng_translation: This woman is very tall and she is slim and is wearing a big trousers.

bem_transcription: Balemoneka kwati nakalimo balipo kumo kabili balenwako nefyakunwa atemwa nidilinki elo bambi balenwa namenshi elo bambi balelanshanya.
eng_translation: It looks like they are somewhere having drinks and others are having water and others are just chatting.

bem_transcription: Nausosa, elo umu mulemoneka kwati nimumuputule wakulilamo, pantu ifyakulya nafifule cine cine emulandu wine beliile mukusendako fimo pantu ifyakulya nafifula icine cine.
eng_translation: You are right and this looks like the dining room because there is plenty of food and that is why they went to get some.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Boi somone alacena umunankwe yu, ilyo bacilapikana acitelela elyo ayapuma umunankwe mumoolu kabili umunankwe naima mumuulu.
eng_translation: Look at how this will hurt the friend. They were playing and this one did a tackle and hit the friend in the legs and now the friend is in the air.

bem_transcription: Iye, nga ni yu uuli panshi natine cine cine icakutila nabikako namaboko pakutila uyu umunankwe emuponena.
eng_translation: If it is this one below, he is very scared that he has even put his hands up so that the friend does not fall ok him.

bem_transcription: Ena boi alaiponena fye pamushili, acimwimya mumuulu elo uyu ena uulambalele apa acilafwaya fye ukuuma umupila.
eng_translation: This one will just fall on the ground. the one below wanted to hit the ball but hit the friend instead and raised him high up.

bem_transcription: Nintemwa ifyo iyi incende bangalilako nangu ukuteyelako umupila ilemoneka, ilemoneka bwino sana kabili balaipapilila.
eng_translation: I love how this place is looking. It is nice and we'll watered.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana ala palemoneka bwino, kabili aba abaice bacisendako inshita yabo pakuti bengatukusha umubili ukupitila mukuteya umupila.
eng_translation: Yes it looks very nice. And these young people found time come and play and exercise.

bem_transcription: Kwaba abantu bamo abaipubya, uyu ena epo aba, kumonafye nafula ishati elo alikwata ubupipi pamubili pamyakwe taulemfwako ne nsoni bushe naumona ifyo alecita?
eng_translation: There are people that make themselves look mad. look at him, he is shirtless with hairs on his body and he is not ashamed. Have you seen what he is doing?

bem_transcription: Nimumona, uyu shitata nakalimo aleumfwa bwino mona fye, ala cilepala kwati nafwenkula icine cine.
eng_translation: This man looks happy and he is dancing.

bem_transcription: Ukusansamuka mune takuibelele fye kweka, acinwamo umwangashi icakuti wamukola afula ne shati lyakwe.
eng_translation: This joy didn't just come on it's own. He must have taken some alcohol and after getting drunk he removed his shirt and started dancing.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo naulungika, nomba kuncende uku ala kuli abantu abengi sana bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: You could be right. But there are a lot of people in this place have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbamona, nomba nacimpapusha fye nafule shati kabili umubili wakwe walifula ubupiipi, elo uku kuli banamayo na bacaice.
eng_translation: Yes that is why I am surprised because he is shirtless and has hairs all over his body and he doesn't care that there are women and children around.

bem_transcription: Boi isa tutambe icangalo icakupunkana, nga cakuti wakwata ka bola akanoono balapepeka elo bakuwila somone ifyo babungene.
eng_translation: Come here and watch rugby with me my friend.

bem_transcription: Ala nimbamona, elo ici cangalo ine nkwena nshacitemwa pantu balapumana ububi balapunkana kwati nifilya nibamotoka bapunkana mubusanso.
eng_translation: I have seen but I don't like this game because they hit themselves badly like the way vehicles collide in an accident.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana emulandu wine bafwalile ifyakuicingilile imitwe icakutila nga aliponene panshi bamwilikisha tekuti bamucene.
eng_translation: You are right that is why they even wear those helmets so.thatnthey don't hurt themselves when they fall.

bem_transcription: Cishinka naulanda bwino, elo abantu nabesa abengi mukubatamba lintu baleteya ici icangalo nomba naumona ifyo icibansa cilemoneka iwe?
eng_translation: You are right and a lot of people have come to watch them play this game. And have you seen how the play ground is looking?

bem_transcription: Nicimona iwe, cilemoneka bwino elo uku baleteyela icangalo kwaba amayanda ayegi kwaba nefimuti ifingi nga nshi.
eng_translation: Yes I have see that it looks very nice. And there are trees and houses around.

bem_transcription: Uwacaice naya mumpanga kabili cilepala kwati nalimo ali fye eka, nomba umu mumpanga aleya mwaliba ifintu ifingi ifngalenga aba mubusanso.
eng_translation: A child has gone in the bush and it looks like it is just alone, but there are a lot of things in there that could hurt the child.

bem_transcription: Ee, nomba nakalimo iyi impanga tayaba nefiswango iyo, yaliba fye bwino emulandu wine bamulekele ukutila aleya mukwangala mumpanga eka.
eng_translation: True. But maybe this forest doesn't have dangerous animals and that is why they have let the child to go alone.

bem_transcription: Naulungika limbi alishiba sana iyi impanga limbi emo angalila cila bushiku kabili iyi impanga yaba ne fimuti ifingi.
eng_translation: You are right maybe the child knows the place very well because it plays from there everyday. The place has a lot of trees.

bem_transcription: Ala iyi impanga yalikwata ifimuti ifikalamba sana kabili ifitali elyo yalikwata nefyani ifingi
eng_translation: This forest has a lot of big tall trees and a lot of grass.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana kaili ifi ifimuti fyalititikana, kaili fikalamba, kaili mumpanga umo aleya mwaba namabwe ayakalamba kaili nayanoono.
eng_translation: It is true there are a lot of big trees that are closely parked, and there are small and big rocks.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nimumona nabifya napamenso, mona ifyo aminike milomo acefya napamenso kwati alewamya.
eng_translation: I have see that he has an angry face.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cimbi ico ntemenwe pali uyu umukashana cakutila nga nakalipa nafwala ifyakufwala ifilemoneka bwino akalishati akamakumbi makumbi notumishishi natusakula bwino.
eng_translation: Something else I love about this woman is that her clothes look very nice. She is wearing a blue shirt and her hair is well combed.

bem_transcription: Elyo uku kuncende kusume icine cine, kumonfye ifyo kulemoneka nangu icikope tacilemoneka bwino bwino.
eng_translation: This place looks very nice even though the picture is not very clear.

bem_transcription: Somone akabwa akanoono kabili akafunda amasako kabili kali kumpanga, nabakaposela kabola akanoono uletontonkanya ukuti kalacite nshi nakabola?
eng_translation: Look at the small fluffy dog that is in the forest. They have thrown a small ball at it. What do you think it is doing with the ball?

bem_transcription: Aka akabwa kalefwaya ukwanka kabola akali mumuulu akakashika, loleshafye ifyo kalolesheko.
eng_translation: This dog wants to catch the flying ball, just look at it's looking.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana, cilepala kwati nalimo uwacikaposela mwine atemwa uwacaice, lelo tatulemumona.
eng_translation: Very true. We can't see who through the ball but it should be the owner or just kids playing with it.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende kwalifula sana ifyani nefimuti, bushe naumona?
eng_translation: This place has a lot of trees and grass. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, ala fyalilelema icine cine kabili filemoneka fye katapa katapa, ala uku ifintu fyalifunda.
eng_translation: Yes they look very nice and very green.

bem_transcription: Abana besukulu bali mukalashi kabili balelembapo fimo elo umo naiminina, bushe uletontonkanya ukuti uyu namayo wiminine ninani?
eng_translation: Pupils are in a class writing and there is one standing. Who could this woman be?

bem_transcription: Uyu nikafundisha, alelanga abana ifyakulemba, nga natumona uyu umwana alelanga naposako sana amano.
eng_translation: This is the teacher showing them how to write and if you notice this child is very focussed.

bem_transcription: CIshinka sana uyu uo alelanga mwana umwaume kaili nafwala ishati lyafiita elo ne mishishi shakwe shinoono kabili shipi.
eng_translation: Yes this one being shown is a boy child and he is wearing a white shirt and has short hair.

bem_transcription: Uyu wine kafundisha ala nafwala icindeleshi icikulu elyo kwena tcilemoneka bwino we.
eng_translation: This teacher is wearing a big dress and it is not looking nice.

bem_transcription: Awe nacimulinga fye bwino apo mukalamba elo uwacaice umwanakashi yu alelembapo fimo mumashiwi kabili naposeshako sana amano.
eng_translation: The dress is fitting just fine just fine because she is a young woman. This child is writing something in words and is focussed.

bem_transcription: Iwe somone kuli icangalo cakucimfyanya uko kabili nabasukusa kamo akalemoneka kwati nakalimo nimbale, lelo aba babili nabema mumuulu, bushe naubamona?
eng_translation: Come and see this competition where they have thrown something that looks like a plate. These two are up in the air have you seen?

bem_transcription: Nimbona aba balefwaya ukukaanka cilepala kwati uwalakekata ninshi ewawina cangalo nacena ici.
eng_translation: Yes these people are trying to catch the disk and it looks like the one who catches it wins.

bem_transcription: Efyo cilepala nomba tacilepilibula ukuti uwalakekata ninshi ewawina, lelo ngo wakekata alasukushila umunankwe.
eng_translation: That's what it looks like but it doesn't mean when you catch it you win but you have to throw it to another person.

bem_transcription: Elo lintu baleteye ci cangalo bushiku, amalaiti nayabasanika bwino, icibansa icakutila conse cilemoneka nabantu balemoneka.
eng_translation: And as they are playing the lights have pointed at them in a way that all of them are visible.

bem_transcription: Elo aba bene abaleteye cangalo bengi sana, bambi nabafwala ifyakashika elo bambi nabafwala ifyabuuta, ala ici icangalo cilemoneka kwati cisuma.
eng_translation: These people playing the game are many. Others are wearing red and others are wearing white and this game looks like it is a very good game.

bem_transcription: Aba bantu boi nababuungana, kabili cilepala kwati nalimo pali ifyo baletamba, nomba nshishibe, bushe uletontonkanya ukuti balemona finshi kaili finshi balekopa?
eng_translation: These people are gathered and it's like there is something they are watching. But I don't know, What do you think they could be looking at and capturing?

bem_transcription: Aba bantu balemona umumana elyo nakabili kuliko no lupili apalepwila amenshi yamumana.
eng_translation: These people are watching the river and there is a mountain where the water from the river is ending.

bem_transcription: Walungika, kuli umumana uukalamba sana kaili kuli nolupili ulukulu emulandu wine belile uku mukutamba kaili balekopa.
eng_translation: You are right. There is a big river and a big mountain. That's is why these people went to watch and get pictures.

bem_transcription: Cimbi ico ntemenwe fintu ifyo incende iyi ilmoneka, ilemoneka iyabusaka icine cine, elyo yalibelako pakamulundu nomba bushe naumone fikuulwa?
eng_translation: Another thing I like is that this place looks very clean and it is at a high land. But have you seen the buildings?

bem_transcription: Nincimone cikuulwa cisuma sana kaili balicikuula bwino kaili cantunti, nga fimuti fyena balifibyala bwino ala umusebo ulemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: I have seen the building. It is beautiful and has been well built and is an upstairs building. The trees too have been well planted and the road looks very nice.

bem_transcription: Mona ifyo alepweneko uyu uwacilumendo, cilepala kwati limbi aleloleshapo fimo, nomba tauletontonkanya ukuti ukupweneka kwakwe kwalamulengesha ukuti alungwe?
eng_translation: Look at how this young man is carried away. It is like he is looking at something. But don't you think this kind of looking can cause a problem to him?

bem_transcription: Ee, kwena kuli ifyo alelolesha nakalimo acitile kwati nifilya bamwita ukuti iwe cite! Elo aloleshako
eng_translation: Yes he is looking at something. It is like someone called out to him and then he turned to look.

bem_transcription: Nakalimo efyo cilepala kabili umu emo bali nimumuputule wakwipikila, kumonafye ifyo aleipika ifyakulya nafiwame cine cine.
eng_translation: It looks like so and they are in the kitchen and just looking at the food they are cooking you can tell it's very tasty.

bem_transcription: Elyo aba bonse abaleipika nabafwala ifyakufwala ifyapalana, nabafwala ifyafiita, ala ifyafiita fisuma pantu teti filambe nomuto.
eng_translation: The ones cooking are all wearing black similar clothes. Black is good because it doesn't get dirty with the soup.

bem_transcription: Cishinka elo umuputule baleipikila ulemoneka bwino, kabili muli ne nsani ishingi ala ifi ifyakulya baleipika fyalawama kubantu abalalya.
eng_translation: Very true and this room looks very good with a lot of dishes. I'm sure this food will be very good to the ones who will be eating.

bem_transcription: Uyu shukulu bantu ali pacikuulwa kabili nakwata inyunshipepala iyo alebelenga, bushe naumona ifyo atontele amenso panyunshipepala.
eng_translation: This man is at a building and is reading a newspaper. Have you seen how this old man is focussed on the news paper?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, nakalimo kuli ilyashi ilyamusungusha, kushelefye ukutila asame akanwa apape.
eng_translation: I have seen. It is like the story has surprised him and he is only remaining with opening his mouth in amazement.

bem_transcription: Kabili inyunshipepala imbi ili pamingomo, kabili imingomo shili shine.
eng_translation: And the other newspapers are on the buckets and the buckets are four in total.

bem_transcription: CIshinka elo apa eminine nipanse fye yacikuulwa nangula ifiibi fyacikuulwa nafisalwa.
eng_translation: True, and where he is standing is outside a building  even though the doors of this building are closed.

bem_transcription: Iciibi bacipangile ne mbao kabili mwapita ne fishimbi kabili ici icikuulwa balicipenta ne langi lyapusanako.
eng_translation: The door has been made with wood and some metal and this building has a unique color.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ala imbwa ishi shisume cine cine kumonafye ifyo amasako yayemba bwino elo abene balibikako amano ukushisamfya.
eng_translation: These dogs are very beautiful. You can just tell by their nice fur and their owners pay attention to bathing them.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana balashiposako amano
eng_translation: It is true they are well kept.

bem_transcription: Ulu ululamba lwamumana takwaba umucanga, ndemonko fye amabwe ayanoono nayo.
eng_translation: This sea shore does not have sand. I can only see small stones.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili uyu umumana walipabuka kabili amenshi yalemoneka fye ayalengama kabili ayasuma.
eng_translation: And this river is wide and the water looks clean and nice.

bem_transcription: Boi somone, umunobe alefwaya ukuibika mukaposa mweo, naima ne ncinga mumuulu bushe naumona?
eng_translation: Friend, come and see! Your friend has put his life at risk have you see how high he has jumped with the bicycle?

bem_transcription: Ah! Nimbona, ah uyu tacindika ubumi ala alaikula ameno mona fye ifyo atolweke.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen! This one doesnt respect life. He will fall, just look at how he has jumped.

bem_transcription: Nimbona nakalimo efyo acita fye cila bushiku nakalimo ici icangalo eco ateya fye cila bushiku.
eng_translation: I have seen. Maybe he does this everyday.

bem_transcription: Elyo nga cakutila aliponene pa mushili apa pantu pakosa pantu pali na mabwe. Bushe naumona ifyo incende ilemoneka?
eng_translation: And if he fell, this ground is hard and has rocks. Have you seen how this place is looking?

bem_transcription: Incende ilemoneka fye bwino kabili yalikwata ifikulwa ifikalmaba kabili no musebo baliwamya bwino mulepita ne myotoka..
eng_translation: This place looks nice and it has big buildings and a well kept road where vehicles are even passing.

bem_transcription: Abaume bane balebutuka ulubilo kabili babili nafwala bakaputula abepi kabili bambi nafwala amatoloshi ayatali.
eng_translation: For men are running wearing small shorts while others are wearing long pants.

bem_transcription: Iciimpapwisheko cakutila iyi incende yalitalala icine cine teti njeshe ukufwala kaputula pakubutuka. Mona elyo bacita notumolu utunono.
eng_translation: What is surprising is that this place is cold and I wouldn't dare wear a short when running. look at them, they even have small legs.

bem_transcription: Nijishiba nacikupapisana lelo aba bantu balibelela pantu kumwabo kwalitalala sana emulandu wine balebutukila umusango uyu.
eng_translation: I know it has surprised you but these people are used because their home is very cold that is why they are able to run like this.

bem_transcription: Cishinka iyi incende balibela abekalako ntemenweko fye ifikulwa ala filemoneka bwino elo babomfeshe fye amatafwali pa ku kuula.
eng_translation: Yes they are used. And the buildings in this place look good even when they just used bricks to build.

bem_transcription: Ee ifikulwa balifikula bwino kabili fitali kabili fikalamba elo mwisamba lya fikulwa muli ne myotoka.
eng_translation: Yes the buildings have been well built, they are big and tall and there are even vehicles below.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo elo na bakashana babili nabeminina umukashana umo alemoneka uwamwentula elo umbi naipeta fye na maboko. Bushe naumona ifyo umwaume acitile?
eng_translation: A young man and two young men are standing, one young woman is smiling and the other is just folding her arms. Have you seen what the young man has done?

bem_transcription: Nimbona uyu umwaume abikile amaboko yakwe mu ca fita nakalimo talefwaya ukuposha aba bakashana.
eng_translation: I have seen. He has out his hands in that black thing it's like he doesn't want to greet these young women.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Naulungika nakalimo umu ni mucikulwa ca bwalwa nabaya mukunwako kumona fye uyu umukashana ulu pakati alemoneka kwati nanwa!
eng_translation: You are right. Maybe they are in a bar where they are drinking because the young woman in the middle looks drunk.

bem_transcription: Cishinka elo cungulo bushiku elo uyu umukashana uo tulemona uku afwele fye akampimpinya kabili uku kuntu kwalitalala kumona fye ifyo afwele umukashana ufwele ifya fita.
eng_translation: It is true and it is in the evening and this other young woman is wearing skimpy clothes even though this place is cold. You can tell by how the other young woman in black is dressed.

bem_transcription: Imbwa isuma sana ileyangala mulubansa.
eng_translation: A beautiful dog is playing in the yard.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elo iyi ine imbwa iya yemba icili iyana tailakula sana.
eng_translation: This same beautiful dog is still just a puppy.

bem_transcription: Elo bushe naumona ati iyi imbwa yaka ena naikwata kantu baikakila mu mukoshi?
eng_translation: Have you seen that this same dog has something around it's neck?

bem_transcription: Eya nikamona cilepala kwati palembwa ishina lya mwine uwaiteka
eng_translation: I have seen. It's like it has the name of the owner of the dog written on it.

bem_transcription: Abana abnono balumendo na bakashana bel-enda mu musebo kabili nabafwala fimo fine. Bushe uletontonkaya finshi balecita?
eng_translation: Young boys and girls are walking in the road and they are wearing the same. What do you think they are doing?

bem_transcription: Aba abana nabemya icikope elyo bele baleimba mu musebo.
eng_translation: These children are raising a picture and they are singing.

bem_transcription: Cishinka sana balimba mu musebo cilepala kwati uwimine apa umukashana ni kafundisha wabo.
eng_translation: Yes they are standing and it's like this woman standing is their teacher.

bem_transcription: Awe uyu tekafundisha eminefye mukubatamba pantu nabesala umusebo elyo alefwaya bapite.
eng_translation: This is not their teacher. She is just standing and watching them because they have closed the road and she wants to pass

bem_transcription: Nakalimo elo uku kwine bali kwaba icikulwa icikalamba ico ba penta ne langi ilya buta kabili cakwata inceshi ishikalamba kabili ishafina.
eng_translation: Maybe. And there is a big building that has been painted white where they are and it has big and heavy pillars.

bem_transcription: Inama ya mpanga ili mu mpanga. bushe naumona ifyo imishe ku kanwa?
eng_translation: A wild animal is in the bush. Have you seen how it's raising its mouth?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona ndemona naikwata nakalimo cimuti ici isendele ku kwanwa.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen and it is carrying something like a stick in its mouth.

bem_transcription: Awe nga nalolekesha sana apa tacilepala kwati kamuti cilepala kwati ka sabi imishe.
eng_translation: If I look closely that doesn't look like a stick but like a fish.

bem_transcription: Eya niwe walanda nalimo cishinka ka sabi.
eng_translation: You are right. Maybe it is a fish.

bem_transcription: Elo uku ni ku mpanga sana pantu no mushili ulemoneka fye uwaibela cilepala kwati incende yaba ukutali no kwikala bantu.
eng_translation: This looks like deep in the bush because even the soil looks unique. It's like this place is isolated from where humans stay.

bem_transcription: Umwana umulumendo aleyangala nakwata ico aleangasha ica kupupusha.
eng_translation: A young boy is playing with a kite.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cishinka elo ifya kufwala afwele nafipalanako nacilya ale pupusha pantu afwele ica kashikila na muli cilya alepupusha muli icakashikila.
eng_translation: True and the colour of the clothes he is wearing are similar to that of his kite because he is wearing red and his kite had red in it.

bem_transcription: Kuncende ali iya kaena intu ya yemba pantu balikulako ne fikulwa ifitali.
eng_translation: The place where he is is very nice and had long buildings.

bem_transcription: Ni ntemwa ifyo ifikulwa filemoneka pantu ifikulwa ni filya ifya ntunti ifitali.
eng_translation: I love how the buildings are looking because they are upstair buildings.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naiminia pa mutenge wacikulwa.
eng_translation: A young man is standing on the roof of a building.

bem_transcription: Uyu Umulumendo ni finshi alecita pa mutenge wa cikulwa ici?
eng_translation: What is this young man doing on the roof of the building?

bem_transcription: Eminine pa mutende mukupupwa umwela.
eng_translation: He is on the roof to get some air.

bem_transcription: Ngo yu umbi umulumendo uulemoneka panshi nga ena afumine mucikuulwe ici?
eng_translation: What about this young man below? Is he from this building?

bem_transcription: Ee, afumine mucikuulwa ici nga namulolesha iciibi naciisuka kunuma yakwe.
eng_translation: Yes he is from this building because if you notice the door is open behind him.

bem_transcription: Abantu nabeminina apo bashitisha ifisabo ifyalekana lekana.
eng_translation: People are standing where they sell different fruits.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona uyu umwaume no mwanalashi abaminine kunuma ukutila balemoneka abalamba?
eng_translation: But have you seen that this man and woman standing behind look dirty?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, balemoneka abalamba, nakalimo bacipitila apo bacilapenta elo penti yabetikila.
eng_translation: Yes they are dirty. Maybe they passed near where they were painting and the paint spilled on them.

bem_transcription: Nga nalolesha bwino sana, nakabili ndemona ili line mukati mwetuuka balabomfya ifi ifisabo ukupangilako ifyakulya.
eng_translation: Is I look closely in this shop, they are using the same fruits to make some food.

bem_transcription: Shitata ali no mwana wakwe namulela pamoolu yakwe.
eng_translation: A man is with his child on his laps.

bem_transcription: Umwana wakwe wine alemoneka nakalimo aleshipula.
eng_translation: The child looks like it is dosing.

bem_transcription: Uku kuncende bali niparka pantu nabantu abengi nabeminina balelesha icitendwe.
eng_translation: This place looks like a park because a lot of people are standing and having leisure.

bem_transcription: Nakuparka yakaena cilepala bacisenda nefyakwanshika pakutusha.
eng_translation: It looks like they took mats to the same park to put below when they want to rest.

bem_transcription: Uyu wine shitata cipalile kwati kuli ifyo alelolesha kuntashi ifisendele amano yakwe sana.
eng_translation: It's like there is something this man is looking at in front of him that has gotten his attention.

bem_transcription: Akabwa akafiitulukila nakeminina.
eng_translation: A blackish dog is standing.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati ine ndemona kwati nakaluba pantu nakalolekesha kuntashi uko.
eng_translation: I think it is lost because it is just looking in front.

bem_transcription: Kabili nga twalolekesha bwino bwino sana cilemoneka nabakakakila pantu nakakwata intambo mumukoshi.
eng_translation: When we look closely it's like it is on a leash because there is a rope around it's neck.

bem_transcription: Elo iyi incende kaliko ni ncende iisuma sana pantu iswilefye namaluba ayabuuta.
eng_translation: This dog is in a beautiful place full of white flowers.

bem_transcription: Akamwana kali mucimushelemuko.
eng_translation: A child is on a slide.

bem_transcription: Mucimushelemuko cakaena mulemoneka umwalibuuta nakalimo mwaliba icisanikilo.
eng_translation: It looks bright in this slide it's like it has lights in it.

bem_transcription: Awe tecisanikilo, lubuto lwakasuba akalefuma panse, kulya umwana aleya mukufumina.
eng_translation: No it doesn't have lights, it's just the light from the sun that is coming from where the child will come out from.

bem_transcription: Eya, niwe walanda bwino elo kabili mumushelemuko wakaena mulemoneka uwakatapa katapa.
eng_translation: You are right and it looks green on this slide.

bem_transcription: Elo uyu wine umushelemuko walitelela sana ici cilangukila abana ukushelemuka bwino.
eng_translation: This slide is very smooth and that is why children can easily slide.

bem_transcription: Abakashana nabalumendo bambi nabeminina elo bambi bekele mumbali yacikuulwa.
eng_translation: Young men and young women are standing while others are sitting on the side of a building.

bem_transcription: Elo pantu bali palemoneka nipesukulu lyamasambililo yakalamba.
eng_translation: It looks like they are at a university.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, pantu nimbona bonse bali notufyola elo uyu umbi alebelengapo nacimo kuminwe.
eng_translation: You are right because they all have bags and this one is reading something in his hands.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili nefikuulwa fine filemoneka ifyayemba nga nshi elyo nifilya ifitali fitali.
eng_translation: And the buildings look very nice and they are tall.

bem_transcription: Kuli umukashana umo naikumbata, cilepala kwati alelolesha uyu umulumendo uulefumina kuntashi yakwe uufwele ifyafiita.
eng_translation: A young woman is folding her arms, it's like she is looking at the young man coming from her front wearing black.

bem_transcription: Akabwa nakakwata cimo kukanwa.
eng_translation: A dog has something in its mouth.

bem_transcription: Ca cine pantu naikwata kabola kukanwa cilepala kuli uo shiletwalila.
eng_translation: Yes it has a ball in its mouth. It's like it's taking it to someone.

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilepala nikulya ukushafula abantu nabantu abekalako bonse balimi.
eng_translation: This place doesn't seem to have a lot of people and the majority of people found here are farmers.

bem_transcription: Cishinka pantu incende yakaena balikako nobucingo.
eng_translation: Yes because the place even has a fence.

bem_transcription: Ubu ubucingo babikako nangula umupaka wakulekanya luno lubali nalulya lubali nokucingilila imbwa ukulaya kubena mupalamano.
eng_translation: That fence they have put is a demarcation between this side and thatside and it is also to prevent the dogs from going to the neighbors places.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo nanina kucimuti icitali mukuswa ifisabo.
eng_translation: A young man has climbed a tall tree to collect some fruits.

bem_transcription: Elyo alemoneka uwansansa pantu naswa icisabo kaili naikata namuminwe.
eng_translation: He looks happy because he has plucked a big fruit and is holding it in his hands.

bem_transcription: Uhm, nomba bushe naumona ifyo ekete, bushe teti apusumuka apona nokupona?
eng_translation: But have you seen how he is holding it? Can he not mis a step and fall?

bem_transcription: Ca cine pantu ekete icimuti nokuboko kumo limbi nalimo teti apone alibelela.
eng_translation: You are right because he is holding the tree with just one hand. But maybe he is used and so he can't fall.

bem_transcription: Nangu kubelesha ukunina icimuti teifyo iyo, mona fye icifuba ifyo catuumuka bwino pamulandu wakunina icimuti cila bushiku.
eng_translation: But even if he is used, it shouldn't be like this. Just look at how big his chest had gotten from climbing the tree daily.

bem_transcription: Abantu abapusana pusana baleenda mumbali yamusebo.
eng_translation: Different people are walking on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Ca cine pantu nashitata umo ifi alemoneka uwapapa.
eng_translation: It is true because even one man looks surprised.

bem_transcription: Nimbona nakalimo efyo acita fye cila bushiku, ici icangalo echo ateyafye cilabushiku.
eng_translation: I have seen. But maybe he plays this game daily.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilemoneka abantu abengi eyo babomfya sana nga balepita.
eng_translation: This place looks like a lot of people pass through it.

bem_transcription: Namayo alebutuka mumabali yamusebo.
eng_translation: A woman is running on the side of the road.

bem_transcription: Nafwala nefyakufwala ifyafiita kabili mwapita nefyabuuta.
eng_translation: She is wearing black clothes with white in them.

bem_transcription: Mukati mwacibumba mulemoneka cibansa umwakwangalila ifyangalo.
eng_translation: Inside the wall, there seems to be a play ground.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili kumbali yamusebo yakaeana takupitana abantu pantu aliko fye eka.
eng_translation: And people don't pass on this side of the road because she is just alone.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati uyu namayo aleipekanishisha ukuyateya icangalo cimo mukati mwa cibansa.
eng_translation: It looks like this woman is preparing herself to go and play a certain game inside the play ground.

bem_transcription: Akabwa akayemba bwino sana akabuuta kaletoloka.
eng_translation: A beautiful white dog is jumping.

bem_transcription: Bushe kutoloka ku? Ndemona nakalimo kubutuka, kalebutuka pakati yamusebo.
eng_translation: Could this be jumping? I think it is running in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Naulungika, cilepala kwati nakanaka nokunaka pantu nakafumya nolulimi.
eng_translation: You are right and it looks tired because it is sticking it's tounge out.

bem_transcription: Elo mumbali yamusebo mwine mulemoneka mwaliba icani cayemba nga nshi icakatapa katapa.
eng_translation: And there is beautiful green grass on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati nipa n'ganda fye epo kaleangalila.
eng_translation: It looks like it is playing at the house.

bem_transcription: Abakashana baleshana.
eng_translation: Young women are dancing.

bem_transcription: Uku baleshanina kulemoneka ukusuma kusuma, nikwisa baleshanina uku?
eng_translation: The place where they are dancing from looks nice. Where could this be?

bem_transcription: Uku baleshanina nikuntu bateyela ubwangalo bwakuminwe ubo batila basketball.
eng_translation: This is where they play basketball from.

bem_transcription: Nomba ukushana uku bushe nakwena ebwangalo bwa basket ball?
eng_translation: Is this dancing also part of playing basketball?

bem_transcription: Awe nakalya, balesansamusha ibumba pamulandu wakutila bakateya ba bwangalo baletusha.
eng_translation: No they are just entertaining the crowd as the players are resting.

bem_transcription: Namayo naikata ifyakulya pa mbale mukati ke tuuka.
eng_translation: A woman is holding food on a plate inside a shop.

bem_transcription: Mwittuka line li mulemoneka nakalimo bashitishamo ifyakulya.
eng_translation: This shop looks like they only seel food in it.

bem_transcription: Elo nakabili alemoneka uwansansa, pantu lintu ekete imbale yakwe naseka nokuseka.
eng_translation: She looks happy because she is even laughing as she is holding the plate.

bem_transcription: Elo icilensansamusha cakwebati ati mwituuka line ifintu balifitantika bwino, balikambatika nemitengo kucibumba.
eng_translation: The amazing thing is things have been well arranged in this shop and thy have stuck the prices for the items on the wall.

bem_transcription: Cishinka elo lilemoneka ilyabusaka, nomulandu balembele imitengo kucibumba kwafwa abaleshita.
eng_translation: You are right and it looks clean.Also they have stuck the prices to help the customers.

bem_transcription: Abantu nabaya kumatuuka mukushita ifintu ifyalekana lekana.
eng_translation: People have gone to the shops to buy different things.

bem_transcription: Umo shitata naiminina pa mwinshi alemona ifyakufwala ifyo batantike.
eng_translation: One man is standing on the entrance looking at the clothes on display.

bem_transcription: Elo ifi fine ifyakufwala fintu alemona filemoneka kwati mashati, limbi ishati lili ilyabuuta, limbi ilyamakumbi makumbi, limbi ilyakatapa katapa.
eng_translation: The clothes he is looking at are shirts. There is a white shirt, a blue one and a green one.

bem_transcription: Ena katwishi ena uko aleya taposeleko namano kufwakufwala.
eng_translation: I don't know where he is going and he is not even paying attention to the clothes.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe uyu wine shitata kuli banamayo babili nabena baleloleshe fyakufwala ifilemoneka kwati fitenge.
eng_translation: There are two women behind this man who look like they are looking at wraps.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo alecofa incinga.
eng_translation: A young man is riding a bicycle.

bem_transcription: Nafwala ne shati ilyakatapakatapa ne cimpompo kumutwe icakatapakatapa.
eng_translation: He is wearing a green shirt and a green helmet.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo alemoneka ali pa cangalo cakucimfyanya icakucofa amacinga.
eng_translation: This young man looks like he is in a cycling competition.

bem_transcription: Nomba pantu alepita palemoneka kwati nalimo palibe cilindi, teti wapona nokupona?
eng_translation: But there seems to be a hole where he is passing. Can't he fall like this?

bem_transcription: Awe, teti apone monafye ifyo atundeme pakucofe ncinga nga kale aponene nomba taponene.
eng_translation: No he can't fall. Just look on how focussed he is as he is riding.

bem_transcription: Shitata nanamayo bali pa cangalo cakushana.
eng_translation: A man and a woman are at a dancing game.

bem_transcription: Namayo afwele ilaya lyakashika ne nsapato ishakashika kabili nefyakuicingilila kuminwe nafyo ifyakashika.
eng_translation: The woman is wearing a red dress, red shoes and red gloves.

bem_transcription: Elo cilepala balishibisha ukushana kumona fye ifyo beminine lintu baleshana.
eng_translation: It looks like these two really know how to dance by just looking at how they are standing.

bem_transcription: Uyu namayo ashintilile kuli shitata, nomba uyu shitata nga aselako fye panono uyu namayo ninshi kuti apona
eng_translation: This woman is leaning on the man. If this man just moves, the woman can fall.

bem_transcription: Eya nimbona patu nashitata wine pakutila eponya uyu namayo naiminina munshila iyakutila teti atalantante.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen. Even this man is standing in a way that he cannot lose his balance and make the woman fall.

bem_transcription: Umukashana nabantu bambi nabaya kuncende uko baimba icishiba cakusambamo mukusamba.
eng_translation: A young woman and other people have gone to a swimming pool.

bem_transcription: Namayo umo ena naikalako fye ena alelolesha pali lamya elo kunuma yakwe fye kuli abakashana babili bena balesamba.
eng_translation: One woman is just sitting looking at her phone but the young women behind her are swimming.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo namayo uyu uulelolesha pali lamya afwele?
eng_translation: But have you seen what this woman looking at her phone is wearing?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona nafwala ifyakusambilamo, elo pambali yakwe nabikapo nakabale apali utufyakulya.
