bem_transcription: Abafyashi babo nababashindika mukuya bafwako mukulumba.
eng_translation: Their parents have gone to cheer them.

bem_transcription: Bushe finshi ulemona uyu umukashana uli pantanshi ufwele icabuta alecita?
eng_translation: What do you think this young woman in front wearing white is doing?

bem_transcription: Alemoneka nakalimo aletotela abanakwe baleangala nomba nga walolekesha futi cilemoneka nakalimo pali abalemukopa icikope.
eng_translation: It looks like she is clapping for her friends who are playing and again it looks like there is someone taking a pictures of her.

bem_transcription: Aba bashitata baka ena balebika umupipe wa menshi
eng_translation: Men are putting a water pipe.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili bali pa mulimo ku ncende iya yemba bwino sana.
eng_translation: Two men are working at a very beautiful place.

bem_transcription: Ee kwena nimbona kunuma kuli ci mazembe icilebafwa ukubomba uyu umulimo.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen there is a grader behind that is helping them do the work.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo bushe naumona ukutila kuli ico balebonfya?
eng_translation: Have you seen that there is something they are using that is behind them?

bem_transcription: Uulelishe ngoma shakaeana afwele icafiita nakwata notumuti kuminwe kabili alemoneka uwafulwa pamenso.
eng_translation: The one playing the drums is wearing black and has two sticks in his hand and is looking angry on his face.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo nomukashana nabekala kumbali yamumana.
eng_translation: A young man and a young woman are seated on the river banks.

bem_transcription: Elyo baleumfwa bwino pantu nabekala mupepi sana nabapalamana.
eng_translation: They are enjoying because they are very close to each other.

bem_transcription: Kumumana wakaena kwaliba ukwayemba sana pantu balipangako notwakutushishamo pakati kamumana.
eng_translation: This place looks very good because they have even made places where you can rest in the middle of the river.

bem_transcription: Elyo kumbali yamumana kulemoneka impili ishitali sana elo mumbali sana mulemoneka namayanda.
eng_translation: And there are very long trees on the sides of the river and some houses too.

bem_transcription: Nomba nga lolekesha bwino sana, aba bekele apa nabafwala ifyampepo nakalimo kwaliba ukwatalala sana kumumana.
eng_translation: If you look closely these people seated here are wearing jerseys. It's like it is very cold here.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo bali pancito umo ali mumotoka alelonga amatafwali, elo umo eulemupelekesha, babili baletamba.
eng_translation: Young men are working. One is in the vehicle unpacking the blocks and another is down getting the blocks from the one in the vehicle and stacking them.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati aya amatafwali eyo balebomfya ukukulila ici icikuulwa icilemoneka kumbali icishilapwa.
eng_translation: It looks like these are the blocks they are using to build this unfinished building on the side.

bem_transcription: Ee, tacilapwa ukukuula ici icikuulwa pantu cilemoneka kwati amatafwali aya baletele eyo balabomfya ukupwishisha ukukuula.
eng_translation: Yes it is unfinished because it looks like these blocks that they have brought are the ones they will use to finish.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo bakaena balemoneka abalamba pantu umulimo wamakuule ulalamfya.
eng_translation: The young men look dirty.

bem_transcription: Niwe walanda, ca cine balemoneka abalamba elyo kabili balemoneka abanaka.
eng_translation: You are right. They look dirty and tired.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu nakwela pali honda.
eng_translation: An old man is on a motorcycle.

bem_transcription: Nge fi afwele ukuifimba umubili onse bushe fyanshi?
eng_translation: What is the use of this thing he is wearing that is covering he whole body?

bem_transcription: Ifi afwele fyakuicingilila ukukanaicena nga apona.
eng_translation: They are to protect him from getting hurt when he falls.

bem_transcription: Nomba alebutushisha kwisa honda ine?
eng_translation: Where is he speeding the motorcycle to?

bem_transcription: Alebutusha kumulandu wakuti balecilikana nabanankwe.
eng_translation: He is speeding because they are competing.

bem_transcription: Umukashana ali mucibansa alemoneka kwati acilateya ubwangalo nomba elo apona.
eng_translation: A young woman is in the pitch. It's like they were playing a game and she fell.

bem_transcription: Ukupona kwakaena cilemoneka kwati kuli fimo ifyo acilafwaya ukwikata efyalenga ukuti apone.
eng_translation: It looks like she was trying to catch something and then she fell.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba aba bene bantu abalemutamba tabafulile banoono fye sana.
eng_translation: The people that are watching are nit many but just a few.

bem_transcription: Abantu beshile mukutamba amangalo nabesa ne myotoka shabo, nabashiminika kumbali yacibansa.
eng_translation: The people that have come to watch the game have come with their personal cars parked outside.

bem_transcription: Shitata ali pancito, cilemoneka alekwempa ifyani.
eng_translation: A man is working. It looks like he is slashing.

bem_transcription: Elyo nafwala icakumucingilisha kumutwe.
eng_translation: And he is wearing a helmet.

bem_transcription: Mupepi yakwe naiminika namotoka iyakashika.
eng_translation: There is a red car parked near him.

bem_transcription: Elo tali eka kuli no munankwe ulya uufuleme mupepi motoka.
eng_translation: And he is not alone but with a friend who has bent there near the car.

bem_transcription: Nomba motoka yakaena ilemoneka iyafiiko nampo nga baiwamishepo nalisa katwishi.
eng_translation: The vehicle looks dirty. I wonder when last it was cleaned.

bem_transcription: Abantu nabemya amaboko mumuulu.
eng_translation: People are raising their hands.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilemoneka kwati baleshana nangula baleimba.
eng_translation: It looks like they are either dancing or singing.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilemoneka cungulo ci pantu kulemoneka ukwafiitililako panoono.
eng_translation: It looks it is in the evening because it looks a bit dark.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo kuli icikuulwa icitali icafiita.
eng_translation: There is a tall dark building behind them.

bem_transcription: Elo nipanse bali apa namakumbi yalemoneka.
eng_translation: And they are outside as we can even see the clouds.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo batatu bali kucibansa nabanina napali bakalwe.
eng_translation: Three young men are at a ground on to top of horses.

bem_transcription: Nabantu nabesa kucibansa mukutamba abalumendo.
eng_translation: People have come to this play ground to watch them.

bem_transcription: Mucibansa cakaena mwalifulisha imicanga.
eng_translation: There is a lot of sand in the same pitch

bem_transcription: Abantu cilepala kwati tabatemwa sana ubu ubwangalo bwabakabalwe pantu banoono beshile mukutamba.
eng_translation: It looks like not a lot of people enjoy this game because very few have come to watch.

bem_transcription: Elo abalumendo bene abaninine pali bakalwe bonse nabafwala ifyapalana notusote utwapalana.
eng_translation: The men on horses are wearing similar clothes and similar hats.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo no mukashana bali mucikuulwa ca bwalwa.
eng_translation: A young man and an young woman are in a bar.

bem_transcription: Elyo kunuma yabo kuli umukashana uwikete akalibotolo kamenshi.
eng_translation: And behind them is a young woman holding a bottle of water.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo no mukashana balemoneka abansansa.
eng_translation: This young man and young woman look happy.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka ubwalwa bacilanwa bukali nabakolwa, elo umukashana alesabaila sana bushe naumona?
eng_translation: It looks like the alcohol was very strong and they are drunk, and the young woman has started wild talking. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Ca cine nimbona elo mucikuulwa cakaena muli abantu abengi sana.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen. And there are a lot of people in the very bar.

bem_transcription: Umukashana ali panse aleyanika ifyakufwala.
eng_translation: A woman is outside hanging clothes on the line.

bem_transcription: Elo alemoneka uyu nikasunga wan'ganda, pantu nafwala ne fyakufwala fyakwa kasunga wan'ganda.
eng_translation: She looks like she's a maid because she is dressed like one.

bem_transcription: Kuntu aleanika ifyakufwala kwalipalamina namumpanga pantu kunuma yakwe kuli ifimuti
eng_translation: Where she is hanging the clothes is near a bush because there are a lot of trees behind her.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ukutila icakufwala aleanika nacibuuta bwino sana?
eng_translation: Have you seen that the clothe she is hanging is very clean?

bem_transcription: Ca cine nacibuuta bwino sana ukubikapo fye necicine icikonkelepo naco nacibuuta.
eng_translation: Yes I have see. Even the one that follows is very clean.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili bali pancito umo nanina pamuulu wamutanto elo umo naikatila umunankwe umutanto.
eng_translation: Two men are working, one is on the ladder and the other is holding the ladder.

bem_transcription: Nakabili cilemoneka kwati balebike fyamalaiti.
eng_translation: It looks like they are putting something electrical.

bem_transcription: Kuncende bali kulemoneka balibikako nokwakwiminika bamotoka.
eng_translation: There is even a parking place where they are.

bem_transcription: Bamotoka babapangila mukati kafikuulwa emo babemika.
eng_translation: The vehicles are parked inside the buildings.

bem_transcription: Ifikuulwa fyakaena fyaba uku kuncende iyi fitali.
eng_translation: The buildings in this place are very tall.

bem_transcription: Umwana  umukashana naiminina naikata ne fyakwangasha ku minwe.
eng_translation: A young girl is standing holding toys in her hands.

bem_transcription: Elyo umu muntu ali ni mu ng'anda pantu kunuma kulemoneka ne fitabo.
eng_translation: It looks like she is in the house because there are even books behind her.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ukutila alikwata imishishi ishitali?
eng_translation: Have you seen that she had long hair?

bem_transcription: Ca cine nimbona imshishi shakwe shitali elyo nafwala nakashti akafita mwapita notwabuta utumiline.
eng_translation: Yes her hair is long and she is wearing a black shirt with white lines.

bem_transcription: Banamayo babili no mulumendo umo bali pa lwendo umo namayo alekunkulusha ne njinga.
eng_translation: Two women and a young man are on a journey. One of the women is wheeling a bicycle.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ukutila pantanshi ya uyu ulekunkulusha incinga aba bantu babili nabekata fimo ku minwe?
eng_translation: Have you seen that the two people in from of this woman wheeling a bicycle are holding something in their hands?

bem_transcription: Ca cine nimbona nabeka imyanfuli.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen that they are holding umbrellas.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati kuli akasuba akakali sana nangula imfula.
eng_translation: It looks like there is either a brazing sun or rains.

bem_transcription: Ca cine elo kuntu bali uku kwaliba ne fikulwa ifitali nga nshi.
eng_translation: Yes and there are very tall buildings in this place where they are.

bem_transcription: Abantu bali mucikulwa ca fyangalo baleangala bambi baletamba.
eng_translation: People are in a games building playing while others are watching.

bem_transcription: Nakabili aba abeminine pakati ebene bafyangalo ebalangala.
eng_translation: These ones standing in the middle are the owners of the games.

bem_transcription: Mu cikulwa ca fyangalo caka ena mwalifula imicanga ishingi.
eng_translation: There is a lot of sand in the same building for games.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ifyo uyu umulumendo ufwele ifya buta acitile?
eng_translation: Have you seen what this young man in white has done?

bem_transcription: Nimbona natoloka ukufuma pa muulu elo kwati alefwaya ukwingisha umutwe pa mucanga.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen. He has jumped from the top and it's like he wants to sink his head into the sand.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo alepunda.
eng_translation: A young man is shouting.

bem_transcription: Ukumolesha cilemoneka napunda sana finshi alepundila?
eng_translation: It looks like he is shouting very much. Why could he be shouting?

bem_transcription: alepunda ukuti abantu bonfwe ifyo aleimba.
eng_translation: He is shouting so that people can hear what he is singing.

bem_transcription: Nge ci ekete mu minwe ni cinshi?
eng_translation: What is that he is holding in his hands?

bem_transcription: Ekete banjo eyo alelisha kukonkamo no lwimbo lwa kwe.
eng_translation: He is holding a guitar that he is playing to accompany his singing.

bem_transcription: Umukashana naimina pakati ya musebo.
eng_translation: A young woman is standing in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Elyo nafwala ishati lya katapa katapa na seketi iya fita.
eng_translation: She is wearing a green shirt and a black skirt.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ku muulu ifyo kulemoeka?
eng_translation: Have you seen how the sky is looking?

bem_transcription: Nimbona cilemoneka kwati umuulu wanfula infula ili mupepi nokutampa ukuloka.
eng_translation: Yes it looks like it is about to start raining.

bem_transcription: Elyo nga twalolekesha bwino sana kulya lubali kulemoneka kuli na motoka ileisa kabili ne fikulwa ifitali.
eng_translation: When we look closely on the other side, there is a vehicle coming and there are also tall buildings.

bem_transcription: Umwana ali na nyina panse yetuka.
eng_translation: A child is with the mother outside a shop.

bem_transcription: Elyo pali ifyo alenwisha umwana wakwe muli kapu.
eng_translation: There is something that she is giving to the child to drink in a cup.

bem_transcription: Nyina wa mwana alikwata imishishi ishitali nafwala ne shati ilya buta mwapita no twafita.
eng_translation: The mother to the child had long hair and is wearing a white shirt with black lines.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Mukati ye tuka namo  muli abantu abekele balelelya ifya kulya na namayo nakwata fimo ifyo alewnwa nafwala ne fakufwala fya katapa katapa.
eng_translation: There are also other people seated and eating something inside the shop and there is a woman drinking something, wearing green clothes.

bem_transcription: Abana abakashana babili baleyangala panse.
eng_translation: Two young girls are playing.

bem_transcription: Elyo baleyangala ku cimpelwa
eng_translation: They are playing on the swing.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ifyo palubansa palemoneka bwino?
eng_translation: Have you seen how beautiful the surroundings are?

bem_transcription: Nimbona pa lubansa lwaka ena lulemoneka bwino sana pantu ulunkoto lwabapo luntu lwa katapa katapa elyo kabili ne cimuti ciliko naco ca katapa katapa
eng_translation: I have seen that it is looking good because there is green grass and a free with green leaves.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati aba abaice nabonfwa bwino sana lintu balepeluka pali ici icimpelwa pantu naba sekelela nabmwentula.
eng_translation: These children seem to be enjoying as they are swinging because they are happy.

bem_transcription: Abashilika abengi bana mayo naba shitata nabeminina.
eng_translation: A number of male and female soldiers are standing.

bem_transcription: Nabafwala utusote twa katapa katapa kabili nama shti nayo yakatapa katapa elo pakubeya paita utwakashika.
eng_translation: They are wearing green hats and green shirts with a red ribbon on the shoulder.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo balemoneka pa menso bonse fye?
eng_translation: But have you seen how they are all looking on their faces?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona bambi balemoneka nakalimo balelila bambi balemoneka ne nsansa katwishi nga nicinshi icilecitika.
eng_translation: Yes others seem to be crying and others seem to be laughing. I don't know what is happening.

bem_transcription: Nga ni uyu na mayo uli pantanshi ena cilepala kwati alelila fye pantu pa menso palemoneka ne nkanshi.
eng_translation: If it is this woman in front, she looks like she is crying because she even has frowns on her face.

bem_transcription: Umwaice nafukama panshi namayo naiminina nakwatako nafimo mu minwe
eng_translation: A child is kneeling on the ground where as a woman is standing and holding something in her hands.

bem_transcription: Elo uyu umwana ufukeme natantamika no tumabwe no tumabwe twaka ena tulemoneka sana bwino nalimo twakushitisha.
eng_translation: This kneeling child has lined up stones which look very good. Maybe they are for selling.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilepala kwati utmabwe aletantika kuti batampa ukuteya icangalo cimo pantu nabatutantika bwino sana
eng_translation: The stones are well arranged like they are starting to play a certain game with them.

bem_transcription: Elyo kunuma ya uyu umwaice natantikako na fimo pama tebulo nakalimo nafyo fyakushitisha.
eng_translation: There are other things too on a table behind this child. Maybe they are also for selling.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwaice nafwala ica kufwala ica kashika ku muulu icipalene ne tebulo ilyo ili kunuma insalu babikilepo naikashika.
eng_translation: This child is wearing a red top similar to the cloth that is on the table behind her.

bem_transcription: Bantu bambi nabekala pa tupuna panse elo umbi umulumendo naiminina.
eng_translation: People are seated on chairs outside and one young man is standing.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili ubu bushiku pantu kumona fye nefyo bekele nabasha no mulilo elyo nabekala pa tupuna baleshimika.
eng_translation: This seems like it is evening because they are seated around a fire chatting.

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilemoneka kwati cikulwa ico bakula fye ukwakutila abantu bengaya bashita ifya kulya no kwikala panse baleshimika.
eng_translation: This place looks like a building that has been built so that people can go and buy food and sit and chat outside.

bem_transcription: Ku ncende yaka ena nabemikako naba motoka kabili kuli no mulumendo umo uwikelelko pakapuna alelisha ne cilimba ca nsale
eng_translation: There are even vehicles parked at this place and there is a young man seated on a chair playing a stringed instrument.

bem_transcription: Elo bonse nabakwata amakapu kuminwe cilepala balenwa amakabe iyi ncende ilemoneka yalitalala.
eng_translation: They all have cups in their hands. Its like they are drinking tea because this place is cold.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naiminina pakati kabakapokola babili.
eng_translation: A young man is standing between two police officers.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili cilemoneka balemulubulwisha pantu kumonafye napamenso ifyo palemoneka kuminwe yakwe nakwata nakabotolo nakalimo kabwalwa.
eng_translation: Looking at his face we can tell that he is being interrogated and he even has a bottle. Maybe is a beer bottle.

bem_transcription: Elyo alemoneka fye uwatiina tiina, nomba bushe naumona itoloshi afwele ifyo lilemoneka?
eng_translation: And he looks scared. Have you seen how his trousers is looking?

bem_transcription: Uhm, awe cacine nimbona, itoloshi lyakaena lilemoneka ilikulu elyo nakabili nalifiita kufiko.
eng_translation: Yes I have, it looks big and dirty.

bem_transcription: Bakapokola nabo balemoneka ababusaka nangula amatoloshi bafwele yakalamba.
eng_translation: The police officers look clean even though the trousers they are wearing are big.

bem_transcription: Banamayo babili nabaya mwituuka bashitishe fyakulya.
eng_translation: Two women are in a restuarant.

bem_transcription: Balelolesha pafikope bakambatikaifya fyaikulya nakalimo balefwaya ukushita.
eng_translation: They are looking at pictures of food that have been stuck on the wall. Maybe they want to buy.

bem_transcription: Elo bonse babili balikwata imishishi ishayemba ishitali kabili ishabeeka.
eng_translation: And they both have long shiny beautiful hair.

bem_transcription: Icakulundapo fye, nabafwala notufyampepo utwapusana, umo afwele akafiita kabili umo afwele akamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: Additionally they are wearing jerseys of different colors. One is wearing a black one and the other is wearing a blue one.

bem_transcription: Elyo uulebshtisha ifyakulya nafwala icabuuta, icakufimba umoona napakanwa.
eng_translation: The one selling food is wearing a white face mask.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naiminina naimya necilimba ca nsaale kuminwe.
eng_translation: A young man is standing, holding a stringed instrument on his arms.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili pantashi yakwe pali necisoselo cilemoneka kwati alefwaya ukwimba.
eng_translation: There is also a microphone below. It looks like he wants to start singing.

bem_transcription: Nimbona cilemoneka nikemba yu pantu nakulubali lwakwe kuli ingoma iyakashika elyo nefisolobelo fimbi ifyo baboomfya.
eng_translation: I have seen. This young man looks like he is a musician because there are also drums on his side and other equipment.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ifyo alemoneka umulumendo wakaena ifyo imishishi shakwe shilemoneka na fintu afwele.
eng_translation: Have you seen how this young man is looking, how his hair and his clothes are looking?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona, imishishi shilemoneka ishalubana lubana ishasakalala ifyakufwala fyakwe fyena filemonekako ifyabusaka pantu fintu fyafiita.
eng_translation: Yes his hair looks uncombed and all over the place. Only his clothes are looking clean because they are black.

bem_transcription: Imbwa iyayemba bwino sana iyafiita mwapita nefyabuuta ileangala palubansa.
eng_translation: A beautiful black dog with white spots is playing in the yard.

bem_transcription: Iyi imbwa yakaena naikwata nakamo eko ileangasha mukanwa bushe naumona?
eng_translation: This dog has something it is playing with in its mouth have you noticed?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona, cilepala kwati nikabola ikwete mukanwa, aka kabola kalemoneka akamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: Yes it looks like it has a blue ball in it's mouth.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili apa palemoneka nipa n'ganda pantu kunuma yambwa kuli nakayanda kamo.
eng_translation: This looks like at the house because there is a small house behind the dog.

bem_transcription: Ulubansa nakabili lulemoneka ulwayemba, pantu ulunkoto lwalifunda bwino sana, cilepala uyu umushili paliba amenshi nangu abene balibikako amano ukwitilila.
eng_translation: The surroundings look very neat because the grass looks very nice. It's like the soil here is very fertile or the owners water a lot.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili balepanga in'ganda yakwangalilamo abana.
eng_translation: Two men are making a children playhouse.

bem_transcription: Bushe iyi in'ganda ni n'ganda yashani? pantu umuntu teti ekale umu.
eng_translation: What kind of a house is this? Because a man can't live in here.

bem_transcription: Iyi n'ganda bapangile yakutolokelamo fye.
eng_translation: This is just a jumping castle.

bem_transcription: So aba abaice nga bali mun'gande yi baletoloka ninshi balasansamuka sana?
eng_translation: So are children very happy as they are jumping on it?

bem_transcription: Balomfwa bwino icine cine pantu in'gande yi yaba iyatemfwa temfwa.
eng_translation: Yes they feel very happy because this house is very soft.

bem_transcription: Akabwa akakwata amasako ayengi sana kabili akanoono kaleangala.
eng_translation: A small fluffy dog is playing.

bem_transcription: Akabwa kakaena kalemoneka nalimo kalefwaya ukwikata kabola akakashika akali mumuulu.
eng_translation: The dog looks like it wants to catch the ball that is in the air.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati aka akabwa kakaena nakakwata umwine uuleangala nako uulekaposela kabola.
eng_translation: It is like this dog is playing with it's owner, who is throwing the ball.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Namasako yakako yalemoneka ayafiita elo yambi ayafiitulukilako.
eng_translation: It's fur look black and others greyish.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali mu cikuulwa ca bwalwa aleshitisha ubwalwa.
eng_translation: A young man is in a bar selling beer.

bem_transcription: Nakwata amakapu yabili kuminwe, cilepala kwati alesankanya ubwalwa.
eng_translation: He has two cups in his hands it looks like he is mixing alcohol.

bem_transcription: Bushe nga walolesha kunuma yakwe finshi ulemonako?
eng_translation: What can you seen behind him when you looks closely?

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe kwena ndemonako amabotolo yabwalwa ubwapusana pusana.
eng_translation: There are a lot of different bottles of alcohol.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili uyu wine shitata afwele icakufwala icafiita, nomulandu afwalile nipakutila ubwalwa tabulanfishe ifyakufwala.
eng_translation: This man is wearing black clothing so that they are not stained by alcohol.

bem_transcription: Abantu abengi nabanina pali batuukutuuku mumusebo.
eng_translation: A lot of people are on motorcycles in the road.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo kuli motoka iilemoneka kwati bacilasefye ciila bushe naumona?
eng_translation: There is a vehicle behind them which looks like they were celebrating something have you noticed?

bem_transcription: Nimbona pantu nabaikobeka ifyakuiyemfya namumuulu mumbali yanshila mufimuti nabakobekako utwakuyemfya umusebo.
eng_translation: Yes because they have decorated it and they have decorated the trees on the side of the road too.

bem_transcription: Umu mumusebo bali aba abalesefya mwaliba nefikuulwa ifitali konse kulubali.
eng_translation: There are tall buildings on either sides of this road.

bem_transcription: Aba bantu bonse cilepala kwati balesefya ubwinga pantu bonse nabafwala ifyapalana ifyabuuta elyo kumutwe babikileko ututambala utwamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: These people look like they are celebrating a wedding because they all are wearing similar white clothes and blue headwraps.

bem_transcription: Shitata napapa akachola elo nanina napa ncinga alecofa mumusebo
eng_translation: A man has a bag on his back and is on a bicycle riding.

bem_transcription: Mumusebo wakaena muli ne myotoka shibili, imbi iyabuuta ili pantashi yakwe kabili imbi iyakashika ili kumbali yamusebo.
eng_translation: There are also two cars in this road. A white one in front of him and a red one on the road side.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ukutila mumbali yamusebo muli nafimbi.
eng_translation: But have you seen that there is something else on the side of the road?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona kuli amayanda elyo kabili neci icikuulwa nakalimo nicalici.
eng_translation: Yes there are houses and a building that looks like a church.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwa shitata yu kuli namotoka iyafiita iilemukonka munuma.
eng_translation: There is also a black vehicle behind this man following him.

bem_transcription: Abantu abapusana pusana bali mumbali yamusebo bambi bali pakatii kamusebo balecita ifyapusana pusana.
eng_translation: Different people are on the roadside and others are in the middle of the road doing different things.

bem_transcription: Ca cine balecita ifyapusana pusana, pantu nga nalolesha uyu shitata uuli pantashi ena alipa kancinga akanoono aleensha kabili kuli fye nabaleyendela fye, nabeminine fye
eng_translation: Yes they are doing different things because of I look closely, this man in front is riding a small bicycle and others are just walking and others are just standing.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati iyi incende kwaciba ifyangalo ifyapusana pusana emulandu wine abantu bafulile.
eng_translation: It looks like there were different games in this place that is why there are a lot of people.

bem_transcription: Mumbaliyamusebo nabakaka nama tenti elo kabili amatenti yakaena yambi yantu yabuuta mwapita nefyafiita elyo yambi yantu yakashika mwapita nefya kashika.
eng_translation: There are also tents hang on the sides of the road. Some of them are white with black patches and others are red.

bem_transcription: Mumatenti umu mulemoneka kwati beleshitishamo fimo elo bambi nabeminina mumbali yayako pakutila bengashita.
eng_translation: It looks like there is something that they are selling in the tents and others are standing on their sides so that they can buy.

bem_transcription: Umukashana ali mucikuulwa cafyangalo aleangala.
eng_translation: A young woman is playing in a building for games.

bem_transcription: Ici cangalo aleangala cangalo cakuposa kabola elo kayauma mumabotolo yapona.
eng_translation: They are bowling.

bem_transcription: Elyo yu umukashana nafwala nakaputula iyamakumbi makumbi neshati ilyafiita.
eng_translation: This young woman is wearing a blue short and a black shirt.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili pamushili aleteyela ubu ubwangalo pantu patelela elo napabeeka sana.
eng_translation: The floor where she is playing this game is very shiny and smooth.

bem_transcription: Nintemwa insapato afwele, ulusapato lu lulemoneka ulwayemba kabili ulwakosa, ulwabuuta mwapita notwafiita.
eng_translation: Love her shoes. They look beautiful and strong. They are white and have black in them.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili bali pamulimo kuncende iyayemba bwino sana.
eng_translation: Two men are working at a very beautiful place.

bem_transcription: Aba bashitata bakaena balebika umupaipi wamenshi.
eng_translation: These men are putting a water pipe.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo bushe naumona ukutila kuli ico balebomfya?
eng_translation: Have you noticed that there is something they are using behind them?

bem_transcription: Ee, kwena nimbona, kunuma kuli cimazembe icilebafwa ukubomba uyu umulimo.
eng_translation: Yes there is an escavater behind them that is helping them do the work.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati uyu umupaipi wamenshi walyonaike emulandu wine balecinjisha nokubikapo na umbi uutali.
eng_translation: It looks like this water pipe was broken that is why they they are changing to a new one.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili nabaya kuncende uko bangalila ifyangalo.
eng_translation: Two men are in a play ground.

bem_transcription: Kuncende bali, ni ncende iyayemba nga nshi pantu takulemonekapo ifiko nangu fimo iyo.
eng_translation: This place looks beautiful because there is no any dirt around.

bem_transcription: Naumona ukutila kunuma yabo kuli ne cikuulwa icayemba bwino sana?
eng_translation: Have you noticed that there is a beautiful building behind them?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, icikuulwa cakaena balicikuula bwino sana nokucipenta bwino sana, cilemoneka icayemba nga nshi.
eng_translation: Yes the building is well built and we'll painted and it looks beautiful.

bem_transcription: Elo uyu uufwele icamakumubi makumbi shitata kuli abantu balya abali mupepi ne cikuulwa bantu aleposha.
eng_translation: There are people near a building that this man in blue is greeting.

bem_transcription: Shitata nabanamayo babili balebomba bali pamulimo.
eng_translation: A man and two women are working.

bem_transcription: Uku bali kulemoneka kwati nikumpanga bali elyo baleposa umufundo pamushili.
eng_translation: The place where they are looks like a forest and they are throwing fertiliser on the ground.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati uku kumpanga eko balimine fisabo, pantu kunuma yabo balibikako napakutushisha.
eng_translation: It's like they have grown their fruits in this forest because they have even put where they can rest.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona fintu bafwele banamayo babili no yu shitata?
eng_translation: Have you seen what these two women and a man are wearing?

bem_transcription: Shitata ali kuncende ukwaba umucanga sana alebomba cimo.
eng_translation: A man is working in a place with a lot of sand.

bem_transcription: Uku kuntu ali cilemoneka nalimo kwalitalalisha kumwena fye kufyakufwala fintu afwele.
eng_translation: Just looking at what he is wearing you can tell that this place is very cold.

bem_transcription: Teico fye ceka, cilemoneka uku nikululamba lwamumana pantu umucanga ulemoneka uwamenshi menshi.
eng_translation: Additionally this looks like the beach because the sand looks wet.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona cintu alebumba ifyo cilemoneka? Ine ndemona nakalimo muntu.
eng_translation: Have you seen how what he is making is looking like? It looks like a person.

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona uyu alemoneka kwati muntu pantu nakwata no moona na menso elo cilepala kwati amubumbile ninshi nafwala icisote.
eng_translation: Yes this looks like a person with a nose and eyes and it looks like it is wearing a hat.

bem_transcription: Imbwa shibili shilepepekana.
eng_translation: Two dogs are chasing each other.

bem_transcription: Nga ilya imbi iishilepepekako bushe finshi ilecita?
eng_translation: What is that other dog that is not chasing doing?

bem_transcription: Ilya imbi ili yayena ifyo ileangala nafyo pantu umu mulepala kwati nimwilinga lyambwa sheka sheka.
eng_translation: That other one looks like it has something that it is doing because it is in a dog fence.

bem_transcription: Bushe iiyi balepepeka bushe balefwaya ukuisuma?
eng_translation: Does this dog want to bite the one it is chasing?

bem_transcription: Awe, tabalefwaya ukuisuma, shilepepekana fye ebwangalo shisalile.
eng_translation: No it doesn't want to bite it. They are just playing.

bem_transcription: Bashitata nabakwata ifilimba fyansaale kabili balefilisha.
eng_translation: Men are playing stringed instruments.

bem_transcription: Aba bashitata bakaena apa bali nipakati ya musebo, elyo bonse nabafwala nefyapalana.
eng_translation: These men are in the middle of the road and are wearing similar things.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati aba bashitata balipanga ibumba ilinoono ilyabakemba kabili bonse nibakemba.
eng_translation: It looks like these men have made a small group of singers.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili kuli abantu abeshile mukubatamba fintu baleimba.
eng_translation: There are also people who have come to see them as they are singing.

bem_transcription: Emulandu wine bafwalile ifyapalana, nabafwala amasuti ayabuuta notusote utwabuuta kabili nabafwala nefyakubacingilila kumenso.
eng_translation: That is why they are wearing similar clothes. They are all wearing white suits and white hats and thy are wearing something to cover their faces.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo natoloka ne ncinga mumuulu.
eng_translation: A young man has jumped high with a bicycle.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili uyu umulumendo nafwala icimpompo kumutwe icakwebati nangu aliponene teti aicene
eng_translation: This young man is wearing a helmet so that he does not hurt himself in an event that he falls.

bem_transcription: Elyo alishibisha ukucofe ncinga pantu tekutila atoloke ne ncinga mumusango yu.
eng_translation: He looks like he is very good at cycling otherwise he wouldn't have jumped like this.

bem_transcription: Elyo kuntu ali kwaliba nefimuti ifitali ifingi ifyakatapakatapa
eng_translation: There are also a lot of tall green trees where he is.

bem_transcription: Nintemwa fintu afwele pantu nafwala ishati ilyabuuta netoloshi ilyafiita.
eng_translation: I love the white shirt and the black trousers that he is wearing.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo nabakashana nabaya kuncende iyaibela mukwangala.
eng_translation: Young men and young women have gone to a special place to play.

bem_transcription: Aba balumendo nakashana baleangla nomupila.
eng_translation: These young men and young women are playing with a ball.

bem_transcription: Nakabili nabatoloka cilepala kwati nabonfwa bwino ukwangala ici icangalo.
eng_translation: And they are jumping. It's like they are enjoying playing this game.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili uku kuntu bali kulemoneka kuntu kwatalala, bushe naumona fintu bafwele bonse?
eng_translation: And this place looks cold. Have you seen what they are wearing?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona nagula cakutila baleangala ici icangalo bonse nabafwala ifya mpepo.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen. Even if they are playing this game, they are all wearing jerseys.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili nabeminina nabekata ne cipampa  apalilembelwe impya.
eng_translation: Two men are standing and holding a sign that has money on it.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka nakalimo apa beminine balebakopa icikope pantu bonse nabacensa.
eng_translation: It looks like they are taking a picture because they are all smiling.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilepala kwati uyu shitata ufwele ishati ilya buta eulepela uyu umunakwe ici icipampa ca mpiya.
eng_translation: It looks like this man in a white shirt is the one giving the sign to the other one.

bem_transcription: Elo kunuma yabo kuli umulumendo uwikleko paka puna nao nafwala ne shati ilya buta.
eng_translation: There is a young man seated on a chair behind wearing a white shirt.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati uyu umulumendo naumbi ulya ulemoneka babomba kumo kwine naba bashitata.
eng_translation: It looks like this young man works at the same company with this other man.

bem_transcription: Abana abanoono elyo nabashinku uwalinga baleangalila apakutoloka.
eng_translation: Young children and middle aged ones are playing at a jumping place.

bem_transcription: Kamo nakekala, tubili natwimininako elo umbi natoloka mumuulu.
eng_translation: One is sitting, two are standing and one is jumping.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo iyi incende ilemoneka?
eng_translation: But have you seen how this place is looking?

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilemoneka ni ncende fye yakwangalilapo pantu panshi palemoneka no mucanga uwabuuta kabili kunuma kwaba nefyani.
eng_translation: This place looks like just somewhere people go to play because there is sand and grass behind.

bem_transcription: Ukulundapo kulemoneka nakabili nabeminikapo bamotoka kunuma yafyani, cilepala emuli abafyashi babana aba.
eng_translation: Additionally there are cars parked behind there and it looks like that is where the parents of these children are.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naikala pakapuna kululamba lwamumana.
eng_translation: A young man is seated on a chair at the sea shore.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo alemoneka nakalimo alelobe sabi.
eng_translation: This young man looks like he is fishing.

bem_transcription: Umumana wakaena ulemoneka uwatekanya bwino pantu tapali namabimbi.
eng_translation: The river looks calm with no waves on it.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo nafwala nakasote, ishati nakaputula.
eng_translation: This young man is wearing a hat, a shirt and a short.

bem_transcription: Elyo pambali yakwe pali necikopo icabuuta cilepala kwati emo alebika isabi.
eng_translation: There is a white bowl on his side. It looks like that is where he is putting the fish.

bem_transcription: Abantu abengi sana nabekala bambi nabekala baletamba abalumendo abali pakati.
eng_translation: A lot of people are seated and others are watching the young men in the middle.

bem_transcription: Aba abalumendo cilepala kwati nakalimo baleshana.
eng_translation: It looks like these men are dancing.

bem_transcription: Cisahinka elo apa eminine ni panse fye ya cikulwa nangula ifi fya cikulwa nafisalwa
eng_translation: And where they standing is outside a building and it appears closed.

bem_transcription: Elo ku ncende bali kwliba ifikulwa ifitali ifingi.
eng_translation: There are tall buildings in the place where they are.

bem_transcription: Napapene bali nipakati ka fikulwa iyi incende yashingulukwa ne fikulwa.
eng_translation: They are in the middle of buildings. This place is surrounded by buildings.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili nabakontama bali pamulu wa cikulwa.
eng_translation: Two young men have bent on top of a building.

bem_transcription: Uku kuntu bali kulemoneka nakalimo ni ku mpili pantu no muulu ulemoneka.
eng_translation: They look like they are at the mountains because we can even see the sky.

bem_transcription: Ee chishinka ni kumpili uko pantu kulemoneka ne mpili shibili ishitali.
eng_translation: Yes they are at the mountains because there are even two tall mountains.

bem_transcription: Kabili nga twalolekesha kulemoneka kulemoneka nakalimo ni kululamba lwa mumna pantu akalamukila kulemoneka amenshi.
eng_translation: Additionally it looks like this is at the sea shore because there seems to be water at a distance.

bem_transcription: Cimbi nacvo cakiyila umuulu ulemoneka uwa mfula mfula cilepala kwati imfula ili mukuloka.
eng_translation: Additionally the sky's look rainy it looks like it is about to rain.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ileangala ku  ncende iya talala sana.
eng_translation: A dog is playing in a very cold place.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende yaka ena ilemoneka iya buta.
eng_translation: This place looks white.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ukutina iyi ine imbwa naikwatako cimo ku kanwa?
eng_translation: Have you seen that there is something in this dogs mouth?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona nalimo baikakila ku kanwa mukweba ati ilasuma abantu.
eng_translation: Yes it is like its mouth is chained so that it doesn't bite people.

bem_transcription: Elo mu mukoshi naikwata ne co bakakila ica kashika.
eng_translation: It also has a red thing around it's neck.

bem_transcription: Umwana umwice ali mu menshi mucibeseni.
eng_translation: A young child is in water in a dish.

bem_transcription: Umu mucibesni ali alesamba nomba amenshi yaka ena nayakwata ipofu.
eng_translation: The child is bathing in this dish and the water in it has foams.

bem_transcription: Naumona ifyo utu mishishi twakwe tulemoneka?
eng_translation: Have you seen how the childs hair is looking?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona utu mishishi twakwe tulemoneka utwatelela kabili utwipi utunono elyo natubomba.
eng_translation: Yes the hair looks smooth and short and curly and it is wet.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilepala kwati uyu umwana, Mwana umwaume.
eng_translation: And it looks like this is a male child.

bem_transcription: Abalumenso baleteya umupila wakuminwe uo beta basket ball.
eng_translation: Young men are playing basketball.

bem_transcription: Nomba ninshi baleteyela ubwangalo ubu bwine mu nshita ya bushiku?
eng_translation: But why are they playing basketball in the night?

bem_transcription: Baleteyela ubushiku pa mulandu wakuti ni bakasukulu akasuba baciba mu ma classes.
eng_translation: They are playing in the night because they are school goers and they were in class in the afternoon.

bem_transcription: So filya aposele bola mu muulu ile ukwingila?
eng_translation: So is that ball that he has thrown going into the basket?

bem_transcription: Ee aleposela ukwingisha.
eng_translation: Yes he is throwing to score.

bem_transcription: Umwana umulumendo natoloka ukwingila mu menshi.
eng_translation: A young man has jumped to dive into the water.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo waka ena tafwele ne shati afwele fye kaputula.
eng_translation: This young man is not even wearing a shirt. Hes only wearing a short.

bem_transcription: Lintu atolweke utumishishi tusontele mu menshi muntu aleingila.
eng_translation: As he has jumped the hair is pointing into the water where he is going.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ati kumbali ya menshi kulya kuli no tupuna?
eng_translation: Have you seen that there are chairs there on the sides of the water?

bem_transcription: Ee utupuna nitumona kulemoneka kwati kuli fye utuna utwingi elo ici icishiba ca menshi cabela fye pa ng'anda.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen the chairs and they seem to be many. This pool appears to be at the house.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali mucibansa nanina pali kabalwe.
eng_translation: A young man is on a horse in the pitch.

bem_transcription: Kabalwe waka ena alebutuka mu cibansa.
eng_translation: The Horse is running in the pitch.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili kuli shitata kumbali ulemulolesha lintu alebutuka.
eng_translation: There is a man on the side who is closely looking at this young man.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili nga nalolekesha bwino uyu uninine pali kabalwe alemoneka ni namayo nalimo te shitata pantu nakwata imishishi ishtali,  Bushe naumona ico?
eng_translation: If I look closely this one on the horse looks like a woman and not a man. Have you seen?

bem_transcription: Ee namona awe ni na mayo elyo na kabili mumbali ya cibansa kuli abantu abali mupepi naba kabalwe besalile
eng_translation: Yes I have seen that she is a woman and on the sides of this pitch are people that are standing near horses that are in cages.

bem_transcription: Shitata naikata impunda ishinono shibili.
eng_translation: A man is holding two young donkeys.

bem_transcription: lyo kabili kuli bana mayo batatu abaletota nakalimo eo baletotela.
eng_translation: There are also three women that are clapping. It's like they are clapping for him.

bem_transcription: Kunuma kwa mpunda kuli umwanakashi uleshindika nafwala ne cakufwala ica kashika.
eng_translation: There is a woman behind these donkeys who is wearing red.

bem_transcription: Kabili ku ncede yaka ena kwaliba ne fimuti nafyo filemoneka fingi
eng_translation: And there are a lot of trees at this place.

bem_transcription: Elyo shitata alemoneka uwa sekelela lintu asendele ishi impunda.
eng_translation: The man looks happy as he is Carrying the donkeys.

bem_transcription: Shitata ali pa nse alebeya na mayo umushishi.
eng_translation: A man is outside cutting a woman's hair.

bem_transcription: Awe nakalya uyu te na mayo alemoneka ni nakulu bantu.
eng_translation: No this is not just a woman but she is an old woman.

bem_transcription: Eya niwebo walungika uyu ni nakulu bantu pantu no mushishi ulemoneka uwabuta.
eng_translation: You are right she is an old woman because even the hair looks white.

bem_transcription: Uyu nakulu bantu waka ena nabamufimba ne ci salu ica buta mwapita ne fyakashika.
eng_translation: This same woman is being covered in a white and red cloth.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe kwaliba no tushimbi tuntu bacingilisha ku ng'anda.
eng_translation: There are metal bars behind her that have fenced the house.

bem_transcription: shitata naikata imfuti ku minwe.
eng_translation: A man is holding a gun in the hands.

bem_transcription: Nafwala ne cisote ca fita ne shati lya fita kabili mukati ye shati lya fita muli ne lyabuta
eng_translation: He is wearing a black hat and a black shirt and he has a white shirt under the black one.

bem_transcription: Elyo ku ntanshi ya mfuti nakwaka umulilo.
eng_translation: There is fire in front of the gun.

bem_transcription: Elyo ubu bulemoneka bushiku pantu nakufika.
eng_translation: It looks like it is in the night because it is dark.

bem_transcription: Shitata waka ena alemoneka uwakalipa cilepala kwati emualndu wine akwatile imfuti.
eng_translation: The man looks angry and it looks like that is why he is holding a gun.

bem_transcription: Abantu aba pusana pusana bali panse ya fikulwa.
eng_translation: Different people are outside the buildings.

bem_transcription: Bambi baleikopa ifikope elyo bambi beminine fye pakati ya musebo baleshimika.
eng_translation: Others are taking pictures while others are just standing in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Elo imisebo shaka ena shapita fye pakati ka fikulwa.
eng_translation: The roads just pass in between buildings.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ati  ifikulwa ifi filemoneka ifyapusana?
eng_translation: Have you seen how different these buildings are?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona pantu fimbi filemoneka kwati ni panse ye calici fimbi kwati nipanse yama tuka emulandu wine  ulu ulubali abantu nabafula.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen. Others are looking like outside a church and others are looking like outside a shop and that is why there are many people.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo nabakashana babili bali mu cikulwa.
eng_translation: A young man and two young women are in a building.

bem_transcription: Ici icikulwa cilemoneka kwati cikulwa cakulilamo ifyakulya.
eng_translation: This building looks like a restuarant.

bem_transcription: Ee niwebo walungika pantu uyu na mayo uwikele pe tebulo pali ifyakulya fintu alelya
eng_translation: Yes you are right because there is food on the table where this woman is sitting and she is eating.

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana alelanshanya no mukashana uwikele pe tebulo.
eng_translation: A young woman is discussing with the young woman seated on the table.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ena alemoneka alebalolesha fye lintu balelanda.
eng_translation: The young man is just looking as they are talking.

bem_transcription: Imbwa iyfiita ileangala.
eng_translation: A black dog is playing.

bem_transcription: Iyi imbwa yakaena iletoloka ukufuma pacishimbi ukuya panshi.
eng_translation: This dog is jumping form a metal bar to the ground.

bem_transcription: Elo uku iliko fye yeka tatulemoneka imbwa shimbi.
eng_translation: And it is only alone because there are no any dogs around.

bem_transcription: Panshi pali kapinga iyayemba bwino sana.
eng_translation: There is very green grass on the ground.

bem_transcription: Elo mumbali mulemoneka muli na tumbi utushimbi uto baiminika.
eng_translation: And there are other metal bars too that are around the place.

bem_transcription: Abantu abengi kabili abapusana umushinku nabaya kumaliketi.
eng_translation: A lot of people of different ages have gone to the market.

bem_transcription: Kumaliketi yakaena kwaliba ne cikuulwa icitali nga nshi pakati.
eng_translation: There is a very tall building in the middle of the market.

bem_transcription: Elyo pantu bashitishisha pamatebulo balikapo namatenti ayakalamba.
eng_translation: There are even tents on the tables where people sell from.

bem_transcription: Kuli namayo umo ifi nashitata baleensha abana.
eng_translation: There is a woman and a man that are wheeling the children.

bem_transcription: Elyo abantu bambi bena nabeminina pamatebulo baleshita ifyakushita shita.
eng_translation: Other people have stopped by the tables buying some things.

bem_transcription: Shitata alelisha icintu icapala umutolilo lelo icikalamba.
eng_translation: A man is playing what looks like a flute but bigger.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe nabakanikako ne nsokoshi.
eng_translation: They have hang some socks behind him.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe cilemoneka kwati nipesa apa ali?
eng_translation: Where does it seem like he is?

bem_transcription: Apa palemoneka nakalimo nipanse yetuuka pantu kufibumba nampo nga nikufiibi nabakambatikako nefipepala,
eng_translation: It looks like he is outside a building because on the walls or is it on the doors, they have hang some papers.

bem_transcription: Nomba nga nalolekesha bwino palemoneka kwati nipa n'ganda fye apa nayo ing'anda yabela fye mumbali yamusebo pantu nabanika ne fintu panse.
eng_translation: If I look closely this looks like it is at a house and the house seems to be just on the roadside and they have even hang something outside.

bem_transcription: Namayo ali pa ncinga alecofa.
eng_translation: A woman is riding a bicycle.

bem_transcription: Alemoneka nabutusha sana incinga yakwe iyi nomba ninshi afwalile amagalashi?
eng_translation: It looks like she is speeding. But why is she wearing glasses?

bem_transcription: Afwalile amagalashi ukucingilila umwela ukwingila mumenshi pantu alecofa bwino.
eng_translation: She is wearing glasses so that the air doesn't enter her eyes.

bem_transcription: Bushe uyu alebutusha pantu nacelwa uko aleya?
eng_translation: Is she speeding because she is late where she is going?

bem_transcription: Ee, alebutusha pantu nacelwa uko alebutukila.
eng_translation: Yes she is speeding because she is late.

bem_transcription: Namayo naikala nakabwa nakekala mupepi.
eng_translation: A woman is sitting and a dog is seated close to her.

bem_transcription: Uyu namayo wakaena aletininka lamya kabili ukuboko kwakwe kumbi kwikete muchola.
eng_translation: A woman is pressing her phone and the other hand is in the bag.

bem_transcription: Bushe finshi fimbi ulemona pali ici icikope?
eng_translation: What can you see in this picture?

bem_transcription: Kwena ndemona kunuma yakwa namayo kulemoneka shitata nangula talemoneka pa menso.
eng_translation: There is a man behind this woman even though I can see his face.

bem_transcription: Cishinka uyu wine shitata alemoneka kwati mukoloci pantu nakwata ne mishishi ishabuuta.
eng_translation: It is true. This same man looks old because he even has white hair.

bem_transcription: Namayo ali mumuputule wakwe alelanda pali lamya.
eng_translation: A woman is in her room speaking on the phone.

bem_transcription: Elo lintu alelanda pali lamya aleilosha pacilolani.
eng_translation: And as she is speaking on the phone she is looking at the mirror.

bem_transcription: Nomba cilepala kwati amano yonse yele kuo alelanda nankwe pali lamya.
eng_translation: But it's like her entire focus is on the one she is speaking with on the phone.

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana cilepala kwati naleka nokuiwamya pantu alelanda pali lamya.
eng_translation: It seems she even stoped cleaning as she talks on phone

bem_transcription: Elyo uyu umukashana alyupwa no kupwa pantu balimufwalika inindaminwe.
eng_translation: This lady is a married woman because she has a ring on her finger.

bem_transcription: Abakashana abacaice babili baleangala.
eng_translation: Two young girls are playing.

bem_transcription: Aba abakashana nabafwala ifyapalana.
eng_translation: The girls are wearing similar clothes.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati aba niba mpundu, bushe naumona ukutila nemishishi nashipalana?
eng_translation: They look like they are twins. Have you noticed taht they have similar hair?.

bem_transcription: Cacine nimbona ne mishishi nashipalana, pantu fyonse ifo bafwele ukutampila kumutwe ukufika nakumakasa nafipalana.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen that even the hair is similar. Everything they are wearing too from the head to the feet is similar.

bem_transcription: Nimbona ukutampila fye kuli bamakapa nabapalana, utumatoloshi tuntu twakashika mwapita notwafiita elyo notumashati tuntu twafiita.
eng_translation: The sandals are the same, the trousers are both red with black lines and the shirts are black.

bem_transcription: Umwana umwaice ali panse ya n'ganda aleangala.
eng_translation: Young child is playing outside the house.

bem_transcription: Uku ukwangala aleangala aleswa utumaluba utwaba fye palukungu.
eng_translation: He is picking the flowers that are on the backyard.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe uyu umwana wakaena, bushe mwaume nangu mwanakashi?
eng_translation: Is this child a boy or a girl?

bem_transcription: Uyu mwaume, nicho fye alikwata imishishi ishitali.
eng_translation: He is a boy. He just has long hair.

bem_transcription: Alikwata cishinka imishishi ishitali pantu nashifimba ne mpumi emulandu cancikosela ukwishiba nga cakutila mwaume nangu mwanakashi.
eng_translation: It is true he has long hair which is covering his forehead. That is why it was difficult for me to tell if he's a boy or a girl.

bem_transcription: Abantu bali mucikuulwa abengi.
eng_translation: A number of people are in a building.

bem_transcription: Babili nabafukamako panshi nalimo baleteya icangalo.
eng_translation: Two are kneeling down. Maybe they are playing a game.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili lubali lumbi kuli umukashana uufukeme, umulumendo uufwele ifyafiita konse kumuulu nakunshi naiminina.
eng_translation: On the other side there is a girl that is kneeling and a boy wearing black top and bottom.

bem_transcription: Aba abakashana abafukeme umo imishishi shitali elyo umo shiipi.
eng_translation: Of the two kneeling, one has long hair while the other has short hair.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya uyu umukashana uukwete imishishi ishitali kuli umulumendo uufwele ishati ilya buuta, uulemoneka kwati alimulubilo.
eng_translation: There is a young man behind this girl with long hair, who is wearing a white shirt and seems to be in a hurry.

bem_transcription: Shitata ali mukati ka ndeke naikala.
eng_translation: A man is sitting in a plane.

bem_transcription: Iyi indeke cilemoneka nakalimo tailama elo ilefwaya ukwima.
eng_translation: It's like this is when the plane is about to take of.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo afwele uyu shitata?
eng_translation: But have you seen what this man is wearing?

bem_transcription: Nimbona, mumatwi nafwala ifyakumfwilako abantu ifyo balelanda, kabili afwala ne shati ilyabuuta.
eng_translation: He is wearing a white shirt and has headphones in the ears.

bem_transcription: Cishinka alemoneka kwati uyu wine ekensha nangula namutekenya uwa ndeke.
eng_translation: Why does he look like he is the pilot?

bem_transcription: Akamwana akamwaice akamulumendo kali kuli parka kaleangala.
