bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende ilemoneka kwati akasuba elyo kati kawe.
eng_translation: This place looks like the sun is just setting.

bem_transcription: Kabili nga twalolekesha bwino kuli na bambi abantu babili abekele mupepi fye no mumana.
eng_translation: If we look closely there are other people too seated close to the river.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili balelisha ama banjo.
eng_translation: Two men are playing guitars.

bem_transcription: Bushe ili ibumba lya bantu likolongene lishile mukutamba aba bene bashitata?
eng_translation: Is this crowd here to watch these men?

bem_transcription: Ee lishile mukutamba aba bene bashitata pantu nibamushika nyimbo.
eng_translation: Yes they have come to watch these men because they are musicians.

bem_transcription: Nomba ninshi tabalelumbila aba bantu bakolongene.
eng_translation: But why are they not cheering?

bem_transcription: Tabalelumbila pa mulandu balefwaya balolele bonfwe ulwimbo baleimba.
eng_translation: They are not cheering because they first want to hear the song they are singing.

bem_transcription: Abana abalumendo baleangala pakati ka musebo.
eng_translation: Boys are playing in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Elyo uku kulemoneka ni kumushi pantu notu mayanda tulemoneka utwa fyani.
eng_translation: This looks like the village because the houses are grass thatched.

bem_transcription: Pantanshi ya aba baice abaleangala abalumendo pali umukashana umo utwikile fimo pa mutwe.
eng_translation: In front of these boys who are playing is a girl carrying something on her head.

bem_transcription: Elyo ku ntanshi ya mukashan utwikile ifintu pa mutwe kuli shitata uninine pa ncinga alecofa.
eng_translation: And in front of this girl with something on her head is a man on a bicycle.

bem_transcription: Kuli uyu umushi waka ena kulemoneka kwalifula ifyani kabili ne fimuti
eng_translation: This village seems to have a lot of trees and grass.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo mu musana wakwe nakakamo intambo ikakilwe ku cintu cimo ico aletinta.
eng_translation: There is a rope around his waist that is tied to something that he is pulling.

bem_transcription: Umumana waka ena ulemoneka ukalamba nga nshi!
eng_translation: The very river looks very big.

bem_transcription: Nakabili tawashika pantu ale-enda fye panshi ukwabula no bwato.
eng_translation: But it is not deep because he is just walking in it without a boat.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili ku mumana waka ena kwalifula ifyani kabili ne fimuti.
eng_translation: There are a lot of trees and grass where this very river is.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo naba kashana bali mu cibansa ca fyangalo.
eng_translation: Young men and young women are in a play ground.

bem_transcription: Elyo ici icibansa cisuma sana cilemoneka ica yemba.
eng_translation: This ground looks very beautiful.

bem_transcription: Aba abalumendo nabakashana nalimo balecinfyana ici icangalo.
eng_translation: Maybe these young men and you g women are competing.

bem_transcription: Elyo abantu batatu bafwele ifyapalana utusote utwabuta nama shati ayabuta.
eng_translation: Three people are wearing similar whit hats and similar white shirts.

bem_transcription: Mumbali ya cibansa mwine mwena muli fye ifimuti nafyo ifingi.
eng_translation: There are a lot of trees around the playing ground.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili nabekala mu muputule baleilenga pa mubili.
eng_translation: Two young men are in a room tattooing themselves.

bem_transcription: Elyo fintu balemulenga filemoneka kwati maluba eyo umunakwe alemulenga ku kuboko
eng_translation: It looks like he's getting a flower tattoo on the arm.

bem_transcription: Uyu wine uo balelenga nakwata ne cikope apo alemona ulemulenga.
eng_translation: The one being tattooed has a picture where he is seeing the one tattooing him.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilemoneka kwati filekalipa pantu pamubili filemoneka ifyakashika kwati filonda.
eng_translation: It looks like it is painting because it looks like fire burns.

bem_transcription: Kumona fye nefyo balemoneka bonse babili tabalesekelela nangu ukucensa eico icilelanga ukuti filekalipa.
eng_translation: It is true. Just looking at how they are not happy and not smilling you can tell that it is painting.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili bali mu muputule wakwipikilamo.
eng_translation: Two young men are in the kitchen.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilemoneka kwati bushiku lintu baleipika mu muputule umu.
eng_translation: It looks it is evening when they are cooking.

bem_transcription: Mu muputule waka ena mulemoneka mwalifula ifintu pantu tamuli ne ncende iyakweba ati ishele fye nakalya iyo.
eng_translation: This room has a lot of things and has no free space.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati ifyakulya balepekanya fingi sana pantu umwakusalwila namwisula.
eng_translation: It looks like they are preparing a lot of food because the pan is full.

bem_transcription: Uyu umuputule baliupanga bwino sana pantu mu muulu balibikamo no mwakwingila icushi nga baleipika.
eng_translation: This place is well made and even has were smoke can escape the room through.

bem_transcription: Shitata ali pancinga pakati yamusebo.
eng_translation: A man is on a bicycle on the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Nomba uyu wine shitata alemoneka fye uwafiita, nefyakufwala afwele nafifiita ne ncinga ilemonekela kumo ukufiita.
eng_translation: This man looks dark and the clothes he is wearing are black and his bicycle too is black.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulandu alemonekela uwafiita mulandu wakwebati alepita mukantelelwe.
eng_translation: This man looks dark because he is passing in the shade.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ifyo icikuulwa icili kunuma yakwe cilemoneka?
eng_translation: Have you seen how the building behind him is looking?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona ici icikuulwa cakaena cikalamba nga nshi elo cilemoneka icabusaka.
eng_translation: Yes the building is big and looks clean.

bem_transcription: Bashitata batatu nanamayo umo nabekala mumuputule.
eng_translation: Three men and a woman are sitting in a room.

bem_transcription: Aba bonse balelanshanya fimo, pantu namayo nakwata necakulembela kuminwe.
eng_translation: They are discussing something because the woman even has a pen in her hands.

bem_transcription: Tecakulembelako fye akwete iyo, uyu namayo nakwata namapepala epo alelemba kabili petebulo balelembelapo balibikapo namaluba.
eng_translation: She doesn't only have a pen but also papers where she is writing. There are also flowers on the table where she is writing from.

bem_transcription: Nomba naumona ifyo bonse balelolesha uyu umwaume uufwele icabuuta?
eng_translation: Have you seen how everyone is looking at this man in white?

bem_transcription: Nimbona uyu uufwele icabuuta balemulolesha nakalimo eulebalondolwela ifyakulemba.
eng_translation: Yes they are looking at him. It is like he is the one telling them what to write.

bem_transcription: Abantu abengi bali panse yacikuulwa nabeminina.
eng_translation: A lot of people are standing outside a building.

bem_transcription: Elyo tabemininefye bambi baleenda nokwenda.
eng_translation: They are not just standing but others are even walking.

bem_transcription: Umo umulumendo uwinine pantashi naiminina naikata ne cipampa.
eng_translation: A young man standing in front is even holding a sign in his hands.

bem_transcription: Lelo uupalamene nankwe umukashanya alemoneka uwafulwa pamenso pantu nabifya nakukanwa.
eng_translation: The woman near him looks unhappy though.

bem_transcription: Kabili incende yakaena baliko cilemoneka bushiku elo uku kuntu nakalimo nakutalala pantu bonse bali mufyampepo.
eng_translation: This looks like it is in the night and the place looks cold because they all are wearing jerseys.

bem_transcription: Akanama akafiita kalebutuka.
eng_translation: A black animal is running.

bem_transcription: Elyo kunuma yakanama kuli umukashana uuleketa napunda naasamuna nakanwa.
eng_translation: There is a girl behind it calling it with her mouth wide open.

bem_transcription: Kabili kuli naumbi umulumendo nao alemoneka alepepekamo.
eng_translation: There seems to be another boy running after it.

bem_transcription: Bushe ulemoneka kwati kanama nshi aka kene?
eng_translation: What do you think this type of an animal is?

bem_transcription: Aka akanama kalemoneka nakalimo kabwa akanoono.
eng_translation: This looks like a small dog.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo wishi aleafwilishako abana ukunina muli cimotoka icilemoneka kwati califwa.
eng_translation: A father is helping the children get in to the vehicle which appears to be broken.

bem_transcription: Uku kuntu bali kulemoneka balibyalako nefisali ifingi.
eng_translation: There are a lot of sugar canes were they are.

bem_transcription: Nomba lolekesha ifyo namayo eminine.
eng_translation: Now look closely at how the woman is standing.

bem_transcription: Uyu namayo alemoneka nalimo nanaka pantu eminine fye naikatako namumusana.
eng_translation: She looks tired because she is standing while putting her hands on her waist.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo alefuma mumenshi.
eng_translation: A young man is coming out of the water.

bem_transcription: Bushe uyu mumana washani uuli pakati ya mayanda?
eng_translation: What kind of river is this that is between the houses.

bem_transcription: Uyu temumana iyo ni swimming pool.
eng_translation: It is not a river but it is a swimming pool.

bem_transcription: So bonse aba bantu abakolongene balesamba umu mu swimming pool?
eng_translation: Are all these people gathered here swimming in this pool?

bem_transcription: Ee, bonse balesamba umu mwine.
eng_translation: Yes they are all swimming in it.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali pali kompyuta mumuputule.
eng_translation: A young man is on a computer in a room.

bem_transcription: Elo aya amakompyuta cilepala kwati babomfya mukumwenako ifinama.
eng_translation: It's like these computers are used for watching the animals.

bem_transcription: Kabili kunuma yakompyuta iilipo uyu umulumendo ndemonapo naumbi umulumendo nao pali ifyo aletinika.
eng_translation: There is another young man behind these computers pressing something.

bem_transcription: Mukati yamuputule mulemoneka muli ne filimba ifilebafwa ukumfwa nelyo ukukutika kufileciitka.
eng_translation: There are even speakers in the room that help them listen to what is happening.

bem_transcription: Muli uyu umuputule balimusunga umwabusaka pantu tamulemonekapo nefiko nangu fimo iyo.
eng_translation: This room is kept clean because there is no any visible dirt.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ilepepeka utoni.
eng_translation: A dog is chasing the birds.

bem_transcription: Elyo kuntu ili nikululamba fye lwamumana.
eng_translation: This dog is at the beach.

bem_transcription: Imbwa yakaena intu yafiita naipalana fye notutwine utoni tuntu ilepepeka.
eng_translation: The dog is just as dark as these very birds.

bem_transcription: Uyu umumana ulemoneka kwati wapitila fye mupepi nomusebo pantu mumbali mulepita namamotoka.
eng_translation: This river is just in the side of the road because there are even vehicles passing on the other side.

bem_transcription: Kabili mumabali yamumana mwine baliminikamo notumuti tubili kambi akakatapakatapa mwapita notwabuuta elo kambi akakashika mwapita notwabuuta.
eng_translation: There are sticks that have been placed on the side of the river. One is green with white stripes and the other is red with white stripes.

bem_transcription: Utubwa tubili utunoono tuleangala.
eng_translation: Two small dogs are playing.

bem_transcription: Palemoneka pali utu utubwa pali akakalamba nakanoono, aka akalemoneka namasako ayabuuta ekakalamba elo aka akakwete ayefiita ekanoono.
eng_translation: There seems to be an older one and a younger one. The one with white fur is the older one while the other with black fur is the younger one.

bem_transcription: Kabili kunuma yatubwa kulemoneka nabeminikako ne ncinga.
eng_translation: There are bicycles parked behind these dogs.

bem_transcription: Apa shileangalila nimukati ka n'ganda palubansa pantu ulubansa lwalicingililwa nokucingililwa.
eng_translation: They are playing inside their yard because the yard is fenced.

bem_transcription: Ishi imbwa shakaena shilemoneka balishisunga nobusaka pantu shilemoneka fye ishabusaka.
eng_translation: The dogs look well kept because they are clean.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: ELo fintu ekele pali ici cine cimpelwa cilemoneka kwati nimotoka aleensha.
eng_translation: The way he is seated on the swing looks like he is driving a car.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwana wakaena nafwala necampepo nakalimo kuntu ali nakutalala.
eng_translation: The child is wearing a jersey it is like it's cold where she is.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ukutila iyi incende ilepala kwati tebana fye beka basangwako?
eng_translation: Have you noticed that it's like not only children are found at this place?

bem_transcription: Ca cine nimbona, pantu nga twalolekesha bwino uku lubali kulemoneka kuli notupuna uto babika fye nalimo pakwikala abantu nga baisa kuncende yi.
eng_translation: Yes I have seen because there are even chairs on the other side where people can sit when they visit this place.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo umusebo mwaliba namatuka ayakalamba.
eng_translation: And there are large shops on this road.

bem_transcription: Amatuka yaka ena nayesalwa elyo kucibumba balilembaulako ne fyakulemba.
eng_translation: The shops are closed and there are things scrabbled on the wall.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati aya matuka tayabomba pantu yalemoneka kwati kale bayeswilepo.
eng_translation: These shops look like they are not in use and haven't been opened in a long time.

bem_transcription: Uyu namayo waka ena nafwala ishati lya buta napapa naka chola  ka fita
eng_translation: The woman is wearing a white shirt and carrying a black bag.

bem_transcription: Umwana umulumendo no mwana umukashana bali panse baleangala.
eng_translation: A young girl and a young girl are playing outside.

bem_transcription: Aka mwana akamukashana nakemya no kuboko kumo elyo nga mulumendo kena nakacensa nakonfwa bwino.
eng_translation: The girl is raising one hand and the boy is smilling and happy.

bem_transcription: Kuncende bali aban aba kwalifula umucanga pantu eulemonekako fye weka weka.
eng_translation: there is a lot of sand where these children are because it is the only thing visible.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya aba abaice balitulikako ne mbao nangula amapulanga.
eng_translation: There are even planks piled behind these children.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwana umulumendo nafwala akasote kabili umwana umukashan nafwala akatambala.
eng_translation: The boy is wearing a hat and the girl is wearing a head wrap.

bem_transcription: Abantu nabekala pa muulu wa cikulwa.
eng_translation: People are seated on top of a building.

bem_transcription: Elyo ici cikulwa balicikula bwino sana pantu cilemoneka icayemba kabili ne nceshi babika babika ishakosa isha nshimbi.
eng_translation: This building looks well built and beautiful with metal pillars.

bem_transcription: Umo namayo uwikele paka puna nafwala amagalshi kabili ne campepo.
eng_translation: One woman seated on a chair is wearing glasses and a jersey.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende balibikapo utumipando utwingi utwakutila ngu abantu nabafula kuti bakuma ukwikala.
eng_translation: This place has a lot of chairs to accommodate a lot of people.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ba namayo batatu bali pa muulu wa cikulwa.
eng_translation: Three women are on top of a building.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati kuli ifyo balebika pantu umbi alemoneka kwati alepimapo fimo.
eng_translation: It's like they are puting something because one of them seems to be doing some measurements.

bem_transcription: Kabili panshi ya cikulwa nga twalolekesha palemoneka nabeminikapo na motoka ya buta.
eng_translation: There is a white vehicle parked below the building.

bem_transcription: Bali aba bana mayo babili bafwele ama shati ya buta elyo umbi afwele ishati ilya fita.
eng_translation: Of the three women, two are wearing white shirts and one is wearing a black one.

bem_transcription: Kabili incende yaka ena kulemoneka kwalifula sana ifikulwa elyo fyalititikana.
eng_translation: There seems to be a lot of buildings clustered in this area.

bem_transcription: Namayo alipakati aka musebo ale-enda.
eng_translation: A woman is walking in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Elyo alemoneka uwainako panono nafwala ne campepo ca fita ku muulu.
eng_translation: She looks a bit fat and is wearing a black jersey.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya kwa na mayo nabeninikako na motoka.
eng_translation: There is a vehicle parked behind this woman.

bem_transcription: Uyu umusebo ulemoneka kwati tamupita sana ama motoka pantu alemoneka kwati ale-endela fye pakati ka musebo.
eng_translation: This road doesnt seem to be used a lot by vehicles because she is walking in the middle of it.

bem_transcription: Kabili kumbali ya musebo kulemonka ne cikulwa cintu bakula bwino.
eng_translation: There is a well built building on the side of the road.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo bali pacipoma ca menshi mu bwato.
eng_translation: Young men are in a boat at a falls.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilemoneka amenshi nayabacinfya nayakwta sana amaka emulandu wine balemoneka kwati balabunda.
eng_translation: They seem to be drowning because it's like the water has a lot of force and it is overpowering them.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ifi bafwele fimpompo ifyakubacingilisha nga cakuti bali isangile mubusanso umutwe kuti wacingililwa.
eng_translation: Since they are wearing helmets, atleast they would protect their heads of they had an accident.

bem_transcription: Ca cine pantu pa menshi yaka ena apa napafula amabwe.
eng_translation: It is true because there are a lot of rocks there.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ilebutuka.
eng_translation: A dog is running.

bem_transcription: Bushe nikwisa ilebutukila imbwa iyi kwati ya mpanga.
eng_translation: Where is this dog that looks like a wild dog look running to?

bem_transcription: Imbwa iyi ilebutuka ilepepeka utunama mu mpanga
eng_translation: It is chasing small wild animals.

bem_transcription: So ninshi imbwa iyi ikala mu mpanga umu mwine olo ilemo fye?
eng_translation: Does it means it also stays in the very forest or it just went there?

bem_transcription: Ilemo fye baisendele fye baisendele fye mukulunga ku bantu  utunama.
eng_translation: It is like it was just taken there by people to hunt wild animals.

bem_transcription: Shitata aleangala ubwangalo bwakushelemuka.
eng_translation: A man is slidding.

bem_transcription: Nomba cilemoneka kwati ali apona pantu amaboko yonse yali panshi amolu nayema mu muulu.
eng_translation: It looks like he has fallen because because the hands are down and the legs are in the air.

bem_transcription: Kabili kulubali kuli abalumendo babili cilemoneka nalimo baletamba shitata uyu uleangala.
eng_translation: There are young men on the side and it appears they are watching him.

bem_transcription: Pali aba balumendo nga ni uyu ufwele ica buta alemoneka kwati aleseka pantu nalolesha panshi.
eng_translation: Of the young men, the one wearing white looks like he is laughing because he is looking down.

bem_transcription: Kabili kunuma yaba lumendo abaletamba uyu shitata kuli na bambi babili abalepita bena baleyendela fye.
eng_translation: There are other people behind these young men who are walking.

bem_transcription: Abana batatu nabekala pe libwe
eng_translation: Three children are seated on a rock.

bem_transcription: Elo nintemwa ifyo aka aka mwana akamukashana akanono pali bonse kacitile kalemoneka akasekelela kabili akansansa.
eng_translation: I love how the youngest girl is looking happy and joyous.

bem_transcription: Aka kena akamulumendo kena nakekekata ne sako mu minwe.
eng_translation: The young boy even has a further in his hands.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo incende iyi ilemoneka?
eng_translation: But have you seen how this place is looking?

bem_transcription: Nimbona uku kulemoneka ni ku mpanga elo kwalifula sana amabwe kabili ne fimuti.
eng_translation: I have seen. This looks like the bush with a lot of trees and rocks.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo baleteya umupila pa menshi.
eng_translation: Young men are playing soccer in the water.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati ici icangalo naciwama pantu cilemoneka kwati bonse fya nabaipakisha.
eng_translation: This game is obviously very good because they all look like they are enjoying.

bem_transcription: Amenshi yaka ena ayo baleangalamo yalemoneka ayabusaka balayasunga bwino sana.
eng_translation: The water where they are playing from looks clean and well kept.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati aya yali mabumba yabili pantu uku kuli abafwele utusote utwabuta elyo ibumba limbi bafwele utusote utwa kashika.
eng_translation: It looks like these are two different teams because others are wearing white hats and others are wearing red ones.

bem_transcription: Awe ine ndemona pali amabumba yatatu pantu ndemona noufwele  akasote ka fita.
eng_translation: I think there are three teams because I can see another one wearing a black hat.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili baleyangala panse yacikulwa.
eng_translation: Two young men are playing outside a building.

bem_transcription: Elyo baletantala mumbali ya cikulwa.
eng_translation: They are stepping on the edges of the building.

bem_transcription: Ici icikulwa bali cikula bwino elo cilemoneka ubusaka pantu cintu ca buta.
eng_translation: This building is well built and looks clean because it is white.

bem_transcription: Nomba naumona ifyo aba bene abalumendo balemoneka?
eng_translation: But have you seen how these young men are looking.

bem_transcription: Nimbona bonse babili nafwala ifyapalana ama shati yakashika kabili namatoloshi yafita.
eng_translation: They are both wearing similar red shirts and similar black trousers.

bem_transcription: Umukashana naikala pakapuna panse alelya.
eng_translation: A young woman is seated on a chair outside, eating.

bem_transcription: Elyuo cilemopneka kwati insala naimutembula pantu alemoneka lushile lushile pa menso.
eng_translation: It looks like she is very hungry because she looks pale on the face.

bem_transcription: Nomba pantu alelila pene awe napalamba fiko fyonse ifi fimbi nafiponaila na panshi.
eng_translation: But the place she is eating from is very dirty with litter all over.

bem_transcription: Nomba kunuma yakwe kuli aka ntemba apo bashitisha ifya kulya elo pali no mulumendo uleshitapo fimo.
eng_translation: Behind her is a booth where they sell food and there is a young man selling.

bem_transcription: Elyo aka ntemba kaka ena kantu kakashika notupuna fye tuntu babika panse nato tuntu twakashika.
eng_translation: The booth is red and the chairs outside it are red.

bem_transcription: Shitata na namyo nabaikumbata.
eng_translation: A man and a woman are hugging.

bem_transcription: Aba bonse balemoneka kwati bali umwana na wishi pantu wishi alemoneka umukote elyo uukashanai alemoneka umwaice.
eng_translation: It's like they are father and daughter because the man looks old and the woman looks young.

bem_transcription: Umu mu muputule bali muli fye na bantu bambi nakalimo paciba ifyo cailasefya.
eng_translation: There are other people too in this room. It's like they were celebrating something.

bem_transcription: Elo uyu umuputule ulemoneka umwafita muli fye iliti limo ilesaninkila bonse.
eng_translation: The room looks dark because there is only one light.

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata no mukashana abaikumbete bonse babili nafwala ifyapalana pantu bafwele ama shati aya buta bonse babili.
eng_translation: The man and the woman that are hugging are both wearing similar white shirts.

bem_transcription: Umukashana ali mu muputule alekama icikolopo.
eng_translation: A young woman is in a room squeezing the mop.

bem_transcription: Alemoneka nanaka cilepala kale atampile ukubomba.
eng_translation: She looks tired and it's like she has been working for a long time.

bem_transcription: Uyu umukashana waka ena nafwala akasote akabuta ishati lya fita kabili ne toloshi ilya makumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: This young woman is wearing a white hat, a black shirt and a blue trousers.

bem_transcription: mu muputule muntu ali ifibumba filemoneka ifya buta elo mubali mwapita ifya fita.
eng_translation: The walls in the room where she is look white with a black linning below.

bem_transcription: Kabili kunuma yakwe nakanika ne cisalu nalimo acilaciwasha.
eng_translation: She has hang a cloth behind her. Maybe she was washing.

bem_transcription: Abana besukulu bali mu muputule balelemba.
eng_translation: Pupils are in class, writing.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilemoneka kwati kulenga uku balelenga pantu bonse nabakwata ifipepala pantu balelemba fimo.
eng_translation: And it looks like they are drawing because they all have papers where they are writing.

bem_transcription: Ee balelenga pantu cilemoneka kwati uyu umuputule baubonfesha fye mukulenga pantu kumwena fye ku fikope fili kucibumba filelanga fye ukweba ati uyu umuputule wakulengelamo.
eng_translation: Yes they are drawing. You can just tell from the pictures in the walls that this is a drawing room.

bem_transcription: Elyo abafulile muli uyu umuputule banakashi abaume balemoneka fye abanono
eng_translation: The majority in this room awe females. There are very few males.

bem_transcription: Elo bonse abali muli ici cikulwa nabafwala ifyapalana elo bonse balikwata imishishi ishapalana bonse shintu sha fita balemoneka fye cimo cine.
eng_translation: They all look the same in this room because they all have dark hair and they are wearing the same.

bem_transcription: Akabwa akafita kaletolokela pa menshi.
eng_translation: A black dog is jumping in the water.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati kuli ifyo kalepepeka pantu nakafundumana.
eng_translation: Its like it is chasing something.

bem_transcription: Aya amenshi yaka ena yalemoneka yabela fye mumbali ya musebo pantu nga twalolekesha bwino palemoneka umusebo mu pepi fye.
eng_translation: This water seems to be just near the road as can be seen when you look closely.

bem_transcription: Cimbi naco cakutila kumbali ya kamana kwaliba aka bulalo akanono
eng_translation: There is also a small bridge on the side of the river.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili kuli iyi incende kwalifula utumaluba utwa katapa katapa.
eng_translation: And there are a lot of green flowers in this place.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili bali pa cisebele baleimba.
eng_translation: Two young men are singing on a stage.

bem_transcription: Umo pali aba ni shitata ufwele isheti ilya kashika nakwata notu myenfu utunono elyo mu mutwe nafwalamo akaslu aka kashika
eng_translation: One of these is a man wearing a red shirt with a little beard and a small head wrap on his head.

bem_transcription: Elo bonse babili nabakwata ifilimba fya nsale kuminwe.
eng_translation: They all have harps in their hands.

bem_transcription: Ici icisebele cilemoneka cikalamba sana pantu mu muulu nacikwata nama liti aya yemba bwino.
eng_translation: This stage looks big with beautiful lights in top.

bem_transcription: Elo pacisebele caka ena nafuti balibikapo ifisoselo ifingi kabili ne fintu btanatiakapo nafyo fingi.
eng_translation: There are also a lot of things in the stage.

bem_transcription: Shitata umo aleimba babili balelisha banjo.
eng_translation: One man is singing and two are playing the guitar.

bem_transcription: So aba balelisha amabanjo balekonka mu fyo uyu muntu aleimba?
eng_translation: Are those that are playing following along as the man is singing?

bem_transcription: Ee balekonka mu fyo aleimba pantu bali bonse pamo.
eng_translation: Yes they are following what he is singing because they are together.

bem_transcription: Umu mwine balimbila ni mucikulwa ca shani?
eng_translation: What kind of building is this that they are singing from?

bem_transcription: Mucikulwa ici baleimbilamo cikulwa ca mapepo.
eng_translation: This is a church.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Pali ishi imbwa kuli imo ilemoneka ikalamba sana kabili iyaina bwino elyo paba nakanono akakwete utumasako utwafulungana
eng_translation: Of the two dogs, there is one looking big and fat and beautiful and then there is a small one with strange fur.

bem_transcription: Uyu umunana waka ena ulemoneka ukalamba sana walifika fye nokutali.
eng_translation: This river looks very big and runs a long way.

bem_transcription: Kululmba lwa mumana kulemoneka utumucanga utunono elyo mwapatanakana no tumabwe utunono
eng_translation: There seems to be small sand mixed with small stones on the seashore.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili mu mbali ya mumana mwine mulemoneka ne fimuti nafyo ifingi sana.
eng_translation: There are also a lot of trees on the sides of the river.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo baleangala icangalo ca mupila kumbali ya mumana.
eng_translation: Young men are playing football on the side of the river.

bem_transcription: Elyo bambi bekele pa cimuti icauma icaba fye mumbali ya mumana baletamba abanabo.
eng_translation: Others are sitting on a dry log near the river watching their friends.

bem_transcription: Kabili mumbali ya mumana mwine muli fye na bantu bambi abekele fye nabo abengi.
eng_translation: There are also a lot of other people that are seated on the river banks.

bem_transcription: Elyo bambi balesamba pakati ka mumana.
eng_translation: Others are swimming in the middle of the river.

bem_transcription: Ku mumana waka ene uyu nag twalolekesha beino kwaliba ne cikulwa ico bakula icitali kabili kwaliba ne fimuti nafyo ifingi.
eng_translation: If we look closely there is a tall building near the river and also a lot of trees.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo nabaice, nabakshana bali ku cibansa nabekala bambi nabeminina.
eng_translation: Young boys and young girls are seated and others are standing at the play ground.

bem_transcription: Elyo kuli aba babice abalumendo abafwele amasheti ya buta abaleteya umupila.
eng_translation: And there are two boys wearing white shirts who are playing football.

bem_transcription: Mumbali ya cibansa nabeminikamo ne myotoka ishingi.
eng_translation: There are cars parked on the sides of the play ground.

bem_transcription: Aba bonse baletaya ici icangalo ca mupila nabakwata amashati ayakalamba nga nshi.
eng_translation: All these playing are wearing big shirts.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili aba bene abaleteya umupila balemoneka nabaka kumona fye nefyo balemoneka pa menso.
eng_translation: By looking at their faces you can tell that these players are tired.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babii nabekala mu muputule balelolesha pali bamashini.
eng_translation: Two men are sitting in a room looking at machines.

bem_transcription: Elyo aba bamashini ni balya babonfya mufipatala nga cakutila balepima fimo.
eng_translation: These machines are those they use in hospitals when they are scanning someone.

bem_transcription: Kabili pama tebulo yabo nabikapo ifipepala ifingi nalimo balelembapo ifyo balemona.
eng_translation: They have put many papers on the table. Maybe they are writing what they are observing.

bem_transcription: Uku kulemoneka niku cipatala pantu kucibumba kuli ne fikope ifilelangilila ukutila ni mucipala umu.
eng_translation: This looks like a hospital as can be seen from the pictures on the wall behind.

bem_transcription: Umo shitata afwele ishati ilya fita kabili notuma galashi elyo umbi nao ena afwele fey ishati ilyabuta.
eng_translation: One man is wearing a black shirt and glasses and the other is wearing a white shirt.

bem_transcription: Abana abakashana babili bali mu muputule baletoloka pa cipuna.
eng_translation: Two young girls are in a room jumping on s couch.

bem_transcription: Nomba aka akalipo akamwana kena nakatolokesha kabili nakonfwa bwino.
eng_translation: The one that looks young has jumped higher and she looks happy.

bem_transcription: Uyu umuputule balimo abana aba ulemoneka uwabusaka fyonse fili ifya busaka.
eng_translation: This room that these children are in looks clean and everything in it is clean.

bem_transcription: Nintemwa kumona fyo bekatene lintu baletoloka pantu bonse nabatoloka mu muulu lelo tabalekene.
eng_translation: I love how they are holding each other and not letting go despite jumping.

bem_transcription: Icakulundapo fye aba babili abana nabafwala nama shati ayapala bonse babili ayabuta.
eng_translation: Additionally these young girls are wearing white shirts.

bem_transcription: Nyina nakumbatila umwana wakwe.
eng_translation: A mother is hugging her child.

bem_transcription: Elyo umwana wakwe nafwala icisote icikalamba ica mafufu ayabuta mwapita no twafita.
eng_translation: The child is wearing a big white fluffy hat with black spots.

bem_transcription: Kabili nyina waka ena alikwata imishishi nga nshi.
eng_translation: The mother has a lot of hair.

bem_transcription: Uyu umwana kuli ifyo alelolesha kunuma yakwa nyina pantu eko atontele fye amenso.
eng_translation: There is something behind the mother that this child is looking at because that's where the focus is.

bem_transcription: Elo umwana waka ene nakabili alemoneka nakalimo pali ifyo alepapa panyu nauma ne nkashi.
eng_translation: This child has frowns on the face it's like there is something surprising he has seen.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali mucikulwa naimina.
eng_translation: A young man is standing in the building.

bem_transcription: Nomba alemoneka kwati nanaka pantu naikata mu musana elyo alolesha kumbi.
eng_translation: It's like he is tired because his hands are raising on his waist and he is looking somewhere else.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati uyu umulumendo euwamya mufimbusu pantu pa mwinshi eminine pali icipampa ca fimbusu.
eng_translation: It's like this young man is the janitor because there is a restroom sign on the door where he is standing.

bem_transcription: Mu fimbusu fyaka ena mulemoneka mwafiko nalimo tabamusunga bwino sana.
eng_translation: These toilets look very dirty. They are not well kept.

bem_transcription: Shitata naikala paka puna panse.
eng_translation: A man is seated on a chair outside.

bem_transcription: Elyo kunuma yakwe kuli umwinshi uwakwingila mu cikulwa umwinshi ulemoneka wa katapa katapa.
eng_translation: There is a green door behind him for entering the building.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Lubali lumbi nimbona balashitishako ne fyakufwala pantu nabakobeka ifyakufwala ifyapusana pusana amashati naba siketi.
eng_translation: On the other side their are selling clothes because I have seen the have hang shirts, skirts and others.

bem_transcription: Pa muulu wa cilimba pene balipangilapo nakalubi ako akalelisha icilimba.
eng_translation: There is a doll on top of the radio that's playing the radio

bem_transcription: Shitata naikala mu muputule pacipuna ne mbwa yakwe.
eng_translation: A man is sitting on a chair in room with his dog.

bem_transcription: Elyo alikwata imbwa isuma nga nshi iya yemba iyaina bwino kabili iyabuta.
eng_translation: He has a very nice chubby white dog.

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata wakaena alemoneka nakalimo nashipula lintu akumbatile imbwa yakwe.
eng_translation: It looks like this man has dozzed off

bem_transcription: Cimbi cakutila uyu shitata alitemwa iyi imbwa pantu naikumbata elyo kabili naitomona.
eng_translation: This man loves his dog because has kissed it and is hugging it.

bem_transcription: Mu muputule waka ena balitantinamo na ma computer ayo babika pe tebulo nalimo ayo abonfya uyu shitata.
eng_translation: There are computers on a table in this room. It's like they are the ones this man uses.

bem_transcription: Bana mayo bali mucibansa ne mbwa shabo.
eng_translation: Women are in the play ground with their dogs.

bem_transcription: Elyo cila muntu naikata imbwa yakwe uyu umbi ena ekete shibili ishabuta sheka sheka.
eng_translation: Each one is holding her dog. But the other one is holding tow white dogs.

bem_transcription: Aba bana mayo baka ena balemoneka bali ne nsansa elo cilemoneka kwati pali ulebakopa icikope.
eng_translation: These women look happy and it's like there is someone taking a picture of them.

bem_transcription: Nga ni uyunufwele icakashika ena alemoneka uwa nsansa sana eylo naikata imbwa ishafita shibili ku minwe yakwe.
eng_translation: If it's this one in red holding two black dogs, she looks very happy.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Uwana umunono aleangsha umuswaki.
eng_translation: A young child is playing with a toothbrush.

bem_transcription: Bushe umwana uyu alishiba ati umuswaki tewakwangasha iyo wakusukushilako?
eng_translation: Does this child know that a toothbrush is nit a toy buy it's for brushing teeth?

bem_transcription: Ee kwena alishiba ukubonfya umuswaki apa ali alelolela fye amenshi ayakubonfya.
eng_translation: Yes he knows it is for brushing teeth. He is just waiting for water to use.

bem_transcription: So ninshi alelolea abafyashi bakwe bese bamwafwe?
eng_translation: Is he waiting for his parents to come to his aid?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya alelolela amenshi yakubonfya.
eng_translation: No he is waiting for water to use.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali pa musebo naimina natwika ne cintu pa mutwe.
eng_translation: A young man is standing on the road with something in his head.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi ni mbeketi intu atwikile pa mutwe mulemoneka mukati muli na menshi.
eng_translation: There seems to be water in this bucket on his head.

bem_transcription: Kumbali ya musebo ndemona nabeminikako naka motoka aka kashika.
eng_translation: There is a red car parked on the side of the road.

bem_transcription: Icikulwa nacena icili fye mupepi na motoka beminike cilemoneka ica fiko tabacisunga ubusaka.
eng_translation: The building next to the parked car looks dirty and not well kept.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo wakaena, ena nafwala ishati lyabuta mwapita ne fyafita kabili ne toloshi lya makumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: This young man is wearing a white shirt with black stripes and a blue trousers.

bem_transcription: Umwaice umulumendo naiminina panse.
eng_translation: A young boy is standing outside.

bem_transcription: Nakabili afwele akasote umupitile utwabuta no twafita afwala ne ca mpepo nakashati mukati
eng_translation: He is wearing a hat with black and white stripes and a jersey with a shirt inside.

bem_transcription: Elyo kunuma yakwe kuli abantu abengi nalimo pali ifyo beshile mukutamba.
eng_translation: Behind him are a lot of people. Maybe they are here to watch something.

bem_transcription: Nomba  naumona ifyo uyu umwaice alemoneka pa menso?
eng_translation: Have you seen how this child is looking on the face?

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Abantu bale-enda kumbali ya musebo kuncende iya talalisha.
eng_translation: People are walking in the roadside in a very cold place.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende ilemoneka yalitalala nga nshi pantu kumona fye ne fyo bafwele fintu ifyakaba
eng_translation: You can tell that this place is cold by the warm clothes they are wearing.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili kuli abantu abali fye pa mwinshi wa cikulwa nakalimo balefwaya ukwingila mu cikulwa.
eng_translation: There are also people standing at the entrance of a building it's like they want to enter.

bem_transcription: Elyo nga twalolekesha na kabili kuli uyu umulumendo upishishe amaboko mwitumba alelolesha uyu umunakwe ufwele akasote aka kashika.
eng_translation: When we look closely there is also this young man who has out his hands in the pockets and is looking at the friend who is wearing a red hat.

bem_transcription: Nomba aya matuka yali mumbali ya musebo yalemoneka tabaleyesula pantu nakutalalisha
eng_translation: These shops along the road look like they will not be opened because it is too cold.

bem_transcription: Ici icikope cikope ca musebo uwaba fye pakati ya mpili.
eng_translation: This road is a picture that is in between two mountains.

bem_transcription: Elyo aka kashila tulande kamusebo akanono kabili umwaisula amabwe.
eng_translation: This is a small rocky road.

bem_transcription: Te mambwe yeka kabli mwalisula ne fyani.
eng_translation: It is not only rocky but has a lot of grass too.

bem_transcription: Bushe naumona ifyo impili ishi shilemonela?
eng_translation: Have you seen how these mountains are looking?

bem_transcription: Ee nimbona ishi impili shaka ena ala shitali nga nshi shile fwaya nokukumya muulu!
eng_translation: Yes these mountains are very tall. They are almost touching the sky's.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali mucibansa nakontama nalimo alefwaya kuwamba ukubutuka.
eng_translation: A young man has bent in the okay ground. It is like he is about to start running.

bem_transcription: Awe mune tekubutuka baletampa ukubutuka cilepala kwati baletampa ukucinfyanya ukufulamuka pantu nga twamona nafulamuka.
eng_translation: It is not running. It is like they are in a flipping competition.

bem_transcription: Ca cine kumona fye ne fyo afwele pantu afwele fye kaputula iya makumbi makumbi abikapo ne nsapato sha fita kabili ne nsokoshi ishabuta.
eng_translation: Yes you can tell by just looking at what he is wearing because he is only wearing a blue short, black shoes and white socks.

bem_transcription: Elyo tali eka kuli ici icangalo kuli na bambi babili umbi afwele icakashika elyo umbi afwele ica fita mwapita no twabuta.
eng_translation: He is not alone but he is with another in red and another black and white.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili kui fye na bantu bambi abeshile mukubatamba.
eng_translation: There are also many other people that have come to watch.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili nabekala panse patupuna.
eng_translation: Two men are sitting in chairs outside.

bem_transcription: Apa palemoneka pali wishi no mwana wishi ni uyu ukwete imfwi mumbali ufwele ishati ilya fita elyo alepanda umwana amano.
eng_translation: It looks like theres the son and the father here. The father is the one with grey hair in the sides of his head who is wearing a black shirt and it's like he is advising the young one.

bem_transcription: Elyo apa bali palemoneka ni panse fya ya ng'anda yabo pantu balibikapo no tupuna utwakutushishapo.
eng_translation: This looks like outside their house because they have even put chairs where you can rest.

bem_transcription: Cilwpala kwati aba baili balitemwana pantu umwana naposako amano kuli wishi lintu alemulangisha.
eng_translation: It's like these two love each other because the son appears to be paying attention to what the father is showing him.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili pa ng'anda yak ena balipasunga apa busaka utufyani tulemoneka utwa katapa katapa kabili mumbali ya tufyani muli utumabwe uto batantamika bwino nga nshi.
eng_translation: This house appears to be well kept with nice green grass and well arranged stones along the edges of the grass.

bem_transcription: Abantu bali pakati ka musebo bale-enda.
eng_translation: People are walking in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Pali na namayo ulemoneka uwaina filya nafwala icampepo abikapo nakasote aka kashika.
eng_translation: There's also a woman who appears to be fat, wearing a jersey and a red hat.

bem_transcription: Bambi abli panatanshi ya uyu namayo uli kunuma nabekata na mu minwe bale-enda bambi nabemya ne fipampa.
eng_translation: Others in front of this woman are holding hands and others are raising signposts.

bem_transcription: Mumbali ya musebo mulemoneka mwaliba nama tuka umo abantu bashita ifintu.
eng_translation: There are shoos on the sides of the road where people sell things.

bem_transcription: Kabili mumbali ya musebo mwine baliminikamo ne myanfuli.
eng_translation: There are even umbrellas that have been placed on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali pakati ka musebo naikalako panshi.
eng_translation: A young man is seated in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati acilayangala elyo apona aiteneka panshi.
eng_translation: It looks like he was playing and then he fell down.

bem_transcription: Kabili kunuma yakwe kuli fye naumbi umulumendo uleyendelela fye nampo nga aleya kwisa?
eng_translation: Behind him is a young man walking. Where could he be going?

bem_transcription: Iyi incende ilemoneka yalitalala sana pantu bonse nabafwala ifya mpepo ifya tikama.
eng_translation: This place looks very cold because everyone is wearing very thick jerseys.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili kuli iyi incede balikulako ifikulwa ifitali nganshi filemoneka ubusaka.
eng_translation: There are also very tall buildings in this place that look very good.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ili mucibansa iletoloka.
eng_translation: A dog is jumping in the play ground.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi in mbwa iyo basambilisha bwino ukubutuka no kwangala ifyangalo ifya pusana pusana.
eng_translation: This dog is well trained to jump and play different games.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya mbwa kuli na bantu fye abekele nalimo pali ifyo balelemba.
eng_translation: Behind the dog are people who are seated. It looks like they are writing something.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati iyi imbwa tailiko fye yeka kuli nashimbi isho abantu aba beshile mukutamba.
eng_translation: It looks like this is not the only dog that people are here to watch. There are other dogs too.

bem_transcription: Ishi imbwa shilemoneka nalimo shilecinfyanya eico abali kunuma balelemba iyacinfya iyinankwe.
eng_translation: These dogs appear to be competing and those behind are writing the scores.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo batatu bali mu cibansa ca mupila.
eng_translation: Three young men are in a football ground.

bem_transcription: Elyo kuli uli pakati ena natampula icilutanfu icikulu!
eng_translation: The one in the middle has made a very big step.

bem_transcription: Babili abalumendo nafwala ifimpompo fyapala kabili nama shati yapalana.
eng_translation: Two young men are wearing similar helmets and similar shirts.

bem_transcription: Elyo umunabo ena afwele ifipusene afwele ifya buta ne cimpompo ica fita.
eng_translation: Their friend is different because he is wearing white clothes and a black helmets.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili ku cibansa caka ena cilemoneka cintu ca busaka pantu takulemoneka fye ifko ifili fyonse.
eng_translation: This play ground looks very clean because there is no any visible dirt around.

bem_transcription: Abantu batatu baletamba ifibumbe fili mukamana.
eng_translation: Three people are watching walls in the river.

bem_transcription: Nomba ifibumbe ifi ninshi bafibumbila mukamana?
eng_translation: Why have these walls been built in the river?

bem_transcription: Ifi fibumbo fyakuwamya akamana.
eng_translation: They are to beautify the river.

bem_transcription: Bushe uyu shibantu atalwike kuli aba bambi bushe ali nabo aba abafwele ifyafituluka?
eng_translation: Is this man that is apart from these people wearing greyish things with them?

bem_transcription: Iyo nakalya ali fye eka.
eng_translation: No he is on his own.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo no mukashana bali kumbali ya mumana nabekatana ne minwe.
eng_translation: A young man and a young woman are on the river bank holding hands.

bem_transcription: Aba babili balemoneka balyupana kabili balemoneka balitemwana, kumona fye fintu bekatene.
eng_translation: These two are married and from the way they are holding each other you can tell that they love each other.

bem_transcription: Uyu umumana uli uku kuncende iyi ulemoneka uunoono taufikile ukutali iyo.
eng_translation: This river looks small and it looks like it doesn't go very far.

bem_transcription: Elyo pali aba bena abatemwana abeminine pali nakabwato akanoono sana ako bemike fye kululamba ulwamumana.
eng_translation: There is also a small boat on the sea shore where these two lovers are standing.

bem_transcription: Kabili kuncende iyi kwalifula ifimuti nafyofinngi fyonse filemoneka fye ifyakatapakatapa.
eng_translation: There are also a lot of trees in this place and they look green.

bem_transcription: Umukashana no mulumendo bali mumuputule baleilolesha.
eng_translation: A young man and young woman are in a room looking at each other.

bem_transcription: Elyo apa bali palemoneka nipamuulu wacikuulwa pantu bali fye mupepi nomutenge.
eng_translation: This looks like they are sitting at a height because they are near the roof.

bem_transcription: Mumuulu wacikuulwa nababikamo notumaluba uto bakambatika kucibumba.
eng_translation: There are also flowers that have been stuck on wall.

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo aba bantu babili balemoneka pa menso?
eng_translation: Have you seen how these two are looking on their faces?

bem_transcription: Ee, nimbona, cilemoneka kwati umulumendo nabika umukashana mwilyashi icakwebati umwanakashi yu nasendwa amano.
eng_translation: Yes it is like this young woman is carried away with the story that this young man is telling.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu naikala panse pakapuna.
eng_translation: An old man is sitting on a chair outside.

bem_transcription: Elyo kulubali lumbi ulwakukuso balikako umwakuposa ifiko.
eng_translation: On the right hand side is a trash bin.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili cilemoneka aka akapuna bakabika fye mumbali yamusebo.
eng_translation: It looks like this chair is just on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Nomba shitata uyu wine alemoneka uwabulanda kwati kuli ifyo aletontonkanya sana.
eng_translation: This old man looks sad like there is something that he is thinking about.

bem_transcription: Ca cine pantu ekele fye uwaikumbata talemonekapo ne nsansa iyo.
eng_translation: Very true he looks sad with his arms folded.

bem_transcription: Banamayo nabashitata bali mumuputule nabeminina.
eng_translation: Men and women are standing in a building.

bem_transcription: Awe lolekesha, tabeminine aba, nabatoloka, bonse nabemya namaboko mu muulu.
eng_translation: Look closer. They are not standing but their are jumping with their hands in the air.

bem_transcription: Eya, niwewalanda, aba bantu, nabatoloka, elo bonse balemoneka abansansa pamenso.
eng_translation: You are right these people are jumping and they all look happy.

bem_transcription: Uyu umuputule ulemoneka kwati nikuntu aba bantu bonse babombela.
eng_translation: This room looks like it is their workplace.

bem_transcription: Ca cine pantu nakunuma yabo kulemoneka fye icisalu ico bafimba pe wiindo.
eng_translation: You are right because even behind them is just a curtain that covers the window.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba nangu eminine amenso yakwe yatontele kumbi, kuli ifyo alelosha ifimusendele amano.
eng_translation: Even though he is standing, his eyes are focussed on something else. There is something he is looking at that had drawn his attention.

bem_transcription: KAbili alemoneka nalimo kuli ifyo aletontonkanya ifilemushupa mumano.
eng_translation: It looks like there is something he is thinking about that is troubling him.

bem_transcription: Lubali lumbi kuli namayo uufwele ifyafiita uukwete icakukopelako muminwe cili kwati alekopa ifi fine namayo alelolesha ifili kuntashi yabo.
eng_translation: on the other hand is a woman wearing black with a camera. It is like she is also capturing what this other woman is looking at.

bem_transcription: Cacine, uyu namayo uuletontonkanya nampo nga kulolesha nafwala ne shati ilyamakumbi makumbi.
eng_translation: Yes you are right. This young woman looking there is wearing a blue shirt.

bem_transcription: Shitata ali kumumana alekopa ifikope.
eng_translation: A man is at the river taking pictures.

bem_transcription: Elyo pamumana, pali amabwato yabili, bumbi ubwakashika elyo bumbi ubwabuuta.
eng_translation: There are two boats in the river, a red one and a white one.

bem_transcription: Uyu umumana wakaena ulemoneka mumana uukalamba nga nshi nakalimo walyendelela fye ukufika ukutali.
eng_translation: This river looks very big. It looks like it has gone very far too.

bem_transcription: Mumbali ya uyu umumana mwashinguluka ifimuti ifingi kabili ifyatitikana.
eng_translation: There are a lot of big thick trees on the sides of this river.

bem_transcription: Mu bwato ubuli pamumana muli na balumendo abekelemo, nampo balelobe sabi nangula bekelemo fye.
eng_translation: There are young men seated in the boat that is on the water. We can't tell if they are fishing or they are just seated.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali mumbali yamusebo naiminina.
eng_translation: A young man is standing on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Mupepi nankwe pali akamwaice akaikumbete akalemoneka akabulanda.
eng_translation: Near him is a child that looks very sad.

bem_transcription: Kabili mumusebo fye mulepita imyotoka ishingi.
eng_translation: And there are a lot of cars passing in the road.

bem_transcription: Elyo umusebo nomushili ulemoneka uwabomba, cilemoneka kwati imfula yafuma mukuloka.
eng_translation: The road appears to be wet. It's like it was raining.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili mumbali yamusebo uku lubali kwaliba ifimuti ifingi nafyo ifikalamba.
eng_translation: There are also big trees on the other side of the road.

bem_transcription: Umwana umulumendo naikala panse pacimpelwa capanshi.
eng_translation: A young boy is outside seated on a swing.

bem_transcription: Elo uyu wine umwana umulumendo alikwata imishishi ishabuuta kwati alikotela limo.
eng_translation: This young boy has white hair like he is already old.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili nafwala ne shati umwapita ifyabuuta, ifyafiita kabili nefyakashika, nakaputula nayo afwele intu yakashika.
eng_translation: He is wearing a shirt that has white, black and red and the short he is wearing is red.

bem_transcription: Elyo pantu aleangalila apa nipa lubansa fye pantu ulubansa lwalicingililwa nokucingililwa notushimbi.
eng_translation: The place where he is playing from is their yard because it is even fenced with metal bars.

bem_transcription: Elo ulubansa lwakaena lonse fye balibyalapo ulunkoto.
eng_translation: The whole yard is covered with grass.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naiminina mumbali yanjanji.
eng_translation: A young man is standing on the side of the rail line.

bem_transcription: Cilepala uyu umulumendo ali nipamulimo pantu nafwala necimpompo naimya nakashimbi.
eng_translation: It appears this young man is working because he is wearing a helmet and has raised a metal bar.

bem_transcription: Uyu umulumendo cilemoneka nalimo alelungisha motoka iili pantashi yakwe.
eng_translation: Maybe this young man is repairing the vehicle below him.

bem_transcription: Nomba uyu wine umulumendo kuli ifyo alepweneka pantu nalolekesha lubali lumbi.
eng_translation: But there is something he is looking at because he is looking on the other side.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili luncende yakaena ali kulemoneka balikuulako ne cikuulwa cimo icisuma icilemoneka bwino nga nshi icabuuta.
eng_translation: There is also a very nice building that has been built at the place where he is.

bem_transcription: Ulupwa nalwikala pamo lulelya.
eng_translation: A family is seated together eating.

bem_transcription: Pali ulu lwine ulupwa pali imishinku ishalekanalekana pali abacaice, abacikoloci elyo nabamishinku fye iyalinga.
eng_translation: There different ages in this family. There's the old, the young and the middle aged.

bem_transcription: Kulemoneka nalimo bushiku elo apa nipanse fye bekele.
eng_translation: It looks like it is in the night and they are seated outside.

bem_transcription: Ulu ulupwa lulemoneka lwalitemwana sana, pantu nokulila pamo balila pamo.
eng_translation: It looks like they love each other in this family because they are even eating together.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili ifyakulya bakwete petebulo nafyo fingi sana.
eng_translation: Also they have plenty of food on their table.

bem_transcription: Abantu balecuuka umusebo.
eng_translation: People are crossing the road.

bem_transcription: Nga aya amashilwa bashila pa musebo aya buta no kufitulukila ninshi bayashilila pa musebo.
eng_translation: Why have they drawn these black and white lines on the road?

bem_transcription: Bayashilila ukweba ati nga balepita imyotoka shilemona pakuti shaiminina  baculuka.
eng_translation: They are pedestrians crossing points.

bem_transcription: mulumendo ufwele ica kashika bushe kuti aba ni kateya wa bola?
eng_translation: Could this young man in red be a football player?

bem_transcription: Ee nikateya wa mupila afuma muku trena.
eng_translation: Yes he is a football player and he is from training.

bem_transcription: Abakashana na balumendo baleshana.
eng_translation: Young men and young women are dancing.

bem_transcription: Ca cine balemoneka baleshana. Nomba baleshanina inshi?
eng_translation: Yes it looks like they are dancing. But why are they dancing?

bem_transcription: Baleshana ku umulandu wakuse fya ukufyalwa kwamunabo.
eng_translation: They are dancing because they are celebrating their friends birthday.

bem_transcription: Bushe ukulolesha kobe bushe kuti wishiba uo balesefesha?
eng_translation: Can you tell who's birthday it is by just looking?

bem_transcription: Ee, uo balesefesha mukashana uuli pakati kumulandu wakwebati nabamucingilila kwibumba.
eng_translation: Yes. The birthday girl is the one seated in the middle because they all are seated around her.

bem_transcription: Kapokola naiminina mumbali yamusebo.
eng_translation: A police officer is standing in the roadside.

bem_transcription: Nomba uyu wine kapokola afwele ifyabuuta konse, kumutwe kuli akasote akabuuta, ishati, itoloshi. fyonse fintu fyabuuta.
eng_translation: What kind of police officer wears everything white? The hat, the shirt, the trousers, everything white?

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili emininefye muli motoka nayo iyabuuta, nakabili iili pantashi intu yafiita.
eng_translation: And he is just standing in an equally white vehicle but the vehicle in front is black.

bem_transcription: Elyo uyu wine kapokola kuli akantu ako akwete mumiwe yakwe ako alelolekesha sana.
eng_translation: This same police officer has something in the hands that he is looking intently at.

bem_transcription: Nakabili mumbali yamusebo, kuli nencinga iyo beminike fye.
eng_translation: On the side of the road there is a parked bicycle.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo nabakashana bali mumuputule emo bapiminamo imiti.
eng_translation: Young men and young women are in a laboratory.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati kuli ifyo balepanga, pantu uyu shitata uwikele panshi aleitulula fimo.
eng_translation: It is like they are making something because this man seated is pouring something.

bem_transcription: Elyo namayo uuli mupepi fye naena alelolekesesha mukwebati amwenekeshe bwino bwino ifilecitika.
eng_translation: The woman near him is also paying looking closely at what is happening.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo nakwena kuli ibumba nabena balecita fimo fine pantu namayo naikatapo fimo kuminwe.
eng_translation: Behind them is another group doing the same because there is a woman holding something.

bem_transcription: Mumuputule wakaena balikamo amatebulo ayengi kabili notupana utwingi utwafiita.
eng_translation: There are a lot of tables and black chairs in the same room.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo ali panse aleputula imbao.
eng_translation: A young man is cutting wood outside.

bem_transcription: Elyo nafwala nefintu fimo kumatwi pakutila icongo camashini cimufulunganya.
eng_translation: He is wearing ear muffs in his ears.

bem_transcription: Kulubali lwakwe naiminikako nabamotoka babili, imo iyakashika kabili imo iyabuuta.
eng_translation: On his side there are two parked cars. One is red and the other one is white.

bem_transcription: Nakabili, uyu umulumendo alemoneka aliishibisha ukubombo yu mulimo.
eng_translation: This young man looks like he is an expert at this work.

bem_transcription: Elo apa ali palemoneka nipa n'ganda fye pantu uko lubali ukuli imyotoka, balicingilishako notumaluba twakatapakatapa.
eng_translation: It looks like he is at the house because there where the cares are parked there are even some green flowers.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo kambi pali utu tubili nakatoloka mumuulu kalefwaya ukwanka kabola akanoono.
eng_translation: One of the two has jumped trying to catch the small ball.

bem_transcription: Kucibansa cakaena kulemoneka ukwabusaka sana takulemonekapo nefiko ifili fyonse iyo.
eng_translation: The play ground looks very clean and there's no any visible dirt.

bem_transcription: Notubwa fye natwena tulemoneka utwabusaka pantu natukwata fyafiita elyo mwapita nefyabuuta .
eng_translation: The dogs too look very clean because they have black as well as white spots.

bem_transcription: Kabili kucibansa cakaena kwaliba nefimuti elo akatalamukila nga nalolesha sana ndemonako namotoka iilepita.
eng_translation: There are even trees near this play ground. And if I look closely I can see a vehicle passing.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ili mucibansa ileangala.
eng_translation: A dog is in the play ground playing.

bem_transcription: Kabili iloleshe akantu ako baiposele mumuulu.
eng_translation: It is looking at something that has been thrown to it.

bem_transcription: Uku kucibansa cakaena takulemonekapo umuntu nangu umo, imbwa ilifye yeka.
eng_translation: There doesn't seem to be anyone at this play ground. The dog is just alone.

bem_transcription: Elyo uku nga twalolekesha sana kulemoneka kwati nikumabala, yalya amabala ayakalamba sana.
eng_translation: These look like they are very big fields.

bem_transcription: Elo nakabili kwaliba icani icisuma nga nshi pantu conse cilemoneka fye icakatapa katapa.
eng_translation: and there is very beautiful green grass.

bem_transcription: Abalumendo babili bali pakati kamusebo baleenda.
eng_translation: Two young men are walking in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Elyo bonse babili nabekata amaboko mutumba lintu baleenda.
eng_translation: Both are putting their hands in their pockets.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yabo kuli fye nabantu bambi abaleyendela, baleya ukwapusana noko baleya.
eng_translation: There are people behind them that are going to various places.

bem_transcription: Elyo cilepala kwati nakutalala pantu bonse babili aba nabafwala ifyampepo, umbi afwele icafiita, umbi icafiita mwapita nefya kashika.
eng_translation: It looks like it's called because both are wearing jerseys. One is wearing a black one and the other is wearing a black one with red stripes.

bem_transcription: Elo nakabili kunuma yabo kulemoneka imyotoka isho beminike fye.
eng_translation: There seems to be parked cars behind them.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Elyo alemoneka kwati iciloto alelota cibi pantu nabifya napamenso lintu alele.
eng_translation: It's like he has a very bad dream because he has a frowned face.

bem_transcription: Ca cine teti akane ukulota pantu namuntu bamulalike mwine namufiita.
eng_translation: True he can dream because he is sleeping in a dark room.

bem_transcription: Ubusanshi bamulalikepo bulemoneka ubwayemba sana.
eng_translation: The bed where he has been put looks very nice.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili nabamufwika nakalishati eko balembapo ati cibili.
eng_translation: He is wearing a shirt where it's written "Tuesday."

bem_transcription: Namayo aleingila mu n'ganda.
eng_translation: A woman is entering the house.

bem_transcription: Nomba cibe talaingila mun'ganda, pamwinshi fye alefula insokoshi.
eng_translation: Before she enters the house she is on the door removing her socks.

bem_transcription: Pa mwinshi fye wan'ganda nga mwaingila palemoneka balitantikapo na ifilubi.
eng_translation: When you just enter the house there are even dolls that have been arranged there.

bem_transcription: Elyo ubu, cilemoneka bushiku, pantu panse palemoneka apafiita namalaiti nayaka.
eng_translation: And this seems to be at night because it looks dark outside.

bem_transcription: Umu mun'ganda aleingila mulemoneka umwabusaka nakucibumba balikambatikako necipampa.
eng_translation: The house she is entering into looks clean with a sign on the wall.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo umwaice naikala pamwinshi wan'ganda.
eng_translation: A young boy is seated on the entrance of the house.

bem_transcription: Elyo uku kulemoneka nikumushi pantu akayanda kalemoneka kakumesa fye.
eng_translation: This looks like it is in the village because the house looks muddy.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba naumona ifyo umutenge wa n'ganda ulemoneka?
eng_translation: But have you noticed how the roof of the house is looking?

bem_transcription: Umutenge wa n'ganda taulemoneka bwino nangu panoono, uyu umutenge tawaikala bwino kabili kuti wapona inshita fye iili yonse.
eng_translation: This roof doesn't look good and it is not safe at all. It can fall anytime.

bem_transcription: Abantu abengi bali mumusebo baleenda.
eng_translation: A lot of people are walking in the road.

bem_transcription: Elyo pali nanamayo uwaina kabili natwika nacimo pamutwe.
eng_translation: There is even a fat lady on the group who is carrying something on her head.

bem_transcription: Abantu bali mumusebo mu balifye abapusana pusana, bonse nabafwala nefyapusana pusana, nakalimo katwishi uko baleya cila muntu pali uko aleya.
eng_translation: The people in this road are wearing different things and they all are going in different directions to different places.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende ilemoneka ili mumusumba uukalamba pantu nefikuulwa fye ifiliko nifilye fikuulwa ifitali sana.
eng_translation: This place seems to be in s big city because there are even big tall buildings around.

bem_transcription: Kabili mumusebo fye mulepita imyotoka ishingi elyo kabili mumbali yamusebo mulemoneka nefimuti.
eng_translation: There are a lot of vehicles passing in the road and there are trees on the roadside.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu aleoca umunani.
eng_translation: An old man is roasting relish.

bem_transcription: Ukumulolesha shibantu alemoneka nasangalala sana, bushe cinshi cingalenga insansa sha so?
eng_translation: This man looks very happy. What could make him this happy?

bem_transcription: Alemoneka uwasangalala kumulandu wakuti umunani aleoca ulemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: He looks happy because what he is roasting looks delicious.

bem_transcription: Ngeci cintu aleocelamo iminani ishi nicinshi?
eng_translation: What is this thing that he is using to roast the relish?

bem_transcription: Ici alebomfya cakocelepo inama.
eng_translation: It is a braai stand.

bem_transcription: Imbwa ili mumpanga ileangala.
eng_translation: A dog is playing in the bush.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka kwati ileangasha icimuti icauma pantu naisumamo nokusumamo.
eng_translation: It looks like it is playing with that dry stick that is in its mouth.

bem_transcription: Iyi imbwa intu yafiita sana.
eng_translation: This dog is very dark.

bem_transcription: Nomba imbwa yakaena ilinso fye liletiinya.
eng_translation: This dogs eye is intimidating.

bem_transcription: Kabili kumpanga yakaena kwalifula ifyani ifingi kabili notumuti utwauma.
eng_translation: There are is a lot of grass and dry sticks in this forest.

bem_transcription: Abana batatu bali panse baleangala.
eng_translation: Three children are playing outside.

bem_transcription: Nga ni uyu ulu pakati ala nasekelela elyo balemoneka aba nsansa.
eng_translation: The one in the middle is very happy and so are the others.

bem_transcription: Uli uku lubali ena nakumbatila uli pakati alemutomona na petobo.
eng_translation: The one of the side is hugging the one in the middle and kissing him on the cheeks.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati aba bana lupwa lumo lwine elyo balitemwana sana.
eng_translation: It looks like these children are siblings and they love each other.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Wishi no mwana bali panse baleangala.
eng_translation: A man and his child are playing outside

bem_transcription: Elyo Umwana alipala sana wishi kumwena fye kumatobo.
eng_translation: The child resembles the father ad you can even tell from the cheeks.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka apa bali nipalubansa fye lwa pa ng'anda yabo.
eng_translation: It looks like they are on their yard.

bem_transcription: Ee cishinka ni pa ng'anda apa pantu kunuma yabo nga walolekesha kulemoneka ne ng'anda elyo balibikako nangula ukucingilishako ulupango.
eng_translation: Yes it is their yard because their is a house behind and it is fenced with planks.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya lupango lwine kulemoneka kuli ne ng'anda na imbi nayo bali icingilila.
eng_translation: There seems to be another house behind this one and it too is fenced.

bem_transcription: Umulumendo naiminina pa muulu wa ntambo.
eng_translation: A young man is standing on top of a rope.

bem_transcription: Cilepala kwati alebonfya ishi shine intambo ukuciluka.
eng_translation: It is like he is using these very ropes to jump.

bem_transcription: Nafwala ne cimpompo icakumucingilila nga ca kweba ati aliponene.
eng_translation: He is even wearing a helmet to protect himself in case he falls.

bem_transcription: Elyo apa ali ni pa muulu sana pantu abantu panshi balemneka kwati baice.
eng_translation: It seems he is very high up because the people below are looking like children.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili panshi pene palemoneka bwino sana apabusaka na bantu balipo balemoneka bwino.
eng_translation: Additionally it looks clean below and the people too look good.

bem_transcription: Abantu bali panse ya cikulwa nabeminina.
eng_translation: people are standing outside a building.

bem_transcription: Elyo kuli notubaice akamwaume naka mwanakashi utulebutuka.
eng_translation: There is a even a boy and a girl running.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nomba bushe naumona ifyo iyi incende ilemoneka?
eng_translation: Have you seen how this place is looking?

bem_transcription: Nimbona iyi incende ilemoneka bwino sana iya busaka ifimuti fye filemoneka ifyabuska fintu fya yemba.
eng_translation: Yes this place looks very nice and clean with beautiful trees.

bem_transcription: Imbwa baleisambilisha ifya kutoloka
eng_translation: A dog is being trained how to jump.

bem_transcription: Elyo nabemika abantu abakwete utushimbi utwabulungana ku minwe yabo umo iyi imbwa iletoloka.
eng_translation: There are people holding round metal bars which this dog is jumping.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya mbwa kuli na bantu fye abekele abaletamba bambi nabeminina.
eng_translation: Behind this dog are people that are standing and watching while others are sitting.

bem_transcription: Elyo mupepi fye ne mbwa kuli na mayo cilepala uyu eulepundilila imbwa ifya kucita.
eng_translation: There is a woman near the dog. It is like she is the one instructing it what to do.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Abantu bale-enda pakati ka nshila.
eng_translation: People are walking in the middle of the road.

bem_transcription: Uyu na mayo alepala kwati afuma mukushitapo fimo mu matuka.
eng_translation: It's like this woman is from buying something from the shop.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili uyu shitata alemoneka kwati aleya ukulefuma namayo.
eng_translation: This man looks like he is going where this woman is coming from

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya kwa na mayo kuli aka mwaice akelebutuka akafuma mucikulwa ici kumbali.
eng_translation: There is a girl behind this woman coming from that building on the side running.

bem_transcription: Icikuwa caka ena cilemoneka cikalamba nga nshi.
eng_translation: The building looks very big.

bem_transcription: Abaice babili baleangala panse ya ng'anda.
eng_translation: Two children are playing outside the house.

bem_transcription: Elyo icangalo baleangala ni cilya icakuteya umupila ukubonfya fye akantu kantu bapanga kwati litebulo.
eng_translation: They are playing table tennis.

bem_transcription: Cilemoneka bonse abeshile uku nabatemwa abantu beshile mukutamba pantu bonse eko baposele amenso.
eng_translation: It's like everyone here likes the people that they have come to watch because they are concentrating.

bem_transcription: Elyo kabili kumbali ya cisebele nakwena nababikako icitunshi tunshi icinono pakweba ati abantu abali ukutali balemwenapo.
eng_translation: There is also a television near the stage where people that are behind can watch from.

bem_transcription: Elyo iyi incende ilemoneka bwino sana kumona fye na pa mushili ifyo palemoneka na bantu kuti baikala na panshi.
eng_translation: This place looks very nice such that people can even sit on the ground.

bem_transcription: Akamwana akamwaume akamwaice kalepeluma pacimpelwa.
eng_translation: A young boy is swinging on the swing.

bem_transcription: Kalemoneka nakonfwa bwino sana pantu nakacensa.
eng_translation: He looks very happy and is smilling.

bem_transcription: Ici icimpelwa opo bacibikila balishungulushapo utumbawe utunono uto baitila pa mushili.
eng_translation: There are small stones on the flow around the swing.

bem_transcription: Elo kabili kumbali ya mushili bali byalako no lunkoto.
eng_translation: There is also some grass.

bem_transcription: Nomba akamwana utumishishi tulemoneka kwati nikalya akamuntu akacibomba elyo utu mishishi twabomba.
eng_translation: The hair of the child looks like it was soaked and is wet.

bem_transcription: Bashitata nabemya icishimbi baletoloka umusebo.
eng_translation: Men are crossing the road lifting s metal.

bem_transcription: Elo kunuma yabo kuli bashitata abekeleko umo alelanda napali lamya.
eng_translation: Behind them are men seated and one is on the phone.

bem_transcription: Aba bene bashitata abemishe icishimbi bonse bafwele amashati ayakashika ku muulu..
eng_translation: These men that are lifting the metal are wearing shirts that are red on top.

bem_transcription: NOT PLAYING
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Nga twalolekesha kuli aba bashitata abekele panshi kulemoneka icibumba ukwaba amaluba aya katapa katapa.
eng_translation: If we look closely where these men are sitting, there is a wall with green flowers.

bem_transcription: Na mayo nakontama ali kulumba lwa mumana.
eng_translation: a woman has bent at the beach.

bem_transcription: Uyu na mayo waka ena alemoneka kwati apli ifyo aletola mumbali ya mumana alebika mu mbeketi.
eng_translation: It's like this woman is picking something and putting in a bucket.

bem_transcription: Elyo umumana ulemoneka ukalamba pantu walipabukisha.
eng_translation: The sea looks very big and wide.

bem_transcription: Kabili kumbali ya mumana wine kwaliba amabwe ayengi sana.
eng_translation: There are also a lot of rocks on the side of the sea.

bem_transcription: Na mayo alikwata imishishi ishitali elo ne fyakufwala afwele afwele ica fita ku muulu ne ca makumbi makumbi unshi
eng_translation: A woman has long hair and is wearing a black top and a blue bottom.

bem_transcription: Na mayo ali no mwana wakwe bale-enda mu musebo.
eng_translation: A woman is walking with her child on the road.

bem_transcription: Elo imfula ileloka umwana wakwa namayo uyu nakwata no mwanfuli.
eng_translation: It is raining and the woman's child has an umbrella.

bem_transcription: Na kabili na mayo ena alelokwa fye cilepala kwati afuma mukusenda uyu umwana umwaume kusukulu.
eng_translation: The woman is just getting soaked. It's like she was picking the child up from school.

bem_transcription: Kunuma ya kwa na mayo no mwana wakwe kuli shitata umo ule ensha incinga nao nalokwa.
eng_translation: Behind the woman and the child is a man riding a bicycle and is also soaked.

bem_transcription: Uyu umusebo kabili ulemoneka balaubonfya sana pantu ama motoka nayafula mu musebo.
eng_translation: It's like this road is busy because there are a lot of cars in it.

bem_transcription: Shitata aleposha abantu cibe ninshi nanina apa sanswike.
eng_translation: A man is standing on a height and greeting people.

bem_transcription: Elyo abantu aleposha balemoneka nabonfwa bwino pantu nao naufwa bwino.
eng_translation: Both him and the people he is greeting look happy.

bem_transcription: Elyo nakabili uyu shitata muntu uwalumbuka eyo abantu abengi balamukonka.
eng_translation: This man is famous and many people follow him

bem_transcription: Uyu shitata waka ena nafwala ne fyakufwala ifya buta fyonse
eng_translation: This man is wearing all white clothes.

bem_transcription: Kunuma yakwe nako kuli no tupuna tutatu utwakashika apakwikala abantu.
eng_translation: There are three red chairs behind him where people can sit.

bem_transcription: Bana mayo babili bali no mwana.
eng_translation: Two women are with a child.

bem_transcription: Balemoneka aba nsansa aba bana mayo bushe cinshi bengasengelela so?
eng_translation: These women look very happy. What could be the reason?

bem_transcription: Balemoneka aba nsansa pa mulandu wakuti ifilesoswa apa fili ifya yana.
eng_translation: They are happy because what is being said is wonderful.

bem_transcription: Bushe umwana uyu naishiba ne filesoswa pa ncede iyi?
eng_translation: Does this child even know what is being said at this place?

bem_transcription: Iy nakalya kana akanya teti keshibe ifilesoswa.
eng_translation: No a baby cannot know what is being said.

bem_transcription: Bashitata babili nabekala patupuna mukati ka muputule.
eng_translation: Two men are sitting on chairs in a room.

bem_transcription: Umo shitata alebelenga icitabo elyo umo alelemba.
eng_translation: One is reading a book while one is writing.

bem_transcription: Nomba uyu ulebelenga afwele akashati aka makumbi makumbi notu mishishi utwipi.
eng_translation: The one reading is wearing a blue shirt and has short hair.

bem_transcription: Elo aba babili bashitata bekele fye mupepi ne cipampa kunuma yabo.
eng_translation: There is a sign behind where these men are seated.

bem_transcription: Nga ni uyu shitata ena ulelemba alemoneka kwati aletontonkanya sana pakutila engakumanisha fye ukulembako fimo
eng_translation: The one writing looks like he is thinking a lot for him to come up with what to write.

bem_transcription: Shikulu bantu alelangisha umukashana umunono.
eng_translation: An old man is showing a young girl something.

bem_transcription: NOT FOUND
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Umulumendo umunono uyu naena ali na shikulu bantu no mwanakashi umunono uyu.
eng_translation: Even this young boy is with this old man and young girl.

bem_transcription: NOT FOUND
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Ifikulwa ifi mayanda yakwikalamo namulungika.
eng_translation: You are right these buildings are houses.

bem_transcription: Shitata na namayo nabekala patupuna.
eng_translation: A man and a woman are sitting on chairs.

bem_transcription: NOT FOUND
eng_translation: NOT PLAYING

bem_transcription: Apa bekele te pang'anda iyo bali ku mpanga uko baile mukutusha.
